#: admin/access.rst:342
msgid ""
"Restricting translation to `Czech` to a selected set of translators, (while "
"keeping translations to other languages public):"
msgstr "將翻譯為 `捷克文` 的權限限制於選取的譯者，同時對其他語言維持公開翻譯："

#: admin/access.rst:345
msgid ""
"Remove the permission to translate `Czech` from all users. In the default "
"configuration this can be done by altering the `Users` :ref:`default team "
"<default-teams>`."
msgstr ""
"移除所有使用者翻譯 `捷克文` 的權限。在預設設定中，可以修改 `使用者` :ref:`預"
"設團隊 <default-teams>` 來完成。"

#: admin/access.rst:349
msgid "Group `Users`"
msgstr "群組 `使用者`"

#: admin/access.rst:352 admin/access.rst:366
msgid "Language selection"
msgstr "語言選取"

#: admin/access.rst:353 admin/access.rst:367
msgid "`As defined`"
msgstr "`如定義`"

#: admin/access.rst:354 admin/access.rst:368 admin/access.rst:491 api.rst:789
#: user/profile.rst:76
msgid "Languages"
msgstr "語言"

#: admin/access.rst:355
msgid "All but `Czech`"
msgstr "除 `捷克語` 以外"

#: admin/access.rst:357
msgid "Add a dedicated team for `Czech` translators."
msgstr "為 `捷克語翻譯者` 新增專門團隊。"

#: admin/access.rst:359
msgid "Group `Czech translators`"
msgstr "`捷克語翻譯者` 群組"

#: admin/access.rst:362 admin/access.rst:487 api.rst:720
msgid "Roles"
msgstr "角色"

#: admin/access.rst:363
msgid "`Power users`"
msgstr "`超級使用者`"

#: admin/access.rst:364
msgid "Project selection"
msgstr "專案選取"

#: admin/access.rst:365
msgid "`All public projects`"
msgstr "`所有公開專案`"

#: admin/access.rst:369
msgid "`Czech`"
msgstr "`捷克語`"

#: admin/access.rst:372
msgid "Add users you wish to give the permissions to into this team."
msgstr "新增團隊中您希望賦予權限的使用者。"

#: admin/access.rst:374
msgid ""
"Management permissions this way is powerful, but can be quite a tedious job. "
"You can only delegate it to other users by granting them Superuser status."
msgstr ""
"這種權限管理方式功能強大，但也可能相當繁瑣。只有授予其他使用者超級使用者狀"
"態，才能將這項工作委派給他們。"

#: admin/access.rst:380
msgid "Users, roles, teams, and permissions"
msgstr "使用者，角色，團隊與權限"

#: admin/access.rst:382
msgid "The authentication models consist of several objects:"
msgstr "身分驗證模型由幾個物件組成："

#: admin/access.rst:384
msgid "`Permission`"
msgstr "`權限`"

#: admin/access.rst:385
msgid ""
"Individual permission defined by Weblate. Permissions cannot be assigned to "
"users, only through assignment of roles."
msgstr "Weblate 定義的個別權限。權限不能直接指派給使用者，只能透過角色指派。"

#: admin/access.rst:387
msgid "`Role`"
msgstr "`角色`"

#: admin/access.rst:388
msgid ""
"A role defines a set of permissions (and can be reused in several places)."
msgstr "角色會定義一組權限，並可在多處重複使用。"

#: admin/access.rst:390
msgid "`User`"
msgstr "`使用者`"

#: admin/access.rst:391
msgid "A user can belong to several teams."
msgstr "一個使用者可隸屬於多個團隊。"

#: admin/access.rst:392
msgid "`Group`"
msgstr "`群組`"

#: admin/access.rst:393
msgid ""
"Groups connect roles and users with authentication objects (projects, "
"languages, components, and component lists)."
msgstr "群組用身分驗證物件（專案、語言、元件和元件清單）連結角色和使用者。"

#: admin/access.rst:411
msgid ""
"A team can have no roles assigned to it, in that case access to browse the "
"project by anyone is assumed (see below)."
msgstr ""
"一個團隊可以沒有分配角色，在這種情況下，假設任何人能存取專案（見下文）。"

#: admin/access.rst:415
msgid "Project-browsing access"
msgstr "專案瀏覽存取"

#: admin/access.rst:417
msgid ""
"A user has to be a member of a team linked to the project, or any component "
"inside that project. Having membership is enough, no specific permissions "
"are needed to browse the project (this is used in the default `Viewers` "
"team, see :ref:`default-teams`)."
msgstr ""
"使用者必須為團隊成員並團隊連結到專案或任何元件的成員。擁有成員身分就足夠了，"
"瀏覽專案不需要特定的權限（這被用於預設的 `檢視者` 小組，見 :ref:`default-"
"teams` ）。"

#: admin/access.rst:423
msgid "Component-browsing access"
msgstr "元件瀏覽存取"

#: admin/access.rst:425
msgid ""
"Granting browsing access to a user in one project gives it access to any "
"component with derived browsing permissions. With :ref:`component-"
"restricted` on, access to components (or component lists) are granted "
"explicitly."
msgstr ""
"授予專案中一名使用者瀏覽權限意味著這名使用者可以存取任何瀏覽權限衍生自該專案"
"的元件。開啟 :ref:`component-restricted` 後，需要明確授予存取元件（或元件清"
"單）的權限。"

#: admin/access.rst:433
msgid "Scope of teams"
msgstr "團隊範圍"

#: admin/access.rst:435
msgid ""
"The scope of the permission assigned by the roles in the teams are applied "
"by the following rules:"
msgstr "團隊中各角色所指派權限的作用範圍，會依下列規則套用："

#: admin/access.rst:438
msgid ""
"If the team specifies any :guilabel:`Component list`, all the permissions "
"given to members of that team are granted for all the components in the "
"component lists attached to the team, and an access with no additional "
"permissions is granted for all the projects these components are "
"in. :guilabel:`Components` and :guilabel:`Projects` are ignored."
msgstr ""
"如果團隊指定任何 :guilabel:`元件清單`，所有在團隊已賦予到成員的權限也將賦權在"
"團隊裡元件清單中的所有元件。若無額外指定的權限在所有的專案，這些元件"
"在 :guilabel:`元件` 與 :guilabel:`專案` 會被忽略。"

#: admin/access.rst:444
msgid ""
"Using huge component lists might have a performance impact, please consider "
"giving access via projects instead."
msgstr "使用龐大的元件清單可能會對效能產生影響，請考慮透過專案提供存取權限。"

#: admin/access.rst:447
msgid ""
"If the team specifies any :guilabel:`Components`, all the permissions given "
"to the members of that team are granted for all the components attached to "
"the team, and an access with no additional permissions is granted for all "
"the projects these components are in. :guilabel:`Projects` are ignored."
msgstr ""
"如果團隊指定了任何 :guilabel:`元件`，則授予團隊成員的所有權限都會套用至附加到"
"該團隊的全部元件；這些元件所屬的專案也會獲得不含額外權限的存取權。此時會忽"
"略 :guilabel:`專案` 設定。"

#: admin/access.rst:452
msgid ""
"Otherwise, if the team specifies any :guilabel:`Projects`, either by "
"directly listing them or by having :guilabel:`Projects selection` set to a "
"value like :guilabel:`All public projects`, all those permissions are "
"applied to all the projects, which effectively grants the same permissions "
"to access all projects :ref:`unrestricted components <component-restricted>`."
msgstr ""
"否則，如果團隊指定了任何 :guilabel:`專案`，無論是直接列出它們還是"
"將 :guilabel:`專案選擇` 設定為類似 :guilabel:`所有公開專案` 的值，所有這些權"
"限都套用於所有專案，這實際上授予了存取所有專案的相同權限 :ref:`unrestricted "
"components <component-restricted>`。"

#: admin/access.rst:458
msgid ""
"The restrictions imposed by a team’s :guilabel:`Languages` are applied "
"separately, when it’s verified if a user has access to perform certain "
"actions. Namely, it’s applied only to actions directly related to the "
"translation process itself like reviewing, saving translations, adding "
"suggestions, etc."
msgstr ""
"驗證使用者是否有權執行特定動作時，團隊 :guilabel:`語言` 所施加的限制會另行套"
"用。也就是說，此限制只適用於直接與翻譯流程相關的動作，例如審查、儲存翻譯、新"
"增建議等。"

#: admin/access.rst:463
msgid ""
"Individual team memberships can further limit these permissions to selected "
"languages. Leaving the per-member language limit empty applies no additional "
"limit beyond the team language selection. The same language limit can be set "
"when inviting new users to a project team. When a per-member language limit "
"is set, the membership grants only permissions that can be evaluated for one "
"of those languages. Project-wide, component-wide and global permissions from "
"that team are not granted for that member."
msgstr ""
"個別團隊成員資格可進一步將這些權限限制於選取的語言。將個別成員的語言限制留"
"空，表示除團隊語言選項外不再施加其他限制。邀請新使用者加入專案團隊時，也可設"
"定相同的語言限制。設定個別成員的語言限制後，該成員資格只會授予可針對其中一種"
"語言評估的權限；該團隊的專案層級、元件層級及全域權限不會授予該成員。"

#: admin/access.rst:473
msgid ""
"Use :guilabel:`Language selection` or :guilabel:`Project selection` to "
"automate inclusion of all languages or projects."
msgstr ""
"使用 :guilabel:`語言選擇` 或 :guilabel:`專案選擇` 來自動包括所有語言或專案。"

#: admin/access.rst:480
msgid ""
"A project ``foo`` with the components: ``foo/bar`` and ``foo/baz``, with "
"reviewing and management rights, in the following team:"
msgstr ""
"在下列團隊中，專案 ``foo`` 含有 ``foo/bar`` 和 ``foo/baz`` 元件，並具備審查及"
"管理權限："

#: admin/access.rst:484
msgid "Group `Spanish Admin-Reviewers`"
msgstr "群組 `西班牙語管理審查員`"

#: admin/access.rst:488
msgid "`Review strings`, `Manage repository`"
msgstr "`審查字串`、`管理儲存庫`"

#: admin/access.rst:489 api.rst:1530
msgid "Components"
msgstr "元件"

#: admin/access.rst:490
msgid "foo/bar"
msgstr "foo/bar"

#: admin/access.rst:492
msgid "`Spanish`"
msgstr "`西班牙語`"

#: admin/access.rst:495
msgid ""
"Members of that team will have these permissions (assuming the default role "
"settings):"
msgstr "該團隊的成員將有這些權限（假設使用預設角色設定）："

#: admin/access.rst:497
msgid ""
"General (browsing) access to the whole project ``foo`` including both "
"components in it: ``foo/bar`` and ``foo/baz``."
msgstr ""
"對整個專案 ``foo`` 的一般（瀏覽）存取，包括其中的兩個元件：\\ ``foo/bar`` 和 "
"``foo/baz``。"

#: admin/access.rst:499
msgid "Review strings in ``foo/bar`` Spanish translation (not elsewhere)."
msgstr "審查 ``foo/bar`` 中的西班牙文翻譯字串（不包括其他位置）。"

#: admin/access.rst:500
msgid ""
"Manage VCS for the whole ``foo/bar`` repository e.g. commit pending changes "
"made by translators for all languages."
msgstr ""
"管理整個 ``foo/bar`` 儲存庫的版本控制系統，例如提交所有語言的譯者所做的待處理"
"變更。"

#: admin/access.rst:506
msgid "Automatic team assignments"
msgstr "自動團隊分派"

#: admin/access.rst:508
msgid ""
"While editing the :guilabel:`Team`, you can "
"specify :guilabel:`Automatic assignments`, which is a list of regular "
"expressions used to automatically assign newly created users to a team based "
"on their e-mail addresses. This assignment only happens upon account "
"creation."
msgstr ""
"編輯 :guilabel:`團隊` 時，您可以指定 :guilabel:`自動指派`。這是一份正規表示式"
"清單，會根據電子郵件地址，在建立帳號時自動將新使用者指派至團隊。只有建立帳號"
"時才會執行這項指派。"

#: admin/access.rst:513
msgid ""
"The most common use-case for the feature is to assign all new users to some "
"default team. This behavior is used for the default `Users` and `Guest` "
"teams (see :ref:`default-teams`). Use regular expression ``^.*$`` to match "
"all users."
msgstr ""
"該功能最常見的使用案例是將所有新使用者指派給某個預設團隊。此行為用於預設的 `"
"使用者` 和 `訪客` 團隊（請參閱 :ref:`default-teams`）。使用正規表達式 "
"``^.*$`` 來相符所有使用者。"

#: admin/access.rst:519
msgid ""
"Another use-case for this option might be to give some additional privileges "
"to employees of your company by default. Assuming all of them use corporate "
"e-mail addresses on your domain, this can be accomplished with an expression "
"like ``^.*@mycompany.com``."
msgstr ""
"此選項的另一個用途，是預設授予公司員工額外權限。假設所有員工都使用公司網域的"
"電子郵件地址，就能以 ``^.*@mycompany.com`` 之類的表示式完成設定。"

#: admin/access.rst:526
msgid ""
"Automatic team assignment to `Users` and `Viewers` is always recreated when "
"upgrading from one Weblate version to another. If you want to turn it off, "
"set the regular expression to ``^$`` (which won’t match anything)."
msgstr ""
"從一個 Weblate 版本升級到另一個版本時，總是會重新建立對 `使用者` 和 `檢視者` "
"的使用者團隊指派。如果您想關閉它，將正規表達式設定為 ``^$`` （不比對任何內"
"容）。"

#: admin/access.rst:532
msgid ""
"Bulk inviting through the user interface creates invitations. Existing users "
"still have to confirm the invitation before they become team members."
msgstr ""
"透過使用者介面批次邀請會建立邀請。既有使用者仍須確認邀請，才會成為團隊成員。"

#: admin/access.rst:536
msgid "Default teams and roles"
msgstr "預設團隊和角色"

#: admin/access.rst:538
msgid ""
"After installation, a default set of teams is created (see :ref:`default-"
"teams`)."
msgstr "安裝後，將建立一組預設的團隊（請參閱 :ref:`default-teams`）。"

#: admin/access.rst:540
msgid ""
"These roles and teams are created upon installation. The built-in roles are "
"always kept up to date by the database migration when upgrading. You can’t "
"actually change them, please define a new role if you want to define your "
"own set of permissions."
msgstr ""
"這些角色和團隊是在安裝時建立的。升級時，內建角色總是透過資料庫移轉以保持最"
"新。您實際上無法變更它們，如果您想定義自己的權限集，請定義一個新角色。"

#: admin/access.rst:551
msgid ""
"Site-wide privileges are not granted to any default role. These are powerful "
"and quite close to the Superuser status. Most of them affect all projects in "
"your Weblate installation."
msgstr ""
"任何預設角色都不會獲得全站權限。這些權限強大，幾乎等同於超級使用者狀態，而且"
"大多會影響 Weblate 安裝環境中的所有專案。"

#: admin/access.rst:560
msgid "List of teams"
msgstr "團隊清單"

#: admin/access.rst:562
msgid ""
"The following teams are created upon installation (or after "
"executing :wladmin:`setupgroups`) and you are free to modify them. The "
"migration will, however, re-create them if you delete or rename them."
msgstr ""
"下列團隊會在安裝時（或執行 :wladmin:`setupgroups` 後）建立，您可以自由修改。"
"不過，如果刪除這些團隊或重新命名，資料庫移轉時會重新建立它們。"

#: admin/access.rst:566
msgid "`Guests`"
msgstr "`訪客`"

#: admin/access.rst:567
msgid "Defines permissions for non-authenticated users."
msgstr "定義未經身分驗證的使用者權限。"

#: admin/access.rst:569
msgid ""
"This team only contains anonymous users (see :setting:`ANONYMOUS_USER_NAME`)."
msgstr "這個團隊只包括匿名使用者（請參閱 :setting:`ANONYMOUS_USER_NAME`）。"

#: admin/access.rst:571
msgid ""
"Remove roles from this team to limit permissions for non-authenticated users."
msgstr "從這個團隊移除角色，即可限制未經身分驗證使用者的權限。"

#: admin/access.rst:574
msgid "Default roles: `Add suggestion`, `Access repository`"
msgstr "預設角色： `Add suggestion` 、 `Access repository`"

#: admin/access.rst:576
msgid "`Viewers`"
msgstr "`檢視者`"

#: admin/access.rst:577
msgid ""
"This role ensures the visibility of public projects to all users. By "
"default, all users are members of this team."
msgstr ""
"這個角色可確保所有使用者都能看到公開專案。依預設，所有使用者都是這個團隊的成"
"員。"

#: admin/access.rst:580 admin/access.rst:588
msgid ""
"By default, :ref:`automatic team assignment <autoteam>` makes all new "
"accounts members of this team when they join."
msgstr ""
"依預設，:ref:`自動團隊指派 <autoteam>` 會在新帳號加入時，使其成為這個團隊的成"
"員。"

#: admin/access.rst:583
msgid "Default roles: none"
msgstr "預設角色：無"

#: admin/access.rst:585 workflows.rst:130 workflows.rst:162 workflows.rst:195
msgid "`Users`"
msgstr "`使用者`"

#: admin/access.rst:586
msgid "Default team for all users."
msgstr "所有使用者的預設群組。"

#: admin/access.rst:591
msgid "Default roles: `Power user`"
msgstr "預設角色： `超級使用者`"

#: admin/access.rst:593 workflows.rst:199
msgid "`Reviewers`"
msgstr "`檢閱者`"

#: admin/access.rst:594
msgid "Group for reviewers (see :ref:`workflows`)."
msgstr "檢閱者群組（請參閱 :ref:`workflows` ）。"

#: admin/access.rst:596
msgid "Default roles: `Review strings`"
msgstr "預設角色： `檢閱字串`"

#: admin/access.rst:598
msgid "`Managers`"
msgstr "`管理員`"

#: admin/access.rst:599
msgid "Group for administrators."
msgstr "管理員專用群組。"

#: admin/access.rst:601
msgid "Default roles: `Administration`"
msgstr "預設角色： `管理權限`"

#: admin/access.rst:603 admin/workspaces.rst:259
msgid "`Project creators`"
msgstr "`專案建立者`"

#: admin/access.rst:606
msgid "Users who can create new projects."
msgstr "可以建立新專案的使用者。"

#: admin/access.rst:608
msgid "Default roles: `Add new projects`"
msgstr "預設角色：`新增新專案`"

#: admin/access.rst:612
msgid ""
"Never remove the predefined Weblate teams and users, as that can lead to "
"unexpected problems! If you have no use for them, simply remove all their "
"privileges instead."
msgstr ""
"請勿移除預先定義的 Weblate 團隊及使用者，否則可能導致預期外的問題。如果不需要"
"這些團隊及使用者，只要移除其所有權限即可。"

#: admin/access.rst:617
msgid "Additional access restrictions"
msgstr "進階存取限制"

#: admin/access.rst:619
msgid ""
"If you want to use your Weblate installation in a less public manner, i.e. "
"allow new users on an invitational basis only, it can be done by configuring "
"Weblate in such a way that only known users have an access to it. In order "
"to do so, you can set :setting:`REGISTRATION_OPEN` to ``False`` to prevent "
"registrations of any new users, and set :setting:`REQUIRE_LOGIN` to ``True`` "
"to require signing in to access all the site pages. This is basically the "
"way to lock your Weblate installation."
msgstr ""
"如果您想以較不公開的方式使用 Weblate，例如只允許受邀的新使用者，可以設定成只"
"有已知使用者能夠存取。請將 :setting:`REGISTRATION_OPEN` 設為 ``False`` 以禁止"
"註冊新使用者，並將 :setting:`REQUIRE_LOGIN` 設為 ``True``，要求登入後才能存取"
"網站上的所有頁面。這就是鎖定 Weblate 執行個體的基本方式。"

#: admin/access.rst:626
msgid ""
"Additionally, changing :setting:`DEFAULT_ACCESS_CONTROL` to ``100`` will "
"make all newly created projects private, requiring explicit access to be "
"granted."
msgstr ""
"另外，變更 :setting:`DEFAULT_ACCESS_CONTROL` 為 ``100`` 會使所有新建立的專案"
"變成私密專案，需要授予明確權限。"

#: admin/access.rst:631
msgid "You can use built-in :ref:`invite-user` to add new users."
msgstr "您可以使用內建的 :ref:`invite-user` 新增使用者。"

#: admin/access.rst:636
msgid "Expiration of user accounts"
msgstr "使用者帳號過期"

#: admin/access.rst:638
msgid ""
"Each account can have an expiry set. After the expiration, the account will "
"be automatically disabled. This is used for :ref:`project-api`, but can be "
"utilized for regular users as well."
msgstr ""
"每個帳號都可以設定到期日。到期後，帳號會自動停用。這項功能用於 :ref:`project-"
"api`，也可用於一般使用者。"

#: admin/addons.rst:7 api.rst:2996 security/threat-model.rst:103
msgid "Add-ons"
msgstr "附加元件"

#: admin/addons.rst:9
msgid ""
"Add-ons provide ways to customize and automate the translation workflow. "
"Admins can add and manage add-ons from the :guilabel:`Operations` "
"↓ :guilabel:`Add-ons` menu of each respective translation project or "
"component. Add-ons can be also installed site-wide in :ref:`management-"
"interface`."
msgstr ""
"附加元件提供了自訂和自動化翻譯工作流程的方法。管理員可以從每個相應翻譯專案或"
"元件的 :guilabel:`操作` ↓ :guilabel:`附加元件` 選單新增和管理附加元件。也可以"
"在 :ref:`management-interface` 中進行全站範圍的附加元件安裝。"

#: admin/addons.rst:15
msgid ""
"You can also configure add-ons using :ref:`API <addons-"
"api>`, :setting:`DEFAULT_ADDONS`, or :wladmin:`install_addon`."
msgstr ""
"您也可以使用 :ref:`API <addons-api>`、:setting:`DEFAULT_ADDONS` "
"或 :wladmin:`install_addon` 來設定附加元件。"

#: admin/addons.rst:18
msgid ""
"Add-ons that opt in to manual triggering can be run from add-on management "
"or using the :ref:`API <addons-api>`. Results are recorded in the add-on "
"activity log."
msgstr ""
"選擇支援手動觸發的附加元件，可從附加元件管理頁面或透過 :ref:`API <addons-"
"api>` 執行。執行結果會記錄在附加元件活動記錄中。"

#: admin/addons.rst:28
msgid "Obsolete add-ons"
msgstr "過時的附加元件"

#: admin/addons.rst:33
msgid "Customize XML output"
msgstr "自訂 XML 輸出"

#: admin/addons.rst:37 admin/addons.rst:44
#: snippets/addons-autogenerated.rst:1027
#: snippets/addons-autogenerated.rst:1555
msgid "Replaced by :ref:`file_format_params`."
msgstr "被 :ref:`file_format_params` 取代。"

#: admin/addons.rst:42
msgid "Customize YAML output"
msgstr "自訂 YAML 輸出"

#: admin/addons.rst:50
msgid "Customizing list of add-ons"
msgstr "自訂附加元件清單"

#: admin/addons.rst:52
msgid ""
"The list of add-ons is configured by :setting:`WEBLATE_ADDONS`. To add "
"another add-on, simply include the absolute class name in this setting."
msgstr ""
"附加元件清單由 :setting:`WEBLATE_ADDONS` 進行設定。要新增其他附加元件，只需在"
"這個設定中包含絕對類別名稱即可。"

#: admin/addons.rst:59
msgid "Writing add-on"
msgstr "編寫附加元件"

#: admin/addons.rst:61
msgid ""
"You can write your own add-ons too, create a subclass "
"of :class:`weblate.addons.base.BaseAddon` to define the add-on metadata, and "
"then implement a callback to do the processing."
msgstr ""
"您也可以編寫自己的附加元件，建立子類"
"別 :class:`weblate.addons.base.BaseAddon` 來定義附加元件詮釋資料，接著實施 "
"callback 來進行處理。"

#: admin/addons.rst:72
msgid "Executing scripts from add-on"
msgstr "從附加元件執行指令稿"

#: admin/addons.rst:74
msgid ""
"Add-ons can also be used to execute external scripts. This used to be "
"integrated in Weblate, but now you have to write some code to wrap your "
"script with an add-on."
msgstr ""
"附加元件還可以用於執行外部指令碼。這曾經整合在 Weblate 中，但現在必須寫一些程"
"式碼將指令碼包裝在附加元件中。"

#: admin/addons.rst:81
msgid "For installation instructions see :ref:`custom-addon-modules`."
msgstr "安裝方法請參閱 :ref:`custom-addon-modules`。"

#: admin/addons.rst:83
msgid ""
"The script is executed with the current directory set to the root of the VCS "
"repository for any given component."
msgstr "執行指令碼時，工作目錄會設為指定元件的 VCS 儲存庫根目錄。"

#: admin/addons.rst:86
msgid "Additionally, the following environment variables are available:"
msgstr "此外，可以存取後面的環境參數："

#: admin/addons.rst:90
msgid "Version control system used."
msgstr "使用的版本控制系統。"

#: admin/addons.rst:94
msgid "Upstream repository URL."
msgstr "上游儲存庫 URL。"

#: admin/addons.rst:98
msgid "Absolute path to VCS repository."
msgstr "版本控制系統儲存庫的絕對路徑。"

#: admin/addons.rst:102
msgid "Repository branch configured in the current component."
msgstr "目前元件設定的儲存庫分支。"

#: admin/addons.rst:106
msgid "File mask for current component."
msgstr "目前元件的檔案遮罩。"

#: admin/addons.rst:110
msgid "Filename of template for monolingual translations (can be empty)."
msgstr "單語言翻譯範本的檔案名稱（可以為空）。"

#: admin/addons.rst:114
msgid "Filename of the file used for creating new translations (can be empty)."
msgstr "建立新的翻譯所使用檔案的檔案名稱（可以為空）。"

#: admin/addons.rst:119
msgid "File format used in current component."
msgstr "在目前專案中使用的檔案格式。"

#: admin/addons.rst:123
msgid ""
"Language of currently processed translation (not available for component-"
"level hooks)."
msgstr "目前處理的翻譯的語言（對於元件層級的掛勾不可用）。"

#: admin/addons.rst:128
msgid ""
"Previous HEAD after update (only available after running the post-update "
"hook)."
msgstr "更新後的上個 HEAD (僅在執行更新後掛勾後可用)。"

#: admin/addons.rst:132
msgid "Component slug used to construct URL."
msgstr "元件代稱用於建構 URL。"

#: admin/addons.rst:136
msgid "Project slug used to construct URL."
msgstr "用於建構 URL 的專案代稱。"

#: admin/addons.rst:140
msgid "Component name."
msgstr "元件名稱。"

#: admin/addons.rst:144
msgid "Project name."
msgstr "專案名稱。"

#: admin/addons.rst:148
msgid "Component URL."
msgstr "元件 URL。"

#: admin/addons.rst:152
msgid "Project engage URL."
msgstr "專案參與 URL。"

#: admin/addons.rst:159
msgid "Post-update repository processing"
msgstr "更新後儲存庫處理"

#: admin/addons.rst:161
msgid ""
"Can be used to update translation files when the VCS upstream source "
"changes. To achieve this, please remember Weblate only sees files committed "
"to the VCS, so you need to commit changes as a part of the script."
msgstr ""
"可用於在 VCS 上游來源變更時更新翻譯檔案。為了達成這個功能，請記住 Weblate 只"
"能看到提交給版本控制系統的檔案，所以您需要將變更作為指令碼的一部分提交。"

#: admin/addons.rst:165
msgid "For example with Gulp you can do it using following code:"
msgstr "例如，使用 Gulp 時可採用下列程式碼："

#: admin/addons.rst:175
msgid "Pre-commit processing of translations"
msgstr "Pre-commit 翻譯處理"

#: admin/addons.rst:177
msgid ""
"Use the commit script to automatically change a translation before it is "
"committed to the repository."
msgstr "在將翻譯提交到儲存庫之前，使用提交指令稿自動變更翻譯。"

#: admin/addons.rst:180
msgid ""
"It is passed as a single parameter consisting of the filename of a current "
"translation."
msgstr "它作為組成目前翻譯檔案名稱的單一參數而透過。"

#: admin/addons.rst:186
msgid "Add-on activity logging"
msgstr "附加元件活動紀錄"

#: admin/addons.rst:188
msgid ""
"Add-on activity log keeps track of the add-on execution and can be used to "
"keep track of add-on activity."
msgstr "附加元件活動記錄會記載附加元件的執行情況，可用於追蹤附加元件活動。"

#: admin/addons.rst:191
msgid ""
"Each entry records whether processing is pending, successful, failed, or "
"skipped. Skipped entries include the reason the add-on did not run, such as "
"an incompatible component, no relevant changes, or a configured schedule "
"that is not due yet. A successful entry can still mean that the add-on "
"checked its inputs but found nothing to change."
msgstr ""
"每筆記錄都會記載處理狀態為待處理、成功、失敗或已略過。已略過的記錄會包含附加"
"元件未執行的原因，例如元件不相容、沒有相關變更，或設定的排程尚未到執行時間。"
"成功的記錄仍可能只表示附加元件已檢查輸入內容，但沒有發現任何需要變更的項目。"

#: admin/addons.rst:197
msgid ""
"For scope-wide add-ons that process components independently, the activity "
"log contains a separate entry for each component."
msgstr ""
"對於作用於整個範圍、且會個別處理元件的附加元件，活動記錄會包含每個元件各自的"
"一筆記錄。"

#: admin/addons.rst:200
msgid ""
"The logs can be pruned after a certain time interval by configuring "
"the :setting:`ADDON_ACTIVITY_LOG_EXPIRY`."
msgstr ""
"可以在一定時間間隔後清除記錄，方法是設"
"定 :setting:`ADDON_ACTIVITY_LOG_EXPIRY`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:4 admin/memory.rst:217
msgid "Management interface"
msgstr "管理介面"

#: admin/admin.rst:6
msgid ""
"The management interface offer administration settings under the :file:`/"
"manage/` URL. It is available for users signed in with admin privileges, "
"accessible by using the wrench icon top right:"
msgstr ""
"管理介面在 :file:`/manage/` 下面提供管理設定。它對於具有管理特權的登入使用者"
"是可用的，透過使用右上角的扳手圖示來存取："

#: admin/admin.rst:12
msgid "It includes basic overview of your Weblate:"
msgstr "它包括您 Weblate 的基本概覽："

#: admin/admin.rst:14
msgid "Support status, see :doc:`support`."
msgstr "支援狀態，請參閱 :doc:`support`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:15
msgid "Backups, see :doc:`backup`."
msgstr "備份，請參閱 :doc:`backup`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:16
msgid "Shared translation memory, see :doc:`memory`."
msgstr "共享的翻譯記憶，請參閱 :doc:`memory`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:17
msgid ""
":ref:`manage-performance` to review Weblate health and length of Celery "
"queues."
msgstr ""
"使用 :ref:`manage-performance` 檢視 Weblate 健全狀態及 Celery 佇列長度。"

#: admin/admin.rst:18
msgid "SSH keys management, see :ref:`ssh-repos`."
msgstr "SSH 金鑰管理，請參閱 :ref:`ssh-repos`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:19
msgid "Alerts overview for all components, see :ref:`alerts`."
msgstr "所有元件的警報概覽，請參閱 :ref:`alerts`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:20
msgid ""
"Users and teams, see :ref:`custom-acl`; site administrators can "
"also :ref:`clean up user contributions <cleanup-user-contributions>`."
msgstr ""
"使用者與團隊請參閱 :ref:`custom-acl`；網站管理員也可以 :ref:`清除使用者貢獻 "
"<cleanup-user-contributions>`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:22
msgid ":ref:`manage-appearance`."
msgstr ":ref:`manage-appearance`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:23
msgid "Configure :ref:`machine-translation-setup`."
msgstr "設定 :ref:`machine-translation-setup`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:24
msgid "Configure site-wide addons, see :ref:`addons`."
msgstr "設定全站範圍的附加元件，見 :ref:`addons`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:29
msgid "Performance report"
msgstr "效能報告"

#: admin/admin.rst:31
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of Weblate configuration and performance "
"status."
msgstr "此頁面提供 Weblate 設定和效能狀態的概覽。"

#: admin/admin.rst:33
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Configuration errors` indicate issues present in your "
"environment. It covers missing optional dependencies (see :ref:`python-"
"deps`), configuration issues or delayed processing of background tasks "
"(see :ref:`celery`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`設定錯誤` 表示環境中存在問題，包括缺少選用相依套件（請參"
"閱 :ref:`python-deps`）、設定問題，或背景工作延遲處理（請參"
"閱 :ref:`celery`）。"

#: admin/admin.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`System checks` lists possible configuration issues. These can be "
"silenced using :setting:`django:SILENCED_SYSTEM_CHECKS`, see "
"also :doc:`django:howto/deployment/checklist`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`系統檢查` 會列出可能的設定問題。您可以使"
"用 :setting:`django:SILENCED_SYSTEM_CHECKS` 隱藏這些問題；另請參"
"閱 :doc:`django:howto/deployment/checklist`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Celery queues` provides overview of Celery queues. These "
"typically should be close to zero. The same can be obtained on the command "
"line using :wladmin:`celery_queues`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Celery 佇列` 提供 Celery 佇列的概覽。這些通常應該接近於零。可"
"用 :wladmin:`celery_queues` 在指令列上取得相同資訊。"

#: admin/admin.rst:45
msgid ""
":guilabel:`HTTP environment` allows you to see HTTP environment observed by "
"Weblate. This is useful when debugging reverse proxy configuration, "
"see :ref:`reverse-proxy`. :guilabel:`HTTP headers` shows complete HTTP "
"request headers to provide additional information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`HTTP 環境` 可讓您查看 Weblate 觀察到的 HTTP 環境，適合用於偵錯反"
"向 Proxy 設定（請參閱 :ref:`reverse-proxy`）。:guilabel:`HTTP 標頭` 則會顯示"
"完整的 HTTP 要求標頭，以提供其他資訊。"

#: admin/admin.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`System encoding` should list ``UTF-8`` encoding in all processes. "
"This needs to be configured in your system, see :ref:`production-encoding`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`系統編碼` 應在所有處理程序中列出 ``UTF-8`` 編碼。這需要在您的系統"
"中進行設定，見 :ref:`production-encoding`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Connectivity` shows latencies to the database, cache, and Celery. "
"This might be useful to diagnose connectivity issues."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`連線狀態` 會顯示資料庫、快取及 Celery 的延遲。這可用於診斷連線問"
"題。"

#: admin/admin.rst:60
msgid "Appearance customization"
msgstr "外觀自訂"

#: admin/admin.rst:66
msgid ""
"The colors are currently used in both dark and light theme, so be careful "
"when choosing them."
msgstr "顏色目前被同時用在深色和淺色主題中，所以請小心選擇它們。"

#: admin/admin.rst:69
msgid "Colors, fonts, and page appearance can be customized here."
msgstr "可以在此處自訂色彩、字型及頁面外觀。"

#: admin/admin.rst:73
msgid "If you are looking for more customization, see :doc:`/admin/customize`."
msgstr "如果需要進一步自訂，請參閱 :doc:`/admin/customize`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:78
msgid "The Django admin interface"
msgstr "Django 管理介面"

#: admin/admin.rst:82
msgid ""
"Use with caution as this is a low level interface. You should not need it in "
"most cases as most things are comfortably approachable through Weblate UI or "
"API."
msgstr ""
"這是低階介面，請謹慎使用。多數情況下不需要使用這個介面，因為大部分操作都能透"
"過 Weblate 使用者介面或 API 輕鬆完成。"

#: admin/admin.rst:85
msgid ""
"Here you can manage objects stored in the database, such as users, "
"translations and other settings."
msgstr "可以在這裡管理資料庫中儲存的物件，如使用者、翻譯和其他設定。"

#: admin/admin.rst:88
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Reports` section, you can check the status of your site, "
"tweak it for :ref:`production`, or manage SSH keys used to access :ref:`vcs-"
"repos`."
msgstr ""
"在 :guilabel:`Reports` 部分，可以檢查網站的狀態，為 :ref:`production` 進行調"
"整，或者管理用於存取的 SSH 金鑰 :ref:`vcs-repos`。"

#: admin/admin.rst:91
msgid ""
"Use the Weblate UI or API for normal operations such as creating projects, "
"creating components, managing users, or posting announcements."
msgstr ""
"建立專案、建立元件、管理使用者或發佈公告等一般操作，請使用 Weblate 使用者介面"
"或 API。"

#: admin/admin.rst:98
msgid "Project and component creation"
msgstr "專案與元件建立"

#: admin/admin.rst:100
msgid ""
"Projects and components are created from the regular Weblate UI. Projects "
"serve as containers for translation components, and components can use "
"bilingual or monolingual translation files. See :ref:`project` "
"and :ref:`component` for the available settings, and :ref:`bimono` for how "
"bilingual and monolingual formats differ."
msgstr ""
"專案和元件都是從一般 Weblate 使用者介面建立。專案是翻譯元件的容器，而元件可以"
"使用雙語或單語翻譯檔案。可用的設定請參閱 :ref:`project` 和 :ref:`component`，"
"雙語與單語格式的差異則請參閱 :ref:`bimono`。"

