#: admin/auth.rst:2
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "身分驗證"

#: admin/auth.rst:5
msgid "User registration"
msgstr "使用者註冊"

#: admin/auth.rst:7
msgid ""
"The default setup for Weblate is to use python-social-auth, a form on the "
"website to handle registration of new users. After confirming their e-mail a "
"new user can contribute or authenticate by using one of the third party "
"services."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 的預設設定使用 python-social-auth，網站上處理新使用者註冊的一種形式。"
"確定電子郵件後，新使用者可以透過使用一種第三方服務來貢獻或證實。"

#: admin/auth.rst:11
msgid ""
"You can also turn off registration of new users "
"using :setting:`REGISTRATION_OPEN`."
msgstr "還可以使用 :setting:`REGISTRATION_OPEN` 關閉新使用者註冊。"

#: admin/auth.rst:14
msgid "The authentication attempts are subject to :ref:`rate-limit`."
msgstr "身分驗證嘗試服從於 :ref:`rate-limit`。"

#: admin/auth.rst:18
msgid "Authentication backends"
msgstr "身分驗證後端"

#: admin/auth.rst:20
msgid ""
"Weblate relies on Django for the authentication. This includes built-in "
"password-based authentication, social authentication, and third-party "
"authentication backends for Django."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 使用 Django 處理身分驗證，包括內建的密碼身分驗證、社群身分驗證，以及 "
"Django 的第三方身分驗證後端。"

#: admin/auth.rst:24
msgid ""
"Using Django's built-in authentication means you can import the user "
"database of other Django-based projects (see :ref:`pootle-migration`)."
msgstr ""
"使用 Django 內建身分驗證，表示您可以匯入其他以 Django 為基礎之專案的使用者資"
"料庫（請參閱 :ref:`pootle-migration`）。"

#: admin/auth.rst:29
msgid ""
":ref:`docker-auth` describes how to configure authentication in the official "
"Docker image."
msgstr ":ref:`docker-auth` 描述瞭解如何設定官方 Docker 映像的身分驗證。"

#: admin/auth.rst:33
msgid "Social authentication"
msgstr "社交身分驗證"

#: admin/auth.rst:35
msgid ""
"Thanks to :doc:`psa:index`, Weblate support authentication using many third "
"party services such as GitLab, Ubuntu, Fedora, etc."
msgstr ""
"由於 :doc:`psa:index`， Weblate 支援很多使用第三方服務的身分驗證，如 "
"GitLab 、 Ubuntu 、 Fedora 等。"

#: admin/auth.rst:38
msgid ""
"Please check their documentation for generic configuration instructions "
"in :doc:`psa:configuration/django`."
msgstr "請檢查 :doc:`psa:configuration/django` 中的通用設定說明的說明文件。"

#: admin/auth.rst:43
msgid ""
"By default, Weblate relies on third-party authentication services to provide "
"a validated e-mail address. If some of the services you want to use don't "
"support this, please enforce e-mail validation on the Weblate side by "
"configuring FORCE_EMAIL_VALIDATION for them. For example:"
msgstr ""
"Weblate 預設依賴於第三方身分驗證服務來提供合法的電子郵件地址。如果想要使用的"
"一些服務不支援，請透過為其設定 FORCE_EMAIL_VALIDATION，來強制 Weblate 網站上"
"的電子郵件驗證："

#: admin/auth.rst:56
msgid ""
"Enabling individual backends is quite easy, it's just a matter of adding an "
"entry to the :setting:`django:AUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS` setting and possibly "
"adding keys needed for a given authentication method. Please note that some "
"backends do not provide user e-mail by default, you have to request it "
"explicitly, otherwise Weblate will not be able to properly credit "
"contributions users make."
msgstr ""
"啟用個別後端相當簡單，只要將項目加"
"入 :setting:`django:AUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS` 設定，並視需要加入該身分驗證方式"
"所需的金鑰。請注意，有些後端預設不提供使用者電子郵件，您必須明確要求提供，否"
"則 Weblate 無法正確標示使用者的貢獻。"

#: admin/auth.rst:64
msgid ""
"Most of the authentication backends require HTTPS. Once HTTPS is enabled in "
"your web server please configure Weblate to report it properly "
"using :setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS`, or by :envvar:`WEBLATE_ENABLE_HTTPS` in the "
"Docker container."
msgstr ""
"大部分的後端授權需要 HTTPS。一旦啟用網頁服務上的 HTTPS，請設定 Weblate 環境參"
"數 :setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS` 或 Docker 環境參"
"數 :envvar:`WEBLATE_ENABLE_HTTPS`。"

#: admin/auth.rst:70
msgid ":doc:`Python Social Auth backend <psa:backends/index>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Python Social Auth 後端 <psa:backends/index>`"

#: admin/auth.rst:73
msgid "OpenID authentication"
msgstr "OpenID 身分驗證"

#: admin/auth.rst:75
msgid ""
"For OpenID-based services it's usually just a matter of enabling them. The "
"following section enables OpenID authentication for OpenSUSE, Fedora and "
"Ubuntu:"
msgstr ""
"對以 OpenID 為基礎的服務而言，通常只要啟用即可。下列設定會為 openSUSE、"
"Fedora 及 Ubuntu 啟用 OpenID 身分驗證："

#: admin/auth.rst:96
msgid "GitHub authentication"
msgstr "GitHub 身分驗證"

#: admin/auth.rst:98
msgid ""
"You need to register an OAuth application on GitHub and then tell Weblate "
"all its secrets:"
msgstr "您需要在 GitHub 上註冊 OAuth 應用程式，並將其全部秘密傳遞給 Weblate："

#: admin/auth.rst:114
msgid ""
"The GitHub should be configured to have callback URL as ``https://WEBLATE "
"SERVER/accounts/complete/github/``."
msgstr ""
"GitHub 的回呼 URL 應設定為 ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/github/"
"``。"

#: admin/auth.rst:117
msgid ""
"There are similar authentication backends for GitHub for Organizations and "
"GitHub for Teams. Their settings are named ``SOCIAL_AUTH_GITHUB_ORG_*`` and "
"``SOCIAL_AUTH_GITHUB_TEAM_*``, and they require additional setting of the "
"scope - ``SOCIAL_AUTH_GITHUB_ORG_NAME`` or ``SOCIAL_AUTH_GITHUB_TEAM_ID``. "
"Their callback URLs are ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/github-"
"org/`` and ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/github-teams/``."
msgstr ""
"GitHub for Organizations 及 GitHub for Teams 也有類似的身分驗證後端。其設定名"
"稱為 ``SOCIAL_AUTH_GITHUB_ORG_*`` 及 ``SOCIAL_AUTH_GITHUB_TEAM_*``，並需要額"
"外設定作用範圍：``SOCIAL_AUTH_GITHUB_ORG_NAME`` 或 "
"``SOCIAL_AUTH_GITHUB_TEAM_ID``。其回呼 URL 為 ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/"
"accounts/complete/github-org/`` 及 ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/"
"complete/github-teams/``。"

#: admin/auth.rst:133
msgid "GitHub EE authentication"
msgstr "GitHub EE 身分驗證"

#: admin/auth.rst:135
msgid ""
"You need to register an OAuth App on GitHub EE and then tell Weblate all its "
"secrets:"
msgstr "您需要在 GitHub EE 註冊 OAuth App，然後將所有機密資訊提供給 Weblate："

#: admin/auth.rst:153
msgid ""
"The GitHub OAuth App should be configured to have callback URL as ``https://"
"WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/github-enterprise/``."
msgstr ""
"GitHub OAuth App 的回呼 URL 應設定為 ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/"
"complete/github-enterprise/``。"

#: admin/auth.rst:156
msgid ""
"Instead GitHub OAuth App, GitHub App can also be used. With GitHub App "
"permissions can be granted on repositories, organisation and/or user level. "
"If you decide to use GitHub App, you need to enable `Access: Read-only` "
"permission for Users - <Email addresses> and Organisation - <Members>."
msgstr ""
"除了 GitHub OAuth App，也可以使用 GitHub App。GitHub App 權限可在儲存庫、組織"
"和／或使用者層級授予。如果決定使用 GitHub App，您需要為 Users - <Email "
"addresses> 及 Organisation - <Members> 啟用 `Access: Read-only` 權限。"

#: admin/auth.rst:170
msgid "Bitbucket authentication"
msgstr "Bitbucket 身分驗證"

#: admin/auth.rst:172
msgid ""
"You need to register an application on Bitbucket and then tell Weblate all "
"its secrets:"
msgstr "需要在 Bitbucket 上註冊應用，然後告訴 Weblate 所有的秘密："

#: admin/auth.rst:197
msgid "Google OAuth 2"
msgstr "Google OAuth 2"

#: admin/auth.rst:199
msgid ""
"To use Google OAuth 2, you need to register an OAuth application at <https://"
"console.developers.google.com/>."
msgstr ""
"要使用 Google OAuth 2，您必須在 <https://console.developers.google.com/> 註"
"冊 OAuth 應用程式。"

#: admin/auth.rst:202
msgid ""
"The redirect URL is ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/google-oauth2/"
"``."
msgstr ""
"重新導向 URL 為 ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/google-oauth2/``。"

#: admin/auth.rst:226
msgid "Facebook OAuth 2"
msgstr "Facebook OAuth 2"

#: admin/auth.rst:228
msgid ""
"As per usual with OAuth 2 services, you need to register your application "
"with Facebook. Once this is done, you can set up Weblate to use it:"
msgstr ""
"與一般 OAuth 2 服務相同，您需要向 Facebook 註冊應用程式。完成後即可設定 "
"Weblate 使用該應用程式："

#: admin/auth.rst:231
msgid ""
"The redirect URL is ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/facebook/``."
msgstr ""
"重新導向 URL 為 ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/facebook/``。"

#: admin/auth.rst:257
msgid "GitLab OAuth 2"
msgstr "GitLab OAuth 2"

#: admin/auth.rst:259
msgid ""
"For using GitLab OAuth 2, you need to register an application at <https://"
"gitlab.com/profile/applications>."
msgstr ""
"若要使用 GitLab OAuth 2，您需要在 <https://gitlab.com/profile/applications> "
"註冊應用程式。"

#: admin/auth.rst:262
msgid ""
"The redirect URL is ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/gitlab/`` and "
"ensure you mark the `read_user` scope."
msgstr ""
"重新導向 URL 為 ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/gitlab/``，並確保"
"您標註 `read_user` 範圍。"

#: admin/auth.rst:291
msgid "Gitea OAuth 2"
msgstr "Gitea OAuth 2"

#: admin/auth.rst:293
msgid ""
"For using Gitea OAuth 2, you need to register an application at ``https://"
"GITEA SERVER/user/settings/applications``."
msgstr ""
"若要使用 Gitea OAuth 2，您需要在 ``https://GITEA SERVER/user/settings/"
"applications`` 註冊應用程式。"

#: admin/auth.rst:296
msgid ""
"The redirect URL is ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/gitea/``."
msgstr "重新導向 URL 為 ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/gitea/``。"

#: admin/auth.rst:318
msgid ""
"The configuration above also works with Forgejo; for an example of "
"production deployment with Forgejo, see `Codeberg Translate <https://"
"translate.codeberg.org>`_."
msgstr ""
"以上設定同樣適用 Forgejo；對於 Forgejo 的正式環境部署範例，請見 `Codeberg "
"Translate <https://translate.codeberg.org>`_。"

#: admin/auth.rst:330 admin/install/docker.rst:1689
msgid "Microsoft Entra ID"
msgstr "Microsoft Entra ID"

#: admin/auth.rst:332
msgid ""
"Azure Active Directory (Azure AD) is now Microsoft Entra ID. Weblate keeps "
"the ``azuread-oauth2`` and ``azuread-tenant-oauth2`` backend names for "
"compatibility with the underlying Python Social Auth backends and existing "
"deployments."
msgstr ""
"Azure Active Directory（Azure AD）現在稱為 Microsoft Entra ID。為了與底層 "
"Python Social Auth 後端及既有部署保持相容，Weblate 仍保留 ``azuread-oauth2`` "
"和 ``azuread-tenant-oauth2`` 後端名稱。"

#: admin/auth.rst:337
msgid ""
"Weblate can be configured to use common or specific tenants for "
"authentication."
msgstr "可以設定 Weblate，使用一般或特定租戶進行身分驗證。"

#: admin/auth.rst:339
msgid ""
"The redirect URL is ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/azuread-"
"oauth2/`` for common and ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/azuread-"
"tenant-oauth2/`` for tenant-specific authentication."
msgstr ""
"常見的重新導向 URL 為 ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/azuread-"
"oauth2/``，而 ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/azuread-tenant-"
"oauth2/`` 用於租戶專屬的身分驗證。"

#: admin/auth.rst:343
msgid "You will need following:"
msgstr "您需要下列項目："

#: admin/auth.rst:345
msgid ""
"*Application (client) ID* is available on the app registration overview in "
"the Microsoft Entra admin center. *Object ID* is not used in Weblate."
msgstr ""
"*Application (client) ID* 位於 Microsoft Entra 管理中心的應用程式註冊概覽。"
"Weblate 不使用 *Object ID*。"

#: admin/auth.rst:347
msgid ""
"*Directory (tenant) ID* is needed for tenant scoped authentication, what is "
"usually desired."
msgstr "租戶範圍的身分驗證需要 *Directory (tenant) ID*，而這通常是所需的設定。"

#: admin/auth.rst:348
msgid ""
"*Secret value* is displayed once you create a client secret for the app "
"registration. *Secret ID* is not used in Weblate."
msgstr ""
"為應用程式註冊建立用戶端密碼後，系統只會顯示一次 *Secret value*。Weblate 不使"
"用 *Secret ID*。"

#: admin/auth.rst:393 admin/install/docker.rst:1752
msgid "Slack"
msgstr "Slack"

#: admin/auth.rst:395
msgid ""
"For using Slack OAuth 2, you need to register an application at <https://"
"api.slack.com/apps>."
msgstr ""
"若要使用 Slack OAuth 2，您需要在 <https://api.slack.com/apps> 註冊應用程式。"

#: admin/auth.rst:398
msgid ""
"The redirect URL is ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/slack/``."
msgstr "重新導向 URL 為 ``https://WEBLATE SERVER/accounts/complete/slack/``。"

#: admin/auth.rst:421
msgid "Overriding authentication method names and icons"
msgstr "覆寫身分驗證方式名稱與圖示"

#: admin/auth.rst:423
msgid ""
"You can override the authentication method display name and icon using "
"settings as ``SOCIAL_AUTH_<NAME>_IMAGE`` and ``SOCIAL_AUTH_<NAME>_TITLE``. "
"For example overriding naming for Auth0 would look like:"
msgstr ""
"您可以使用 ``SOCIAL_AUTH_<NAME>_IMAGE`` 及 ``SOCIAL_AUTH_<NAME>_TITLE`` 等設"
"定，覆寫身分驗證方法的顯示名稱及圖示。例如，覆寫 Auth0 名稱的設定如下："

#: admin/auth.rst:435
msgid "Turning off password authentication"
msgstr "關閉密碼身分驗證"

#: admin/auth.rst:437
msgid ""
"E-mail and password authentication can be turned off by removing "
"``social_core.backends.email.EmailAuth`` "
"from :setting:`django:AUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS`. Always keep "
"``weblate.accounts.auth.WeblateUserBackend`` there, it is needed for core "
"Weblate functionality."
msgstr ""
"從 :setting:`django:AUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS` 移除 "
"``social_core.backends.email.EmailAuth``，即可停用電子郵件及密碼身分驗證。請"
"務必保留 ``weblate.accounts.auth.WeblateUserBackend``，因為 Weblate 核心功能"
"需要這個後端。"

#: admin/auth.rst:443
msgid ""
"Disabling e-mail authentication will disable all e-mail related "
"functionality – user invitation or password reset feature."
msgstr ""
"停用電子郵件身分驗證，也會停用所有電子郵件相關功能，包括邀請使用者及重設密"
"碼。"

#: admin/auth.rst:448
msgid ""
"You can still use password authentication for the admin interface, for users "
"you manually create there. Just navigate to ``/admin/login/``."
msgstr ""
"對於手動建立的使用者，可以仍然在管理介面使用密碼身分驗證。只需導覽到 ``/"
"admin/login/``。"

#: admin/auth.rst:451
msgid ""
"For example authentication using only the openSUSE Open ID provider can be "
"achieved using the following:"
msgstr ""
"例如，只使用 openSUSE Open ID 服務提供者進行身分驗證，可以採用下列設定："

#: admin/auth.rst:465
msgid "Password authentication"
msgstr "密碼驗證"

#: admin/auth.rst:467
msgid ""
"The default :file:`settings.py` comes with a reasonable set "
"of :setting:`django:AUTH_PASSWORD_VALIDATORS` that ensures that weak "
"passwords are not allowed. You can customize this setting to match your "
"password policy."
msgstr ""
"預設 :file:`settings.py` 隨附一組合理"
"的 :setting:`django:AUTH_PASSWORD_VALIDATORS`，可確保不允許弱密碼。您可以自訂"
"此設定，以符合自身密碼原則。"

#: admin/auth.rst:471
msgid ""
"Additionally you can also install `django-zxcvbn-password-validator <https://"
"github.com/Pierre-Sassoulas/django-zxcvbn-password-validator>`_ which gives "
"quite realistic estimates of password difficulty and allows rejecting "
"passwords below a certain threshold."
