#: admin/auth.rst:795
msgid "Configuring third party Django authentication"
msgstr "設定第三方 Django 身分驗證"

#: admin/auth.rst:797
msgid ""
"Generally any Django authentication plugin should work with Weblate. Just "
"follow the instructions for the plugin, just remember to keep the Weblate "
"user backend installed."
msgstr ""
"一般地，任何 Django 身分驗證附加元件應該可以在 Weblate 上工作。只需要按照附加"
"元件的說明，只記住安裝了 Weblate 使用者後臺。"

#: admin/auth.rst:806
msgid ""
"Typically the installation will consist of adding an authentication backend "
"to :setting:`django:AUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS` and installing an "
"authentication app (if there is any) into :setting:`django:INSTALLED_APPS`:"
msgstr ""
"典型的安裝包括，將身分驗證後端新增"
"到 :setting:`django:AUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS`，並將身分驗證 app （如果有的話）"
"安裝到 :setting:`django:INSTALLED_APPS` ："

#: admin/auth.rst:825
msgid "Two-factor authentication"
msgstr "雙重要素身分驗證"

#: admin/auth.rst:831
msgid ""
"Two-factor authentication adds another layer of security to your account by "
"requiring more than just a password to sign in."
msgstr ""
"雙重因素身分驗證藉由在登入時要求密碼外的驗證方式，使您的帳號增加了一層額外的"
"安全性。"

#: admin/auth.rst:833
msgid "Weblate supports the following second factors:"
msgstr "Weblate 支援下列第二身分驗證因素："

#: admin/auth.rst:835
msgid "Security keys (WebAuthn)"
msgstr "安全金鑰 (WebAuthn)"

#: admin/auth.rst:836
msgid "Both, Passkeys and security keys are supported."
msgstr "Passkey 和安全金鑰都受到支援。"

#: admin/auth.rst:838
msgid ""
"Passkeys validate your identity using touch, facial recognition, a device "
"password, or a PIN as they include user verification."
msgstr ""
"Passkey 包含使用者驗證功能，可透過觸控、臉部辨識、裝置密碼或 PIN 碼驗證您的身"
"分。"

#: admin/auth.rst:840
msgid ""
"Security keys are WebAuthn credentials that can only be used as a second "
"factor of authentication, and these only validate user presence."
msgstr ""
"安全金鑰是只能作為第二身分驗證因素使用的 WebAuthn 憑證，而且只會驗證使用者是"
"否在場。"

#: admin/auth.rst:842
msgid "Authenticator apps (TOTP)"
msgstr "身分驗證器應用程式 （TOTP）"

#: admin/auth.rst:843
msgid ""
"Authenticator apps and browser extensions like Aegis, Bitwarden, Google "
"Authenticator, 1Password, Authy, Microsoft Authenticator, etc. generate time-"
"based one-time passwords that are used as a second factor to verify your "
"identity when prompted during sign-in."
msgstr ""
"Aegis、Bitwarden、Google Authenticator、1Password、Authy、Microsoft "
"Authenticator 等身分驗證器應用程式及瀏覽器擴充功能，會產生以時間為基礎的一次"
"性密碼，在登入時依提示作為第二因素驗證您的身分。"

#: admin/auth.rst:848
msgid "Recovery codes"
msgstr "復原碼"

#: admin/auth.rst:849
msgid ""
"Recovery codes can be used to access your account if you lose access to your "
"device and cannot receive two-factor authentication codes."
msgstr "如果您無法使用裝置且收不到雙重要素驗證碼，可以使用復原碼存取帳號。"

#: admin/auth.rst:851
msgid ""
"Keep your recovery codes as safe as your password. We recommend saving them "
"with a password manager such as Bitwarden, 1Password, Authy, or Keeper."
msgstr ""
"請像保管密碼一樣安全保管復原碼。我們建議使用 Bitwarden、1Password、Authy 或 "
"Keeper 等密碼管理工具儲存。"

#: admin/auth.rst:855
msgid ""
"Each user can configure this in :ref:`profile-account` and second factor "
"will be required to sign in addition to the existing authentication method."
msgstr ""
"每位使用者都可以在 :ref:`profile-account` 中設定第二因素。登入時，除了既有的"
"身分驗證方式外，還必須提供第二因素。"

#: admin/auth.rst:858
msgid ""
"This can be enforced for users at the project (see :ref:`project-"
"enforced_2fa`) or team level. In site-wide deployments, this can also be "
"used to enforce two-factor authentication for all users by enabling it on "
"the default :guilabel:`Users` team, which is assigned automatically to new "
"users by :ref:`automatic team assignment <autoteam>`."
msgstr ""
"可以在專案（請參閱 :ref:`project-enforced_2fa`）或團隊層級強制使用者啟用這項"
"功能。在全站部署中，也可以在預設 :guilabel:`使用者` 團隊啟用，對所有使用者強"
"制使用雙因素身分驗證；新使用者會透過 :ref:`自動團隊指派 <autoteam>` 自動加入"
"這個團隊。"

#: admin/auth.rst:864
msgid ""
"The permissions of a team with enforced two-factor authentication won't be "
"applied to users who do not have it configured."
msgstr ""
"強制雙因素身分驗證的團隊，不會將權限套用於尚未設定雙因素身分驗證的使用者。"

#: admin/backup.rst:4
msgid "Backing up and moving Weblate"
msgstr "備份和移動 Weblate"

#: admin/backup.rst:9
msgid "Project level backups"
msgstr "專案層級備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:13
msgid ""
"The project backups all translation content from Weblate (project, "
"components, translations, string comments, suggestions or checks). It is "
"suitable for transferring a project to another Weblate instance."
msgstr ""
"專案會從 Weblate 備份所有翻譯內容（專案、元件、翻譯、字串評論、建議或檢查）。"
"這適合用在轉移專案到另一個 Weblate 翻譯平台。"

#: admin/backup.rst:17
msgid ""
"You can perform a project backup in :guilabel:`Operations` "
"↓ :guilabel:`Backups`. The backup can be restored when creating a project "
"(see :ref:`adding-projects`)."
msgstr ""
"您可以在 :guilabel:`操作` ↓ :guilabel:`備份` 中進行專案備份。在建立專案時可以"
"還原備份（參閱 :ref:`adding-projects`）。"

#: admin/backup.rst:23
msgid ""
"Project backups can also be created, listed, and downloaded through "
"the :ref:`api` since version 2026.7;"
msgstr "自 2026.7 版起，也可以透過 :ref:`api` 建立、列出及下載專案備份；"

#: admin/backup.rst:26
msgid ""
"The backups currently do not include access control information and history."
msgstr "目前備份資料不包含存取控制與歷史資訊。"

#: admin/backup.rst:28
msgid ""
"The comments and suggestions are backed up with the username of the user who "
"did create them. Upon import it is assigned to a matching user. If there is "
"no user with such username, it is assigned to anonymous user."
msgstr ""
"留言及建議會連同建立者的使用者名稱一起備份。匯入時，系統會將內容指派給使用者"
"名稱相符的使用者；如果找不到相符的使用者，則會指派給匿名使用者。"

#: admin/backup.rst:32
msgid ""
"The generated backups are kept on the server as configured "
"by :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_KEEP_DAYS` "
"and :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_KEEP_COUNT` (it defaults to keep at most 3 "
"backups for 30 days)."
msgstr ""
"產生的備份會依 :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_KEEP_DAYS` "
"及 :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_KEEP_COUNT` 的設定保留在伺服器上（預設最多保留 3 "
"個備份，並保留 30 天）。"

#: admin/backup.rst:36
msgid ""
"Import validation of uploaded project backups can be tuned "
"using :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_MEMBERS`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_TOTAL_UNCOMPRESSED_SIZE`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_SIZE`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MIN_RATIO_SIZE`, "
"and :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_RATIO`."
msgstr ""
"可以使"
"用 :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_MEMBERS`、:setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_TOTAL_UNCOMPRESSED_SIZE`、:setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_SIZE`、:setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MIN_RATIO_SIZE` "
"和 :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_RATIO` 來調整上傳專案"
"備份的匯入驗證。"

#: admin/backup.rst:43
msgid ""
"Use the generated file to import project when :ref:`adding-projects` or "
"in :wladmin:`import_projectbackup`."
msgstr ""
"於 :ref:`adding-projects` 時或透過 :wladmin:`import_projectbackup` 使用產生的"
"檔案匯入專案。"

#: admin/backup.rst:47
msgid ""
"Restoring of the backup might fail if the restoring server has different set "
"of :ref:`languages` or different configuration "
"of :setting:`SIMPLIFY_LANGUAGES`. The restore will tell you which language "
"codes could not be processed and you can then add missing language "
"definitions manually."
msgstr ""
"如果還原伺服器的 :ref:`languages` 集合或 :setting:`SIMPLIFY_LANGUAGES` 設定不"
"同，可能無法還原備份。還原程序會指出無法處理的語言代碼，您可以再手動新增缺少"
"的語言定義。"

#: admin/backup.rst:56
msgid "Automated backup using BorgBackup"
msgstr "使用 BorgBackup 自動備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:58
msgid ""
"Weblate has built-in support for creating service backups using "
"`BorgBackup`_. Borg creates space-effective encrypted backups which can be "
"safely stored in the cloud. The backups can be controlled in the management "
"interface from the :guilabel:`Backups` tab."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 內建了對使用 `BorgBackup`_ 建立服務備份的支援。 Borg 建立了節省空間的"
"加密備份，可以安全地儲存在雲中。可以從管理介面中的 :guilabel:`Backups` 分頁上"
"控制備份。"

#: admin/backup.rst:65
msgid "PostgreSQL databases are included in the automated backups."
msgstr "PostgreSQL 資料庫包含在自動備份中。"

#: admin/backup.rst:67
msgid ""
"The backups using Borg are incremental and Weblate is configured to keep "
"following backups:"
msgstr "使用 Borg 的備份是遞增的， Weblate 設定為保留後面的備份："

#: admin/backup.rst:69
msgid "Daily backups for 14 days back"
msgstr "近 14 日的每日備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:70
msgid "Weekly backups for 8 weeks back"
msgstr "近 8 週的每週備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:71
msgid "Monthly backups for 6 months back"
msgstr "近 6 個月的每月備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:78
msgid "Borg encryption key"
msgstr "Borg 加密金鑰"

#: admin/backup.rst:80
msgid ""
"`BorgBackup`_ creates encrypted backups and you wouldn’t be able to restore "
"them without the passphrase. The passphrase is generated when adding a new "
"backup service and you should copy it and keep it in a secure place."
msgstr ""
"`BorgBackup`_ 建立加密的備份，如果沒有密碼，您將無法還原它們。密碼是在新增新"
"的備份服務時產生的，您應該複製它並將其儲存在一個安全的地方。"

#: admin/backup.rst:84
msgid ""
"If you are using :ref:`cloudbackup`, please backup your private SSH key too, "
"as it’s used to access your backups."
msgstr ""
"如果您使用 :ref:`cloudbackup`，也請備份私密 SSH 金鑰，因為存取備份時會用到"
"它。"

#: admin/backup.rst:92
msgid "Customizing backup"
msgstr "自訂備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:94
msgid "The database backup can be configured via :setting:`DATABASE_BACKUP`."
msgstr "資料庫備份可透過 :setting:`DATABASE_BACKUP` 設定。"

#: admin/backup.rst:95
msgid "The backup creation can be customized using :setting:`BORG_EXTRA_ARGS`."
msgstr "備份建立可以使用 :setting:`BORG_EXTRA_ARGS` 進行自訂。"

#: admin/backup.rst:100
msgid "Weblate provisioned backup storage"
msgstr "Weblate 支援備份儲存"

#: admin/backup.rst:102
msgid ""
"The easiest way of backing up your Weblate instance is purchasing the "
"`backup service at weblate.org <https://weblate.org/support/#backup>`_. This "
"is how you get it running:"
msgstr ""
"備份您的 Weblate 執行個體最簡單方式是在 weblate.org 購買 `備份服務 <https://"
"weblate.org/support/#backup>`_ 。這是您如何讓它執行起來的方式："

#: admin/backup.rst:106
msgid "Purchase the `Backup service` on https://weblate.org/support/#backup."
msgstr "在 https://weblate.org/support/#backup 購買 `備份服務`。"

#: admin/backup.rst:107
msgid ""
"Enter the obtained key in the management interface, see :ref:`activate-"
"support`."
msgstr "在管理介面輸入得到的金鑰，請參閱 :ref:`activate-support`。"

#: admin/backup.rst:108
msgid ""
"Weblate connects to the cloud service and obtains access info for the "
"backups."
msgstr "Weblate 將連線到雲端服務，並取得備份的存取資訊。"

#: admin/backup.rst:109
msgid "Turn on the new backup configuration from the :guilabel:`Backups` tab."
msgstr "從 :guilabel:`Backups` 標籤開啟新的備份設定。"

#: admin/backup.rst:110
msgid ""
"Backup your Borg credentials to be able to restore the backups, "
"see :ref:`borg-keys`."
msgstr "備份您的 Borg 憑證以至可從憑證還原您的備份，參閱： :ref:`borg-keys` 。"

#: admin/backup.rst:114
msgid ""
"The manual step of turning everything on is there for your safety. Without "
"your consent no data is sent to the backup repository obtained through the "
"registration process."
msgstr ""
"為了安全起見，有開啟所有東西的手動步驟。沒有您的同意，就不會有資料傳送到透過"
"註冊步驟得到的備份儲存庫。"

#: admin/backup.rst:121
msgid "Using custom backup storage"
msgstr "使用使用者的備份儲存"

#: admin/backup.rst:123
msgid ""
"You can also use your own storage for the backups. SSH can be used to store "
"backups in the remote destination, the target server needs to have "
"`BorgBackup`_ installed."
msgstr ""
"也可以使用自己的儲存來備份。 SSH 可以用於在遠端目的地儲存備份，目標伺服器需要"
"安裝 `BorgBackup`_。"

#: admin/backup.rst:129
msgid ":doc:`borg:usage/general` in the Borg documentation"
msgstr ":doc:`borg:usage/general` 在 Borg 說明文件中"

#: admin/backup.rst:132
msgid "Local filesystem"
msgstr "本機檔案系統"

#: admin/backup.rst:134
msgid ""
"It is recommended to specify the absolute path for the local backup, for "
"example `/path/to/backup`. The directory has to be writable by the user "
"running Weblate (see :ref:`file-permissions`). If it doesn't exist, Weblate "
"attempts to create it but needs the appropriate permissions to do so."
msgstr ""
"建議去指定本機備份的絕對路徑，例如 `/path/to/backup`。該目錄必須可由執行 "
"weblate 的使用者寫入（請參閱 :ref:`file-permissions`）。在目錄不存在的情況"
"下，Weblate 會嘗試新增它，但需要適當的權限才能這麼做。"

#: admin/backup.rst:141
msgid ""
"When running Weblate in Docker, please ensure the backup location is exposed "
"as a volume from the Weblate container. Otherwise the backups will be "
"discarded by Docker upon restarting the container it is in."
msgstr ""
"在 Docker 中執行 Weblate時，請確保備份位置揭露為來自 Weblate 容器的一個儲存"
"區。否則，備份檔案將在其所在的容器重啟時被 Docker 丟棄。"

#: admin/backup.rst:145
msgid ""
"One option is to place backups into an existing volume, for example :file:`/"
"app/data/borgbackup`. This is an existing volume in the container."
msgstr ""
"您可以將備份放入現有的磁碟區，例如 :file:`/app/data/borgbackup`；這是容器中現"
"有的磁碟區。"

#: admin/backup.rst:148
msgid ""
"You can also add a new container for the backups in the Docker Compose file "
"for example by using :file:`/borgbackup`:"
msgstr ""
"您也可以在 Docker 的編寫檔案中為備份目的新增一個新的容器，例如使用 :file:`/"
"borgbackup`:"

#: admin/backup.rst:159
msgid ""
"The directory where backups will be stored has to be owned by UID 1000, "
"otherwise Weblate won’t be able to write the backups there."
msgstr "儲存備份的目錄必須屬於 UID 1000，否則 Weblate 無法將備份寫入其中。"

#: admin/backup.rst:163
msgid "Remote backups"
msgstr "遠端備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:165
msgid ""
"For creating remote backups, you will have to install `BorgBackup`_ onto "
"another server that’s accessible for your Weblate deployment via SSH using "
"the Weblate SSH key:"
msgstr ""
"要建立遠端備份，您必須將 `BorgBackup`_ 安裝到另一個伺服器上，確保它可接受透"
"過 SSH 金鑰的連線："

#: admin/backup.rst:169
msgid "Prepare a server where your backups will be stored."
msgstr "準備一個您的備份將用來存放的伺服器。"

#: admin/backup.rst:170
msgid ""
"Install the SSH server on it (you will get it by default with most Linux "
"distributions)."
msgstr "將其安裝 SSH 服務（在大部分的 Linux 發行版本中您將能預設的取得）。"

#: admin/backup.rst:171
msgid ""
"Install `BorgBackup`_ on that server; most Linux distributions have packages "
"available (see :doc:`borg:installation`)."
msgstr ""
"安裝 `BorgBackup`_ 在伺服器中。大部分的 Linux 發行版本擁有可取得的套件（參"
"閱 :doc:`borg:installation`）。"

#: admin/backup.rst:172
msgid ""
"Choose an existing user or create a new user that will be used for backing "
"up."
msgstr "選擇一個現有的使用者或建立新的使用者將於備份使用。"

#: admin/backup.rst:173
msgid ""
"Add Weblate SSH key to the user's `.ssh/authorized_keys` file, so that "
"Weblate can SSH to the server without a password (see :ref:`weblate-ssh-"
"key`)."
msgstr ""
"將 Weblate SSH 金鑰加入使用者的 `.ssh/authorized_keys` 檔案，讓 Weblate 可以"
"不使用密碼即透過 SSH 連線至伺服器（請參閱 :ref:`weblate-ssh-key`）。"

#: admin/backup.rst:174
msgid ""
"Create a user-writable directory where Weblate can remotely set up the Borg "
"backup repository, for example in the home directory (i.e. ``/home/borg/"
"backups``)."
msgstr ""
"建立 Weblate 可以在主目錄（即 ``/home/borg/backups``）遠端建立 Borg 備份儲存"
"庫的使用者可寫的目錄。"

#: admin/backup.rst:175
msgid ""
"Configure the backup location in Weblate as ``user@host:/home/borg/backups`` "
"or ``ssh://user@host:port/home/borg/backups``."
msgstr ""
"在 Weblate 中將備份位置設為 ``user@host:/home/borg/backups`` 或 ``ssh://"
"user@host:port/home/borg/backups``。"

#: admin/backup.rst:176
msgid ""
"Once enabled, the backups will be triggered automatically daily. You can "
"also manually trigger a backup from the Weblate UI or using :ref:`backup-"
"management-command`."
msgstr ""
"啟用後，系統會每天自動觸發備份。您也可以從 Weblate 使用者介面，或使"
"用 :ref:`backup-management-command` 手動觸發備份。"

#: admin/backup.rst:180
msgid ""
":ref:`cloudbackup` provides you automated remote backups without any effort."
msgstr ":ref:`cloudbackup` 為您提供自動化遠端備份，無需費力。"

#: admin/backup.rst:190
msgid "Restoring from BorgBackup"
msgstr "從 BorgBackup 復原備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:192
msgid ""
"Restore access to your backup repository and prepare your backup passphrase."
msgstr "還原功能會存取您的備份儲存庫，並準備備份密碼。"

#: admin/backup.rst:194
msgid "List all the backups on the server using ``borg list REPOSITORY``."
msgstr "用 ``borg list REPOSITORY`` 列出伺服器上的所有備份。"

#: admin/backup.rst:196
msgid ""
"Restore the desired backup to the current directory using ``borg extract "
"REPOSITORY::ARCHIVE``."
msgstr "使用 ``borg extract REPOSITORY::ARCHIVE`` 將所需備份還原到目前目錄。"

#: admin/backup.rst:198
msgid ""
"Restore the database from the SQL dump placed in the ``backup`` directory in "
"the Weblate data dir (see :ref:`backup-dumps`)."
msgstr ""
"從放置在 Weblate 資料目錄下 ``backup`` 目錄中的 SQL 備份中還原資料庫（請參"
"閱 :ref:`backup-dumps`）。"

#: admin/backup.rst:200
msgid ""
"Copy the Weblate configuration (:file:`backups/settings.py`, "
"see :ref:`backup-dumps`) to the correct location, see :ref:`configuration`."
msgstr ""
"將 Weblate 設定 （ :file:`backups/settings.py`，請參閱 :ref:`backup-dumps` ）"
"複製到正確的位置，請參閱 :ref:`configuration`。"

#: admin/backup.rst:203
msgid ""
"When using Docker container, the settings file is already included in the "
"container and you should restore the original environment variables. "
"The :file:`environment.yml` file might help you with this (see :ref:`backup-"
"dumps`)."
msgstr ""
"當使用 Docker 容器時，設定檔已經包含在容器中，您應該還原原始的環境變"
"數。 :file:`environment.yml` 檔案或許能幫助您（參閱 :ref:`backup-dumps`）。"

#: admin/backup.rst:207
msgid ""
"Copy the whole restored data dir to the location configured "
"by :setting:`DATA_DIR`."
msgstr "將整個儲存的資料目錄複製到 :setting:`DATA_DIR` 所設定的位置。"

#: admin/backup.rst:210
msgid ""
"When using Docker container place the data into the data volume, "
"see :ref:`docker-volume`."
msgstr "使用 Docker 容器時，將資料置於資料磁碟區，見 :ref:`docker-volume`。"

#: admin/backup.rst:213
msgid ""
"Please ensure the files have correct ownership and permissions, "
"see :ref:`file-permissions`."
msgstr "請確認檔案是否擁有正確的擁有權或權限，參閱 :ref:`file-permissions`。"

#: admin/backup.rst:215
msgid "The Borg session might look like this:"
msgstr "Borg 工作階段可能看上去是這個樣子的："

#: admin/backup.rst:234
msgid "Restoring Docker based setup"
msgstr "還原以 Docker 為基礎的安裝環境"

#: admin/backup.rst:236
msgid ""
"The following steps assume the official Docker Compose setup using the "
"bundled PostgreSQL and Valkey services, see :doc:`install/docker`. If your "
"deployment uses an external database or a customized Compose file, adapt the "
"database and volume steps to that environment."
msgstr ""
"下列步驟假設您使用官方 Docker Compose 設定及隨附的 PostgreSQL 和 Valkey 服"
"務，請參閱 :doc:`install/docker`。如果您的部署使用外部資料庫或自訂 Compose 檔"
"案，請依該環境調整資料庫及磁碟區步驟。"

#: admin/backup.rst:241
msgid ""
"Start with a Docker Compose checkout matching the restored deployment. "
"Restore your original Compose overrides, secrets, and environment variables. "
"The :file:`environment.yml` file from :ref:`backup-dumps` can help with "
"this, but it is not imported automatically."
msgstr ""
"請先使用與要還原之部署相符的 Docker Compose 簽出版本。還原原始的 Compose 覆寫"
"設定、機密資訊及環境變數。:ref:`backup-dumps` 的 :file:`environment.yml` 檔案"
"可以協助完成這項工作，但不會自動匯入。"

#: admin/backup.rst:246
msgid ""
"Restore the backup archive using :ref:`restore-borg` or unpack your manual "
"backup so that the Weblate data directory and :file:`backups/database.sql` "
"are available."
msgstr ""
"使用 :ref:`restore-borg` 還原備份封存檔，或解壓縮手動備份，確保 Weblate 資料"
"目錄及 :file:`backups/database.sql` 可供使用。"

#: admin/backup.rst:250
msgid "Stop the services which can write to the database or data volume:"
msgstr "停止可以寫入資料庫或資料儲存區的服務："

#: admin/backup.rst:256
msgid "Recreate the PostgreSQL volume."
msgstr "重新建立 PostgreSQL 儲存區。"

#: admin/backup.rst:264
msgid ""
"The volume name depends on the Compose project name and can differ "
"from :file:`weblate-docker_postgres-data`. Check your setup before removing "
"any volume."
msgstr ""
"磁碟區名稱取決於 Compose 專案名稱，可能不是 :file:`weblate-docker_postgres-"
"data`。移除任何磁碟區前，請先檢查自己的設定。"

#: admin/backup.rst:268
msgid "Start the database service:"
msgstr "啟動資料庫服務："

#: admin/backup.rst:274
msgid "Restore the database dump:"
msgstr "還原資料庫傾印："

#: admin/backup.rst:280
msgid ""
"Check that the database name matches :envvar:`POSTGRES_DB` and the user "
"matches :envvar:`POSTGRES_USER` in your Compose configuration."
msgstr ""
"確認資料庫名稱與 :envvar:`POSTGRES_DB` 相符，且使用者與 Compose 設定中"
"的 :envvar:`POSTGRES_USER` 相符。"

#: admin/backup.rst:283
msgid ""
"Restore the Weblate data directory to the Docker data volume mounted "
"as :file:`/app/data`, see :ref:`docker-volume`. Files in this volume have to "
"be owned by UID 1000, see :ref:`file-permissions`."
msgstr ""
"將 Weblate 資料目錄還原到掛載為 :file:`/app/data` 的 Docker 資料磁碟區，"
"見 :ref:`docker-volume`。此磁碟區中的檔案必須為 UID 1000 所有，見 :ref:`file-"
"permissions`。"

#: admin/backup.rst:287
msgid "Start the remaining services and follow the logs:"
msgstr "啟動其餘服務並查看記錄："

#: admin/backup.rst:294
msgid ""
"The Weblate container performs database migrations on startup. If you are "
"also upgrading Weblate, follow :ref:`upgrading-docker`."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 容器在啟動時執行資料庫移轉。如果您也在升級 Weblate，請遵"
"照 :ref:`upgrading-docker`。"

#: admin/backup.rst:297
msgid "Refresh the repositories after the restore:"
msgstr "還原後重新整理儲存庫："

#: admin/backup.rst:314
msgid "Manual backup"
msgstr "手動備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:316
msgid ""
"Depending on what you want to save, back up the type of data Weblate stores "
"in each respective place."
msgstr "請根據要儲存的內容，備份 Weblate 在各個位置儲存的相應資料類型。"

#: admin/backup.rst:320
msgid ""
"If you are doing the manual backups, you might want to silence Weblate's "
"warning about a lack of backups by adding ``weblate.I028`` "
"to :setting:`django:SILENCED_SYSTEM_CHECKS` in :file:`settings.py` "
"or :envvar:`WEBLATE_SILENCED_SYSTEM_CHECKS` for Docker."
msgstr ""
"如果您正進行手動備份，您也許想要關閉Weblate 關於缺乏備份的警告，方法是新增 "
"``weblate.I028`` 到 :file:`settings.py` 中"
"的 :setting:`django:SILENCED_SYSTEM_CHECKS`；對於Docker，則"
"是 :envvar:`WEBLATE_SILENCED_SYSTEM_CHECKS`。"

#: admin/backup.rst:330 admin/install.rst:142
msgid "Database"
msgstr "資料庫"

#: admin/backup.rst:332
msgid "The actual storage location depends on your database setup."
msgstr "實際儲存位置依賴於資料庫的設定。"

#: admin/backup.rst:336
msgid ""
"The database is the most important storage. Set up regular backups of your "
"database. Without the database, all the translations are gone."
msgstr ""
"資料庫是最重要的儲存。定期對資料庫進行備份。沒有資料庫，所有的翻譯都會消失。"

#: admin/backup.rst:340
msgid "Native database backup"
msgstr "原生資料庫備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:342
msgid ""
"The recommended approach is to save a dump of the database using database-"
"native tools such as :program:`pg_dump`. It usually performs better than "
"Django backup, and it restores complete tables with all their data."
msgstr ""
"建議使用 :program:`pg_dump` 等資料庫原生工具儲存資料庫傾印。這類工具通常比 "
"Django 備份效能更好，而且能還原包含所有資料的完整資料表。"

#: admin/backup.rst:346
msgid ""
"You can restore this backup in a newer Weblate release, it will perform all "
"the necessary migrations when running in :wladmin:`migrate`. Please "
"consult :doc:`upgrade` on more detailed info on how to upgrade between "
"versions."
msgstr ""
"您可以在較新的 Weblate 發行版本中還原此備份；執行 :wladmin:`migrate` 時會進行"
"所有必要的移轉。如需不同版本間的詳細升級資訊，請參閱 :doc:`upgrade`。"

#: admin/backup.rst:351
msgid "Django database backup"
msgstr "Django 資料庫備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:353
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can back up your database using "
"Django's :djadmin:`django:dumpdata` command. That way the backup is database "
"agnostic and can be used in case you want to change the database backend."
msgstr ""
"另外，可以使用 Django 的 :djadmin:`django:dumpdata` 指令備份您的資料庫。那種"
"方式是不依托資料庫的，並且可以用於先要變更資料庫後端的情況。"

#: admin/backup.rst:357
msgid ""
"Prior to restoring the database you need to be running exactly the same "
"Weblate version the backup was made on. This is necessary as the database "
"structure does change between releases and you would end up corrupting the "
"data in some way. After installing the same version, run all database "
"migrations using :wladmin:`migrate`."
msgstr ""
"還原資料庫前，執行的 Weblate 版本必須與建立備份時完全相同。這是因為資料庫結構"
"會隨版本變更，否則可能造成資料損毀。安裝相同版本後，請使"
"用 :wladmin:`migrate` 執行所有資料庫移轉。"

#: admin/backup.rst:363
msgid ""
"Afterwards some entries will already be created in the database and you will "
"have them in the database backup as well. The recommended approach is to "
"delete such entries manually using the management shell (see :ref:`invoke-"
"manage`):"
msgstr ""
"之後，一些條目將已經在資料庫中建立，您也會在資料庫備份中看到它們。建議的方法"
"是使用管理 shell 手動刪除這些條目 (見 :ref:`invoke-manage`)："

#: admin/backup.rst:374
msgid "Files"
msgstr "檔案"

#: admin/backup.rst:376
msgid ""
"If you have enough backup space, simply back up the "
"whole :setting:`DATA_DIR`. This is a safe bet even if it includes some files "
"you don't want. The following sections describe what you should back up and "
"what you can skip in detail."
msgstr ""
"如果您有足夠的備份空間，只需備份整個 :setting:`DATA_DIR`。這是一個安全帶，即"
"使它包含一些您不想要的檔案。下面的部分詳細描述了應該備份和可以略過的內容。"

#: admin/backup.rst:384
msgid "Dumped data for backups"
msgstr "下載的資料用於備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:388
msgid ""
"The environment dump was added as :file:`environment.yml` to help in "
"restoring in the Docker environments."
msgstr ""
"環境設定匯出到檔案 :file:`environment.yml` ，協助在復原 Docker 環境設定時使"
"用。"

#: admin/backup.rst:391
msgid "Stored in :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/backups``."
msgstr "儲存在 :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/backups`` 中。"

#: admin/backup.rst:393
msgid ""
"Weblate dumps various data here, and you can include these files for more "
"complete backups. The files are updated daily (requires a running Celery "
"beats server, see :ref:`celery`). Currently, this includes:"
msgstr ""
"Weblate 這裡備份各種資料，可以包括這些檔案用於更完整的備份。檔案每日更新（需"
"要執行 Celery beat 伺服器，請參閱 :ref:`celery` ）。目前，這包括："

#: admin/backup.rst:397
msgid ""
"Weblate settings as :file:`settings.py` (there is also expanded version "
"in :file:`settings-expanded.py`)."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 設定為 :file:`settings.py` （還有擴充套件版，在 :file:`settings-"
"expanded.py` ）。"

#: admin/backup.rst:398
msgid "PostgreSQL database backup as :file:`database.sql`."
msgstr "PostgreSQL 資料庫備份為 :file:`database.sql`。"

#: admin/backup.rst:399
msgid "Environment dump as :file:`environment.yml`."
msgstr "環境設定匯出檔案 :file:`environment.yml`。"

#: admin/backup.rst:401
msgid ""
"The database backups are saved as plain text by default, but they can also "
"be compressed or entirely skipped using :setting:`DATABASE_BACKUP`."
msgstr ""
"資料庫備份預設儲存為純文字，但也可以透過 :setting:`DATABASE_BACKUP` 來進行壓"
"縮或整個略過。"

#: admin/backup.rst:404
msgid ""
"To restore the database backup, load it using database tools, for example:"
msgstr "要還原資料庫備份，請使用資料庫工具載入它，例如："

#: admin/backup.rst:411
msgid "Version control repositories"
msgstr "版本控制儲存庫"

#: admin/backup.rst:413
msgid "Stored in :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/vcs``."
msgstr "儲存在 :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/vcs`` 中。"

#: admin/backup.rst:415
msgid ""
"The version control repositories contain a copy of your upstream "
"repositories with Weblate changes. If you have :ref:`component-"
"push_on_commit` enabled for all your translation components, all Weblate "
"changes are included upstream. No need to back up the repositories on the "
"Weblate side as they can be cloned again from the upstream location with no "
"data loss."
msgstr ""
"版本控制儲存庫內容包含上游儲存庫及 Weblate 變更的副本。如果所有翻譯元件都啟"
"用 :ref:`component-push_on_commit`，Weblate 的所有變更都會傳回上游。此時不需"
"在 Weblate 端備份儲存庫，因為可以從上游位置重新複製而不會遺失資料。"

#: admin/backup.rst:422
msgid "SSH and GPG keys"
msgstr "SSH 與 GPG 金鑰"

#: admin/backup.rst:424
msgid ""
"Stored in :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/ssh`` and :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/home``."
msgstr ""
"儲存在 :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/ssh`` 和 :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/home`` 中。"

#: admin/backup.rst:426
msgid ""
"If you are using SSH or GPG keys generated by Weblate, you should back up "
"these locations. Otherwise you will lose the private keys and you will have "
"to regenerate new ones."
msgstr ""
"如果正在使用 Weblate 產生的 SSH 或 GPG 金鑰，您應該備份這些位置。否則將遺失私"
"有金鑰，並且您將不得不重新產生新的金鑰。"

#: admin/backup.rst:430
msgid ""
"Generated SSH wrapper scripts are stored in :setting:`CACHE_DIR` and do not "
"need to be backed up."
msgstr "產生的 SSH 包裝器指令碼儲存在 :setting:`CACHE_DIR`，無需備份。"

#: admin/backup.rst:434
msgid "User uploaded files"
msgstr "使用者上傳的檔案"

#: admin/backup.rst:436
msgid "Stored in :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/media``."
msgstr "儲存在 :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/media`` 中。"

#: admin/backup.rst:438
msgid "You should back up all user uploaded files (e.g. :ref:`screenshots`)."
msgstr "您應備份所有使用者上傳的檔案（例如 :ref:`screenshots` ）。"

#: admin/backup.rst:441
msgid "Celery tasks"
msgstr "Celery 工作"

#: admin/backup.rst:443
msgid ""
"The Celery task queue might contain some info, but is usually not needed for "
"a backup. At most you will lose updates not yet been processed to "
"translation memory. It is recommended to perform the fulltext or repository "
"update upon restoration anyhow, so there is no problem in losing these."
msgstr ""
"Celery 工作佇列可能會包含一些資訊，但通常無需進行備份。您最多只會遺失尚未被翻"
"譯記憶處理的更新。無論如何，建議在還原時執行全文或儲存庫更新，這樣就不會有丟"
"失這些內容的問題。"

#: admin/backup.rst:453
msgid "Command-line for manual backup"
msgstr "適用於手動備份的指令列"

#: admin/backup.rst:455
msgid ""
"Using a cron job, you can set up a Bash command to be executed on a daily "
"basis, for example:"
msgstr "使用 cron 作業，您可以設定一條每天執行的 Bash 指令，例如："

#: admin/backup.rst:461
msgid ""
"You can adjust the list of folders and files to your needs. To avoid saving "
"the translation memory (in backups folder), you can use:"
msgstr ""
"您可以根據需要調整資料夾和檔案的清單。為了避免儲存翻譯記憶（在備份資料夾"
"中），您可以使用："

#: admin/backup.rst:468
msgid "Restoring manual backup"
msgstr "復原手動備份"

#: admin/backup.rst:470
msgid "Restore all data you have backed up."
msgstr "將已經備份的所有資料還原。"

#: admin/backup.rst:472
msgid "Update all repositories using :wladmin:`updategit`."
msgstr "使用 :wladmin:`updategit` 更新所有儲存庫。"

#: admin/backup.rst:479
msgid "Moving a Weblate installation"
msgstr "移動 Weblate 安裝"

#: admin/backup.rst:481
msgid ""
"Relocate your installation to a different system by following the backing up "
"and restoration instructions above."
msgstr "按照上面備份與還原說明，將您的安裝移轉到不同系統。"

#: admin/backup.rst:486
msgid ""
"`Upgrading from Python 2 to Python 3 in the Weblate 3.11.1 documentation "
"<https://docs.weblate.org/en/weblate-3.11.1/admin/upgrade.html#upgrading-"
"from-python-2-to-python-3>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Weblate 3.11.1 說明文件中關於從 Python 2 升級到 Python 3 的部分 <https://"
"docs.weblate.org/en/weblate-3.11.1/admin/upgrade.html#upgrading-from-"
"python-2-to-python-3>`_"

#: admin/checks.rst:2 user/checks.rst:2
msgid "Checks and fixups"
msgstr "檢查與修復"

#: admin/checks.rst:7
msgid "Custom automatic fixups"
msgstr "自訂自動修復"

#: admin/checks.rst:9
msgid ""
"You can also implement your own automatic fixup in addition to the standard "
"ones and include them in :setting:`AUTOFIX_LIST`."
msgstr ""
"還可以應用除了自動修正以外自己的自動修正，並將它們包括"
"到 :setting:`AUTOFIX_LIST`。"

#: admin/checks.rst:12
msgid ""
"The automatic fixes are powerful, but can also cause damage; be careful when "
"writing one."
msgstr "自動修復很強大，但可能導致損壞；寫指令碼的時候要小心。"

#: admin/checks.rst:15
msgid ""
"For example, the following automatic fixup would replace every occurrence of "
"the string ``foo`` in a translation with ``bar``:"
msgstr ""
"例如，後面的自動修復會將每次出現的字串 ``foo`` 在翻譯中替換為 ``bar`` ："

#: admin/checks.rst:21
msgid ""
"To install custom checks, provide a fully-qualified path to the Python class "
"in the :setting:`AUTOFIX_LIST`, see :ref:`custom-check-modules`."
msgstr ""
"為了安裝自訂的檢查，在 :setting:`AUTOFIX_LIST` 中為 Python 類提供完全合規的路"
"徑，請參閱 :ref:`custom-check-modules`。"

#: admin/checks.rst:27
msgid "Customizing behavior using flags"
msgstr "使用旗標自訂行為"

#: admin/checks.rst:29
msgid ""
"You can fine-tune Weblate's behavior by using flags. The flags provide "
"visual feedback to the translators and help them to improve their "
"translation. The flags are merged from following sources:"
msgstr ""
"您可以使用旗標微調 Weblate 的行為。旗標會為譯者提供視覺回饋，並協助他們改善翻"
"譯。旗標會從下列來源合併："

#: admin/checks.rst:33
msgid "Source string additional flags:"
msgstr "來源字串額外旗標："

#: admin/checks.rst:35
msgid ":ref:`additional` describes manual editing."
msgstr ":ref:`additional` 描述手動編輯。"

#: admin/checks.rst:36
msgid ":ref:`bulk-edit` can be used to apply flags in batch."
msgstr ":ref:`bulk-edit` 可用於批次套用旗標。"

#: admin/checks.rst:37
msgid ":ref:`addon-weblate.flags.bulk` add-on can apply flags automatically."
msgstr ":ref:`addon-weblate.flags.bulk` 附加元件可自動套用旗標。"

#: admin/checks.rst:39
msgid "Per-string flags extracted from the file format, see :ref:`formats`."
msgstr "從檔案格式擷取的個別字串旗標，請參閱 :ref:`formats`。"

#: admin/checks.rst:40
msgid ""
"Translation flags (currently only ``read-only`` flag for bilingual source "
"string or when monolingual template editing is turned off)."
msgstr ""
"翻譯旗標（目前只有雙語來源字串，或停用單語範本編輯時所用的 ``read-only`` 旗"
"標）。"

#: admin/checks.rst:41
msgid "File-format specific flags."
msgstr "檔案格式特定旗標。"

#: admin/checks.rst:42
msgid ":ref:`component` (:ref:`component-check_flags`)."
msgstr ":ref:`component` （:ref:`component-check_flags`）。"

#: admin/checks.rst:43
msgid ":ref:`project` (:ref:`project-check_flags`)."
msgstr ":ref:`project` (:ref:`project-check_flags`)。"

#: admin/checks.rst:45
msgid ""
"The flags are comma-separated; if they have parameters, they are separated "
"with colon. You can use quotes to include whitespaces or special characters "
"in the string. For example:"
msgstr ""
"旗標以逗號分隔；如果帶有參數，則以冒號分隔。您可以使用引號，在字串中包含空白"
"或特殊字元。例如："

#: admin/checks.rst:53
msgid ""
"Both single and double quotes are accepted, special characters are being "
"escaped using backslash:"
msgstr "單引號和雙引號都可使用，特殊字元會使用反斜線逸出："

#: admin/checks.rst:63
msgid ""
"To verify that translators do not change the heading of a Markdown document. "
"A failing check will be triggered if the string ``### Index`` is translated "
"as ``# Indice``."
msgstr ""
"用於確認譯者沒有變更 Markdown 文件的標題。如果字串 ``### Index`` 被翻譯成 "
"``# Indice``，檢查就會失敗。"

#: admin/checks.rst:70
msgid ""
"To ensure that internal links are not being translated (i.e. `[test](../"
"checks)` does not become `[test](../chequeos)`."
msgstr ""
"用於確保內部連結沒有遭到翻譯（例如 `[test](../checks)` 不應變成 `[test](../"
"chequeos)`）。"

#: admin/checks.rst:73
msgid ""
"The flags defined on a higher level can be discarded using the "
"``discard:NAME`` syntax. For example, if a component is configured to ``safe-"
"html``, you can add ``discard:safe-html`` to the string flags to skip it for "
"this particular string."
msgstr ""
"可以使用 ``discard:NAME`` 語法捨棄較高層級定義的旗標。例如，如果元件設定為 "
"``safe-html``，可在字串旗標中新增 ``discard:safe-html``，讓這個特定字串略過該"
"旗標。"

#: admin/checks.rst:78
msgid "Here is a list of flags currently accepted:"
msgstr "這裡是目前接受的旗標清單："

#: admin/checks.rst:84
msgid ""
"Generally the rule is named ``ignore-*`` for any check, using its "
"identifier, so you can use this even for your custom checks."
msgstr ""
"通一般則是，任何檢查都使用辨識文字來命名 ``ignore-*``，所以能夠將規則應用在自"
"訂檢查中。"

#: admin/checks.rst:87
msgid ""
"These flags are understood both in :ref:`component` settings, per source "
"string settings and in the translation file itself (for example in GNU "
"gettext)."
msgstr ""
"每個來源字串的設定，在 :ref:`component` 設定中，並且在翻譯檔案自身中（例如在 "
"GNU gettex 中），能夠理解這些標記。"

#: admin/checks.rst:93
msgid "Location-based flags"
msgstr "基於位置的旗標"

#: admin/checks.rst:95
msgid ""
"Some flags are added to strings by default, based on their locations. This "
"means that certain checks will be automatically enabled depending on where "
"the string is used."
msgstr ""
"系統預設會根據位置將某些旗標加入字串。這表示系統會依字串的使用位置自動啟用特"
"定檢查。"

#: admin/checks.rst:98
msgid ""
"``rst-text``: This flag is automatically added to strings in "
"reStructuredText files, if location extension is ``.rst``."
msgstr ""
"``rst-text``：如果位置的副檔名是 ``.rst``，這個旗標會自動加入 "
"reStructuredText 檔案的字串。"

#: admin/checks.rst:99
msgid ""
"``md-text``: This flag is automatically added to strings in Markdown and MDX "
"files, if location extension is ``.md``, ``.markdown``, or ``.mdx``."
msgstr ""
"``md-text``：如果位置的副檔名是 ``.md``、``.markdown`` 或 ``.mdx``，這個旗標"
"會自動加入 Markdown 及 MDX 檔案的字串。"

#: admin/checks.rst:104
msgid "Enforcing checks"
msgstr "強制執行檢查"

#: admin/checks.rst:106
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The enforced checks cannot be dismissed and mark string as :guilabel:`Needs "
"editing` (see :ref:`states`). This prevents translators from hiding such "
"checks."
msgstr ""
"強制檢查無法略過，並會將字串標示為 :guilabel:`需要編輯`（請參"
"閱 :ref:`states`）。這可防止譯者隱藏此類檢查。"

#: admin/checks.rst:112
msgid ""
"Turning on check enforcing doesn't enable it automatically. Some checks have "
"to be turned on by adding the corresponding flag to the string or component "
"flags."
msgstr ""
"啟用強制檢查不會自動啟用該檢查。有些檢查必須在字串或元件旗標中加入對應旗標才"
"會啟用。"

#: admin/checks.rst:116
msgid ""
"This is best used with checks that can cause serious issues when used like "
"checks for :ref:`check-formats`. Using for style checks like :ref:`check-"
"same` is not recommended because dismissal is sometimes a reasonable "
"approach in these."
msgstr ""
"這項功能最適合用於 :ref:`check-formats` 等檢查，因為不處理這類檢查可能造成嚴"
"重問題。不建議用於 :ref:`check-same` 等樣式檢查，因為略過這類檢查有時是合理的"
"處理方式。"

#: admin/checks.rst:120
msgid ""
"The :ref:`project-commit_policy` can then be used to exclude strings needing "
"editing from being committed to the version control."
msgstr ""
"接著可使用 :ref:`project-commit_policy`，排除將需要編輯的字串提交至版本控制系"
"統。"

#: admin/checks.rst:135
msgid "Managing fonts"
msgstr "管理字型"

#: admin/checks.rst:139
msgid ""
"Fonts uploaded into Weblate are used purely for purposes of the :ref:`check-"
"max-size` check, they do not have an effect in Weblate user interface."
msgstr ""
"上傳到 Weblate 的字型僅用於 :ref:`check-max-size` 檢查，它們對 Weblate 使用者"
"介面沒有影響。"

#: admin/checks.rst:143
msgid ""
"The :ref:`check-max-size` check used to calculate dimensions of the rendered "
"text needs font to be loaded into Weblate and selected using a translation "
"flag (see :ref:`custom-checks`)."
msgstr ""
"用於計算所呈現文字尺寸的 :ref:`check-max-size` 檢查需要將字型載入到 Weblate "
"中，並使用翻譯標記選取（請參閱 :ref:`custom-checks`）。"

#: admin/checks.rst:147
msgid ""
"Weblate font management tool in :guilabel:`Fonts` under "
"the :guilabel:`Operations` menu of your translation project provides "
"interface to upload and manage fonts. TrueType or OpenType fonts can be "
"uploaded, set up font-groups and use those in the check."
msgstr ""
"翻譯專案 :guilabel:`操作` 選單中的 :guilabel:`字型` 是 Weblate 字型管理工具，"
"提供上傳及管理字型的介面。您可以上傳 TrueType 或 OpenType 字型、建立字型群"
"組，並在檢查中使用這些群組。"

#: admin/checks.rst:152
msgid ""
"The font-groups allow you to define different fonts for different languages, "
"which is typically needed for non-latin languages:"
msgstr "字型群組允許您為不同語言定義不同字型，非拉丁語言通常需要："

#: admin/checks.rst:157
msgid ""
"The font-groups are identified by name, which can not contain whitespace or "
"special characters, so that it can be easily used in the check definition:"
msgstr ""
"字型群組透過名稱辨識，名稱不能包含空白字元或特殊字元，這使它能夠容易地用在檢"
"查定義中："

#: admin/checks.rst:162
msgid ""
"Font-family and style are automatically recognized after uploading them:"
msgstr "上傳後，系統會自動辨識字型系列與樣式："

#: admin/checks.rst:166
msgid "You can have a number of fonts loaded into Weblate:"
msgstr "您可以將幾種字型載入到 Weblate 中："

#: admin/checks.rst:170
msgid ""
"To use the fonts for checking the string length, pass it the appropriate "
"flags (see :ref:`custom-checks`). You will probably need the following ones:"
msgstr ""
"為了使用字型來檢查字串長度，將適當的標記傳遞給它 （請參閱 :ref:`custom-"
"checks`）。可能會需要後面這些："

#: admin/checks.rst:173
msgid "``max-size:500`` / ``max-size:300:5``"
msgstr "``max-size:500`` / ``max-size:300:5``"

#: admin/checks.rst:174
msgid ""
"Defines maximal width in pixels and, optionally, the maximum number of "
"lines. Word wrapping is applied when more than one line is configured."
msgstr "定義最大寬度（像素），並選用擇定義最多行數。設定為多行時會自動換行。"

#: admin/checks.rst:176
msgid "Defines font group to use by specifying its identifier."
msgstr "指定辨識碼，以定義要使用的字型群組。"

#: admin/checks.rst:178
msgid "Defines font size in pixels."
msgstr "以像素為單位定義字型大小。"

#: admin/checks.rst:184
msgid "Writing own checks"
msgstr "撰寫自訂檢查"

#: admin/checks.rst:186
msgid ""
"A wide range of quality checks are built-in, (see :ref:`checks`), though "
"they might not cover everything you want to check. The list of performed "
"checks can be adjusted using :setting:`CHECK_LIST`, and you can also add "
"custom checks."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 內建了很大範圍的品質檢查，（請參閱 :ref:`checks` ），儘管可能沒有覆寫"
"想要檢查的所有內容。可以使用 :setting:`CHECK_LIST` 來調整執行檢查的清單，也可"
"以新增自訂的檢查。"

#: admin/checks.rst:190
msgid "Subclass the `weblate.checks.Check`"
msgstr "`weblate.checks.Check` 子類別"

#: admin/checks.rst:191
msgid "Set a few attributes."
msgstr "設定一些屬性。"

#: admin/checks.rst:192
msgid ""
"Implement either the ``check`` (if you want to deal with plurals in your "
"code) or the ``check_single`` method (which does it for you)."
msgstr ""
"應用 ``check`` （如果想要處理程式碼中的複數的話）或 ``check_single`` 方法（它"
"將為您完成）。"

#: admin/checks.rst:195
msgid "Some examples:"
msgstr "一些範例："

#: admin/checks.rst:197
msgid ""
"To install custom checks, provide a fully-qualified path to the Python class "
"in the :setting:`CHECK_LIST`, see :ref:`custom-check-modules`."
msgstr ""
"為了安裝自訂的檢查，在 :setting:`CHECK_LIST` 中為 Python 類提供完全合格的路"
"徑，請參閱 :ref:`custom-check-modules`。"

#: admin/checks.rst:201
msgid "Checking translation text does not contain \"foo\""
msgstr "檢查翻譯文字不含有 “ foo ”"

#: admin/checks.rst:203
msgid ""
"This is a pretty simple check which just checks whether the translation is "
"missing the string \"foo\"."
msgstr "這是一項很簡單的檢查，只會確認譯文是否缺少字串 \"foo\"。"

#: admin/checks.rst:210
msgid "Checking that Czech translation text plurals differ"
msgstr "檢查捷克語翻譯文字的複數差異"

#: admin/checks.rst:212
msgid ""
"Check using language info to verify the two plural forms in Czech language "
"are not same."
msgstr "使用語言資訊來驗證捷克語中的兩種複數形式並不相同。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:4
msgid "Code-hosting integrations"
msgstr "程式碼託管整合"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:6
msgid ""
"Weblate integrates with code-hosting sites in several separate places: "
"repository access, incoming notifications, and pushing translations back. "
"The exact setup depends on whether you use Hosted Weblate or run your own "
"Weblate instance, and on whether Weblate should push directly or create pull "
"or merge requests."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 會在多個不同環節與程式碼託管網站整合，包括儲存庫存取、傳入通知，以及"
"將翻譯推送回儲存庫。實際設定取決於您使用 Hosted Weblate 或自行執行 Weblate 執"
"行個體，也取決於 Weblate 應直接推送，還是建立 Pull Request 或 Merge Request。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:11
msgid ""
"Use this page as a provider-oriented checklist. The individual setting pages "
"remain the canonical reference for setting syntax."
msgstr ""
"請將本頁作為依服務提供者分類的檢查清單。各設定頁面仍是設定語法的標準參考資"
"料。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:15
msgid "Setup overview"
msgstr "設定概覽"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:17
msgid "Grant Weblate access to the repository."
msgstr "授予儲存庫權限給 Weblate。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:19
msgid ""
"For GitHub repositories on Hosted Weblate, use the `Hosted Weblate app "
"<https://github.com/apps/hosted-weblate>`_ from Weblate's :guilabel:`Connect "
"GitHub account` flow. The App gives Hosted Weblate repository access without "
"inviting the hosted :guilabel:`weblate` user."
msgstr ""
"對於 Hosted Weblate 上的 GitHub 儲存庫，請從 Weblate 的 :guilabel:`連接 "
"GitHub 帳號` 流程使用 `Hosted Weblate app <https://github.com/apps/hosted-"
"weblate>`_。此 App 可讓 Hosted Weblate 存取儲存庫，不必邀請 Hosted Weblate "
"的 :guilabel:`weblate` 使用者。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:24
msgid ""
"For other Hosted Weblate repositories, and for direct SSH pushes outside the "
"GitHub App workflow, add the hosted :guilabel:`weblate` user where it is "
"available, see :ref:`hosted-push`."
msgstr ""
"對於其他 Hosted Weblate 儲存庫，以及 GitHub App 工作流程以外的直接 SSH 推送，"
"請在可用處加入 Hosted Weblate 的 :guilabel:`weblate` 使用者；請參"
"閱 :ref:`hosted-push`。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:27
msgid ""
"For self-hosted Weblate, create a dedicated code-hosting user and grant "
"access using Weblate's SSH key or an HTTPS token, see :ref:`vcs-repos-code-"
"hosting`."
msgstr ""
"對於自行託管的 Weblate，請建立專用的程式碼託管使用者，並使用 Weblate 的 SSH "
"金鑰或 HTTPS 權杖授予存取權；請參閱 :ref:`vcs-repos-code-hosting`。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:31
msgid "Configure :ref:`component-repo` so Weblate can clone the repository."
msgstr "設定 :ref:`component-repo` 所以 Weblate 可以複製儲存庫。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:33
msgid ""
"Configure incoming notifications so Weblate pulls changes soon after a push. "
"The repository webhook or app must point to the matching Weblate hook URL, "
"and the project must have :ref:`project-enable_hooks` enabled."
msgstr ""
"請設定傳入通知，讓 Weblate 在推送後盡快拉取變更。儲存庫 Webhook 或 App 必須指"
"向相符的 Weblate Hook URL，而且專案必須啟用 :ref:`project-enable_hooks`。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:37
msgid "Decide how Weblate should push translations back:"
msgstr "決定 Weblate 應如何將翻譯推送回儲存庫："

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:39
msgid ""
"Use :ref:`vcs-git` or :ref:`vcs-mercurial` and :ref:`component-push` to push "
"directly."
msgstr ""
"使用 :ref:`vcs-git` 或 :ref:`vcs-mercurial` 與 :ref:`component-push` 以直接推"
"送。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:41
msgid ""
"Use a provider-specific VCS backend, such as :guilabel:`GitHub` "
"or :guilabel:`GitLab`, to create pull or merge requests. These backends need "
"API credentials in the Weblate settings."
msgstr ""
"若要建立拉取請求或合併請求，請使用特定服務提供者的 VCS 後端，例"
"如 :guilabel:`GitHub` 或 :guilabel:`GitLab`。這些後端需要在 Weblate 設定中提"
"供 API 憑證。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:45
msgid ""
"Optionally set :ref:`component-push_branch` when Weblate should push to a "
"branch in the upstream repository instead of using a fork where supported."
msgstr ""
"如果 Weblate 應推送至上游儲存庫中的分支，而非在支援的情況下使用 fork，可以選"
"擇性設定 :ref:`component-push_branch`。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:51 admin/continuous.rst:378
msgid "Pushing changes from Weblate"
msgstr "從 Weblate 推送變更"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:53
msgid ""
"Each translation component can have a push URL set up (see :ref:`component-"
"push`), and in that case Weblate will be able to push changes to the remote "
"repository. Weblate can also be configured to automatically push changes on "
"every commit; this is enabled by default, see :ref:`component-"
"push_on_commit`."
msgstr ""
"每個翻譯元件都可以設定推送 URL（請參閱 :ref:`component-push`），設定後 "
"Weblate 就能將變更推送到遠端儲存庫。也可以將 Weblate 設定為每次提交時自動推送"
"變更；此功能預設啟用，請參閱 :ref:`component-push_on_commit`。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:59
msgid ""
"If you do not want changes to be pushed automatically, you can push manually "
"under :guilabel:`Repository maintenance` or using the API via :option:`wlc "
"push`."
msgstr ""
"如果不希望自動推送變更，可以在 :guilabel:`儲存庫維護` 下手動推送，或透過 API "
"使用 :option:`wlc push`。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:63
msgid ""
"In case you do not want direct pushes by Weblate, there is support "
"for :ref:`code-hosting-github-pull-requests`, :ref:`code-hosting-gitlab-"
"merge-requests`, :ref:`code-hosting-gitea-pull-requests`, :ref:`code-hosting-"
"pagure-merge-requests`, :ref:`code-hosting-azure-devops-pull-requests`, "
"or :ref:`code-hosting-gerrit` reviews. You can activate these by "
"choosing :guilabel:`GitHub`, :guilabel:`GitLab`, :guilabel:`Gitea`, :guilabel:`Gerrit`, :guilabel:`Azure "
"DevOps`, or :guilabel:`Pagure` as :ref:`component-vcs` in :ref:`component`."
msgstr ""
"如果您不想由 Weblate 直接推送，我們支援 :ref:`code-hosting-github-pull-"
"requests` 、 :ref:`code-hosting-gitlab-merge-requests` 、 :ref:`code-hosting-"
"gitea-pull-requests` 、 :ref:`code-hosting-pagure-merge-"
"requests` 、 :ref:`code-hosting-azure-devops-pull-requests` 或 :ref:`code-"
"hosting-gerrit` 檢閱。您可以透過在 :ref:`component` 中選"
"擇 :guilabel:`GitHub` 、 :guilabel:`GitLab` 、 :guilabel:`Gitea` 、 :guilabel:`Gerrit` 、 :guilabel:`Azure "
"DevOps` 或 :guilabel:`Pagure` 作為 :ref:`component-vcs` 來啟動它們。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:74
msgid ""
"Overall, following options are available with Git, Mercurial, GitHub, "
"GitLab, Gitea, Pagure, Azure DevOps, Gerrit, Bitbucket Data Center and "
"Bitbucket Cloud:"
msgstr ""
"整體而言，Git、Mercurial、GitHub、GitLab、Gitea、Pagure、Azure DevOps、"
"Gerrit、Bitbucket Data Center 及 Bitbucket Cloud 提供下列選項："

