#: admin/code-hosting.rst:190 admin/install/docker.rst:1620
msgid "GitHub"
msgstr "GitHub"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:195
msgid "GitHub repository access"
msgstr "GitHub 儲存庫存取"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:198
msgid "Hosted Weblate GitHub App"
msgstr "Hosted Weblate GitHub App"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:200
msgid ""
"On Hosted Weblate, the recommended setup is to connect the `Hosted Weblate "
"app <https://github.com/apps/hosted-weblate>`_ from the Weblate workspace "
"where your project lives. Use the :guilabel:`Connect GitHub account` flow, "
"install the App on the GitHub user or organization that owns your "
"repositories, grant it access to the repositories you want to translate, and "
"import components from the connected GitHub account."
msgstr ""
"在 Hosted Weblate 上，建議的設定方式是從專案所在的 Weblate 工作空間連接 "
"`Hosted Weblate app <https://github.com/apps/hosted-weblate>`_。使"
"用 :guilabel:`連接 GitHub 帳號` 流程，將 App 安裝到擁有儲存庫的 GitHub 使用者"
"或組織、授予 App 對待翻譯儲存庫的存取權，再從已連接的 GitHub 帳號匯入元件。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:207
msgid ""
"The App-backed workflow uses GitHub installation access tokens for cloning, "
"pushing translation branches, creating pull requests, and receiving incoming "
"notifications. You do not need to invite the Hosted "
"Weblate :guilabel:`weblate` GitHub user or configure a separate repository "
"webhook for components imported this way."
msgstr ""
"以 App 為基礎的工作流程會使用 GitHub App 安裝項目存取權杖來複製儲存庫、推送翻"
"譯分支、建立拉取請求，以及接收傳入通知。使用這個方式匯入元件時，不必邀請 "
"Hosted Weblate 的 :guilabel:`weblate` GitHub 使用者，也不必另行設定儲存庫 "
"Webhook。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:213
msgid ""
"Use the Hosted Weblate :guilabel:`weblate` GitHub user only when you "
"intentionally configure direct SSH pushes outside the GitHub App workflow, "
"see :ref:`hosted-push`."
msgstr ""
"只有在您刻意設定 GitHub App 工作流程以外的直接 SSH 推送時，才使用 Hosted "
"Weblate 的 :guilabel:`weblate` GitHub 使用者；請參閱 :ref:`hosted-push`。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:218
msgid "HTTPS with personal access token"
msgstr "使用個人存取權杖的 HTTPS"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:222
msgid "To use this approach:"
msgstr "要使用這種方式："

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:224
msgid ""
"Create a personal access token as described in `Creating an access token for "
"command-line use`_."
msgstr "依照 `建立供指令列使用的存取權杖`_ 的說明建立個人存取權杖。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:225
msgid ""
"Include the token in your repository URL: ``https://"
"username:token@github.com/owner/repo.git``."
msgstr ""
"在您的儲存庫 URL 中包含權杖： ``https://username:token@github.com/owner/"
"repo.git``。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:228
msgid ""
"This is suitable when you are starting with Weblate or working with a single "
"repository."
msgstr "這適合剛開始使用 Weblate 或只有單一儲存庫的情況。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:233 admin/code-hosting.rst:417
#: admin/code-hosting.rst:489 admin/code-hosting.rst:567
#: admin/code-hosting.rst:664 admin/code-hosting.rst:721
#: admin/code-hosting.rst:777
msgid "SSH with a dedicated user"
msgstr "使用專用使用者的 SSH"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:237
msgid ""
"For GitHub, create a dedicated user, for example ``weblate-bot``, and use "
"GitHub SSH URLs for your repositories, for example ``git@github.com:owner/"
"repo.git``."
msgstr ""
"對於 GitHub，請建立專用使用者（例如 ``weblate-bot``），並為儲存庫使用 GitHub "
"SSH URL，例如 ``git@github.com:owner/repo.git``。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:241
msgid ""
"On Hosted Weblate, use this SSH-user workflow only for direct SSH pushes "
"outside the recommended `Hosted Weblate app <https://github.com/apps/hosted-"
"weblate>`_ workflow."
msgstr ""
"在 Hosted Weblate 上，只有在建議的 `Hosted Weblate app <https://github.com/"
"apps/hosted-weblate>`_ 工作流程之外需要直接以 SSH 推送時，才使用這個 SSH 使用"
"者工作流程。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:247
msgid ""
"When using :guilabel:`GitHub` for pull requests, the :ref:`component-"
"push_branch` configuration affects the behavior: if not set, the project is "
"forked and changes are pushed through a fork. If set, changes are pushed to "
"the upstream repository and the chosen branch."
msgstr ""
"使用 :guilabel:`GitHub` 建立拉取請求時，:ref:`component-push_branch` 設定會影"
"響行為：未設定時，專案會建立 fork，並透過該 fork 推送變更；設定後，變更會推送"
"至上游儲存庫的指定分支。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:255
msgid "GitHub notifications"
msgstr "GitHub 通知"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:257
msgid "Weblate comes with native support for GitHub."
msgstr "Weblate 原生支援 GitHub。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:259
msgid ""
"If you are using Hosted Weblate, use the `Hosted Weblate app <https://"
"github.com/apps/hosted-weblate>`_ from Weblate's :guilabel:`Connect GitHub "
"account` flow. It uses GitHub App webhooks, so you do not need to configure "
"a separate :guilabel:`Webhook` in GitHub. Components imported from the "
"connected GitHub account also use the App for repository access and pull "
"requests, without inviting the Hosted Weblate :guilabel:`weblate` GitHub "
"user."
msgstr ""
"如果使用 Hosted Weblate，請在 Weblate 的 :guilabel:`連結 GitHub 帳號` 流程中"
"使用 `Hosted Weblate App <https://github.com/apps/hosted-weblate>`_。這個 "
"App 使用 GitHub App Webhook，因此不需在 GitHub 中另行設"
"定 :guilabel:`Webhook`。從已連結 GitHub 帳號匯入的元件，也會使用該 App 存取儲"
"存庫及建立拉取請求，無需邀請 Hosted Weblate 的 :guilabel:`weblate` GitHub 使"
"用者。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:267
msgid ""
"The `Hosted Weblate legacy app`_ is kept for existing webhook-only setups. "
"Use it only when you need the legacy app to deliver GitHub notifications to "
"Hosted Weblate."
msgstr ""
"`Hosted Weblate legacy app`_ 是為既有且僅使用 Webhook 的設定而保留。只有在需"
"要舊版 App 將 GitHub 通知傳送至 Hosted Weblate 時才使用。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:273
msgid ""
"For self-hosted Weblate, register the GitHub App using the in-app "
"registration flow described below. Weblate generates the App manifest, "
"GitHub returns the credentials, and they are stored in the database - there "
"is no settings-based configuration."
msgstr ""
"對於自行託管的 Weblate，請依照下方說明的應用程式內註冊流程註冊 GitHub App。"
"Weblate 會產生 App 資訊清單、GitHub 會傳回憑證，而憑證會儲存在資料庫中，因此"
"不需要在設定中另行組態。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:281
msgid "Registering the GitHub App from Weblate"
msgstr "從 Weblate 註冊 GitHub App"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:283
msgid ""
"The fastest way to add the GitHub App is to let Weblate generate a GitHub "
"App manifest with the correct permissions, events, and webhook URL pre-"
"filled:"
msgstr ""
"新增 GitHub App 最快的方法，是讓 Weblate 產生已預先填入正確權限、事件及 "
"Webhook URL 的 GitHub App 資訊清單："

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:286
msgid "Sign in to Weblate with an account that has management access."
msgstr "使用具備管理存取權的帳號登入 Weblate。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:287
msgid ""
"Open :guilabel:`Manage → Code-hosting connections → Register Weblate GitHub "
"App`."
msgstr "開啟 :guilabel:`管理 → 程式碼託管連線 → 註冊 Weblate GitHub App`。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:289
msgid ""
"Fill in the form. The :guilabel:`GitHub host` defaults to ``github.com``; "
"change it to your GitHub Enterprise hostname if needed. "
"Leave :guilabel:`Organization` blank to register the App under your personal "
"account, or enter an organization slug to register it under that org."
msgstr ""
"填寫表單。:guilabel:`GitHub 主機` 預設為 ``github.com``；如有需要，請將其變更"
"為您的 GitHub Enterprise 主機名稱。將 :guilabel:`組織` 留空會在個人帳號下註"
"冊 App；輸入組織代稱則會在該組織下註冊。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:293
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Continue to GitHub` and confirm on "
"GitHub's :guilabel:`Create GitHub App` page (you can still rename the App "
"there)."
msgstr ""
"按一下 :guilabel:`繼續前往 GitHub`，並在 GitHub 的 :guilabel:`建立 GitHub "
"App` 頁面確認（仍可在該頁重新命名 App）。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:295
msgid ""
"GitHub redirects back to Weblate, which exchanges the temporary code for the "
"App ID, private key, webhook secret, and slug and stores them in the "
"database. The :guilabel:`Connect GitHub account` button is available "
"immediately afterwards."
msgstr ""
"GitHub 會重新導向回 Weblate；Weblate 會以暫時性程式碼交換 App ID、私密金鑰、"
"Webhook 密碼及代稱，並將這些資料儲存至資料庫。之後即可立即使用 :guilabel:`連"
"接 GitHub 帳號` 按鈕。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:300
msgid ""
"The manifest requests the permissions and event subscriptions Weblate needs "
"(``Contents`` and ``Pull requests`` read/write, ``Metadata`` read-only, "
"``Organization administration`` read-only, ``Workflows`` read/write, and the "
"``Installation``, ``Meta`` and ``Push`` events), and sets the callback, "
"setup and per-app webhook URLs automatically, so no manual GitHub App "
"configuration is required. GitHub delivers the ``Installation`` and "
"``Installation repositories`` events to all GitHub Apps by default."
msgstr ""
"此資訊清單會要求 Weblate 所需的權限與事件訂閱（``Contents`` 和 ``Pull "
"requests`` 的讀寫權、``Metadata`` 的唯讀權、``Organization administration`` "
"的唯讀權、``Workflows`` 的讀寫權，以及 ``Installation``、``Meta`` 和 "
"``Push`` 事件），並自動設定回呼 URL、設定 URL 及每個 App 的 webhook URL，因此"
"不必手動設定 GitHub App。GitHub 預設會將 ``Installation`` 和 ``Installation "
"repositories`` 事件傳送給所有 GitHub App。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:308
msgid ""
"GitHub only offers accounts where the signed-in GitHub user can install or "
"request the app. If an organization is not shown during the install flow, "
"check the user's organization role and the organization's GitHub App "
"installation restrictions. On GitHub.com, public apps can be installed on "
"other accounts; private apps can only be installed on the account that owns "
"the app."
msgstr ""
"GitHub 只會提供已登入的 GitHub 使用者可以安裝或要求安裝 App 的帳號。如果安裝"
"流程中未顯示某個組織，請檢查使用者的組織角色，以及該組織對 GitHub App 的安裝"
"限制。在 GitHub.com 上，公開 App 可以安裝到其他帳號；私人 App 只能安裝到擁有"
"該 App 的帳號。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:315
msgid "Connecting a workspace"
msgstr "連線工作空間"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:317
msgid ""
"Connected GitHub accounts are bound to a Weblate :ref:`workspace "
"<workspaces>`. A user with project administration rights for any project in "
"a workspace can connect a GitHub account on that workspace. After "
"connecting, every project in the workspace can import components from "
"repositories the GitHub App installation has access to. For organization "
"accounts, Weblate verifies that the install-time GitHub user can administer "
"the organization installation."
msgstr ""
"已連接的 GitHub 帳號會綁定至 Weblate :ref:`工作空間 <workspaces>`。只要使用者"
"對工作空間中的任一專案具備專案管理權限，就能在該工作空間連接 GitHub 帳號。連"
"接後，工作空間中的每個專案都能從 GitHub App 安裝項目可存取的儲存庫匯入元件。"
"對於組織帳號，Weblate 會驗證安裝時的 GitHub 使用者是否能管理該組織的安裝項"
"目。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:324
msgid ""
"Projects that are not in a workspace cannot connect a GitHub account through "
"the GitHub App."
msgstr "不在工作空間中的專案無法透過 GitHub App 連接 GitHub 帳號。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:327
msgid ""
"Components imported through the GitHub App flow use the "
"dedicated :guilabel:`GitHub (via Weblate GitHub app)` VCS backend. The "
"component settings UI keeps the repository URL read-only to prevent the App-"
"issued credentials from being redirected to an unrelated repository."
msgstr ""
"透過 GitHub App 流程匯入的元件會使用專用的 :guilabel:`GitHub (透過 Weblate "
"GitHub app)` VCS 後端。元件設定使用者介面會將儲存庫 URL 保持為唯讀，避免 App "
"核發的憑證被重新導向至不相關的儲存庫。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:335
msgid "App webhook URL"
msgstr "應用程式 webhook URL"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:337
msgid ""
"Each registered Weblate GitHub App has its own webhook URL containing an "
"opaque token that uniquely identifies a single registered App:"
msgstr ""
