#: admin/code-hosting.rst:365 vcs.rst:334
msgid "GitHub pull requests"
msgstr "GitHub 拉取請求"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:367
msgid ""
"This adds a thin layer atop :ref:`vcs-git` using the `GitHub API`_ to allow "
"pushing translation changes as pull requests, instead of pushing directly to "
"the repository."
msgstr ""
"這在 :ref:`vcs-git` 頂部新增了一個薄層，使用 `GitHub API`_ 允許將翻譯變更作為"
"拉取請求推送，而不是直接推送到儲存庫。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:371
msgid ""
":ref:`vcs-git` pushes changes directly to a repository, while "
"the :guilabel:`GitHub` backend creates pull requests. The latter is not "
"needed for merely accessing Git repositories."
msgstr ""
":ref:`vcs-git` 將變更直接推送到儲存庫，而 :guilabel:`GitHub` 後端建立拉取請"
"求。僅存取 Git 儲存庫不需要後者。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:375
msgid ""
"To create pull requests, select :guilabel:`GitHub` as :ref:`component-vcs` "
"and configure :setting:`GITHUB_CREDENTIALS`. For GitHub.com, use "
"``api.github.com`` as the API host. The token must allow Weblate to read and "
"write repository contents and create pull requests. If Weblate should fork "
"private repositories, the token might also need administration access."
msgstr ""
"若要建立拉取請求，請選取 :guilabel:`GitHub` 作為 :ref:`component-vcs`，並設"
"定 :setting:`GITHUB_CREDENTIALS`。對於 GitHub.com，請使用 ``api.github.com`` "
"作為 API 主機。權杖必須允許 Weblate 讀寫儲存庫內容及建立拉取請求。如果 "
"Weblate 應 fork 私人儲存庫，權杖可能也需要管理存取權。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:387 admin/install/docker.rst:1671
msgid "GitLab"
msgstr "GitLab"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:392
msgid "GitLab repository access"
msgstr "GitLab 儲存庫存取"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:395
msgid "HTTPS with personal or project access token"
msgstr "使用個人或專案存取權杖的 HTTPS"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:399
msgid ""
"For GitLab, the token needs :guilabel:`write_repository` scope to be able to "
"push changes to the repository. The project access token "
"requires :guilabel:`Developer` role for pushing."
msgstr ""
"對 GitLab 而言，權杖需要 :guilabel:`write_repository` 作用範圍，才能將變更推"
"送至儲存庫。專案存取權杖則需要 :guilabel:`Developer` 角色才能推送。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:403
msgid ""
"The URL needs to contain a username. For a personal access token, it is the "
"actual username: ``https://user:personal_access_token@gitlab.com/example/"
"example.git``. For project access tokens it can be a non-blank value: "
"``https://example:project_access_token@gitlab.com/example/example.git``."
msgstr ""
"URL 需要包含使用者名稱。對個人存取權杖，它是實際使用者名稱：``https://"
"user:personal_access_token@gitlab.com/example/example.git``；對專案存取權杖，"
"可以是非空白值：``https://example:project_access_token@gitlab.com/example/"
"example.git`` 。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:411
msgid ""
"The rules for using project access tokens have changed between GitLab "
"releases, the non-blank value is the current requirement, but older versions "
"had different expectations (project name, bot user name). Check GitLab "
"documentation matching your version if unsure."
msgstr ""
"不同的 GitLab 版本使用專案存取權杖的規則各異。非空白值是目前要求，但較老版本"
"有不同預期（專案名、bot 使用者名稱）。如不確定請檢視相符您版本的 GitLab 文"
"件。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:421
msgid ""
"For GitLab, create a dedicated user and use GitLab SSH URLs, for example "
"``git@gitlab.com:group/project.git``."
msgstr ""
"對於 GitLab，請建立專用使用者並使用 GitLab SSH URL，例如 "
"``git@gitlab.com:group/project.git``。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:424
msgid ""
"For Hosted Weblate repositories on GitLab, add the "
"hosted :guilabel:`weblate` user with the required repository permissions, "
"see :ref:`hosted-push`."
msgstr ""
"對於 GitLab 上的 Hosted Weblate 儲存庫，請加入 Hosted Weblate "
"的 :guilabel:`weblate` 使用者，並授予必要的儲存庫權限；請參閱 :ref:`hosted-"
"push`。"

