#: admin/code-hosting.rst:730
msgid ""
"Weblate has support for Pagure hooks. Add a webhook with destination to ``/"
"hooks/pagure/`` URL on your Weblate installation, for example ``https://"
"hosted.weblate.org/hooks/pagure/``. This can be done in :guilabel:`Activate "
"Web-hooks` under :guilabel:`Project options`:"
msgstr ""
"Weblate 已經支援 Pagure hooks。新增專案的 webhook，目的地為您的 Weblate 安裝"
"上的 ``/hooks/pagure/``\\ （例如 ``https://hosted.weblate.org/hooks/pagure/"
"``）。這可以在 :guilabel:`Project options` 之下的 :guilabel:`Activate Web-"
"hooks` 中完成："

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:739
msgid ":http:post:`/hooks/pagure/`"
msgstr ":http:post:`/hooks/pagure/`"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:745 vcs.rst:380
msgid "Pagure merge requests"
msgstr "Pagure 合併請求"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:749
msgid ""
"This adds a thin layer atop :ref:`vcs-git` using the `Pagure API`_ to allow "
"pushing translation changes as merge requests instead of pushing directly to "
"the repository."
msgstr ""
"這使用 `Pagure API`_ 在 :ref:`vcs-git` 上新增了一個薄層，以允許將翻譯變更作為"
"合併請求推送，而不是直接推送到儲存庫。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:753
msgid ""
"There is no need to use this to access Git repositories, ordinary :ref:`vcs-"
"git` works the same, the only difference is how pushing to a repository is "
"handled. With :ref:`vcs-git` changes are pushed directly to the repository, "
"while the :guilabel:`Pagure` backend creates a merge request."
msgstr ""
"存取 Git 儲存庫時不需使用此後端，一般的 :ref:`vcs-git` 運作方式相同，唯一差別"
"是如何處理儲存庫推送。:ref:`vcs-git` 會將變更直接推送至儲存"
"庫，:guilabel:`Pagure` 後端則會建立合併請求。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:758
msgid ""
"To create merge requests, select :guilabel:`Pagure` as :ref:`component-vcs` "
"and configure :setting:`PAGURE_CREDENTIALS`."
msgstr ""
"要建立合併請求，請選擇 :guilabel:`Pagure` 作為 :ref:`component-vcs` 並設"
"定 :setting:`PAGURE_CREDENTIALS`。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:764
msgid "Other workflows"
msgstr "其他工作流程"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:769
