msgstr "Gitee 通知"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:786
msgid ""
"Weblate has support for Gitee webhooks. Add a :guilabel:`WebHook` "
"for :guilabel:`Push` event with destination to ``/hooks/gitee/`` URL on your "
"Weblate installation, for example ``https://hosted.weblate.org/hooks/gitee/"
"``. This can be done in :guilabel:`WebHooks` under "
"repository :guilabel:`Management`."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 已經支援 Gitee webhooks。為 :guilabel:`Push` 事件新"
"增 :guilabel:`Webhook`，目的地為您的 Weblate 安裝上的 ``/hooks/gitee/`` URL，"
"例如 ``https://hosted.weblate.org/hooks/gitee/``。這可以"
"在 :guilabel:`Management` 之下的 :guilabel:`Webhooks` 中完成。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:794
msgid "`Webhooks in Gitee manual <https://help.gitee.com/webhook>`_"
msgstr "`Gitee 手冊中的 Webhook <https://help.gitee.com/webhook>`_"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:795
msgid ":http:post:`/hooks/gitee/`"
msgstr ":http:post:`/hooks/gitee/`"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:801
msgid "Gerrit review requests"
msgstr "Gerrit 檢閱請求"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:803
msgid ""
"Gerrit support adds a thin layer atop :ref:`vcs-git` using the :pypi:`git-"
"review` tool to allow pushing translation changes as Gerrit review requests, "
"instead of pushing them directly to the repository."
msgstr ""
"Gerrit 支援使用 :pypi:`git-review` 工具在 :ref:`vcs-git` 上新增一個薄層，以允"
"許將翻譯變更作為 Gerrit 審查請求推送，而不是將它們直接推送到儲存庫。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:807
msgid ""
"The optional :ref:`component-push_branch` setting selects the target branch "
"for the Gerrit review. Leave it empty to use :ref:`component-branch`. Use "
"the short branch name, such as ``main``; Weblate and ``git-review`` push the "
"review to ``refs/for/<branch>`` automatically. Gerrit push options can be "
"appended after ``%`` in either setting, for example ``main%topic=l10n``. "
"Gerrit interprets these options as the configured Weblate Gerrit account and "
"applies its own permissions."
msgstr ""
"選用的 :ref:`component-push_branch` 設定會選取 Gerrit 審查的目標分支。將其留"
"空會使用 :ref:`component-branch`。請使用簡短分支名稱（例如 ``main``）；"
"Weblate 和 ``git-review`` 會自動將審查推送至 ``refs/for/<branch>``。Gerrit 推"
"送選項可以附加在任一設定的 ``%`` 後方，例如 ``main%topic=l10n``。Gerrit 會將"
"這些選項解讀為已設定的 Weblate Gerrit 帳號，並套用其本身的權限。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:815
msgid ""
"The Gerrit documentation has the details on the configuration necessary to "
"set up such repositories. There is no separate code-hosting credential "
"setting for this backend."
msgstr ""
"Gerrit 文件詳細說明建立此類儲存庫所需的設定。此後端沒有獨立的程式碼託管認證資"
"訊設定。"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:820
msgid "Docker credentials"
msgstr "Docker 憑證"

#: admin/code-hosting.rst:822
msgid ""
"For Docker installations, code-hosting API credentials can also be provided "
"through environment variables, see :ref:`docker-vcs-config`."
msgstr ""
"對於 Docker 安裝，程式碼託管 API 認證資訊也可以透過環境變數提供，請參"
"閱 :ref:`docker-vcs-config`。"

#: admin/componentlists.rst:4
msgid "Component Lists"
msgstr "元件清單"

#: admin/componentlists.rst:6
msgid ""
"Specify multiple lists of components to appear as options on the user "
"dashboard, from which users can pick one as their default view. "
"See :ref:`dashboard` to learn more."
msgstr ""
"指定多個清單的元件，出現在使用者儀表板上作為選項，從用使用者可以選擇一個作為"
"預設檢視。請參閱 :ref:`dashboard` 來瞭解更多資訊。"

#: admin/componentlists.rst:12
msgid ""
"A status will be presented for each component list presented on the "
"dashboard."
msgstr "儀表板上出現的每個元件清單都會顯示狀態。"

#: admin/componentlists.rst:14
msgid ""
"Each component list has a name displayed to the user and a slug used in the "
"URL. Component lists can be managed using the :ref:`api`. Instance "
"administrators can also use the low-level :ref:`admin-interface` when direct "
"database-object management is necessary."
msgstr ""
"每個元件清單都有向使用者顯示的名稱，以及 URL 中使用的代稱。元件清單可以使"
"用 :ref:`api` 管理。執行個體管理員在需要直接管理資料庫物件時，也可以使用低階"
"的 :ref:`admin-interface`。"

#: admin/componentlists.rst:22
msgid ""
"Change dashboard settings for anonymous users from the admin interface, "
"altering what dashboard is presented to unauthenticated users."
msgstr ""
"從管理介面變更匿名使用者的控制台設定，以調整未經身分驗證使用者看到的控制台。"

#: admin/componentlists.rst:26
msgid "Automatic component lists"
msgstr "自動元件清單"

#: admin/componentlists.rst:28
msgid ""
"Add components to the list automatically based on their slug by "
"creating :guilabel:`Automatic component list assignment` rules."
msgstr ""
"建立 :guilabel:`自動指派元件清單` 規則，即可根據元件代稱自動將元件加入清單。"

#: admin/componentlists.rst:31
msgid ""
"Useful for maintaining component lists for large installations, or in case "
"you want to have one component list with all components on your Weblate "
"installation."
msgstr ""
"對於維護大型安裝的逐漸清單有用，或者如果您希望在 Weblate 安裝中有一個包含所有"
"元件的元件清單。"

#: admin/componentlists.rst:36
msgid ""
"Make a component list containing all the components of your Weblate "
"installation."
msgstr "製作元件清單，包含自己的 Weblate 安裝時的所有元件。"

#: admin/componentlists.rst:38
msgid ""
"Define :guilabel:`Automatic component list assignment` with ``^.*$`` as "
"regular expression in both the project and the component fields."
msgstr ""
"在專案及元件欄位中都以 ``^.*$`` 作為正規表示式，定義 :guilabel:`自動指派元件"
"清單`。"

#: admin/config.rst:4 admin/install/kubernetes.rst:26
#: admin/install/openshift.rst:102 faq.rst:5
#: snippets/addons-autogenerated.rst:0 snippets/machines-autogenerated.rst:0
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "設定"

#: admin/config.rst:6
msgid ""
"All settings are stored in :file:`settings.py` (as is usual for Django)."
msgstr "如 Django 的一般做法，所有設定都儲存在 :file:`settings.py` 中。"

#: admin/config.rst:10
msgid ""
"After changing any of these settings, you need to restart Weblate — both "
"WSGI and Celery processes."
msgstr "變更這些設定後，必須重新啟動 Weblate，包括 WSGI 及 Celery 處理程序。"

#: admin/config.rst:13
msgid ""
"In case it is run as ``mod_wsgi``, you need to restart Apache to reload the "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"在它作為 ``mod_wsgi`` 執行的情況下，需要重新啟動 Apache，來重新載入設定。"

#: admin/config.rst:18
msgid ""
"Please also check :doc:`Django's documentation <django:ref/settings>` for "
"parameters configuring Django itself."
msgstr ""
"還要請檢視 :doc:`Django's documentation <django:ref/settings>` 中關於設定 "
"Django 自身的參數。"

#: admin/config.rst:26
msgid ""
"Configures where contact form sends e-mails. If not configured, e-mail "
"addresses from :setting:`ADMINS` are used."
msgstr ""
"設定聯絡表單向何處傳送電子郵件。如未設定，將使用來自 :setting:`ADMINS` 的電子"
"郵件地址。"

#: admin/config.rst:29
msgid "Configure this as a list of e-mail addresses:"
msgstr "請將此值設為電子郵件地址清單："

#: admin/config.rst:48
msgid "Configures which domains are allowed for fetching assets in Weblate."
msgstr "設定允許哪些網域取得 Weblate 中的資產。"

#: admin/config.rst:50
msgid ""
"This enhances security by preventing loading assets from untrusted sources. "
"Assets are downloaded once by the Weblate server and stored locally, rather "
"than being served directly from external domains to users."
msgstr ""
"這會防止從不受信任的來源載入資產，藉此強化安全性。資產由 Weblate 伺服器下載一"
"次後儲存於本機，而不是直接從外部網域提供給使用者。"

#: admin/config.rst:54
msgid ""
"The allowlist is applied to the initial URL and to every HTTP redirect "
"target before Weblate follows it. Redirects to hosts outside of this "
"allowlist are rejected."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 會先將允許清單套用至初始 URL 及每個 HTTP 重新導向目標，再決定是否跟"
"隨。若主機不在允許清單中，就會拒絕重新導向。"

#: admin/config.rst:58
msgid ""
"It expects a list of host/domain names. You can use fully qualified names "
"(e.g ``www.example.com``) or prepend with a period as a wildcard to match "
"all subdomains (e.g ``.example.com`` will match ``cdn.example.com`` or "
"``static.example.com``)."
msgstr ""
"此設定應為主機名稱或網域清單。您可以使用完整限定名稱（例如 "
"``www.example.com``），也可以在前方加上句點作為萬用字元，以比對所有子網域（例"
"如 ``.example.com`` 會比對 ``cdn.example.com`` 及 ``static.example.com``）。"

#: admin/config.rst:62
msgid "Defaults to ``[\"*\"]``, which allows all domains."
msgstr "預設為 ``[\"*\"]``，代表允許所有網域。"

#: admin/config.rst:64
msgid "**Example**"
msgstr "**範例**"

#: admin/config.rst:75
msgid "This is currently used in the following places:"
msgstr "目前用於下列位置："

#: admin/config.rst:77
msgid "Screenshot uploads, see :ref:`screenshots`"
msgstr "螢幕擷圖上傳，請參閱 :ref:`screenshots`"

#: admin/config.rst:78
msgid "Remote HTML downloads for the :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.cdnjs` add-on"
msgstr "適用於 :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.cdnjs` 附加元件的遠端 HTML 下載"

#: admin/config.rst:91
msgid ""
"Configures which custom machinery domains are explicitly allowed in project-"
"level machine translation configuration."
msgstr "設定專案層級機器翻譯設定明確允許哪些自訂機制網域。"

#: admin/config.rst:94
msgid ""
"This setting applies only to machinery services and does not "
"affect :setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_DOMAINS`."
msgstr ""
"此設定僅適用於機器翻譯服務，不會影響 :setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_DOMAINS`。"

#: admin/config.rst:97
msgid ""
"It expects a list of host/domain names. You can use fully qualified names or "
"prepend with a period as a wildcard to match all subdomains."
msgstr ""
"此設定應為主機名稱或網域清單。您可以使用完整限定名稱，也可在前方加上句點作為"
"萬用字元，以比對所有子網域。"

#: admin/config.rst:100
msgid "Defaults to ``[]``."
msgstr "預設為 ``[]``。"

#: admin/config.rst:102
msgid ""
"The allowlist affects project-managed machinery in two ways: it permits the "
"configured endpoint during outbound validation, and it marks matching hosts "
"as trusted when deciding whether remote provider error details or response "
"bodies can be shown to the user. For direct connections, runtime checks "
"still reject destinations that resolve to private or otherwise non-public "
"addresses. When an HTTP(S) proxy is used, runtime validation falls back to "
"hostname validation and does not perform the same local DNS or peer-IP "
"checks."
msgstr ""
"允許清單對專案管理的機器翻譯服務的影響體現在兩個方面：一是在出站驗證期間允許"
"設定的端點，二是在決定是否可以向使用者顯示遠端服務提供者錯誤詳情或回應內容時"
"將相符主機標記為可信。對於直接連線，執行時檢查仍會拒絕解析為私有或非公開地址"
"的目標。使用 HTTP(S) 代理時，執行時驗證將回退到主機名稱驗證，並且不會執行相同"
"的本機 DNS 或對等 IP 檢查。"

#: admin/config.rst:117
msgid ""
"Configures size limit in bytes for fetching or uploading assets into "
"Weblate. Defaults to 10 MB."
msgstr ""
"設定擷取或上傳至 Weblate 的資產大小上限（單位為位元組）。預設為 10 MB。"

#: admin/config.rst:132
msgid ""
"Defines hostnames or domains exempt from :setting:`ASSET_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` "
"for remote asset downloads that enforce private-target checks. Entries "
"follow Django host matching semantics, so values such as "
"``assets.internal.example`` or ``.internal.example`` can be used."
msgstr ""
"定義遠端資產下載在執行私人目標檢查時，可豁"
"免 :setting:`ASSET_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` 的主機名稱或網域。項目遵循 Django 主機比"
"對語意，因此可以使用 ``assets.internal.example`` 或 ``.internal.example`` 等"
"值。"

#: admin/config.rst:137
msgid ""
"This does not replace :setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_DOMAINS`; remote assets must "
"still match the asset domain allowlist."
msgstr ""
"這不會取代 :setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_DOMAINS`；遠端資產仍必須符合資產網域允許清"
"單。"

#: admin/config.rst:140 admin/config.rst:1946 admin/config.rst:1980
#: admin/config.rst:2057
msgid "Default configuration:"
msgstr "預設設定："

#: admin/config.rst:158
msgid ""
"Reject remote asset URLs pointing to internal or non-public addresses unless "
"the target host is included in :setting:`ASSET_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST`. On by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"拒絕指向內部或非公開地址的遠端資產 URL，除非目標主機包含"
"在 :setting:`ASSET_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST` 中。預設開啟。"

#: admin/config.rst:162
msgid ""
"When enabled, hostnames that cannot be resolved during validation are "
"rejected unless they are explicitly included "
"in :setting:`ASSET_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST`. This currently applies to screenshot "
"URL uploads and remote HTML downloads for the :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.cdnjs` "
"add-on."
msgstr ""
"啟用後，系統會拒絕在驗證期間無法解析的主機名稱，除非已明確將它們加"
"入 :setting:`ASSET_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST`。此設定目前適用於螢幕擷圖 URL 上傳，以"
"及 :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.cdnjs` 附加元件的遠端 HTML 下載。"

#: admin/config.rst:181
msgid ""
"Argon2id time cost for the ALTCHA proof-of-work challenge. Defaults to ``3``."
msgstr "ALTCHA 工作量證明挑戰的 Argon2id 時間成本。預設為 ``3``。"

#: admin/config.rst:183
msgid ""
"Replaces ``ALTCHA_MAX_NUMBER``, which applied to the removed ALTCHA widget "
"v2."
msgstr "取代套用於已移除 ALTCHA Widget v2 的 ``ALTCHA_MAX_NUMBER``。"

#: admin/config.rst:192
msgid "Argon2id memory cost in KiB. Defaults to ``65536``."
msgstr "Argon2id 記憶體成本（單位為 KiB）。預設為 ``65536``。"

#: admin/config.rst:201
msgid "Argon2id parallelism factor. Defaults to ``1``."
msgstr "Argon2id 平行係數。預設為 ``1``。"

#: admin/config.rst:205
msgid ""
"`ALTCHA Proof of Work Mechanism <https://altcha.org/docs/proof-of-work/>`_"
msgstr "`ALTCHA 工作量證明機制 <https://altcha.org/docs/proof-of-work/>`_"

#: admin/config.rst:212
msgid "Username of users that are not signed in."
msgstr "未登入使用者的使用者名稱。"

#: admin/config.rst:223
msgid ""
"The maximum number of days Weblate will keep audit logs containing "
"information about the account activity."
msgstr "Weblate 保留含有帳號活動資訊之稽核記錄的最長天數。"

#: admin/config.rst:226 admin/config.rst:317
msgid "Defaults to 180 days."
msgstr "預設為 180 天。"

#: admin/config.rst:233
msgid ""
"Maximum number of failed authentication attempts before rate limiting is "
"applied."
msgstr "在rate限制應用前，授權嘗試失敗的最多次數。"

#: admin/config.rst:235
msgid "This is currently applied in the following locations:"
msgstr "目前，這應用在後面的位置："

#: admin/config.rst:237
msgid ""
"Sign in. Deletes the account password, preventing the user from signing in "
"without requesting a new password."
msgstr "登入。刪除帳號密碼，防止使用者不請求新的密碼而登入。"

#: admin/config.rst:239
msgid ""
"Password reset. Prevents new e-mails from being sent, avoiding spamming "
"users with too many password-reset attempts."
msgstr ""
"密碼重設。防止傳送新的電子郵件，避免過多密碼重設嘗試造成使用者收到大量信件。"

#: admin/config.rst:242
