#: admin/config.rst:274
msgid ""
"This requires that :ref:`celery` is working, and will take effect after it "
"is restarted."
msgstr "這需要 :ref:`celery` 工作，並在重啟後生效。"

#: admin/config.rst:281
msgid ""
"Prefix for constructing avatar URLs as: ``${AVATAR_URL_PREFIX}/avatar/$"
"{MAIL_HASH}?${PARAMS}``. The following services are known to work:"
msgstr ""
"建構頭像 URL 的前置字串，格式如下：``${AVATAR_URL_PREFIX}/avatar/$"
"{MAIL_HASH}?${PARAMS}``。已知下列服務可正常運作："

#: admin/config.rst:285
msgid "Gravatar (default), as per https://gravatar.com/"
msgstr "Gravatar（預設）：https://gravatar.com/"

#: admin/config.rst:287
