msgstr "控制 Weblate 公開自身版本的顯著程度。"

#: admin/config.rst:1219 admin/install/docker.rst:830
#: admin/install/docker.rst:924
msgid "Supported values are:"
msgstr "支援的值有："

#: admin/config.rst:1222
msgid ""
"Show the version in shared UI such as the footer and expose it "
"in :http:get:`/api/metrics/`."
msgstr ""
"在頁尾等共用使用者介面中顯示版本，並於 :http:get:`/api/metrics/` 中提供版本資"
"訊。"

#: admin/config.rst:1226
msgid ""
"Hide the version from prominent shared UI, while keeping it discoverable on "
"the :guilabel:`About` page and in :http:get:`/api/metrics/`."
msgstr ""
"在顯眼的共享使用者介面中隱藏版本，但在 :guilabel:`關於` 頁面和 :http:get:`/"
"api/metrics/` 中讓版本可發現。"

#: admin/config.rst:1230
msgid ""
"Hide the version from shared UI and :http:get:`/api/metrics/`. This also "
"makes anonymous documentation links point to the latest documentation "
"instead of the version matching the installed release."
msgstr ""
"在共享的使用者介面和 :http:get:`/api/metrics/` 中隱藏版本。這還會使匿名文件連"
"結指向最新文件而不是相符已安裝 Weblate 版本的文件。"

#: admin/config.rst:1234
msgid ""
"Hiding the version is a recommended security practice in some corporations, "
"but it does not prevent an attacker from inferring the version by probing "
"behavior."
msgstr ""
"隱藏版本是某些企業建議的安全實踐，但不能防止攻擊者透過試探行為來推測版本。"

#: admin/config.rst:1240
msgid "The default is ``show``."
msgstr "預設值為 ``show``。"

#: admin/config.rst:1250
msgid ""
"Compatibility alias for :setting:`VERSION_DISPLAY`. Set this to ``True`` to "
"get the same behavior as ``VERSION_DISPLAY = \"hide\"``."
msgstr ""
":setting:`VERSION_DISPLAY` 的相容性別稱。將這個設為 ``True`` 以取得和 "
"``VERSION_DISPLAY = \"hide\"`` 相同的行為。"

#: admin/config.rst:1260
msgid ""
"Template used to generate e-mail addresses for internal Weblate bot "
"accounts. Defaults to ``\"noreply-{scope}-{name}@weblate.org\"``."
msgstr ""
"用於產生內部 Weblate 機器人帳號電子郵件地址的範本。預設為 ``\"noreply-"
"{scope}-{name}@weblate.org\"``。"

#: admin/config.rst:1263
msgid ""
"It can contain ``{scope}``, ``{name}``, ``{username}``, ``{site_title}``, "
"and ``{site_domain}``."
msgstr ""
"它可以包含 ``{scope}`` 、 ``{name}`` 、 ``{username}`` 、 ``{site_title}`` "
"和 ``{site_domain}`` 。"

#: admin/config.rst:1266
msgid ""
"Use ``{scope}`` and ``{name}`` when generating the e-mail local part. The "
"``{username}`` value contains the internal ``scope:name`` username."
msgstr ""
"產生電子郵件地址的 @ 前部分時，請使用 ``{scope}`` 和 ``{name}``。``{username}"
"`` 值包含內部的 ``scope:name`` 使用者名稱。"

#: admin/config.rst:1269
msgid ""
"Existing internal bot accounts are updated when :wladmin:`migrate` is run. "
"Project API token accounts are not affected."
msgstr ""
"執行 :wladmin:`migrate` 時會更新既有的內部機器人帳號。專案 API 權杖帳號不受影"
"響。"

#: admin/config.rst:1277
msgid "Indicates whether Weblate is running behind a reverse proxy."
msgstr "說明 Weblate 是否在反向代理後面執行。"

#: admin/config.rst:1279
msgid ""
"If set to ``True``, Weblate gets IP address from a header defined "
"by :setting:`IP_PROXY_HEADER`."
msgstr ""
"如果設定為 ``True``， Weblate 會從 :setting:`IP_PROXY_HEADER` 定義的標頭中得"
"到 IP 位址。"

#: admin/config.rst:1284
msgid ""
"Ensure you are actually using a reverse proxy and that it sets this header, "
"otherwise users will be able to fake the IP address."
msgstr ""
"確保真正使用反向代理，並且設定了這個標頭，否則使用者將能夠假冒 IP 位址。"

#: admin/config.rst:1289
msgid "This is not on by default."
msgstr "這並非預設啟用。"

#: admin/config.rst:1303
msgid ""
"Indicates which header Weblate should obtain the IP address from "
"when :setting:`IP_BEHIND_REVERSE_PROXY` is turned on."
msgstr ""
"說明當 :setting:`IP_BEHIND_REVERSE_PROXY` 開啟時，Weblate應該從那個標頭得到 "
"IP 位址。"

#: admin/config.rst:1306
msgid "Defaults to ``HTTP_X_FORWARDED_FOR``."
msgstr "預設為 ``HTTP_X_FORWARDED_FOR``。"

#: admin/config.rst:1323
msgid "The default changed from 1 to -1."
msgstr "預設已從 1 變更為 -1。"

#: admin/config.rst:1325
msgid ""
"Indicates which part of :setting:`IP_PROXY_HEADER` is used as client IP "
"address."
msgstr "說明 :setting:`IP_PROXY_HEADER` 的哪部分用作用戶端 IP 位址。"

#: admin/config.rst:1328
msgid ""
"Depending on your setup, this header might consist of several IP addresses, "
"(for example ``X-Forwarded-For: client-ip, proxy-a, proxy-b``) and you can "
"configure which address from the header is used as client IP address here."
msgstr ""
"取決於您的設定，這個標頭會包括幾個 IP 地址，（例如 ``X-Forwarded-For: client-"
"ip, proxy-a, proxy-b``），並且可以設定標頭的哪個地址在這裡用作客戶端 IP 地"
"址。"

#: admin/config.rst:1334
msgid ""
"Setting this affects the security of your installation. You should only "
"configure it to use trusted proxies for determining the IP address. Please "
"check <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Reference/Headers/X-"
"Forwarded-For#security_and_privacy_concerns> for more details."
msgstr ""
"這項設定會影響安裝環境的安全性。只有在透過受信任的 Proxy 判斷 IP 位址時才應設"
"定。詳細資訊請參閱 <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/"
"Reference/Headers/X-Forwarded-For#security_and_privacy_concerns>。"

#: admin/config.rst:1338
msgid "Defaults to -1."
msgstr "預設為 -1。"

#: admin/config.rst:1355
msgid "CSS class added to the wrappers around legal document templates."
msgstr "新增至法律文件範本外層包裝元素的 CSS 類別。"

#: admin/config.rst:1357
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Defaults to ``\"tos\"``, which enables the built-in legal document "
#| "numbering and spacing rules. Set this to an empty string to render legal "
#| "documents without the built-in numbering."
msgid ""
"Defaults to ``\"tos\"``. Weblate does not attach styling to this class; "
"custom legal styles can use it to target document wrappers. Set this to an "
"empty string to render legal documents without a wrapper class."
msgstr ""
"預設為 ``\"tos\"``，這會啟用內建的法律文件編號與間距規則。將此值設為空白字"
"串，即可在沒有內建編號的情況下轉譯法律文件。"

#: admin/config.rst:1377
msgid "List of legal document page identifiers to hide from the legal module."
msgstr "要從法律模組隱藏的法律文件頁面辨識碼清單。"

#: admin/config.rst:1379
msgid ""
"The ``index`` page is always visible. Supported document identifiers are "
"``terms``, ``cookies``, ``privacy``, and ``contracts``."
msgstr ""
"``index`` 頁面永遠可見。支援的文件辨識碼為 ``terms``、``cookies``、"
"``privacy`` 和 ``contracts``。"

#: admin/config.rst:1382
msgid ""
"Hidden pages are removed from the legal menu and return a 404 response when "
"requested directly. Hiding ``terms`` or ``privacy`` is not recommended when "
"terms of service confirmation is enabled."
msgstr ""
"隱藏的頁面會從法律選單中移除，直接要求時則傳回 404 回應。啟用服務條款確認功能"
"時，不建議隱藏 ``terms`` 或 ``privacy``。"

#: admin/config.rst:1386
msgid ""
"When ``terms`` or ``privacy`` is hidden, links exposed through the "
"``terms_url`` and ``privacy_url`` template variables "
"use :setting:`LEGAL_URL` and :setting:`PRIVACY_URL` as fallbacks when "
