msgstr "此整合不支援 Matomo Tag Manager。"

#: admin/config.rst:1578
msgid ""
"Full URL (including trailing slash) of a Matomo (formerly Piwik) "
"installation you want to use to track Weblate use. Please check <https://"
"matomo.org/> for more details."
msgstr ""
"您想用於跟蹤 Weblate 使用情況的 Matomo（以前的 Piwik）安裝的完整 URL（包括結"
"尾的斜槓）。請查閱 <https://matomo.org/> 瞭解詳情。"

#: admin/config.rst:1601
msgid "Number of nearby strings to show in each direction in the full editor."
msgstr "在完整編輯器中要在各方向顯示的相鄰字串數。"

#: admin/config.rst:1603
msgid ""
"This is just a default value, users can adjust this in :ref:`user-profile`."
msgstr "這只是預設值，使用者可以在 :ref:`user-profile` 中調整。"

#: admin/config.rst:1612
msgid "Default number of elements to display when pagination is active."
msgstr "分頁啟用時顯示的預設元素數量。"

#: admin/config.rst:1621
msgid "List for credentials for Pagure servers."
msgstr "Pagure 伺服器憑證清單。"

#: admin/config.rst:1637
msgid "`Pagure API <https://pagure.io/api/0/>`_"
msgstr "`Pagure API <https://pagure.io/api/0/>`_"

#: admin/config.rst:1646
msgid ""
"Minimal password score as evaluated by the `zxcvbn <https://github.com/"
"dwolfhub/zxcvbn-python>`_ password strength estimator."
msgstr ""
"最小的密碼得分由 `zxcvbn <https://github.com/dwolfhub/zxcvbn-python>`_ 密碼長"
"度預測器進行評估。"

#: admin/config.rst:1649
msgid "Defaults to 0, which means strength checking is disabled."
msgstr "預設為 0，表示停用強度檢查。"

#: admin/config.rst:1663
msgid ""
"URL for password reset when authentication is handled by an external "
"identity provider, such as LDAP, SAML, or OAuth."
msgstr ""
"當身分驗證由 LDAP、SAML 或 OAuth 等外部身分提供方處理時的密碼重置 URL。"

#: admin/config.rst:1665
msgid ""
"When set, :guilabel:`Forgot your password?` on the sign-in page links to "
"this URL instead of Weblate's built-in password reset page."
msgstr ""
"設定後，登入頁上的 :guilabel:`忘記密碼了嗎？` 連結到此 URL 而不是 Weblate 內"
"建的密碼重置頁面。"

#: admin/config.rst:1675
msgid "URL where your Weblate instance shows its privacy policy."
msgstr "您的 Weblate 執行個體顯示其隱私政策的 URL。"

#: admin/config.rst:1679
msgid ""
"Useful if you host your privacy policy outside Weblate instead of using "
"the :ref:`legal` module. When the legal module is enabled, Weblate links to "
"the internal legal pages by default."
msgstr ""
"如果您將隱私權政策託管在 Weblate 之外，而非使用 :ref:`legal` 模組，這項設定就"
"很實用。啟用法律模組時，Weblate 預設會連結至內部法律頁面。"

#: admin/config.rst:1700
msgid ""
"Configures whether the private commit e-mail is opt-in or opt-out (by "
"default it is opt-in)."
msgstr "設定私密提交電子郵件是手動啟用還是預設啟用（預設情況下為手動啟用）。"

#: admin/config.rst:1704
msgid ""
"This setting only applies to users which have not explicitly chosen a commit "
"e-mail."
msgstr "此設定僅適用於未明確選擇提交電子郵件的使用者。"

#: admin/config.rst:1718
msgid ""
"Template to generate a private commit e-mail for a user. Defaults to "
"``\"{username}@users.noreply.{site_domain}\"``."
msgstr ""
"為使用者產生私密提交電子郵件的範本。預設為 ``\"{username}@users.noreply."
"{site_domain}\"`` 。"

#: admin/config.rst:1720 admin/config.rst:1757
msgid ""
"It can contain ``{user_id}``, ``{username}``, ``{site_title}``, and "
"``{site_domain}``."
msgstr ""
"其可以包含 ``{user_id}`` 、 ``{username}`` 、 ``{site_title}`` 與 "
"``{site_domain}``。"

#: admin/config.rst:1722 admin/config.rst:1759
msgid "Set to blank string to disable."
msgstr "設為空白字串以停用。"

#: admin/config.rst:1726
msgid ""
"Using a different commit e-mail is opt-in for users unless configured "
"by :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_OPT_IN`. Users can configure their commit "
"e-mail in the :ref:`profile`."
msgstr ""
"除非透過 :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_OPT_IN` 設定，否則使用不同的提交電子"
"郵件對使用者而言預設處於手動啟用狀態。使用者可以在 :ref:`profile` 中設定提交"
"電子郵件。"

#: admin/config.rst:1737
msgid ""
"Configures whether the private commit name is opt-in or opt-out (by default "
"it is opt-in)."
msgstr "設定私密提交名稱是手動啟用還是預設啟用（預設情況下為手動啟用）。"

#: admin/config.rst:1741
msgid ""
"This setting only applies to users which have not explicitly chosen a commit "
"name."
msgstr "此設定僅適用於未明確選擇提交名稱的使用者。"

#: admin/config.rst:1755
msgid ""
"Template to generate a private commit name for a user. Defaults to "
"``\"{site_title} user {user_id}\"``."
msgstr ""
"為使用者產生私密提交名稱的範本。預設為 ``\"{site_title} user {user_id}\"``."

#: admin/config.rst:1763
msgid ""
"Using a different commit name is opt-in for users unless configured "
"by :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_NAME_OPT_IN`. Users can configure their commit "
"name in the :ref:`profile`."
msgstr ""
"除非透過 :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_NAME_OPT_IN` 設定，否則使用不同的提交名稱對"
"使用者處於手動啟用狀態。使用者可以在 :ref:`profile` 中設定提交名稱。"

#: admin/config.rst:1774
msgid ""
"Defines how many backups per project are kept on the server. Defaults to 3."
msgstr "定義每個專案在伺服器上保留多少備份，預設值為 3。"

#: admin/config.rst:1787
msgid ""
"Defines how long the project backups will be kept on the server. Defaults to "
"30 days."
msgstr "定義每個專案的備份將存放多久在伺服器上。預設為 30 天。"

#: admin/config.rst:1800
msgid ""
"Configures the maximum size, in bytes, for uploaded project backup ZIP "
"files. Defaults to 536870912 bytes (512 MiB)."
msgstr ""
"設定上傳元件備份 ZIP 檔案的最大大小，單位為位元組。預設 536870912 位元組"
"（512 MiB）。"

#: admin/config.rst:1803
msgid ""
"In Docker, configure this using the "
"``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE`` environment variable. Docker "
"setups can also be constrained by :envvar:`CLIENT_MAX_BODY_SIZE`; other "
"deployments can be constrained by their reverse proxy request body-size "
"limit."
msgstr ""
"在 Docker 中，請使用 ``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE`` 環境變數進行"
"設定。Docker 設定也可能受 :envvar:`CLIENT_MAX_BODY_SIZE` 限制；其他部署則可能"
"受反向 Proxy 的要求本文大小限制。"

#: admin/config.rst:1819
msgid ""
"Defines the maximum number of ZIP entries allowed when importing a project "
"backup."
msgstr "定義匯入專案備份時允許的 ZIP 條目的最大數量。"

#: admin/config.rst:1822
msgid ""
"This is a safeguard against malformed or intentionally fragmented archives. "
"Defaults to 100000 entries."
msgstr ""
"這是針對格式錯誤或刻意碎片化歸檔檔案的一種防護措施。預設為 100000 個條目。"

#: admin/config.rst:1825
msgid ""
"In Docker, configure this using the "
"``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_MEMBERS`` environment variable."
msgstr ""
"在 Docker 中，使用 ``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_MEMBERS`` 環境變數設定"
"這個。"

#: admin/config.rst:1839
msgid ""
"Defines the maximum total uncompressed size, in bytes, for ZIP entries in an "
"imported project backup. Defaults to 536870912 bytes (512 MiB)."
msgstr ""
"定義匯入的專案備份中 ZIP 項的最大的總未壓縮大小。預設為 536870912 位元組"
"（512 MiB）。"

#: admin/config.rst:1842
msgid ""
"This limits archives that are small when uploaded but expand to much more "
"data during validation or restore."
msgstr "這會限制上傳時很小，但在驗證或還原期間會展開成大量資料的封存檔。"

#: admin/config.rst:1845
msgid ""
"In Docker, configure this using the "
"``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_TOTAL_UNCOMPRESSED_SIZE`` environment "
"variable."
msgstr ""
"在 Docker 中，使用 "
"``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_TOTAL_UNCOMPRESSED_SIZE`` 環境變數設定這"
"個。"

#: admin/config.rst:1860
msgid ""
"Defines the maximum uncompressed size, in bytes, for a single highly "
"compressed ZIP entry in an imported project backup."
msgstr ""
"定義匯入的專案備份中單一高度壓縮的 ZIP 條目的最大未壓縮大小（以位元組為單"
"位）。"

#: admin/config.rst:1863
msgid ""
"This limit is only applied to entries that are large enough and compress "
"enough to look suspicious. Large low-compression files are intentionally "
"allowed here and are expected to be constrained by the HTTP upload limit. "
"Defaults to 262144000 bytes (250 MiB)."
msgstr ""
"此限制僅適用於那些體積足夠大且壓縮程度足夠高、看起來可疑的條目。這裡特意允許"
"使用體積大但壓縮率低的檔案，並且預計會受到 HTTP 上傳限制的約束。預設為 "
"262144000 位元組（250 MiB）。"

#: admin/config.rst:1868
msgid ""
"In Docker, configure this using the "
"``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_SIZE`` environment "
"variable."
msgstr ""
"在 Docker 中，使用 "
"``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_SIZE`` 環境變數設定這"
"個。"

#: admin/config.rst:1883
msgid ""
"Defines the minimum uncompressed size, in bytes, at which Weblate starts "
"considering the ZIP compression ratio during project backup import."
msgstr ""
"定義 Weblate 在專案備份匯入期間開始考慮 ZIP 壓縮比的最小未壓縮大小（以位元組"
"為單位）。"

#: admin/config.rst:1886
msgid ""
"Smaller files are ignored for the compression-ratio-based validation to "
"avoid rejecting reasonably sized files that compress well. Defaults to "
"1048576 bytes (1 MiB)."
msgstr ""
"基於壓縮比的驗證會忽略較小的檔案，以避免拒絕那些壓縮效果良好且大小合理的檔"
"案。預設為 1048576 位元組（1 MiB）。"

#: admin/config.rst:1890
msgid ""
"In Docker, configure this using the "
"``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MIN_RATIO_SIZE`` environment variable."
msgstr ""
"在 Docker 中，使用 ``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MIN_RATIO_SIZE`` 環境變數"
"設定這個。"

#: admin/config.rst:1904
msgid ""
"Defines the maximum allowed ratio between the uncompressed and compressed "
"size for a large ZIP entry during project backup import."
msgstr ""
"定義專案備份匯入期間大型 ZIP 條目的未壓縮大小和壓縮大小之間允許的最大比例。"

#: admin/config.rst:1907
msgid ""
"This is used together "
"with :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_SIZE` "
"and :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MIN_RATIO_SIZE` to detect suspiciously "
"compressed entries while still allowing large repository pack files and "
"other low-compression content. Defaults to 250."
msgstr ""
"此設定與 :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_SIZE` "
"和 :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MIN_RATIO_SIZE` 配合使用來檢測可疑的壓縮條"
"目，同時仍然允許大型儲存庫打包檔案和其他低壓縮率內容。預設為 250。"

#: admin/config.rst:1913
msgid ""
"In Docker, configure this using the "
"``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_RATIO`` environment "
"variable."
msgstr ""
"在 Docker 中，使用 "
"``WEBLATE_PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_RATIO`` 環境變數設定這"
"個。"

#: admin/config.rst:1928
msgid ""
"Defines a regular expression to restrict project naming. Any matching names "
"will be rejected."
msgstr "定義用於限制專案命名的正規表示式。任何相符的名稱都將被拒絕。"

#: admin/config.rst:1941
msgid ""
"Reject using certain hosts in project website. Any subdomain is matched, so "
"including ``example.com`` will block ``test.example.com`` as well. The list "
"should contain lower case strings only, the parsed domain is lower cased "
"before matching."
msgstr ""
"在專案網站中拒絕使用特定的主機。相符任何子網域，因此包含 ``example.com`` 會同"
"樣攔截 ``test.example.com``. 此清單只應包含小寫字串，進行相符前，解析的網網域"
"稱會轉為小寫。"

#: admin/config.rst:1967
msgid ""
"Defines a set of project slugs exempt "
"from :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_HOST`, :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_NUMERIC`, :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, "
"and :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_RE` when validating the project website. "
"Project slugs are matched case-insensitively."
msgstr ""
"定義一組驗證專案網站時排除"
"在 :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_HOST`、:setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_NUMERIC`、:setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` "
"和 :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_RE` 之外的專案辨識符號。專案辨識符號相符不"
"區分大小寫。"

#: admin/config.rst:1975
msgid ""
"This exemption weakens outbound URL protections for matching projects, "
"including the private-target restriction enforced "
"by :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`. Use it only for trusted, "
"administrator-managed projects where bypassing these checks is intentional."
msgstr ""
"此排除削弱對相符專案的外聯 URL 保護，包"
"括 :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` 所強制的內網目標限制。請只把它用於"
"受信任的由管理員管理的專案，繞過這些檢查在此類專案中是有意為之的。"

#: admin/config.rst:2002
msgid "Reject using numeric IP address in project website. On by default."
msgstr "拒絕在專案網站中使用數字 IP 位址。預設啟用。"

#: admin/config.rst:2018
msgid ""
"Reject using project website and repository browser URLs pointing to "
"internal or non-public addresses. On by default."
msgstr "拒絕使用指向內部或非公開地址的專案網站和儲存庫瀏覽器 URL。預設開啟。"

#: admin/config.rst:2036
msgid ""
"Defines a regular expression to limit what can be entered as :ref:`project-"
"web`. Any matching URLs will be rejected."
msgstr ""
"定義正規表示式限制什麼可以被輸入為 :ref:`project-web`。任何相符的 URL 都將被"
"拒絕。"

#: admin/config.rst:2052
msgid ""
"Defines hostnames or domains exempt from :setting:`WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` "
"for outbound webhook delivery. Entries follow Django host matching "
"semantics, so values such as ``hooks.internal.example`` or "
"``.internal.example`` can be used."
msgstr ""
"定於免於對外 webhook 傳送限制 :setting:`WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` 設定的主機"
"名稱或網域。條目遵守 Django 主機相符語義，因此可以使用 "
"``hooks.internal.example`` 或 ``.internal.example`` 等值。"

#: admin/config.rst:2074
msgid ""
"Reject webhook URLs pointing to internal or non-public addresses unless the "
"target host is included in :setting:`WEBHOOK_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST`. On by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"拒絕指向內部或非公開地址的 webhook URL，除非目標主機包含"
"在 :setting:`WEBHOOK_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST` 中。預設開啟。"

#: admin/config.rst:2077
msgid ""
"When enabled, hostnames that cannot be resolved during validation are "
"rejected unless they are explicitly included "
"in :setting:`WEBHOOK_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST`."
msgstr ""
"啟用後將拒絕驗證期間無法解析的主機名稱，除非"
"在 :setting:`WEBHOOK_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST` 中明確允許它們。"

#: admin/config.rst:2092
msgid "Allows public engage page even with :setting:`REQUIRE_LOGIN`."
msgstr "即使設定了 :setting:`REQUIRE_LOGIN`，仍允許公眾參與頁面。"

#: admin/config.rst:2103
msgid ""
"Defines how many days generated translation reports are retained. Defaults "
"to 90 days. Changing the value also changes when existing reports become "
"eligible for removal by the daily cleanup task."
msgstr ""
"定義所產生的翻譯報告要保留多少天。預設為 90 天。變更此值也會改變現有報告何時"
"符合每日清理工作的移除條件。"

#: admin/config.rst:2114
msgid "Limits how many notifications for a single user will be sent out."
msgstr "限制向單一使用者傳送多少條通知。"

#: admin/config.rst:2116
msgid "The default setting is:"
msgstr "預設設定為："

#: admin/config.rst:2137
msgid ""
"Maximum number of authentication attempts before rate limiting is applied."
msgstr "在應用次數限制前，身分驗證嘗試的最多次數。"

#: admin/config.rst:2139
msgid "Defaults to 5."
msgstr "預設為 5。"

#: admin/config.rst:2152
msgid "How long authentication is accepted after rate limiting applies."
msgstr "套用速率限制後，身分驗證可維持有效的時間。"

#: admin/config.rst:2154
msgid "An amount of seconds, defaulting to 300 (5 minutes)."
msgstr "秒數預設為 300（5 分鐘）。"

#: admin/config.rst:2167
msgid "How long authentication is locked after rate limiting applies."
msgstr "在應用次數限制後，身分驗證鎖定多久。"

#: admin/config.rst:2169
msgid "An amount of seconds defaulting to 600 (10 minutes)."
msgstr "秒數預設為 600 （ 10 分鐘）。"

#: admin/config.rst:2184
msgid ""
"List of authentication backends to allow registration from. This only limits "
"new registrations, users can still authenticate and add authentication using "
"all configured authentication backends."
msgstr ""
"身分驗證後端的清單，允許從中註冊。這只限制新的註冊，使用者可以使用設定的身分"
"驗證後端，來進行身分驗證和新增身分驗證。"

#: admin/config.rst:2188
msgid ""
"It is recommended to keep :setting:`REGISTRATION_OPEN` on while limiting "
"registration backends, otherwise users will be able to register, but Weblate "
"will not show links to register in the user interface."
msgstr ""
"限制註冊後端的同時，建議保持 :setting:`REGISTRATION_OPEN` 為開啟狀態，否則使"
"用者將能夠註冊，但Weblate不會在使用者介面顯示註冊的連結。"

#: admin/config.rst:2200
msgid "The backend names match names used in the URL for authentication."
msgstr "與身分驗證 URL 中使用的名稱相符的後端名稱。"

#: admin/config.rst:2212
msgid ""
"Whether registration of new accounts is protected by a CAPTCHA. Defaults to "
"enabled."
msgstr "新帳號註冊是否受 CAPTCHA 的保護。此功能預設開啟。"

#: admin/config.rst:2214
msgid ""
"If turned on, a CAPTCHA is added to all pages where a user enters their e-"
"mail address:"
msgstr "啟用後，所有要求使用者輸入電子郵件地址的頁面都會加入 CAPTCHA："

#: admin/config.rst:2216
msgid "New account registration."
msgstr "新帳號註冊。"

#: admin/config.rst:2217
msgid "Password recovery."
msgstr "找回密碼。"

#: admin/config.rst:2218
msgid "Adding e-mail to an account."
msgstr "將電子郵件地址新增到帳號中。"

#: admin/config.rst:2219
msgid "Contact form for users that are not signed in."
msgstr "供未登入使用者使用的聯絡表單。"

#: admin/config.rst:2221
msgid "The protection currently consists of following steps:"
msgstr "保護目前由下列步驟組成："

#: admin/config.rst:2223
msgid "Mathematical captcha to be solved by the user."
msgstr "使用者要解決的數學人機驗證。"

#: admin/config.rst:2224
msgid ""
"Proof of work challenge calculated by the browser. The difficulty can be "
"adjusted using :setting:`ALTCHA_COST`, :setting:`ALTCHA_MEMORY_COST`, "
"and :setting:`ALTCHA_PARALLELISM`."
msgstr ""
"給瀏覽器計算的工作量證明挑戰。其難度可以使"
"用 :setting:`ALTCHA_COST` 、 :setting:`ALTCHA_MEMORY_COST` "
"與 :setting:`ALTCHA_PARALLELISM` 調整。"

#: admin/config.rst:2231
msgid "Allows you to filter which e-mail addresses can register."
msgstr "允許您篩選哪個電子郵件地址可以註冊。"

#: admin/config.rst:2233
msgid "Defaults to ``.*``, which allows any e-mail address to be registered."
msgstr "預設為 ``.*``，允許使用任何電子郵件地址註冊。"

#: admin/config.rst:2235
msgid "You can use it to restrict registration to a single e-mail domain:"
msgstr "可以用它限制註冊到單一的電子郵件網域："

#: admin/config.rst:2248
msgid ""
"Allow registration with disposable e-mail domains. When enabled, the "
"disposable domain blocklist is bypassed. Default is ``False``."
msgstr ""
"允許使用一次性電子郵件網域進行註冊。啟用後，會繞過一次性網域遮蔽清單。預設為 "
"``False``。"

#: admin/config.rst:2261
msgid ""
"Whether registration of new accounts is currently permitted. Defaults to "
"enabled."
msgstr "目前是否允許註冊新帳號。預設為允許。"

#: admin/config.rst:2264
msgid ""
"This setting affects built-in authentication by e-mail address or through "
"the Python Social Auth (you can allow certain back-ends "
