"可供使用的附加元件清單。為了使用，必須為給定的翻譯元件啟用它們。預設包括了所"
"有內建附加元件，當擴充套件清單時您可能希望保持現有的附加元件處於啟用狀態，例"
"如："

#: admin/config.rst:2856
msgid ""
"Removing the add-on from the list does not uninstall it from the components. "
"Weblate will crash in that case. Please uninstall the add-on from all "
"components prior to removing it from this list."
msgstr ""
"從清單中刪除附加元件並不能將其從元件中解除安裝。Weblate 在這種情況下會崩潰。"
"請先從所有元件中解除安裝附加元件，然後再將其從此清單中刪除。"

#: admin/config.rst:2874
msgid ""
"Configures how long activity logs for add-ons are kept. Defaults to 180 days."
msgstr "設定要保留附加元件活動記錄多長時間。預設為 180 天。"

#: admin/config.rst:2883
msgid ""
"List of available exporters offering translation downloads or glossaries in "
"various file formats."
msgstr "可用的匯出工具清單，其中的工具提供多種檔案格式的翻譯下載或術語庫。"

#: admin/config.rst:2895
msgid "List of file formats available for use."
msgstr "可供使用的檔案格式清單。"

#: admin/config.rst:2899
msgid "The default list already has the common formats."
msgstr "預設清單已經具有了常見格式。"

#: admin/config.rst:2913
msgid "List of machinery services available for use."
msgstr "可供使用的檔案格式清單。"

#: admin/config.rst:2926
msgid "Identity used by Weblate to sign Git commits, for example:"
msgstr "Weblate 對 Git 提交進行簽名的身分，例如："

#: admin/config.rst:2932
msgid ""
"The Weblate GPG keyring is searched for a matching key (:file:`home/.gnupg` "
"under :setting:`DATA_DIR`). If not found, a key is generated, please "
"check :ref:`gpg-sign` for more details."
msgstr ""
"在 Weblate GPG 金鑰環中搜尋相符的金鑰（:setting:`DATA_DIR` 下"
"的 :file:`home/.gnupg`）。如果找不到，則會產生一個金鑰，請查閱 :ref:`gpg-"
"sign` 瞭解詳情。"

#: admin/config.rst:2945
msgid ""
"Defines whether :ref:`project-web` has to be specified when creating a "
"project. On by default, as that suits public server setups."
msgstr ""
"定義了在建立專案時是否需要指定 :ref:`project-web`。預設開啟，因為這適合公共伺"
"服器的設定。"

#: admin/config.rst:2955
msgid "Default: ``True``"
msgstr "預設：``True``"

#: admin/config.rst:2957
msgid ""
"Defines whether Weblate should check project website availability and show "
"alerts for unreachable project websites."
msgstr "定義 Weblate 是否應檢查專案網站可用性並對無法存取的專案網站顯示警報。"

#: admin/config.rst:2960
msgid ""
"When set to ``False``, Weblate will skip website availability checks and "
"will not generate project website alerts. This is useful when:"
msgstr ""
"當設定為 ``False`` 時，Weblate 將跳過網站可用性檢查，並且不會產生專案網站警"
"報。這在以下情況下非常有用："

#: admin/config.rst:2963
msgid "Your websites are behind firewalls that block Weblate's requests"
msgstr "您的網站位於防火牆後面，會阻止 Weblate 的請求"

#: admin/config.rst:2964
msgid "You want to avoid 403/503-type errors from bot protection"
msgstr "您希望避免因機器人防護而導致的 403/503 型別的錯誤"

#: admin/config.rst:2965
msgid "Project website availability is not a concern for your installation"
msgstr "專案網站的可用性並非您安裝所關注的問題"

#: admin/config.rst:2974
msgid "Configuring version control credentials"
msgstr "設定版本控制憑證"

#: admin/config.rst:2978
msgid ""
"This section describes VCS credential variables "
"as :setting:`GITHUB_CREDENTIALS`, :setting:`GITLAB_CREDENTIALS`, :setting:`GITEA_CREDENTIALS`, :setting:`PAGURE_CREDENTIALS`, :setting:`BITBUCKETSERVER_CREDENTIALS`."
msgstr ""
"此部分將 VCS 憑證描述"
"為 :setting:`GITHUB_CREDENTIALS`、:setting:`GITLAB_CREDENTIALS`、:setting:`GITEA_CREDENTIALS`、:setting:`PAGURE_CREDENTIALS`、:setting:`BITBUCKETSERVER_CREDENTIALS`。"

#: admin/config.rst:2987
msgid ""
"The credentials can also be overridden in :ref:`component-push` "
"or :ref:`component-repo` (if push URL is not configured), these take "
"precedence over the ones specified in the configuration file."
msgstr ""
"憑證也可以在 :ref:`component-push` 或 :ref:`component-repo` 中被覆蓋（如果沒"
"有設定 URL），這些憑證的優先順序高於設定檔案中所指定的憑證。"

#: admin/config.rst:2994
msgid "API user, required."
msgstr "API 使用者，必填。"

#: admin/config.rst:3000
msgid ""
"Scheme override. Weblate attempts to parse scheme from the repository URL "
"and falls backs to ``https``. If you are running the API server internally, "
"you might want to use ``http`` instead, but consider security."
msgstr ""
"方案覆蓋。Weblate 嘗試從儲存庫 URL 解析方案並退回到 ``https``。如果您正在內部"
"執行 API 伺服器，您也許想轉而使用 ``http``，但考慮安全性。"

#: admin/config.rst:3006
msgid ""
"In the Docker container, the credentials can be configured using environment "
"variables, see :ref:`docker-vcs-config`."
msgstr ""
"在 Docker 容器中，可使用環境變數設定憑證，見 :ref:`docker-vcs-config`。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:4
msgid "Continuous localization"
msgstr "持續在地化"

#: admin/continuous.rst:6
msgid ""
"There is infrastructure in place so that your translation closely follows "
"development. This way translators can work on translations the entire time, "
"instead of working through huge amount of new text just prior to release."
msgstr ""
"有適當的基礎結構，因此您的翻譯緊隨開發。這樣，翻譯人員可以一直進行翻譯，而不"
"必在釋出之前處理大量的新文字。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:12
msgid ""
":doc:`/devel/integration` describes basic ways to integrate your development "
"with Weblate. :doc:`/admin/code-hosting` lists provider-specific setup steps "
"for common code-hosting sites."
msgstr ""
":doc:`/devel/integration` 說明將開發流程與 Weblate 整合的基本方式。:doc:`/"
"admin/code-hosting` 列出常見程式碼託管網站各服務提供者的設定步驟。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:17
msgid "This is the process:"
msgstr "這是過程："

#: admin/continuous.rst:19
msgid "Developers make changes and push them to the VCS repository."
msgstr "開發人員進行變更並將其推送到版本控制系統儲存庫。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:20
msgid ""
"Optionally the translation files are updated, see :ref:`translations-update`."
msgstr "可以選擇更新翻譯檔案，請參閱 :ref:`translations-update`。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:21
msgid ""
"Weblate pulls changes from the VCS repository, parses translation files and "
"updates its database, see :ref:`update-vcs`."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 從版本控制系統儲存庫中拉取變更，解析翻譯檔案並更新其資料庫，"
"見 :ref:`update-vcs`。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:22
msgid ""
"Translators submit translations using the Weblate web interface, or upload "
"offline changes."
msgstr "翻譯者使用 Weblate Web 介面提交翻譯，或上傳離線變更。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:23
msgid ""
"Once the translators are finished, Weblate commits the changes to the local "
"repository (see :ref:`lazy-commit`)."
msgstr ""
"譯者完成後，Weblate 會將變更提交到本機儲存庫（請參閱 :ref:`lazy-commit`）。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:24
msgid ""
"Changes are pushed back to the upstream repository (see :ref:`code-hosting-"
"push-options`)."
msgstr "變更被推送回上游儲存庫（見 :ref:`code-hosting-push-options`）。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:76
msgid ""
"Upstream code-hosting site is not necessary, you can use Weblate "
"with :ref:`vcs-local` where there is only the repository inside Weblate."
msgstr ""
"上游程式碼託管網站並非必要。您可以搭配 :ref:`vcs-local` 使用 Weblate，這種方"
"式只會使用 Weblate 內的儲存庫。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:82
msgid "Updating repositories"
msgstr "更新儲存庫"

#: admin/continuous.rst:84
msgid ""
"You should set up some way of updating backend repositories from their "
"source."
msgstr "您應該設定某種方法來從來源更新後端儲存庫。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:87
msgid ""
"Use :ref:`hooks` to integrate with the majority of common code-hosting "
"services, see :doc:`/admin/code-hosting`. You must also :ref:`project-"
"enable_hooks` for this to work."
msgstr ""
"使用 :ref:`hooks` 與大多數常見的程式碼託管服務整合，請參閱 :doc:`/admin/code-"
"hosting`。您還必須啟用 :ref:`project-enable_hooks`，這項功能才能運作。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:91
msgid ""
"Manually trigger update either in the repository management or "
"using :ref:`api` or :ref:`wlc`"
msgstr "在儲存庫管理中或使用 :ref:`api` 或 :ref:`wlc` 來手動觸發更新"

#: admin/continuous.rst:93
msgid ""
"Enable :setting:`AUTO_UPDATE` to automatically update all components on your "
"Weblate instance"
msgstr ""
"啟用 :setting:`AUTO_UPDATE` 以自動更新您的 Weblate 執行個體上的所有元件"

#: admin/continuous.rst:95
msgid ""
"Execute :wladmin:`updategit` (with selection of project or ``--all`` to "
"update all)"
msgstr "執行 :wladmin:`updategit`\\ （選擇專案，或 ``--all`` 來更新全部）"

#: admin/continuous.rst:97
msgid ""
"Whenever Weblate updates the repository, the post-update addons will be "
"triggered, see :ref:`addons`."
msgstr ""
"每當 Weblate 更新儲存庫時，更新後附加元件都將被觸發，請參閱 :ref:`addons`。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:103
msgid "Avoiding merge conflicts"
msgstr "避免發生合併衝突"

#: admin/continuous.rst:105
msgid ""
"The merge conflicts from Weblate arise when same file was changed both in "
"Weblate and outside it. Depending on the situation, there are several "
"approaches that might help here:"
msgstr ""
"當同一檔案在 Weblate 內外都被變更時，就會出現來自 Weblate 的合併衝突。根據情"
"況不同，有幾種方法可能會有幫助："

#: admin/continuous.rst:115
msgid "Avoiding merge conflicts by changing translation files in Weblate only"
msgstr "只變更 Weblate 中的翻譯檔案來避免合併衝突"

#: admin/continuous.rst:117
msgid ""
"Avoiding edits outside Weblate is easy with monolingual files — you can add "
"new strings within Weblate and leave whole editing of the files there. For "
"bilingual files, there is usually some kind of message extraction process to "
"generate translatable files from the source code. In some cases, this can be "
"split into two parts:"
msgstr ""
"對於單語檔案來說，避免 Weblate 之外的編輯是容易的——您可以在 Weblate 中新增新"
"字串，並將檔案的整個編輯留在那裡。對於雙語檔案，通常存在某種資訊提取過程可以"
"從原始碼產生可翻譯檔案。在一些情況下，這可以分成兩部分："

#: admin/continuous.rst:123
msgid ""
"The extraction generates template (for example gettext POT is generated "
"using :program:`xgettext`)."
msgstr "該提取產生範本（例如，gettext POT 是用 :program:`xgettext` 產生的）。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:124
msgid ""
"Further process merges it into actual translations (the gettext PO files are "
"updated using :program:`msgmerge`)."
msgstr ""
"進一步的過程將它合併入實際翻譯（gettext PO 檔案用 :program:`msgmerge` 更"
"新）。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:126
msgid ""
"You can perform the second step within Weblate and it will ensure that all "
"pending changes are included before this operation."
msgstr ""
"您可以在 Weblate 內執行第二步，它會確保所有未提交變更在此操作前被包含在內。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:132
msgid "Avoiding merge conflicts by locking Weblate while doing outside changes"
msgstr "做外部變更時鎖定 Weblate 來避免合併衝突"

#: admin/continuous.rst:134
msgid ""
"Integrating Weblate into your updating process so that it flushes changes "
"before updating the files outside Weblate can be achieved by "
"using :ref:`api` to force Weblate to push all pending changes and lock the "
"translation while you are doing changes on your side."
msgstr ""
"您可以將 Weblate 整合到更新流程：先透過 :ref:`api` 強制 Weblate 推送所有待處"
"理變更並鎖定翻譯，再於 Weblate 外部更新檔案。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:138
msgid "The script for doing updates can look like this:"
msgstr "進行更新的指令碼看起來像這樣："

#: admin/continuous.rst:159
msgid ""
"If you have multiple components sharing the same repository, you need to "
"lock them all separately:"
msgstr "如果多個元件分享相同的儲存庫，需要分別將他們全部鎖定："

#: admin/continuous.rst:170
msgid ""
"The example uses :ref:`wlc`, which needs configuration (API keys) to be able "
"to control Weblate remotely. You can also achieve this using any HTTP client "
"instead of :ref:`wlc`, for example curl, see :ref:`api`."
msgstr ""
"範例使用了 :ref:`wlc`，這需要設定（API 金鑰）來遠端控制 Weblate。可以透過使"
"用 HTTP 客戶端代替 :ref:`wlc` 來達成這一點，例如 curl，請參閱 :ref:`api`。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:177
msgid "Repository maintenance"
msgstr "儲存庫維護"

#: admin/continuous.rst:179
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Repository maintenance` view shows repository status for a "
"project, component, or translation and lets privileged users run maintenance "
"operations from the user interface."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`儲存庫維護` 檢視顯示專案、元件或翻譯的儲存庫狀態，並讓特權使用者從"
"使用者介面執行維護操作。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:183
msgid ""
"The same actions can also be triggered using :ref:`api` or, for the "
"supported subset, :ref:`wlc`."
msgstr ""
"也可用 :ref:`api` 觸發相同操作，或為受支援的子集觸發相同操作，:ref:`wlc`。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:186
msgid ""
"Availability of individual actions depends on permissions, the configured "
"version control system, whether pushing is configured, and whether the "
"selected object can be locked."
msgstr ""
"單獨操作的可用性取決於權限，設定的 VCS，是否設定了推送，是否所選物件可被鎖"
"定。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:190
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`File management` actions are available only "
"from :guilabel:`Repository maintenance` for an individual translation. These "
"actions rewrite that translation file and commit the result; they are not "
"project-wide or component-wide operations."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`檔案管理` 動作只能從個別翻譯的 :guilabel:`儲存庫維護` 使用。這些動"
"作會重寫該翻譯檔案並提交結果；它們不是全專案或全元件的操作。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:195
msgid ""
"Operations that read repository content, such as updating, resetting, or "
"rescanning, also reconcile translation files in Weblate. Added or removed "
"translation files are reflected after this processing finishes. Glossary "
"language synchronization and cleanup are described in :ref:`glossary-"
"language-sync`."
msgstr ""
"讀取儲存庫內容的操作（例如更新、重設或重新掃描）也會讓 Weblate 中的翻譯檔案保"
"持一致。處理完成後，新增或移除的翻譯檔案都會反映出來。詞彙表語言同步與清除的"
"說明請參閱 :ref:`glossary-language-sync`。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:204
msgid "Action"
msgstr "動作"

#: admin/continuous.rst:205
msgid "What it does"
msgstr "它做什麼"

#: admin/continuous.rst:206
msgid "Typical use"
msgstr "典型使用"

#: admin/continuous.rst:208
msgid ":guilabel:`Commit`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`提交`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:209
msgid "Commits pending changes stored in Weblate to the local repository."
msgstr "將儲存在 Weblate 中的未提交變更提交到本機儲存庫。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:210
msgid "Flush pending Weblate changes before doing repository work elsewhere."
msgstr "在其他地方進行儲存庫操作前，先提交 Weblate 的待處理變更。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:212
msgid ":guilabel:`Push`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`推送`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:213
msgid "Pushes committed local repository changes to the configured upstream."
msgstr "將提交的本機儲存庫變更推送到設定的上游。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:214
msgid ""
"Send committed translations upstream when automatic push is disabled or "
"delayed."
msgstr "當自動推送停用或延遲時向上遊傳送提交的譯文。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:216
msgid ":guilabel:`Update`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`更新`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:217
msgid ""
"Fetches upstream changes, integrates them using the component's "
"configured :ref:`component-merge_style`, and reconciles translation files."
msgstr ""
"取得上游變更，用元件已設定的 :ref:`component-merge_style` 整合它們並核對翻譯"
"檔案。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:218
msgid ""
"Bring Weblate in sync with upstream using the default integration strategy."
msgstr "用預設整合策略讓 Weblate 和上游同步。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:220
msgid ":guilabel:`Update with merge`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`以合併方式更新`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:221
msgid "Fetches upstream changes and integrates them with an explicit merge."
msgstr "擷取上游變更，並透過明確的合併操作進行整合。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:222
msgid "Override the default merge style for a single update."
msgstr "覆蓋單一更新的預設合併樣式。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:224
msgid ":guilabel:`Update with rebase`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`以變基方式更新`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:225
msgid ""
"Fetches upstream changes and rebases local Weblate commits on top of "
"upstream."
msgstr "取得上游變更並在上游基礎上變基本機 Weblate 提交。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:226
msgid "Keep history linear when that matches your workflow."
msgstr "當歷史記錄相符工作流時保持歷史記錄線性。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:228
msgid ":guilabel:`Update with merge without fast-forward`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`用不含快進的合併進行更新`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:229
msgid ""
"Fetches upstream changes and creates an explicit merge commit even when a "
"fast-forward would be possible."
msgstr "擷取上游變更，且即使可以快進，仍明確建立合併提交。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:230
msgid "Preserve merge commits for auditing or branch-management reasons."
msgstr "出於審計或分支管理理由保留合併提交。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:232
msgid ":guilabel:`Lock` / :guilabel:`Unlock`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`鎖定` / :guilabel:`解鎖`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:233
msgid "Prevents or allows translators to make further changes in Weblate."
msgstr "阻止或允許譯者在 Weblate 中進行進一步變更。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:234
msgid ""
"Freeze translation changes while doing repository maintenance outside "
"Weblate."
msgstr "在 Weblate 以外維護儲存庫時凍結翻譯變更。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:236
msgid ":guilabel:`Reset and discard`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`重設並丟棄`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:237
msgid ""
"Resets Weblate's local repository to upstream, discards pending Weblate "
"changes, and reconciles translation files."
msgstr ""
"重置 Weblate 的本機儲存庫到上游，丟棄未提交的 Weblate 變更並核對翻譯檔案。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:238
msgid "Use when upstream should overwrite the local Weblate repository state."
msgstr "當上遊應覆蓋本機 Weblate 儲存庫狀態時使用。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:240
msgid ":guilabel:`Reset and reapply`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`重設並重新套用`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:241
msgid ""
"Resets Weblate's local repository to upstream, reconciles translation files, "
"and reapplies pending translations. See :ref:`manage-vcs-reset-reapply`."
msgstr ""
"重置 Weblate 的本機儲存庫到上游，核對翻譯檔案並重新應用未提交的變更。"
"見 :ref:`manage-vcs-reset-reapply`。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:242
msgid ""
"Recover from diverged history while keeping pending Weblate translations."
msgstr "從有差異的歷史記錄復原，同時保留未提交的 Weblate 翻譯。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:244
msgid ":guilabel:`Cleanup`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`清理`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:245
msgid ""
"Removes untracked files and stale branches from the local repository "
"checkout."
msgstr "從本機儲存庫簽出中移除未跟蹤的檔案和過時分支。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:246
msgid ""
"Clean up leftover files or stale repository state in Weblate's checkout."
msgstr "清理 Weblate 簽出中殘留檔案或過時儲存庫狀態。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:248
msgid ":guilabel:`Synchronize`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`同步`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:249
msgid ""
"Forces Weblate to write all known translations back to the repository files."
msgstr "強制 Weblate 將所有已知的譯文寫回儲存庫檔案。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:250
msgid ""
"Repair cases where repository files became out of sync with the database "
"state."
msgstr "修復儲存庫檔案與資料庫狀態不同步的情況。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:252
msgid ":guilabel:`Rescan`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`重新掃描`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:253
msgid ""
"Re-reads translation files from the local repository into Weblate and "
"removes translations whose files no longer match the component configuration."
msgstr ""
"將來自本機儲存庫的翻譯檔案重新讀取到 Weblate 中並刪除檔案不再相符元件設定的翻"
"譯。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:254
msgid "Import file changes after manual repository work or file creation."
msgstr "在手動進行儲存庫操作或建立檔案後匯入檔案變更。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:256
msgid ":guilabel:`Remove duplicates`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`刪除重複項`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:257
msgid ""
"Removes repeated strings with the same identifier from one translation file."
msgstr "從單一翻譯檔案中刪除辨識符號相同的重複字串。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:258
msgid ""
"Repair duplicate strings reported by Weblate when the file contains repeated "
"units."
msgstr "修復 Weblate 回報的重複字串，也就是檔案中包含重複翻譯單元的情況。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:260
msgid ":guilabel:`Cleanup unused`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`清除未使用項目`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:261
msgid ""
"Removes strings no longer present in the base file from one translation "
"file. The :ref:`addon-weblate.cleanup.generic` add-on can perform this "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"從單一翻譯檔案移除基礎檔案中已不存在的字串。:ref:`addon-"
"weblate.cleanup.generic` 附加元件可以自動執行此操作。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:262
msgid "Run a one-time cleanup without installing the add-on."
msgstr "在不安裝附加元件的情況下執行一次性清除。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:264
msgid ":guilabel:`Remove obsolete`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`移除陳舊項`"

#: admin/continuous.rst:265
msgid "Removes obsolete strings from one PO translation file."
msgstr "從單一 PO 翻譯檔案中刪除陳舊字串。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:266
msgid ""
"Run a one-time PO cleanup without enabling automatic obsolete string removal."
msgstr "在不啟用自動移除過時字串的情況下，執行一次性 PO 清除。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:271
msgid "Reset and reapply recovery behavior"
msgstr "重置並重新應用復原行為"

#: admin/continuous.rst:273
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Reset and reapply` operation keeps pending translations from "
"Weblate while resetting the local repository state to match upstream."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`重置和重新應用` 操作保留來自 Weblate 的待提交變更，同時重置本機儲"
"存庫狀態來相符上游。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:276
msgid ""
"The operation can restore pending translations only when the target language "
"files still exist after the reset or when Weblate can create them for the "
"component, for example using a valid :ref:`component-new_base`."
msgstr ""
"該操作只有在重置後目標語言檔案仍存在或者 Weblate 能用有效的 :ref:`component-"
"new_base` 為該元件建立這些檔案時可以還原未提交的翻譯。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:280
msgid ""
"If neither of these conditions is met, Weblate keeps the pending changes in "
"its database and reports a recovery error instead of failing later with a "
"generic parse error."
msgstr ""
"如果這些條件均不滿足，Weblate 會在其資料庫中保留未提交的變更並報告復原錯誤，"
"而不是稍後因一般性的解析錯誤而出現故障。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:287
msgid "Avoiding merge conflicts by focusing on Git operations"
msgstr "聚焦 Git 操作避免合併衝突"

#: admin/continuous.rst:289
msgid ""
"Even when Weblate is the single source of the changes in the translation "
"files, conflicts can appear when using :ref:`addon-weblate.git.squash` add-"
"on, :ref:`component-merge_style` is configured to :guilabel:`Rebase`, or you "
"are squashing commits outside of Weblate (for example, when merging a pull "
"request)."
msgstr ""
"即使 Weblate 是翻譯檔案變更的唯一來源，使用 :ref:`addon-weblate.git.squash` "
"附加元件、將 :ref:`component-merge_style` 設為 :guilabel:`Rebase`，或在 "
"Weblate 外部壓縮提交（例如合併拉取請求時），仍可能發生衝突。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:294
msgid ""
"The reason for merge conflicts is different in this case. Weblate can have "
"new local commits after you merge earlier Weblate commits upstream. This "
"typically happens if merging is not automated and changes wait for days or "
"weeks for a human review. Git is then sometimes no longer able to identify "
"upstream changes as matching the Weblate ones and refuses to perform a "
"rebase."
msgstr ""
"此情形下，合併衝突的原因不同。例如，您在上游合併之前的 Weblate 提交後，"
"Weblate 可能有新的本機提交。出現這種情況通常是因為合併操作不是自動進行的，變"
"更要等待幾天或數週進行人工稽核。Git 有時會無法辨識上游的變更是否與 Weblate 相"
"符，並拒絕執行變基操作。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:300
msgid ""
"Squash merging Weblate changes makes this harder to recover from. A squash "
"merge creates a new commit instead of preserving the individual Weblate "
"commits in the upstream history. Weblate still has the original commits in "
"its local repository, and Git can no longer prove that upstream already "
"contains them. If the conflict was also resolved manually, the file contents "
"can differ from both repositories, so Weblate can keep failing to update "
"even after the pull request was merged upstream."
msgstr ""
"以 squash 方式合併 Weblate 變更，會使這類問題更難復原。Squash 合併會建立新的"
"提交，而非在上游歷程中保留個別 Weblate 提交。Weblate 的本機儲存庫仍有原始提"
"交，但 Git 無法再證明上游已包含這些提交。如果衝突也是手動解決，檔案內容可能與"
"兩個儲存庫都不同，因此即使拉取請求已在上游合併，Weblate 仍可能持續無法更新。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:308
msgid ""
"If upstream no longer contains Weblate commits because they were squash "
"merged, updating the repository might not be enough. Use :guilabel:`Reset "
"and reapply` from :guilabel:`Repository maintenance` to reset Weblate to "
"upstream while keeping pending translations; see :ref:`manage-vcs-reset-"
"reapply`. Use :guilabel:`Reset and discard` only when upstream should fully "
"replace Weblate's local changes."
msgstr ""
"如果上游因 squash 合併而不再包含 Weblate 提交，僅更新儲存庫可能還不夠。請"
"從 :guilabel:`儲存庫維護` 使用 :guilabel:`重設並重新套用`，在保留待處理翻譯的"
"同時將 Weblate 重設至上游；請參閱 :ref:`manage-vcs-reset-reapply`。只有在上游"
"應完全取代 Weblate 本機變更時，才使用 :guilabel:`重設並捨棄`。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:315
msgid ""
"To approach this, you either need to minimize the amount of pending changes "
"in Weblate when you merge a pull request, or avoid the conflicts completely "
"by not squashing changes."
msgstr ""
"要解決此問題，您需要在合併拉取請求時儘量減少 Weblate 中的待處理變更，或者透過"
"不擠壓變更來完全避免衝突。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:319
msgid "Here are few options how to avoid that:"
msgstr "這裡有幾個避免這一問題的選項："

#: admin/continuous.rst:321
msgid ""
"Do not use :ref:`addon-weblate.git.squash` or squash merging for Weblate "
"changes. Squashing is why Git might no longer recognize the changes after "
"merging."
msgstr ""
"別對 Weblate 變更使用 :ref:`addon-weblate.git.squash` 或擠壓合併。擠壓操作是 "
"Git 為何在合併後不再辨識變更的原因。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:324
msgid ""
"When resolving conflicts outside Weblate, merge the Weblate commits with a "
"regular merge commit and push that result upstream. Do not squash merge the "
"conflict-resolution pull request."
msgstr ""
"在 Weblate 外部解決衝突時，請使用一般合併提交來合併 Weblate 提交，並將結果推"
"送至上游。請勿以 squash 方式合併用於解決衝突的拉取請求。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:327
msgid ""
"Let Weblate commit pending changes before merging. This will update the pull "
"request with all its changes, and both repositories will be in sync."
msgstr ""
"在合併前讓 Weblate 提交未提交變更。這會更新拉取請求的所有變更，且兩個儲存庫會"
"處於同步狀態。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:328
msgid ""
"Use the review features in Weblate (see :doc:`/workflows`) so that you can "
"automatically merge GitHub pull requests after CI passes."
msgstr ""
"使用 Weblate 中的審閱功能（見 :doc:`/workflows`），這樣您可以在 CI 透過後自動"
"合併 GitHub 拉取請求。"

#: admin/continuous.rst:329
msgid ""
"Use locking in Weblate to avoid changes while GitHub pull request is in "
"review."
msgstr "在 Weblate 中使用鎖定避免在稽核 GitHub 拉取請求時的變更。"

