msgstr "其他設定"

#: admin/install.rst:522
msgid "Configuring outgoing e-mail"
msgstr "設定外寄電子郵件"

#: admin/install.rst:524
msgid ""
"Weblate sends out e-mails on various occasions - for account activation and "
"on various notifications configured by users. For this it needs access to an "
"SMTP server."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 在各種情況下會發出電子郵件——用於啟動帳號，以及使用者設定的各種通知。"
"對於這些需要存取 SMTP 伺服器。"

#: admin/install.rst:528
msgid ""
"The mail server setup is configured using these "
"settings: :setting:`django:EMAIL_HOST`, :setting:`django:EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD`, :setting:`django:EMAIL_USE_TLS`, :setting:`django:EMAIL_USE_SSL`, :setting:`django:EMAIL_HOST_USER` "
"and :setting:`django:EMAIL_PORT`. Their names are quite self-explanatory, "
"but you can find more info in the Django documentation."
msgstr ""
"電子郵件伺服器使用這些設定進行設"
"定: :setting:`django:EMAIL_HOST`, :setting:`django:EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD`, :setting:`django:EMAIL_USE_TLS`, :setting:`django:EMAIL_USE_SSL`, :setting:`django:EMAIL_HOST_USER` "
"and :setting:`django:EMAIL_PORT`。從名稱就可以大概知道它們的含義，但是您可以"
"在Django說明文件中找到更多資訊。"

#: admin/install.rst:537
msgid ""
"In case you get error about not supported authentication (for "
"example :samp:`SMTP AUTH extension not supported by server`), it is most "
"likely caused by using insecure connection and server refuses to "
"authenticate this way. Try enabling :setting:`django:EMAIL_USE_TLS` in such "
"case."
msgstr ""
"如果您收到不受支援的身分驗證的錯誤（例如，:samp:`SMTP AUTH extension not "
"supported by server`），這最可能因為使用不安全的連結並且伺服器拒絕以這種方式"
"認證而導致。在這種情況下嘗試啟動 :setting:`django:EMAIL_USE_TLS`。"

#: admin/install.rst:545
msgid ":ref:`Configuring outgoing e-mail in Docker container <docker-mail>`"
msgstr ":ref:`在 Docker 容器中設定電子郵件傳送 <docker-mail>`"

#: admin/install.rst:550
msgid "Running behind reverse proxy"
msgstr "在反向代理後面執行"

#: admin/install.rst:552
msgid ""
"Several features in Weblate rely on correct HTTP headers being passed to "
"Weblate. When using reverse proxy, please make sure that the needed "
"information is correctly passed."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 中的幾個功能依賴於傳遞給 Weblate 的正確 HTTP 標頭。使用反向代理時，請"
"確保所需資訊被正確傳遞。"

#: admin/install.rst:556
msgid ""
"To debug this configuration, you can look at :guilabel:`HTTP environment` "
"in :ref:`manage-performance`."
msgstr ""
"要除錯該設定，可以看一看 :ref:`manage-performance` 中的 :guilabel:`HTTP "
"environment`。"

#: admin/install.rst:559
msgid "Client IP address"
msgstr "用戶端 IP 位址"

#: admin/install.rst:560
msgid "This is needed for :ref:`rate-limit` or :ref:`audit-log`."
msgstr ":ref:`rate-limit` 或 :ref:`audit-log` 需要。"

#: admin/install.rst:562
msgid ""
"Weblate parses IP address from the ``REMOTE_ADDR``, which is set by the WSGI "
"handler. This might be empty (when using socket for WSGI) or contain a "
"reverse proxy address, so Weblate needs an additional HTTP header with a "
"client IP address."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 從 WGSI 處理程式設定的 ``REMOTE_ADDR`` 解析 IP 地址。這可能是空的（當"
"對 WGSI 使用 socket 時）或者包括反向代理地址，因此 Weblate 需要帶客戶端 IP 地"
"址的附加 HTTP 標頭。"

#: admin/install.rst:567
msgid ""
"Enabling :setting:`IP_BEHIND_REVERSE_PROXY` should be sufficient for the "
"most usual setups, but you might need to adjust :setting:`IP_PROXY_HEADER` "
"and :setting:`IP_PROXY_OFFSET` as well "
"(use :envvar:`WEBLATE_IP_PROXY_HEADER` and :envvar:`WEBLATE_IP_PROXY_OFFSET` "
"in the Docker container)."
msgstr ""
"啟用 :setting:`IP_BEHIND_REVERSE_PROXY` 對多數通常設定應該夠了，但您可能也需"
"要調整 :setting:`IP_PROXY_HEADER` 和 :setting:`IP_PROXY_OFFSET`\\ （使用 "
"Docker 容器內的 :envvar:`WEBLATE_IP_PROXY_HEADER` "
"和 :envvar:`WEBLATE_IP_PROXY_OFFSET`）。"

#: admin/install.rst:574
msgid ""
"This configuration cannot be turned on by default, because it would allow IP "
"address spoofing on installations that don't have a properly configured "
"reverse proxy."
msgstr ""
"此設定預設無法啟用，因其會在沒有正確設定反向代理的安裝上允許 IP 地址偽造。"

#: admin/install.rst:578
msgid "Server host name"
msgstr "伺服器主機名稱"

#: admin/install.rst:579
msgid ""
"The :http:header:`Host` header should match to whatever is configured "
"as :setting:`SITE_DOMAIN`. Additional configuration might be needed in your "
"reverse proxy (for example use ``ProxyPreserveHost On`` for Apache or "
"``proxy_set_header Host $host;`` with nginx)."
msgstr ""
":http:header:`Host` 標頭應該與 :setting:`SITE_DOMAIN` 中的內容一致。在反向代"
"理中可能需要其他設定（例如，在 Apache 使用 ``ProxyPreserveHost On``，或在 "
"nginx 中使用 ``proxy_set_header Host $host;``）。"

#: admin/install.rst:586
msgid ""
"CSRF verification failed errors are often caused by a mismatch between "
"the :http:header:`Host` header and configured :setting:`SITE_DOMAIN`."
msgstr ""
"CSRF 驗證失敗錯誤常由 :http:header:`Host` 標頭和設定"
"的 :setting:`SITE_DOMAIN` 不相符所導致。"

#: admin/install.rst:589
msgid "Client protocol"
msgstr "用戶端協定"

#: admin/install.rst:590
msgid ""
"Not passing correct protocol may cause Weblate to end up in redirection loop "
"trying to upgrade client to HTTPS. Make sure it is correctly exposed by the "
"reverse proxy as :http:header:`X-Forwarded-Proto`."
msgstr ""
"未傳遞正確的協議可能導致 Weblate 最後陷入試圖升級客戶端到 HTTPS 的重定向迴圈"
"中。確保反向代理正確地將它暴露為 :http:header:`X-Forwarded-Proto`。"

#: admin/install.rst:594
msgid ""
"This header then needs to be configured "
"in :setting:`django:SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER` (:file:`settings.py`) "
"or :envvar:`WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER` (Docker environment)."
msgstr ""
"然後需要在 :setting:`django:SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER` (:file:`settings.py`) "
"或 :envvar:`WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER` (Docker 環境) 中設定這個標頭。"

#: admin/install.rst:600
msgid ""
"The header value is case-sensitive in the configuration, so "
"``WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER=HTTP_X_FORWARDED_PROTO,https`` and "
"``WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER=HTTP_X_FORWARDED_PROTO,HTTPS`` are not "
"interchangeable."
msgstr ""
"標頭值在設定中區分大小寫，因此 "
"``WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER=HTTP_X_FORWARDED_PROTO,https`` 和 "
"``WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER=HTTP_X_FORWARDED_PROTO,HTTPS`` 不可互換。"

#: admin/install.rst:607
msgid ""
"If you are getting a \"Too many redirects\" error from the browser, this is "
"most likely caused by mismatch between the actual protocol (HTTPS) and what "
"is observed by Weblate."
msgstr ""
"如果瀏覽器顯示“太多重定向”錯誤，最有可能的原因是實際協議(HTTPS) 和 Weblate 觀"
"察到的協議不相符。"

#: admin/install.rst:613
