"Create a :file:`docker-compose.override.yml` file with your settings. "
"See :ref:`docker-environment` for full list of environment variables."
msgstr ""
"建立一個 :file:`docker-compose.override.yml` 檔案並調整為您所需的設定。參"
"閱 :ref:`docker-environment` 瞭解更多相關設定參數。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:48
msgid ""
"If :envvar:`WEBLATE_ADMIN_PASSWORD` is not set, the admin user is created "
"with a random password shown on first startup."
msgstr ""
"如果未設定 :envvar:`WEBLATE_ADMIN_PASSWORD`，則使用首次啟動時顯示的隨機密碼建"
"立管理員使用者。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:51
