"The provided example makes Weblate listen on port 80, edit the port mapping "
"in the :file:`docker-compose.override.yml` file to change it."
msgstr ""
"提供的範例使 Weblate 偵聽連接埠 80，在 :file:`docker-compose.override.yml` 檔"
