#: admin/install/docker.rst:2347
msgid "Container settings"
msgstr "容器設定"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2353
msgid ""
"Base number of worker processes running in the container. When not set it is "
"determined automatically on container startup based on number of CPU cores "
"available."
msgstr ""
"在容器中執行的工人行程基數。未設定時，基於可用的CPU核心數，在容器啟動時自動確"
"定。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2357
msgid ""
"It is used to "
"determine :envvar:`CELERY_MAIN_OPTIONS`, :envvar:`CELERY_NOTIFY_OPTIONS`, :envvar:`CELERY_MEMORY_OPTIONS`, :envvar:`CELERY_TRANSLATE_OPTIONS`, :envvar:`CELERY_BACKUP_OPTIONS`, :envvar:`CELERY_BEAT_OPTIONS`, :envvar:`WEB_WORKERS`, "
"and :envvar:`WEB_BLOCKING_THREADS`. You can use these settings to fine-tune."
msgstr ""
"其用於決"
"定 :envvar:`CELERY_MAIN_OPTIONS`、:envvar:`CELERY_NOTIFY_OPTIONS`、:envvar:`CELERY_MEMORY_OPTIONS`、:envvar:`CELERY_TRANSLATE_OPTIONS`、:envvar:`CELERY_BACKUP_OPTIONS`、:envvar:`CELERY_BEAT_OPTIONS`、:envvar:`WEB_WORKERS` "
"及 :envvar:`WEB_BLOCKING_THREADS`。您可以使用這些設定進行微調。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2370
msgid ""
"These variables allow you to adjust Celery worker options. It can be useful "
"to adjust concurrency (``--concurrency 16``), prefetching (``--prefetch-"
"multiplier 4``), or use different pool implementation (``--pool=gevent``). "
"Command-line options take precedence over corresponding Celery settings, "
"allowing each worker category to use a different prefetch multiplier."
msgstr ""
"這些變數可讓您調整 Celery worker 選項。您可以用它們調整並行處理數（``--"
"concurrency 16``）、預先擷取（``--prefetch-multiplier 4``），或改用其他 pool "
"實作（``--pool=gevent``）。命令列選項的優先順序高於對應的 Celery 設定，因此每"
"一類 worker 都可使用不同的預先擷取倍數。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2377
msgid ""
"By default, the number of concurrent workers is based "
"on :envvar:`WEBLATE_WORKERS`."
msgstr "並行 workers 的數量預設基於 :envvar:`WEBLATE_WORKERS`。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2388
msgid ":doc:`Celery worker options <celery:reference/celery.bin.worker>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Celery worker 選項 <celery:reference/celery.bin.worker>`"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2395
msgid ""
"This variable can be set to ``1`` to run only one celery process. This "
"reduces memory usage but may impact Weblate performance."
msgstr ""
"此變數可以設定為 ``1``，以便只執行一個 Celery 處理程序。這會減少記憶體使用，"
"但可能會影響 Weblate 效能。"

