msgid "Configure how many WSGI workers should be executed."
msgstr "設定應該執行多少個 WSGI workers。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2410
msgid ""
"It defaults to half of :envvar:`WEBLATE_WORKERS`, but is always at least 2."
msgstr "預設為 :envvar:`WEBLATE_WORKERS` 的一半，但始終至少為 2。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2421
msgid ""
":envvar:`WEB_WORKERS` configures how many worker processes will be used "
"by :program:`granian`."
msgstr ""
":envvar:`WEB_WORKERS` 設定 :program:`granian` 要使用的 worker 處理程序數量。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2425
msgid ""
"Configure how many blocking WSGI threads each :program:`granian` worker can "
"use. It defaults to twice :envvar:`WEBLATE_WORKERS`."
msgstr ""
"設定每個 :program:`granian` worker 可使用的阻塞式 WSGI 執行緒數量。預設值"
"為 :envvar:`WEBLATE_WORKERS` 的 2 倍。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2428
msgid ""
"The maximum number of simultaneous WSGI requests is "
"approximately :envvar:`WEB_WORKERS` multiplied "
"by :envvar:`WEB_BLOCKING_THREADS`. Each thread can hold its own database "
"connection, so keep the resulting total within the database connection limit."
msgstr ""
"同時處理的 WSGI 請求數上限約為 :envvar:`WEB_WORKERS` 乘"
"以 :envvar:`WEB_BLOCKING_THREADS`。每個執行緒都可能各自占用一個資料庫連線，因"
"此請確保計算後的總數不超過資料庫連線上限。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2443
msgid ""
