#: admin/install/docker.rst:2700
msgid "Customizing code"
msgstr "自訂程式碼"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2704
msgid ""
"The internal Weblate API may vary significantly between releases and is not "
"meant to be stable. Please review your custom code interacting with Weblate "
"internals on each upgrade."
msgstr ""
"不同版本的 Weblate 內部 API 可能差異巨大，並不穩定。請在每次升級時稽核與 "
"Weblate 內部 API 互動的自訂程式碼。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2708
msgid ""
"You can place additional Python code into :file:`/app/data/python/customize` "
"(see :ref:`docker-volume`). It is already installed as a Django application "
"inside Weblate (this is used for customizing templates and static files as "
"described above)."
msgstr ""
"您可以將額外的 Python 程式碼放進 :file:`/app/data/python/customize`\\ "
"（見：:ref:`docker-volume`）。它已作為 Weblate 內的一個 Django 程式被安裝（如"
"上所述，這是用來自訂範本和靜態檔案）。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2713
msgid ""
"This can be used to place any code (for example :ref:`own-checks`) or to add "
"custom maintenance tasks to the Celery task scheduler."
msgstr ""
"這可被用來放置任何程式碼（如 :ref:`own-checks`）或新增自訂維護任務到 Celery "
"任務計劃程式。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2721
msgid "Integrating third-party containers"
msgstr "整合第三方容器"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2723
msgid ""
"The Weblate Docker setup can be extended with additional containers to "
"provide complementary services such as machine translation, spell checking, "
"or other tools that enhance the translation workflow. These services can be "
"integrated into your Docker Compose configuration and work alongside Weblate."
msgstr ""
"可以用附加容器擴充套件 Weblate Docker 設定來提供補充性服務，例如機器翻譯、拼"
"寫檢查或其他增強翻譯工作流的工具。這些服務可以整合進 Docker Compose 設定中，"
"和 Weblate 一起工作。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2728
msgid "When adding third-party containers, consider the following:"
msgstr "新增第三方容器時，考慮下列因素："

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2730
msgid ""
"**Network connectivity**: Ensure containers can communicate with each other "
"by placing them on the same Docker network"
msgstr "**網路連線**：將容器放在相同的 Docker 網路上確保不同容器能彼此通訊"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2731
msgid ""
"**Data persistence**: Use volumes for services that need to persist data"
msgstr "**資料永續性**：對需要留存資料的服務使用磁碟區"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2732
msgid ""
"**Security**: Configure appropriate access controls and avoid exposing "
"unnecessary ports"
msgstr "**安全**：設定恰當的存取控制，避免暴露不必要的埠"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2737
msgid "LibreTranslate Docker container integration"
msgstr "LibreTranslate Docker 容器整合"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2739
msgid ""
"`LibreTranslate <https://libretranslate.com/>`_ is a free and open-source "
"machine translation service that can be self-hosted. Integrating it with "
"Weblate provides offline machine translation capabilities without relying on "
"external services."
msgstr ""
"`LibreTranslate <https://libretranslate.com/>`_ 是可以自託管的自由開源的機器"
"翻譯服務。將它與 Weblate 整合提供不依賴外部服務的離線機器翻譯能力。"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2743
msgid ""
"You can incorporate the LibreTranslate service into your Weblate deployment "
"by including it in a :file:`docker-compose.override.yml` file. Since it runs "
"within the Docker network, it's only accessible to Weblate and not exposed "
"to the public internet."
msgstr ""
