#: admin/install/openshift.rst:78
msgid ""
"After container setup, you can sign in as `admin` user with password "
"provided in ``WEBLATE_ADMIN_PASSWORD``, or a random password generated on "
"first start if that was not set."
msgstr ""
"設定容器之後，您可以使用 ``WEBLATE_ADMIN_PASSWORD`` 中提供的密碼以 `管理員` "
