#: admin/install/source.rst:55
msgid ""
"The dependency versions in :file:`pyproject.toml` describe the runtime "
"environment tested by the Weblate project. They are intentionally strict for "
"installs from PyPI and for the Weblate release process, because Weblate "
"cannot validate every dependency-version combination covered by wider "
"version ranges."
msgstr ""
":file:`pyproject.toml` 中的相依套件版本描述 Weblate 專案已測試的執行階段環"
"境。從 PyPI 安裝及進行 Weblate 發行流程時，這些版本範圍會刻意保持嚴格，因為 "
"Weblate 無法驗證較寬鬆版本範圍所涵蓋的每一種相依套件版本組合。"

#: admin/install/source.rst:60
msgid ""
"Distribution packages can replace those Python packages with versions from "
"the distribution package set. When doing so, run Weblate's test suite "
"against the packaged dependency set and treat passing tests as the "
"compatibility signal for the distribution package."
msgstr ""
"發行版套件可以用發行版套件集中的版本取代這些 Python 套件。這樣做時，請針對封"
"裝後的相依套件集執行 Weblate 測試套件，並以測試通過作為該發行版套件的相容性依"
"據。"

#: admin/install/source.rst:65
msgid ""
"Keep Weblate's tightly coupled companion packages in sync with the Weblate "
"release:"
msgstr "請讓與 Weblate 緊密耦合的配套套件和 Weblate 發行版本保持同步："

#: admin/install/source.rst:74
msgid ""
"Mismatched versions of these packages are more likely to break at runtime or "
"during tests than other Python dependency substitutions."
msgstr ""
"相較於其他 Python 相依套件替代項目，這些套件的版本不相符更可能在執行階段或測"
"試期間造成問題。"

#: admin/install/source.rst:79
msgid ""
"See :ref:`local-tests` for test setup and :ref:`release-cycle` for Weblate's "
"release cadence."
msgstr ""
"測試設定請參閱 :ref:`local-tests`，Weblate 的發行週期則請參閱 :ref:`release-"
"cycle`。"

#: admin/install/steps/adjust-config.rst:1
msgid ""
"Adjust the values in the new :file:`settings.py` file to your liking. You "
"will need to provide at least the database credentials and Django secret "
"key, but you will want more changes for production setup, "
"see :ref:`configuration`."
msgstr ""
"將新的 :file:`settings.py` 檔案中的值調整為您所需要的。您至少需要提供資料庫憑"
"證和 Django 金鑰，但在生產安裝中需要做更多的變更，參"
"閱：:ref:`configuration`。"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:2
msgid "Hardware requirements"
msgstr "硬體需求"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:4
msgid ""
"Weblate should run on any contemporary hardware without problems, the "
"following is the minimal configuration required to run Weblate on a single "
"host (Weblate, database and web server):"
msgstr ""
"Weblate 應該可以在任何現代硬體上正常執行，以下是在單一主機（Weblate、資料庫"
"和 Web 伺服器）上執行 Weblate 所需的最低設定："

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:8
msgid "3 GB of RAM"
msgstr "3 GB 記憶體"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:9
msgid "2 CPU cores"
msgstr "2 個 CPU 核心"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:10
msgid "1 GB of storage space"
msgstr "1 GB 儲存空間"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:14
msgid ""
"Actual requirements for your installation of Weblate vary heavily based on "
"the size of the translations managed in it."
msgstr "根據 Weblate 中管理的翻譯大小，安裝 Weblate 的實際需求差異很大。"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:18
msgid "Memory usage"
msgstr "記憶體使用"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:20
msgid ""
"The more memory the better - it is used for caching on all levels (file "
"system, database and Weblate). For hundreds of translation components, at "
"least 4 GB of RAM is recommended."
msgstr ""
"記憶體越多越好——用於所有層級的快取（檔案系統，資料庫和 Weblate）。如果有幾百"
"個翻譯元件，那麼建議的最小記憶體為 4 GB。"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:27
msgid ""
"For systems with less memory than recommended, :ref:`minimal-celery` is "
"recommended."
msgstr "對於記憶體低於建議值的系統，建議使用 :ref:`minimal-celery`。"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:30
msgid "CPU usage"
msgstr "CPU 使用"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:32
msgid "Many concurrent users increase the amount of needed CPU cores."
msgstr "大量並行使用者會提高需要的 CPU 核心數。"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:35
msgid "Storage usage"
msgstr "儲存空間使用"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:37
msgid ""
"The typical database storage usage is around 300 MB per 1 million hosted "
"words."
msgstr "典型的資料庫儲存用量為大約 300 MB/每 100 萬託管字詞。"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:39
msgid ""
"Storage space needed for cloned repositories varies, but Weblate tries to "
"keep their size minimal by doing shallow clones."
msgstr ""
"複製儲存庫所需的儲存空間會因情況而異，但 Weblate 會透過淺層複製來盡量降低所需"
"空間。"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:43
msgid "Nodes"
msgstr "節點"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:45
msgid ""
"For small and medium-sized sites (millions of hosted words), all Weblate "
"components (see :ref:`architecture`) can be run on a single node."
msgstr ""
"對中小網站（幾百萬託管字詞），所有的 Weblate 元件（見 :ref:`architecture`）可"
"以執行在單一節點上。"

#: admin/install/steps/hw.rst:48
msgid ""
"When you grow to hundreds of millions of hosted words, it is recommended to "
"have a dedicated node for database (see :ref:`database-setup`)."
msgstr ""
"當託管字詞數增長到數以億計時，建議使用專門的資料庫節點（見 :ref:`database-"
"setup`）。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:2
msgid "After installation"
msgstr "安裝後"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:4
msgid ""
"Congratulations, your Weblate server is now running and you can start using "
"it."
msgstr "恭喜，您的 Weblate 服務現在已上線了，您可以開始使用它。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:6
msgid "You can now access Weblate on ``http://localhost:8000/``."
msgstr "您可以在 ``http://localhost:8000/`` 存取 Weblate。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:7
msgid ""
"Sign in with admin credentials obtained during installation or register with "
"new users."
msgstr "使用安裝期間獲得的管理憑證登入或註冊新使用者。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:8
msgid ""
"You can now run Weblate commands using :command:`weblate` command when "
"Weblate Python environment is active, see :ref:`manage`."
msgstr ""
"現在當 Weblate 的 Python 環境啟用時，您可以使用 :command:`weblate` 來執行 "
"Weblate 指令，請參閱 :ref:`manage`。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:10
msgid "You can stop the test server with :kbd:`Ctrl+C`."
msgstr "您可以使用 :kbd:`Ctrl+C` 停止測試的伺服器。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:11
msgid ""
"Review potential issues with your installation either on ``/manage/"
"performance/`` URL (see :ref:`manage-performance`) or "
"using :command:`weblate check --deploy`, see :ref:`production`."
msgstr ""
"要檢查您安裝的潛在問題，有兩個途徑。一是 ``/manage/performance/`` URL (參"
"閱 :ref:`manage-performance`)，二是使用 :command:`weblate check --deploy`，參"
"閱 :ref:`production`。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:14
msgid "Adding translation"
msgstr "新增翻譯"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:16
msgid ""
"Open the admin interface (``http://localhost:8000/create/project/``) and "
"create the project you want to translate. See :ref:`project` for more "
"details."
msgstr ""
"開啟管理介面（ ``http://localhost:8000/create/project/`` ），並新增您想要翻譯"
"的專案。更多細節請參閱 :ref:`project`。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:19
msgid "All you need to specify here is the project name and its website."
msgstr "這裡所有需要您指定的只是專案名稱及其網站。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:21
msgid ""
"Create a component which is the real object for translation - it points to "
"the VCS repository, and selects which files to translate. "
"See :ref:`component` for more details."
msgstr ""
"建立一個元件，該元件是要翻譯的實際物件——它指向版本控制系統儲存庫，並選擇要翻"
"譯的檔案。更多詳細資訊請參閱 :ref:`component`。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:25
msgid ""
"The important fields here are: :ref:`component-name`, :ref:`component-repo`, "
"and :ref:`component-filemask` for finding translatable files. Weblate "
"supports a wide range of formats "
"including :ref:`gettext`, :ref:`aresource`, :ref:`apple`, :ref:`javaprop`, :ref:`stringsdict` "
"or :ref:`fluent`, see :ref:`formats` for more details."
msgstr ""
"此處的重要欄位為：:ref:`component-name`、:ref:`component-repo` 及用於尋找可翻"
"譯檔案的 :ref:`component-filemask`。Weblate 支援多種格式，包"
"括 :ref:`gettext`、:ref:`aresource`、:ref:`apple`、:ref:`javaprop`、:ref:`stringsdict` "
"或 :ref:`fluent`，更多細節見 :ref:`formats`。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-after.rst:31
msgid ""
"Once the above is completed (it can be lengthy process depending on the size "
"of your VCS repository, and number of messages to translate), you can start "
"translating."
msgstr ""
"一旦完成上面的工作（根據您的版本控制系統 VCS 儲存庫的大小，以及需要翻譯的資訊"
"數量，這可能是個漫長的過程），您就可以開始翻譯了。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-configure.rst:2
msgid "Configuring Weblate"
msgstr "設定 Weblate"

#: admin/install/steps/install-configure.rst:6
msgid ""
"The following assumes the Python environment used by Weblate is activated "
"(by executing ``. ~/weblate-env/bin/activate``). If not, specify the full "
"path to the :command:`weblate` command as ``~/weblate-env/bin/weblate``."
msgstr ""
"以下內容假設 Weblate 使用的 Python 環境已經啟用（可以透過 ``. ~/weblate-env/"
"bin/activate`` 來達成）。如果沒有，請指定 :command:`weblate` 指令的完整路徑"
"為 ``~/weblate-env/bin/weblate``。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-configure.rst:10
msgid ""
"Copy the file :file:`~/weblate-env/lib/python3.9/site-packages/weblate/"
"settings_example.py` to :file:`~/weblate-env/lib/python3.9/site-packages/"
"weblate/settings.py`."
msgstr ""
"將檔案 :file:`~/weblate-env/lib/python3.9/site-packages/weblate/"
"settings_example.py` 複製為 :file:`~/weblate-env/lib/python3.9/site-packages/"
"weblate/settings.py`。"

#: admin/install/steps/install-configure.rst:16
msgid ""
"Create the database and its structure for Weblate (the example settings use "
"PostgreSQL, check :ref:`database-setup` for a production-ready setup):"
msgstr ""
"為 Weblate 建立資料庫及其結構（範例中的設定使用 PostgreSQL，已經準備好的生產"
"設定請檢視 :ref:`database-setup`）："

#: admin/install/steps/install-configure.rst:27
msgid ""
"Create an administrator user account ``admin``, generate its password, and "
"copy it to the clipboard; remember to save it for later use:"
msgstr ""
"建立管理員使用者帳號 ``admin``，產生帳號密碼並將密碼複製到剪貼簿；記得儲存密"
"碼供日後使用："

#: admin/install/steps/install-configure.rst:36
msgid ""
"If you previously missed/lost the admin password, you can generate a new one "
"with the following command:"
msgstr "如果您之前丟失了 admin 密碼，可以使用以下指令產生一個新的 admin 密碼："

#: admin/install/steps/install-configure.rst:46
msgid ""
"Collect the static files for your web server (see :ref:`server` "
"and :ref:`static-files`):"
msgstr ""
"為您的收集 Web 伺服器用的靜態檔案（請參閱 :ref:`server` 和 :ref:`static-"
"files`）："

#: admin/install/steps/install-configure.rst:52
msgid ""
"Start the Celery workers. This is not necessary for development purposes, "
"but strongly recommended otherwise. :ref:`celery` has more info:"
msgstr ""
"啟動 Celery 工作程序。這對開發來說是不必要的，但強烈建議在其他場景這樣做。更"
"多資訊請參閱 :ref:`celery`："

#: admin/install/steps/install-configure.rst:59
msgid ""
"Start the development server (:ref:`server` details a production setup):"
msgstr "啟動開發伺服器（生產設定請參閱 :ref:`server` ）："

