#: admin/languages.rst:4 admin/languages.rst:103
msgid "Language definitions"
msgstr "語言定義"

#: admin/languages.rst:6
msgid ""
"To present different translations properly, info about language name, text "
"direction, plural definitions and language code are needed."
msgstr ""
"為了恰當地呈現不同的翻譯，需要提供有關語言名稱、文字方向、複數定義和語言程式"
"碼的資訊。"

#: admin/languages.rst:12
msgid "Built-in language definitions"
msgstr "內建語言定義"

#: admin/languages.rst:14
msgid ""
"Definitions for about 800 languages are included in Weblate and the list is "
"extended in every release. Whenever Weblate is upgraded (more specifically "
"whenever :wladmin:`migrate` is executed, see :ref:`generic-upgrade-"
"instructions`) the database of languages is updated to include all language "
"definitions shipped in Weblate."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 中包含了大約 800 種語言的定義，而且該語言清單在每個發行版中都會進行擴"
"充。每當升級 Weblate 時（更確切地說，是每當執行 :wladmin:`migrate` 時，請參"
"閱 :ref:`generic-upgrade-instructions`）語言資料庫都會更新，以包含 Weblate 提"
"供的所有語言定義。"

#: admin/languages.rst:20
msgid ""
"This feature can be disabled using :setting:`UPDATE_LANGUAGES`. You can also "
"enforce updating the database to match Weblate built-in data "
"using :wladmin:`setuplang`."
msgstr ""
"這個特性可以使用 :setting:`UPDATE_LANGUAGES` 來禁止。還可以使"
"用 :wladmin:`setuplang` 來強制更新資料庫，從而相符 Weblate 內建資料。"

#: admin/languages.rst:27
msgid ""
"`Current language definitions <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/language-data/"
"blob/main/languages.csv>`_"
msgstr ""
"`目前語言定義 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/language-data/blob/main/"
"languages.csv>`_"

#: admin/languages.rst:32
msgid "Parsing language codes"
msgstr "解析語言代碼"

#: admin/languages.rst:34
msgid ""
"While parsing translations, Weblate attempts to map language code (usually "
"the ISO 639-1 one) from the :ref:`component-filemask` to any existing "
"language object."
msgstr ""
"解析翻譯時，Weblate 試圖從 :ref:`component-filemask` 將語言程式碼（通常為 "
"ISO 639-1）對映到任何現有的語言物件。"

#: admin/languages.rst:38
msgid ""
"You can further adjust this mapping at project level by :ref:`project-"
"language_aliases`."
msgstr ""
"您可以通過 :ref:`project-language_aliases` 在專案層次來進一步調整這種映射。"

#: admin/languages.rst:40
msgid ""
"If no exact match can be found, an attempt will be made to best fit it into "
"an existing language. Following steps are tried:"
msgstr "如果無法找到精確的相符，將嘗試把其融入一種現有的語言。已嘗試以下措施："

#: admin/languages.rst:43
msgid "Case insensitive lookups."
msgstr "大小寫不敏感的查詢。"

#: admin/languages.rst:44
msgid "Normalizing underscores and dashes."
msgstr "將下劃線和破折號標準化。"

#: admin/languages.rst:45
msgid "Looking up built-in language aliases."
msgstr "查詢內建語言別名。"

#: admin/languages.rst:46
msgid "Looking up by language name."
msgstr "按語言名稱查詢。"

#: admin/languages.rst:47
msgid ""
"Ignoring the default country code for a given language—choosing ``cs`` "
"instead of ``cs_CZ``."
msgstr "忽略給定語言的預設國家代碼 — 選擇 ``cs`` 而非 ``cs_CZ``。"

#: admin/languages.rst:49
msgid ""
"Should that also fail, a new language definition will be created using the "
"defaults (left to right text direction, one plural). The automatically "
"created language with code ``xx_XX`` will be named as :guilabel:`xx_XX "
"(generated)`. You might want to change this in the admin interface later, "
"(see :ref:`changing-languages`) and report it to the issue tracker "
"(see :ref:`contributing`), so that the proper definition can be added to the "
"upcoming Weblate release."
msgstr ""
"如果這也失敗了，將使用預設值（從左到右的文字方向，一個複數）建立一個新的語言"
"定義。自動建立的程式碼為 ``xx_XX`` 的語言將被命名為 :guilabel:`xx_XX "
"(generated)`。您可能想稍後在管理介面中變更這個（見 :ref:`changing-"
"languages`），並將它報告給問題跟蹤器（見 :ref:`contributing`），這樣的話，正"
"確的定義就可以新增到即將釋出的 Weblate 版本中。"

#: admin/languages.rst:59
msgid ""
"In case you see something unwanted as a language, you might want to "
"adjust :ref:`component-language_regex` to ignore such file when parsing "
"translations."
msgstr ""
"在您看到有些不想要的內容作為語言的情況下，您會想要調整 :ref:`component-"
"language_regex`，當分析翻譯時忽略這樣的檔案。"

#: admin/languages.rst:72
msgid "Changing language definitions"
msgstr "變更語言定義"

#: admin/languages.rst:74
msgid ""
"You can change language definitions in the languages interface (:file:`/"
"languages/` URL)."
msgstr "您可以在語言介面來變更語言定義（ :file:`/languages/` URL ）。"

#: admin/languages.rst:77
msgid ""
"While editing, ensure all fields are correct (especially plurals and text "
"direction), otherwise translators will be unable to properly edit those "
"translations."
msgstr ""
"當編輯時，確認所有欄位都是正確的（特別是複數和本文方向），否則翻譯者將不能正"
"常編輯這些翻譯。"

#: admin/languages.rst:83
msgid ""
"Please consider contributing your changes back, see :ref:`extending-"
"languages`."
msgstr "請考慮將您的變更貢獻回來，見 :ref:`extending-languages`。"

#: admin/languages.rst:88
msgid "Ambiguous language codes and macrolanguages"
msgstr "模稜兩可的語言代碼和巨集語言"

#: admin/languages.rst:90
msgid ""
"In many cases it is not a good idea to use macrolanguage code for a "
"translation. The typical problematic case might be Kurdish language, which "
"might be written in Arabic or Latin script, depending on actual variant. To "
"get correct behavior in Weblate, it is recommended to use individual "
"language codes only and avoid macrolanguages."
msgstr ""
"在很多情況下，最好不要為翻譯使用宏語言程式碼。可能會出問題的典型範例是庫爾德"
"語，它可以用阿拉伯文或拉丁字母書寫，這取決於實際的變體。為了讓 Weblate 可以正"
"確地執行，建議只使用單獨的語言程式碼，避免使用宏語言程式碼。"

#: admin/languages.rst:98
msgid ""
"`Macrolanguages at Wikipedia <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"ISO_639_macrolanguage>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Wikipedia 上的巨集語言 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"ISO_639_macrolanguage>`_"

#: admin/languages.rst:105
msgid "Each language consists of following fields:"
msgstr "每種語言都包括後面的欄位："

#: admin/languages.rst:110 admin/projects.rst:1384
msgid "Language code"
msgstr "語言代碼"

#: admin/languages.rst:112
msgid ""
"Code identifying the language. Weblate prefers two letter codes as defined "
"by `ISO 639-1 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_639-1>`_, but uses `ISO "
"639-2 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_639-2>`_ or `ISO 639-3 <https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_639-3>`_ codes for languages that do not have two "
"letter code. It can also support extended codes as defined by `BCP 47`_."
msgstr ""
"辨識語言的程式碼。Weblate 使用兩個字母程式碼，如 `ISO 639-1 <https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_639-1>`_ 所定義的，但對於沒有兩個字母程式碼的語言，"
"使用會使用 `ISO 639-2 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_639-2>`_ 或 `ISO "
"639-3 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_639-3>`_ 程式碼。它還支援 `BCP 47`_ "
"定義的擴充套件程式碼。"

#: admin/languages.rst:128 admin/projects.rst:1386
msgid "Language name"
msgstr "語言名稱"

#: admin/languages.rst:130
msgid ""
"Visible name of the language. The language names included in Weblate are "
"also being localized depending on user interface language."
msgstr ""
"語言的可見名稱。還要根據使用者介面語言將 Weblate 中包括的語言名稱進行在地化。"

#: admin/languages.rst:135
msgid "Text direction"
msgstr "文字方向"

#: admin/languages.rst:137
msgid ""
"Determines whether language is written right to left or left to right. This "
"property is autodetected correctly for most of the languages."
msgstr ""
"確定語言的書寫方向是由左至右還是由右至左。此屬性對於大多數語言都能正確地自動"
"偵測到。"

#: admin/languages.rst:143
msgid "Number of speakers"
msgstr "語言使用者數量"

#: admin/languages.rst:145
msgid "Number of worldwide speakers of this language."
msgstr "此語言的全球使用人數。"

#: admin/languages.rst:151
msgid "Plural definitions"
msgstr "複數定義"

#: admin/languages.rst:153
msgid ""
"Weblate comes with a built-in set of plural definitions. These are based on "
"file-format specifications, CLDR, and other sources."
msgstr "Weblate 有內建的複數定義集。它們時基於檔案格式規範、CLDR及其他來源。"

#: admin/languages.rst:158
msgid ""
"Doing changes to the built-in plural definitions will most likely won't have "
"desired effect, as these rules need to match underlying implementation."
msgstr ""
"變更內建的複數定義很可能不會生產您期望的效果，因為這些規則需相符底層實作。"

#: admin/languages.rst:161
msgid ""
"Changing plural number or formula will affect only displaying of the "
"strings, but not parsing and storing strings to the files. Should you think "
"Weblate behaves incorrectly, please file an issue in our issue tracker."
msgstr ""
"變更複數或配方只會影響字串顯示，但不會影響解析字串並將字串儲存到檔案中。如果"
"您認為 Weblate 的行為有誤，請在我們的問題追蹤器上新開一個工單。"

#: admin/languages.rst:169
msgid "Plural number"
msgstr "複數數量"

#: admin/languages.rst:171
msgid "Number of plurals used in the language."
msgstr "語言中使用的複數的數量。"

#: admin/languages.rst:176
msgid "Plural formula"
msgstr "複數公式"

#: admin/languages.rst:178
msgid ""
"Gettext compatible plural formula used to determine which plural form is "
"used for given count."
msgstr "Gettxt 相容的複數公式，用於確定給定數量使用哪種複數形式。"

#: admin/languages.rst:180
msgid ""
"The formula uses the same expression syntax as the ``plural=`` part of the "
"Gettext ``Plural-Forms`` header. The ``nplurals`` value sets how many plural "
"forms the language has, and the formula returns the zero-based index of the "
"plural form to use for a count ``n``."
msgstr ""
"此公式使用與 Gettext ``Plural-Forms`` 標頭中 ``plural=`` 部分相同的運算式語"
"法。``nplurals`` 值設定語言具有多少種複數形式，而公式會傳回計數 ``n`` 應使用"
"的複數形式索引（從零開始）。"

#: admin/languages.rst:185
msgid ""
"Weblate validates the formula using the Gettext parser provided by Python. "
"The accepted syntax is a C-like integer expression with ``n`` as the only "
"variable. It can use decimal numbers, parentheses, arithmetic operators "
"(``+``, ``-``, ``*``, ``/``, ``%``), comparison and equality operators, "
"logical operators (``&&``, ``||``, ``!``), and the ternary operator "
"(``condition ? value1 : value2``). The result must be between ``0`` and "
"``nplurals - 1``."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 會使用 Python 提供的 Gettext 剖析器驗證公式。可接受的語法是類似 C 的"
"整數運算式，並以 ``n`` 作為唯一變數。可以使用十進位數字、括號、算術運算子"
"（``+``、``-``、``*``、``/``、``%``）、比較及相等運算子、邏輯運算子（``&&``、"
"``||``、``!``），以及三元運算子（``condition ? value1 : value2``）。結果必須"
"介於 ``0`` 和 ``nplurals - 1`` 之間。"

#: admin/languages.rst:193
msgid "For example, English uses:"
msgstr "例如，英語使用："

#: admin/languages.rst:202
msgid "`GNU gettext manual for plural forms`_"
msgstr "`GNU gettext 的複數形式手冊`_"

#: admin/languages.rst:203
msgid "`GNU gettext plural formula parser`_"
msgstr "`GNU gettext 複數公式解析器`_"

#: admin/languages.rst:204
msgid "`Language Plural Rules by the Unicode Consortium`_"
msgstr "`Unicode 聯盟的語言複數規則`_"

#: admin/licensing.rst:2
msgid "Licensing translations"
msgstr "翻譯授權"

#: admin/licensing.rst:3
msgid ""
"You can specify which license translations are contributed under. This is "
"especially important to do if translations are open to the public, to "
"stipulate what they can be used for."
msgstr ""
"您可以指定翻譯貢獻採用的授權條款。若翻譯開放給大眾參與，這點尤其重要，因為必"
"須明確規範翻譯的使用方式。"

#: admin/licensing.rst:7
msgid ""
"You should specify :ref:`component` license info. You should avoid requiring "
"a contributor license agreement, though it is possible."
msgstr ""
"您應該指定 :ref:`component` 授權資訊。您應該避免要求與貢獻者簽訂授權合約，儘"
"管這是可能的。"

#: admin/licensing.rst:11
msgid "License info"
msgstr "授權資訊"

#: admin/licensing.rst:13
msgid ""
"Upon specifying license info (license name and URL), this info is shown in "
"the translation info section of the respective :ref:`component`."
msgstr ""
"在指定授權資訊的時候（授權名稱和 URL）後，這個資訊將顯示在各"
"個 :ref:`component` 的翻譯資訊部分。"

#: admin/licensing.rst:16
msgid ""
"Usually this is best place to post licensing info if no explicit consent is "
"required. If your project or translation is not libre you most probably need "
"prior consent."
msgstr ""
"如果不需要特別同意的話，這通常是放置許可資訊的最佳位置。如果您的專案或翻譯不"
"是自由的，您很可能需要事先同意。"

#: admin/licensing.rst:20 admin/projects.rst:188 admin/projects.rst:892
#: admin/workspaces.rst:106
msgid "Contributor license agreement"
msgstr "貢獻者授權協議"

#: admin/licensing.rst:22
msgid ""
"If you specify a :ref:`component-agreement`, only users who have agreed to "
"it will be able to contribute. This is a clearly visible step when accessing "
"the translation:"
msgstr ""
"如果您指定了 :ref:`component-agreement`，那麼只有同意該協議的使用者能夠作貢"
"獻。在存取翻譯時，這是一個清晰可見的步驟："

#: admin/licensing.rst:28
msgid "User licenses"
msgstr "使用者授權"

#: admin/licensing.rst:30
msgid ""
"Any user can review all translation licenses of all public projects on the "
"instance from their profile:"
msgstr ""
"任何使用者都可以在其個人資料中檢視執行個體上所有公共專案的所有翻譯授權："

#: admin/machine.rst:4 snippets/permissions.rst:77 user/translating.rst:430
msgid "Automatic suggestions"
msgstr "自動建議"

#: admin/machine.rst:8
msgid ""
"Prior to Weblate 4.13, the services were configured in the :ref:`config`."
msgstr "在 Weblate 4.13 之前，這些服務是在 :ref:`config` 中設定的。"

#: admin/machine.rst:10
msgid ""
"The support for several machine translation and translation memory services "
"is built-in. Each service can be turned on by the administrator for whole "
"site (under :guilabel:`Automatic suggestions` in :ref:`management-"
"interface`) or at the project settings:"
msgstr ""
"內建了對幾種機器翻譯和翻譯記憶服務的支援。管理員可以為整站開啟每項服務"
"（在 :ref:`management-interface` 中的 :guilabel:`Automatic suggestions`），也"
"可以在專案設定中為特定專案開啟："

#: admin/machine.rst:19
msgid ""
"They come subject to their terms of use, so ensure you are allowed to use "
"them how you want. Third-party services can receive source strings, "
"translations, and related context from Weblate."
msgstr ""
"它們受到其使用條款的約束，所以確保您被允許以您想要的方式使用它們。第三方服務"
"可從 Weblate 接收來源字串、翻譯、和相關的情境。"

#: admin/machine.rst:23
msgid ""
"The services translate from the source language as configured "
"at :ref:`component`, see :ref:`component-source_language`."
msgstr ""
"該服務從 :ref:`component` 設定的原始檔進行翻譯，請參考 :ref:`component-"
"source_language`。"

#: admin/machine.rst:26
msgid ""
"Per-project automatic suggestion can also be configured via the :ref:`api`."
msgstr "可透過 :ref:`api` 設定每個專案的自動建議。"

#: admin/machine.rst:35
msgid "Priority of machine translation and translation memory services"
msgstr "機器翻譯與翻譯記憶服務的優先順序"

#: admin/machine.rst:37
msgid ""
":ref:`mt-weblate-translation-memory` matches with 100% score take priority "
"over machine translation services. If 100% match in translation memory is "
"found, no machine translation is performed. If several 100% matches occur, "
"the first one returned by the database is used."
msgstr ""
":ref:`mt-weblate-translation-memory` 的相符結果若為 100%，其優先順序高於機器"
"翻譯服務。如果翻譯記憶中有 100% 相符結果，就不會執行機器翻譯。如果有多筆 "
"100% 相符結果，系統會使用資料庫傳回的第一筆結果。"

#: admin/machine.rst:39
msgid ""
"Each machine translation service has a predefined maximum score it can "
"produce. The use of installed translation services is ordered according to "
"their maximum score. For each string with translation score lower than the "
"service's maximum, the service is asked to produce a translation. "
"Translations with a score exceeding the current one are accepted."
msgstr ""
"每個機器翻譯服務都有一個預定義的可以產生的最高分。系統按照它們的最高分確定使"
"用安裝的翻譯服務的順序。如果字串譯文的分低於機器翻譯服務的最高分，那麼將請求"
"該服務產生翻譯。如果譯文得分超過目前得分，那麼系統將接受該譯文。"

#: admin/machine.rst:44
msgid "Source strings for the machine translation"
msgstr "機器翻譯的來源字串。"

#: admin/machine.rst:48
msgid ""
"The origin of source strings for all third-party services can be configured. "
"This can be used to tweak the service to get the best results. Following "
"choices are available:"
msgstr ""
"可以設定所有第三方服務的來源字串來源。這可以用來微調服務獲得最好結果。有以下"
"選項可用："

#: admin/machine.rst:51
msgid ":guilabel:`Automatic selection`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`自動選擇`"

#: admin/machine.rst:52
msgid "Chooses the best source language automatically."
msgstr "自動選擇最佳來源語言。"

#: admin/machine.rst:54
msgid "This is the default behavior."
msgstr "這是預設行為。"

#: admin/machine.rst:55
msgid ":guilabel:`Component source language`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`元件來源語言`"

#: admin/machine.rst:56
msgid "Uses the component source language."
msgstr "使用元件來源語言。"

#: admin/machine.rst:58
msgid "This was the behavior before the 5.11 release."
msgstr "此為 5.11 版本前的行為。"

#: admin/machine.rst:59
msgid ":guilabel:`Secondary language defined in project or component`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`專案或元件中定義的第二語言`"

#: admin/machine.rst:60
msgid ""
"Use project :ref:`project-secondary_language` or component :ref:`component-"
"secondary_language`."
msgstr ""
"使用專案 :ref:`project-secondary_language` 或元件 :ref:`component-"
"secondary_language`。"

#: admin/machine.rst:62
msgid ""
"Falls back to the automatic selection of the source language if the "
"secondary language not configured."
msgstr "退回到自動選擇來源語言，如果未設定第二語言。"

#: admin/machine.rst:67
msgid "LLM translation context"
msgstr "LLM 翻譯情境"

#: admin/machine.rst:69
msgid ""
"LLM-based automatic suggestion services receive additional context about "
"each translated string, when available. This includes the string context or "
"monolingual key, additional explanation, configured secondary-language "
"translation, plural information, failing quality checks, and placeholder "
"contents. Matching glossary entries are passed with their explanations and "
"selected flags, so duplicate glossary terms can be disambiguated."
msgstr ""
"有額外內容可用時，以 LLM 為基礎的自動建議服務會接收每個待翻譯字串的相關內容。"
"這包括字串情境或單語鍵、額外說明、已設定的第二語言翻譯、複數資訊、未通過的品"
"質檢查，以及預留位置內容。相符的詞彙表項目會連同其說明和選取的旗標一併傳送，"
"以便區分重複的詞彙表詞彙。"

#: admin/machine.rst:76
msgid ""
"You can add target-language-specific instructions in :guilabel:`Language-"
"specific instructions` using a JSON object mapping language codes to text. "
"Language codes have to exist in Weblate and are matched exactly; whitespace "
"is not ignored. Each instruction can contain up to 1000 characters. Weblate "
"first looks for the exact target language code and then falls back to the "
"base language code."
msgstr ""
"您可以在 :guilabel:`特定語言的操作指南` 中，使用將語言代碼對應至文字的 JSON "
"物件，新增目標語言專用的說明。語言代碼必須存在於 Weblate 中，且會進行完全比"
"對；不會忽略空白字元。每項說明最多可包含 1000 個字元。Weblate 會先尋找完全相"
"符的目標語言代碼，再退回使用基礎語言代碼。"

#: admin/machine.rst:83
msgid ""
"The added metadata is used only to guide the generated suggestion; the "
"returned translation still has to preserve the source placeholders and "
"markup. Weblate also sends a short previous chat exchange to LLM services to "
"demonstrate the expected JSON response format. The exchange uses bundled "
"translated examples when available for the source and target language pair, "
"or language-neutral formatting examples otherwise. Existing translations for "
"the same target language can be appended as additional examples."
msgstr ""
"新增的中繼資料只用於引導產生建議；傳回的翻譯仍必須保留來源的預留位置和標記。"
"Weblate 也會向 LLM 服務傳送一小段先前的對話，示範預期的 JSON 回應格式。來源語"
"言和目標語言的組合有可用範例時，對話會使用隨附的已翻譯範例，否則會使用與語言"
"無關的格式範例。也可以附加相同目標語言的既有翻譯作為其他範例。"

#: admin/machine.rst:97
msgid "Custom machine translation"
msgstr "自訂機器翻譯"

#: admin/machine.rst:99
msgid ""
"You can also implement your own machine translation services using a few "
"lines of Python code. Place the code in a module Weblate can import "
"(see :ref:`custom-module` or :ref:`docker-python-override`) and add fully "
"qualified class name to :setting:`WEBLATE_MACHINERY`."
msgstr ""
"您也可以使用幾行 Python 程式碼來實作自己的機器翻譯服務。將程式碼放在 Weblate "
"可以匯入的模組中 （請參閱 :ref:`custom-module` 或 :ref:`docker-python-"
"override`） 並新增完整限定類別名稱至 :setting:`WEBLATE_MACHINERY`。"

#: admin/management.rst:4 security/threat-model.rst:109
#: security/threat-model.rst:446
msgid "Management commands"
msgstr "管理指令"

#: admin/management.rst:8
msgid ""
"Running management commands under a different user than the one running your "
"webserver can result in files getting wrong permissions, please "
"check :ref:`file-permissions` for more details."
msgstr ""
"在與執行 web 伺服器的使用者不同的使用者下執行管理指令，可能會導致檔案獲得錯誤"
"的權限，請查閱 :ref:`file-permissions` 瞭解詳情。"

#: admin/management.rst:12
msgid ""
"You will find basic management commands (available as :file:`./manage.py` in "
"the Django sources, or as an extended set in a script "
"called :command:`weblate` installable atop Weblate)."
msgstr ""
"您會看到基本管理指令：Django 原始碼中的 :file:`./manage.py`，或安裝於 "
"Weblate 上層、名為 :command:`weblate` 的指令碼所提供的擴充指令集。"

#: admin/management.rst:18
msgid "Invoking management commands"
msgstr "呼叫管理指令"

#: admin/management.rst:20
msgid "As mentioned before, invocation depends on how you installed Weblate."
msgstr "如上面所提到的，如何呼叫取決於您如何安裝 Weblate。"

#: admin/management.rst:22
msgid ""
"If using a Python environment for Weblate, you can either specify the full "
"path to :command:`weblate`, or activate the Python environment prior to "
"invoking it:"
msgstr ""
"如果使用 Python 環境執行 Weblate，您可以指定 :command:`weblate` 的完整路徑，"
"或在呼叫它之前先啟用該環境："

#: admin/management.rst:34
msgid ""
"If you are using source code directly (either from a tarball or Git "
"checkout), the management script is :file:`./manage.py` available in the "
"Weblate sources. To run it:"
msgstr ""
"如果您直接使用原始碼（來源於 tarball 或 Git checkout），管理指令碼可以在 "
"Weblate 原始檔的 :file:`./manage.py` 中獲得。要執行它："

#: admin/management.rst:42
msgid ""
"If you've installed Weblate using the pip installer, or by using "
"the :file:`./setup.py` script, the :command:`weblate` is installed to your "
"path (or Python environment path), from where you can use it to control "
"Weblate:"
msgstr ""
"如果您是使用 pip 安裝程式或 :file:`./setup.py` 安裝 Weblate，"
"則 :command:`weblate` 會被安裝到您的 PATH（或 Python 環境 PATH），您可以從那"
"裡使用它來控制 Weblate："

#: admin/management.rst:50
msgid ""
"For the Docker image, the script is installed like above, and you can run it "
"using :command:`docker exec`:"
msgstr ""
"對於 Docker 映像，此指令稿會依照上述方式安裝，並且您可以使"
"用 :command:`docker exec` 執行它："

#: admin/management.rst:57
msgid ""
"For :program:`docker-compose-plugin` the process is similar, you just have "
"to use :command:`docker compose exec`:"
msgstr ""
"對於 :program:`docker-compose-plugin`，過程是相似的，您只是必須使"
"用 :command:`docker compose exec`："

#: admin/management.rst:64
msgid "In case you need to pass it a file, you can temporary add a volume:"
msgstr "如果需要傳遞檔案給它，您可以臨時新增一個儲存區："

#: admin/management.rst:84
msgid ""
"Imports a translation from the file to use as a suggestion for the given "
"translation. It skips duplicated translations; only different ones are added."
msgstr ""
"從檔案匯入翻譯，用作給定翻譯的建議。它會跳過重複的翻譯；只會新增不同的內容。"

#: admin/management.rst:104
msgid ""
"Analyzes change history to estimate realistic translator throughput per day. "
"The command includes only active human users and unit-backed manual "
"translation changes, and applies daily minimum and maximum thresholds to "
"skip obvious outliers, bots, bulk imports, uploads, and other events that "
"would pollute the result."
msgstr ""
"分析變更歷程，以估算符合實際情況的翻譯者每日處理量。此指令只納入活躍的人類使"
