"Configures default groups and optionally assigns all users to that default "
"group."
msgstr "設定預設群組，並選用擇將所有使用者分配到該預設群組。"

#: admin/management.rst:1092
msgid "Updates list of defined languages in Weblate."
msgstr "將 Weblate 中的確定語言的清單更新。"

#: admin/management.rst:1103
msgid "Updates all checks for all strings."
msgstr "更新對所有字串的所有檢查。"

#: admin/management.rst:1107
msgid "Useful for upgrades which do major changes to checks."
msgstr "對檢查進行主要變更的更新是有用的。"

#: admin/management.rst:1114
msgid ""
"Checks are recalculated regularly by Weblate in the background, the "
"frequency can be configured via :setting:`BACKGROUND_TASKS`."
msgstr ""
"檢查由 Weblate 定期在後臺重新計算，可以使用 :setting:`BACKGROUND_TASKS` 設定"
"頻率。"

#: admin/management.rst:1122
msgid "Fetches remote VCS repositories and updates the internal cache."
msgstr "取得遠端 VCS 儲存庫並更新內部快取。"

#: admin/management.rst:1129
msgid ""
"Usually it is better to configure hooks in the repository to "
"trigger :ref:`hooks`, instead of regular triggering the updates "
"by :wladmin:`updategit`."
msgstr ""
"通常最好在儲存庫中設定掛勾，來觸發 :ref:`hooks`，而不是定期透"
"過 :wladmin:`updategit` 來觸發更新。"

#: admin/memory.rst:5
msgid "Translation Memory"
msgstr "翻譯記憶"

#: admin/memory.rst:7
msgid "Weblate comes with a built-in translation memory consisting of:"
msgstr "Weblate 帶有內建的翻譯記憶，其組成部分為："

#: admin/memory.rst:9
msgid "Manually imported translation memory (see :ref:`memory-user`)."
msgstr "手動匯入的翻譯記憶（請參閱 :ref:`memory-user`）。"

#: admin/memory.rst:10
msgid ""
"Automatically stored translations performed in Weblate (depending "
"on :ref:`memory-scopes`)."
msgstr "自動儲存 Weblate 中進行的翻譯（取決於 :ref:`memory-scopes`）。"

#: admin/memory.rst:11
msgid "Automatically imported past translations."
msgstr "自動匯入了過去的翻譯。"

#: admin/memory.rst:13
msgid ""
"Content in the translation memory can be applied to strings in several ways:"
msgstr "翻譯記憶中的內容可以透過多種方式套用於字串："

#: admin/memory.rst:15
msgid ""
"User can accept suggestions from the :ref:`machine-translation` tab while "
"editing the string."
msgstr "使用者可以在編輯字串時從 :ref:`machine-translation` 標籤頁接受建議。"

#: admin/memory.rst:16
msgid ""
"The selected strings can be processed using :ref:`auto-translation` from "
"the :guilabel:`Operations` menu."
msgstr ""
"可以從 :guilabel:`操作` 選單使用 :ref:`auto-translation` 處理所選的字串。"

#: admin/memory.rst:17
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.autotranslate.autotranslate` add-on can automatically "
"apply changes to new and existing strings."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.autotranslate.autotranslate` 附加元件可以自動將變更應用於"
"新的和現有的字串。"

#: admin/memory.rst:19
msgid ""
"For installation tips, see :ref:`mt-weblate-translation-memory`, which is "
"turned on by default."
msgstr ""
"對於安裝提示，請參閱 :ref:`mt-weblate-translation-memory`，它預設是開啟的。"

#: admin/memory.rst:26
msgid "Translation-memory scopes"
msgstr "翻譯記憶範圍"

#: admin/memory.rst:28
msgid ""
"The translation-memory scopes ensure privacy for different projects and "
"users. Sharing of translations is also available."
msgstr "翻譯記憶的範圍確保不同專案和使用者的隱私。也可以用來共享譯文。"

#: admin/memory.rst:33
msgid ""
"When upgrading from older Weblate releases, existing translation-memory "
"entries are converted to scopes by a periodic Celery background task. Until "
"this backfill finishes, existing entries can be temporarily unavailable in "
"suggestions and memory management views. Keep Celery running after the "
"upgrade so the periodic task can start or resume the migration. Site "
"administrators can monitor the backfill and duplicate-entry consolidation "
"in :guilabel:`Administration` > :guilabel:`Performance report`."
msgstr ""
"從較舊的 Weblate 發行版本升級時，既有翻譯記憶項目會由定期 Celery 背景工作轉換"
"成不同作用範圍。在回填完成前，既有項目可能暫時不會出現在建議和翻譯記憶管理檢"
"視中。升級後請讓 Celery 保持執行，以便定期工作開始或繼續移轉。網站管理員可以"
"在 :guilabel:`管理` > :guilabel:`效能報告` 中監看回填及重複項目整併作業。"

#: admin/memory.rst:42
msgid "Imported translation memory"
msgstr "已匯入的翻譯記憶"

#: admin/memory.rst:44
msgid ""
"Importing arbitrary translation memory data using "
"the :wladmin:`import_memory` command makes memory content available to all "
"users and projects."
msgstr ""
"使用 :wladmin:`import_memory` 指令匯入任何翻譯記憶資料會使記憶內容可用於所有"
"使用者與專案。"

#: admin/memory.rst:48
msgid "Per-user translation memory"
msgstr "每個使用者的翻譯記憶"

#: admin/memory.rst:50
msgid ""
"Stores all user translations automatically in the personal translation "
"memory of each respective user."
msgstr "在每個單獨使用者的個人翻譯記憶中自動儲存使用者的翻譯。"

#: admin/memory.rst:52
msgid ""
"The default value for new users is automatically adjusted based on "
"the :ref:`autoclean-tm` configuration. If automatic cleanup is enabled, this "
"is disabled by default to prevent reintroducing inconsistent translations."
msgstr ""
"系統會依 :ref:`autoclean-tm` 設定自動調整新使用者的預設值。如果啟用自動清除，"
"這項設定預設會停用，以免重新加入不一致的翻譯。"

#: admin/memory.rst:57
msgid "Per-project translation memory"
msgstr "每個專案的翻譯記憶"

#: admin/memory.rst:59
msgid ""
"All translations within a project are automatically stored in a project "
"translation memory only available for this project."
msgstr ""
"專案內的所有翻譯都自動儲存在專案翻譯記憶中，這個翻譯記憶只在專案內可用。"

#: admin/memory.rst:63
msgid "Workspace translation memory"
msgstr "工作空間翻譯記憶"

#: admin/memory.rst:65
msgid ""
"Projects in the same workspace can share translation memory without enabling "
"the global shared translation memory. Workspace translation memory has to be "
"enabled both in the workspace settings and in the individual project "
"workflow settings."
msgstr ""
"同一工作空間中的專案可以共用翻譯記憶，而不必啟用全域共用翻譯記憶。工作空間設"
"定和個別專案工作流程設定都必須啟用工作空間翻譯記憶。"

#: admin/memory.rst:80
msgid "Shared translation memory"
msgstr "共享的翻譯記憶"

#: admin/memory.rst:82
msgid ""
"All translations within projects with shared translation memory turned on "
"are stored in a shared translation memory available to all projects. Turning "
"off contribution to shared translation memory stops previously contributed "
"automatic entries from being used as shared suggestions."
msgstr ""
"開啟翻譯記憶共享的專案內的所有翻譯都儲存在共享的翻譯記憶中，可用於所有專案。"
"關閉對共享翻譯記憶的貢獻會阻止之前貢獻的自動條目被用作共享的建議。"

#: admin/memory.rst:87
msgid ""
"Please consider carefully whether to turn this feature on for shared Weblate "
"installations, as it can have severe implications:"
msgstr ""
"對於分享的 Weblate 安裝，請仔細考慮是否開啟這個特性，因為可能導致嚴重的影響："

#: admin/memory.rst:90
msgid "The translations can be used by anybody else."
msgstr "翻譯可以被任何人使用。"

#: admin/memory.rst:91
msgid "This might lead to disclosing secret information."
msgstr "這會導致洩露秘密資訊。"

#: admin/memory.rst:92
msgid "Make sure the translations you share have good quality."
msgstr "請確保您共享的譯文品質上乘。"

#: admin/memory.rst:102
msgid "Translation memory status"
msgstr "翻譯記憶狀態"

#: admin/memory.rst:106
msgid ""
"Translation memory entries can have two different statuses: **active** and "
"**pending**. Pending entries are included in suggestions, but with a quality "
"penalty applied. If :ref:`autoclean-tm` is enabled, matching pending entries "
"are removed when a translation becomes active."
msgstr ""
"翻譯記憶項目有兩種狀態：**使用中** 和 **待處理**。待處理項目會納入建議，但會"
"套用品質扣分。啟用 :ref:`autoclean-tm` 後，翻譯轉為使用中狀態時，會移除相符的"
"待處理項目。"

#: admin/memory.rst:114 admin/projects.rst:247
msgid "Autoclean translation memory"
msgstr "自動清理翻譯記憶"

#: admin/memory.rst:118
msgid ""
"When enabled for a project, Weblate replaces older automatically created "
"translation memory entries when a translation becomes active:"
msgstr "對專案啟用後，當翻譯生效時 Weblate 替換舊的自動產生的翻譯記憶條目："

#: admin/memory.rst:121
msgid ""
"With :ref:`project-translation_review` enabled, cleanup happens when the "
"translation is approved."
msgstr "啟用 :ref:`project-translation_review` 時，清理在批准翻譯時發生。"

#: admin/memory.rst:123
msgid ""
"Without review, cleanup happens as soon as the translation reaches the "
"translated state."
msgstr "如果沒有審校，譯文一轉為已翻譯狀態就會被清理。"

#: admin/memory.rst:126
msgid ""
"For the same source string, component, context, and source/target language "
"pair, Weblate removes matching non-file entries from translation memory, "
"including entries with a different target text. This applies across "
"personal, project, and shared translation memory scopes. The current "
"translation is then stored again as an active entry in the scopes that are "
"enabled for that change."
msgstr ""
"對於同一來源字串、元件、情境和源/目標語言對，Weblate 從翻譯記憶中刪除相符的非"
"檔案條目，包括目標文字不同的條目。這應用於個人、專案和共享的翻譯記憶範圍。然"
"後目前翻譯被在為此變更啟用的範圍中再次儲存為活躍條目。"

#: admin/memory.rst:132
msgid ""
"Entries imported from external translation memory files are not cleaned up "
"automatically. Entries with a different context are kept."
msgstr "不自動清理從外部翻譯記憶匯入的條目。保留情境不同的條目。"

#: admin/memory.rst:135
msgid ""
"In the Docker container this can be configured "
"using :envvar:`WEBLATE_DEFAULT_AUTOCLEAN_TM`."
msgstr ""
"在 Docker 容器中這可以使用 :envvar:`WEBLATE_DEFAULT_AUTOCLEAN_TM` 設定。"

#: admin/memory.rst:138
msgid ""
"Enabling automatic cleanup also changes the default for new user profiles to "
"not contribute to personal translation memory. This prevents reintroducing "
"inconsistent translations that were supposed to be cleaned up."
msgstr ""
"開啟自動清理還會將新使用者個人資料的預設值變更為不錄入個人翻譯記憶。這防止重"
"新引入打算要清理的不一致的譯文。"

#: admin/memory.rst:148
msgid "Managing the Translation Memory"
msgstr "管理翻譯記憶"

#: admin/memory.rst:153
msgid "User interface"
msgstr "使用者介面"

#: admin/memory.rst:155
msgid ""
"Translation memory can be managed from several places in the Weblate UI:"
msgstr "可以從 Weblate 使用者介面的幾個地方管理翻譯記憶："

#: admin/memory.rst:157
msgid ""
"Open the user menu and choose :guilabel:`Translation memory` to manage your "
"personal translation memory."
msgstr "開啟使用者選單，選擇 :guilabel:`翻譯記憶` 管理您的個人翻譯記憶。"

#: admin/memory.rst:159
msgid ""
"Open a project and choose :guilabel:`Translation memory` from the project "
"menu to manage translation memory for that project."
msgstr "開啟專案，從專案選單選擇 :guilabel:`翻譯記憶` 來管理專案的翻譯記憶。"

#: admin/memory.rst:161
msgid ""
"Open :guilabel:`Administration` and choose :guilabel:`Translation memory` to "
"manage uploaded translation memory for the whole Weblate instance."
msgstr ""
"開啟 :guilabel:`管理`，選擇 :guilabel:`翻譯記憶` 管理整個 Weblate 執行個體的"
"已上傳的翻譯記憶。"

#: admin/memory.rst:164
msgid ""
"The translation memory page shows entry counts for the selected scope. "
"Depending on the scope, it also lists entries by origin, component, or "
"language pair. The listed entries can be downloaded as JSON or TMX. Users "
"with the required permissions can delete entries, and the project view can "
"rebuild translation memory for the whole project or for individual "
"components from the current translations."
msgstr ""
"翻譯記憶頁面顯示所選範圍的條目數。根據範圍不同，頁面還按照來源、元件或語言對"
"列出條目。所列條目可下載為 JSON 或 TMX。有所需權限的使用者可以刪除條目，專案"
"檢視可以從目前翻譯重建整個專案或單獨元件的翻譯記憶。"

#: admin/memory.rst:171
msgid ""
"The project view also shows whether shared translation memory and autoclean "
"translation memory are enabled for the project, with a link to the project "
"workflow settings when the user can edit the project."
msgstr ""
"專案檢視還顯示專案是否啟用了共享的翻譯記憶和自動清理翻譯記憶，當使用者可以編"
"輯專案時會顯示到專案工作流設定的連結。"

#: admin/memory.rst:175
msgid ""
"Translation memory files can be imported on the same page. Uploaded files "
"are stored in the selected scope:"
msgstr "可以在相同頁面上匯入翻譯記憶。上傳的檔案儲存在所選範圍中："

#: admin/memory.rst:178
msgid "Personal uploads are available in your personal translation memory."
msgstr "個人上傳在個人翻譯記憶中。"

#: admin/memory.rst:179
msgid ""
"Project uploads are available in the selected project's translation memory."
msgstr "專案上傳在所選專案的翻譯記憶中。"

#: admin/memory.rst:180
msgid ""
"Administration uploads are available as uploaded shared entries for the "
"whole Weblate instance."
msgstr "管理性質的上傳作為上傳的共享條目對整個執行個體可用。"

#: admin/memory.rst:184
msgid ""
"Translation memories in various formats can be imported into Weblate. The "
"TMX format is provided for interoperability with other tools. All supported "
"formats are TMX, JSON, XLIFF, PO, and CSV."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 可以匯入各種格式的翻譯記憶。TMX 格式是為了與其他工具進行互通而提供"
"的。所有支援格式為 TMX 、 JSON 、 XLIFF 、 PO 與 CSV。"

#: admin/memory.rst:188
msgid ""
"Source and target languages must be selected when uploading XLIFF, PO, or "
"CSV files if the language information is not provided by the file itself."
msgstr ""
"如果 XLIFF、PO 或 CSV 檔案本身未提供語言資訊，那麼上傳這些型別的檔案時必須選"
"擇來源語言和目標語言。"

#: admin/memory.rst:197
msgid ""
"You can search translation memory while editing strings from "
"the :ref:`machine-translation` tab."
msgstr ""
"您可以在搜尋翻譯記憶的同時編輯來自 :ref:`machine-translation` 分頁的字串。"

#: admin/memory.rst:201
msgid "Admin interface"
msgstr "管理介面"

#: admin/memory.rst:203
msgid ""
"Administrative users have additional translation memory management controls. "
"In :guilabel:`Administration` > :guilabel:`Translation memory`, the page "
"lists uploaded shared entries, shared entries, and total entries for the "
"Weblate instance. Depending on permissions, it can import uploaded shared "
"memory, delete uploaded entries, and download uploaded, shared, or all "
"entries as JSON or TMX."
msgstr ""
"管理型使用者擁有額外的翻譯記憶管理控制。在 :guilabel:`管理` > :guilabel:`翻譯"
"記憶` 中，此頁面列出 Weblate 執行個體的已上傳共享條目、共享條目和總條目。根據"
"權限不同，它可匯入上傳的共享記憶庫，刪除上傳的條目，下載已上傳的、共享的、或"
"者所有條目為 JSON 或 TMX 檔案。"

#: admin/memory.rst:211
msgid ""
"The project translation memory view also allows rebuilding parts of or the "
"entire project translation memory. Existing entries for the selected "
"component or project are deleted, and the memory is populated again from the "
"current translations in the background."
msgstr ""
"專案翻譯記憶檢視也允許重建部分或完整的專案翻譯記憶。所選元件或專案的現有條目"
"被刪除，記憶庫在後臺從目前翻譯再次被填充。"

#: admin/memory.rst:219
msgid ""
"Several management commands can manipulate translation memory content. These "
"operate on the translation memory as a whole, unfiltered by scopes (unless "
"requested by parameters):"
msgstr ""
"有幾個管理指令可以控制翻譯記憶的內容。這些指令將翻譯記憶視同一個整體進行操"
"作，不受範圍影響（除非透過引數進行請求）："

#: admin/memory.rst:224
msgid "Exports the memory into JSON"
msgstr "匯出記憶至 JSON"

#: admin/memory.rst:226
msgid "Imports TMX or JSON files into the translation memory"
msgstr "將 TMX 或 JSON 檔案匯入翻譯記憶"

#: admin/memory.rst:228
msgid "Removes all entries with pending status from the translation memory"
msgstr "從翻譯記憶中移除所有狀態為待處理的項目"

#: admin/memory.rst:232
msgid ""
"The Weblate API covers the translation memory. This allows automated "
"manipulation for different purposes, or based on events in the translation "
"cycle."
msgstr ""
"Weblate API 涵蓋了翻譯記憶。這允許出於不同目的或基於翻譯週期事件的自動操控。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:2
msgid "Optional Weblate modules"
msgstr "選用 Weblate 模組"

#: admin/optionals.rst:4
msgid "Several optional modules are available for your setup."
msgstr "您的安裝環境可使用多個選用模組。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:9
msgid "Git exporter"
msgstr "Git 匯出器"

#: admin/optionals.rst:11
msgid ""
"Provides you read-only access to the underlying Git repository using HTTP(S)."
msgstr "使用 HTTP(S) 為您提供對底層 Git 儲存庫的唯讀存取。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:16
msgid "Add ``weblate.gitexport`` to installed apps in :file:`settings.py`:"
msgstr ""
"將 ``weblate.gitexport`` 加入 :file:`settings.py` 的已安裝應用程式清單："

#: admin/optionals.rst:22
msgid ""
"Export existing repositories by migrating your database after installation:"
msgstr "透過安裝後移轉資料庫，將現有的儲存庫匯出："

#: admin/optionals.rst:30
msgid ""
"Git exporter is turned on in our official Docker image. To turn it off, use:"
msgstr "Git 匯出器在我們的官方 Docker 映像中處於開啟狀態。要關閉它，使用："

#: admin/optionals.rst:37 admin/optionals.rst:104 admin/optionals.rst:212
#: faq.rst:340
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "使用"

#: admin/optionals.rst:39
msgid ""
"The module automatically hooks into Weblate and sets the exported repository "
"URL in the :ref:`component`. The repositories are accessible under the ``/"
"git/`` part of the Weblate URL, for example ``https://example.org/git/"
"weblate/main/``."
msgstr ""
"模組自動鉤入 Weblate，並且在 :ref:`component` 中設定匯出儲存庫 URL。儲存庫在 "
"Weblate URL的 ``/git/`` 部分下是可以存取的，例如 ``https://example.org/git/"
"weblate/main/``。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:44
msgid ""
"Repositories for publicly available projects can be cloned without "
"authentication:"
msgstr "公開可用專案的儲存庫可以被複製而無需認證："

#: admin/optionals.rst:50
msgid ""
"Access to browse the repositories with restricted access (with "
"`Private` :ref:`access control <acl>` or when :setting:`REQUIRE_LOGIN` is "
"enabled) requires an API token which can be obtained in your :ref:`user "
"profile <user-profile>`:"
msgstr ""
"受限瀏覽儲存庫的權限（對於 `私密` :ref:`存取控制 <acl>` 專案或者當開"
"啟 :setting:`REQUIRE_LOGIN` 時）需要可在 :ref:`使用者個人資料 <user-"
"profile>` 獲得的 API 權杖："

#: admin/optionals.rst:63
msgid ""
"By default members of :guilabel:`Users` group and anonymous user have access "
"to the repositories for public projects via :guilabel:`Access repository` "
"and :guilabel:`Power user` roles."
msgstr ""
"預設情況下，:guilabel:`使用者` 群組的使用者與匿名使用者預設透過 :guilabel:`存"
"取儲存庫` 和 :guilabel:`高階使用者` 角色存取公開專案。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:71 admin/workspaces.rst:269
msgid "Billing"
msgstr "帳單"

#: admin/optionals.rst:73
msgid ""
"This is used on `Hosted Weblate <https://weblate.org/hosting/>`_ to define "
"billing plans, track invoices and usage limits."
msgstr ""
"這在 `Hosted Weblate <https://weblate.org/hosting/>`_ 上用於確定付費套餐、跟"
"蹤發票和使用限制。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:79
msgid "1. Add ``weblate.billing`` to installed apps in :file:`settings.py`:"
msgstr ""
"1. 在 :file:`settings.py` 中將 ``weblate.billing`` 新增到安裝的應用中："

#: admin/optionals.rst:86 admin/optionals.rst:186
msgid ""
"Run the database migration to optionally install additional database "
"structures for the module:"
msgstr "執行資料庫移轉，以選擇性安裝模組所需的額外資料庫結構："

#: admin/optionals.rst:93
msgid "Billing plan creation and assignment"
msgstr "付費套餐建立和分配"

#: admin/optionals.rst:95
msgid ""
"You first need to create a billing plan to activate billing. Navigate to the "
"`Administration` section (represented by the wrench icon) and open the "
"`Tools` screen. From there, proceed to the `Django admin interface`."
msgstr ""
"您必須先建立計費方案，才能啟用計費功能。前往 `管理` 區段（扳手圖示）並開啟 `"
"工具` 畫面，再進入 `Django 管理介面`。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:97
msgid ""
"In the Django admin interface, locate the `BILLING` section and add a "
"billing plan. For instance, you can add a `Free` plan with no cost."
msgstr ""
"在 Django 管理介面中找到 `BILLING` 區段，然後新增計費方案。例如，可以新增費用"
"為零的 `Free` 方案。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:99
msgid ""
"If you wish to assign a billing plan to an existing project, this can also "
"be done within the `Django admin interface` using the `Customer billings` "
"option."
msgstr ""
"若要將計費方案指派給既有專案，也可以在 `Django 管理介面` 中使用 `Customer "
"billings` 選項完成。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:101
msgid ""
"Lastly, the `Django admin interface` provides an `Invoice` option for "
"logging your customer payments."
msgstr "最後，`Django 管理介面` 提供 `發票` 選項用於記錄您的客戶付款。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:106
msgid ""
"After installation you can control billing in the admin interface. Users "
"with billing enabled will get new :guilabel:`Billing` tab in "
"their :ref:`user-profile`."
msgstr ""
"安裝後您可以在管理介面控制帳單。啟用了帳單模組的使用者將在他們的 :ref:`user-"
"profile` 中看到新的 :guilabel:`帳單` 分頁。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:110
msgid ""
"The billing module additionally allows users to create new projects and "
"components without being superusers (see :ref:`adding-projects`). This is "
"possible when following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"此外，計費模組允許非超級使用者建立新專案及元件（請參閱 :ref:`adding-"
"projects`）。必須符合下列條件："

#: admin/optionals.rst:114
msgid ""
"The billing is in its configured limits (any overusage results in blocking "
"of project/component creation) and paid (if its price is non zero)"
msgstr ""
"計費用量仍在設定限制內（超額使用會阻止建立專案或元件），而且已付款（如果方案"
"費用不為零）"

#: admin/optionals.rst:116
msgid ""
"The user has :guilabel:`Add projects to workspace` permission for the "
"workspace covered by the billing plan."
msgstr ""
"使用者對計費方案涵蓋的工作空間具備 :guilabel:`新增專案至工作空間` 權限。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:119
msgid ""
"Upon project creation user is able to choose which workspace should contain "
"the project. Projects created in a workspace with billing count against the "
"billing plan assigned to that workspace. Users with the :guilabel:`Edit "
"workspace settings` permission can view and pay the billing plan; billing "
"notification e-mails are sent to these users. See :ref:`workspace-billing` "
"for details."
msgstr ""
"建立專案時，使用者可以選擇專案所屬的工作空間。在有計費功能的工作空間中建立的"
"專案，會計入指派給該工作空間的計費方案。具備 :guilabel:`編輯工作空間設定` 權"
"限的使用者可以檢視及支付計費方案；計費通知電子郵件會寄給這些使用者。詳細資訊"
"請參閱 :ref:`workspace-billing`。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:129
msgid "Legal module"
msgstr "法律模組"

#: admin/optionals.rst:131
msgid ""
"This is used on `Hosted Weblate <https://weblate.org/hosting/>`_ to provide "
"required legal documents. It comes provided with blank documents, and you "
"are expected to fill out the following templates in the documents:"
msgstr ""
"這用在 `Hosted Weblate <https://weblate.org/hosting/>`_ 上，來提供所需的法律"
"檔案。它開始時提供空白文件，會希望您填充文件中後面的範本："

#: admin/optionals.rst:136
msgid "Terms of service document"
msgstr "服務條款文件"

#: admin/optionals.rst:138
msgid "Privacy policy document"
msgstr "隱私政策文件"

#: admin/optionals.rst:140
msgid "Short overview of the terms of service and privacy policy"
msgstr "服務條款與隱私政策的簡短概覽"

#: admin/optionals.rst:142
msgid "Subcontractor information"
msgstr "分包商資訊"

#: admin/optionals.rst:144
msgid ""
"The legal module embeds these templates inside Weblate and uses :file:`legal/"
"documents/tos.html` for terms of service confirmation. This is separate "
"from :setting:`LEGAL_URL` and :setting:`PRIVACY_URL`, which are meant for "
"linking to externally hosted legal documents from the footer when the legal "
"module is not enabled. When the legal module is enabled, Weblate links to "
"the internal legal pages by default."
msgstr ""
"法律模組會將這些範本嵌入 Weblate，並使用 :file:`legal/documents/tos.html` 進"
"行服務條款確認。這與 :setting:`LEGAL_URL` 和 :setting:`PRIVACY_URL` 不同；未"
"啟用法律模組時，後兩者用於從頁尾連結至外部託管的法律檔案。啟用法律模組時，"
"Weblate 預設會連結至內部法律頁面。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:151
msgid ""
"On changing the terms of service documents, please "
"adjust :setting:`LEGAL_TOS_DATE` so that users are forced to agree with the "
"updated documents."
msgstr ""
"變更服務條款文件時，請調整 :setting:`LEGAL_TOS_DATE` 迫使使用者接受更新的文"
"件。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:157
msgid ""
"Legal documents for the Hosted Weblate service operated by Weblate s.r.o. "
"are available in this Git repository: <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/wllegal/"
"tree/main/wllegal/templates/legal/documents>."
msgstr ""
"可以在這個 Git 儲存庫 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/wllegal/tree/main/"
"wllegal/templates/legal/documents> 中取得 Weblate s.r.o. 運營的 Hosted "
"Weblate 的法律檔案。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:161
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The bundled terms of service and related legal documents are specific to "
#| "that service and are not intended for general use. They might still come "
#| "in handy as a starting point if adjusted to meet your needs."
msgid ""
"The bundled terms of service and related legal documents are specific to "
"services operated by Weblate s.r.o. They can serve as an implementation "
"example, but should not be used as a basis for legal documents of other "
"services."
msgstr ""
"捆綁的服務條款和相關法律文件僅針對該服務，不用於一般用途。但如果進行調整來滿"
"足您的需求，它們作為起點仍然可能派得上用處。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:169
msgid "1. Add ``weblate.legal`` to installed apps in :file:`settings.py`:"
msgstr ""
"1. 將 ``weblate.legal`` 加入 :file:`settings.py` 的已安裝應用程式清單："

#: admin/optionals.rst:192
msgid ""
"Provide legal document templates matching your service, as described "
"in :ref:`legal-customization`."
msgstr ""

#: admin/optionals.rst:197
msgid ""
"In Docker deployments, enable the legal module "
