"python/customize/templates/legal/documents`, see :ref:`docker-static-"
"override`."
msgstr ""
"在 Docker 部署中，用 :envvar:`WEBLATE_LEGAL_INTEGRATION` 開啟法律模組而不是編"
"輯 :file:`settings.py`。用 ``tos-confirm`` 啟用法律模組和服務條款確認強制，或"
"者用 ``wllegal`` 額外載入Weblate s.r.o. 運營服務使用的託管的法律檔案範本。這"
"些範本不用於一般用途。要在 Docker 中提供自己的範本，請將它們放在 :file:`/app/"
"data/python/customize/templates/legal/documents` 中, 見 :ref:`docker-static-"
"override`。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:207
msgid ""
"Recreate the Docker container after changing environment variables, for "
"example using :program:`docker compose up -d`. Restarting an existing "
"container does not apply changed environment values."
msgstr ""
"變更環境變數後，請重新建立 Docker 容器，例如使用 :program:`docker compose up "
"-d`。重新啟動既有容器不會套用已變更的環境值。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:214
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "After installation and editing, the legal documents are shown in the "
#| "Weblate UI."
msgid ""
"After installation and customization, the legal documents are shown in the "
