msgstr "安裝並編輯後，法律檔案顯示在 Weblate 介面中。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:216
msgid ""
"The legal document templates are regular Django templates. Text is "
"translated only when you use Django translation tags such as ``{% translate "
"%}`` or ``{% blocktranslate %}``; plain HTML text is shown as written."
msgstr ""
"法律文件範本是一般 Django 範本。只有使用 ``{% translate %}`` 或 ``{% "
"blocktranslate %}`` 等 Django 翻譯標籤時才會翻譯文字；純 HTML 文字會依原樣顯"
"示。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:220
msgid ""
"Legal pages and the sign-in and registration overview provide ``terms_url`` "
"and ``privacy_url`` variables for linking to the terms of service and "
"privacy policy documents."
msgstr ""
"法律頁面及登入與註冊概覽會提供 ``terms_url`` 和 ``privacy_url`` 變數，用於連"
"結至服務條款和隱私權政策文件。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:227
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Customizing behavior using flags"
msgid "Customizing legal documents and styles"
msgstr "使用旗標自訂行為"

#: admin/optionals.rst:229
msgid ""
"Provide your own legal documents by overriding these templates in "
"a :ref:`custom-module`:"
msgstr ""

#: admin/optionals.rst:239
msgid ""
"Place the customization app before ``weblate.legal`` and any other app "
"providing legal template overrides in :setting:`django:INSTALLED_APPS` so "
"that Django selects its templates. Only templates you provide are "
"overridden; the remaining legal templates continue to use the defaults from "
"later apps."
msgstr ""

#: admin/optionals.rst:244
msgid ""
"The :file:`legal/styles.html` template is included in the HTML head of every "
"legal page. Use it to load a stylesheet from your customization app:"
msgstr ""

#: admin/optionals.rst:253
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Run :samp:`weblate collectstatic --noinput`, to collect static files "
#| "served to clients."
msgid ""
"Run :samp:`weblate collectstatic --noinput` after adding or changing the "
"static file."
msgstr ""
"執行 :samp:`weblate collectstatic --noinput`，來收集提供給用戶端的靜態檔案。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:256
msgid ""
"In Docker deployments, place document templates in :file:`/app/data/python/"
"customize/templates/legal/documents`, :file:`styles.html` in :file:`/app/"
"data/python/customize/templates/legal/styles.html`, and the stylesheet "
"in :file:`/app/data/python/customize/static/legal.css`. The stylesheet "
"template then uses ``{% static 'legal.css' %}``. Restart the container to "
"apply the changes, see :ref:`docker-static-override`."
msgstr ""

#: admin/optionals.rst:264
msgid ""
"By default, legal document wrappers use the ``tos`` CSS class. Weblate does "
"not attach any styling to this class; target it from your custom stylesheet, "
"or set :setting:`LEGAL_DOCUMENT_CSS_CLASS` to another class matching your "
"document markup. Set the setting to an empty string if no wrapper class is "
"needed."
msgstr ""

#: admin/optionals.rst:269
msgid ""
"Use :setting:`LEGAL_HIDDEN_DOCUMENTS` to hide optional legal pages such as "
"subcontractors from the legal menu. Hidden pages return a 404 response when "
"requested directly. If ``terms`` or ``privacy`` is hidden, links using "
"``terms_url`` or ``privacy_url`` fall back to :setting:`LEGAL_URL` "
"or :setting:`PRIVACY_URL` when configured, otherwise the link is omitted."
msgstr ""
"使用 :setting:`LEGAL_HIDDEN_DOCUMENTS`，從法律選單隱藏分包商等選用法律頁面。"
"直接要求隱藏頁面時會傳回 404 回應。如果隱藏 ``terms`` 或 ``privacy``，則使用 "
"``terms_url`` 或 ``privacy_url`` 的連結會在已設定時退回使"
"用 :setting:`LEGAL_URL` 或 :setting:`PRIVACY_URL`，否則會省略連結。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:275
msgid ""
"To use externally hosted legal documents with terms confirmation, "
"configure :setting:`LEGAL_HIDDEN_DOCUMENTS` to hide ``terms`` and "
"``privacy`` and set :setting:`LEGAL_URL` and :setting:`PRIVACY_URL`. The "
"confirmation page then links to those external documents without requiring "
"a :file:`legal/documents/tos.html` template override."
msgstr ""
"若要搭配條款確認功能使用外部託管的法律檔案，請設"
"定 :setting:`LEGAL_HIDDEN_DOCUMENTS` 以隱藏 ``terms`` 和 ``privacy``，並設"
"定 :setting:`LEGAL_URL` 和 :setting:`PRIVACY_URL`。確認頁面隨後會連結至這些外"
"部檔案，而不需要覆寫 :file:`legal/documents/tos.html` 範本。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:284
msgid "Avatars"
msgstr "頭像"

#: admin/optionals.rst:286
msgid ""
"Avatars are downloaded and cached server-side to reduce information leaks to "
"the sites serving them by default. The built-in support for fetching avatars "
"from e-mails addresses configured for it can be turned off "
"using :setting:`ENABLE_AVATARS`."
msgstr ""
"頭像在伺服器端下載並快取，來減少對預設服務的網站的洩露。透過為其設定的電子郵"
"件地址來取回頭像的內建支援，可以使用 :setting:`ENABLE_AVATARS` 來關閉。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:290
msgid "Weblate currently supports:"
msgstr "Weblate 目前支援："

#: admin/optionals.rst:292
msgid "`Gravatar <https://gravatar.com/>`_"
msgstr "`Gravatar <https://gravatar.com/>`_"

#: admin/optionals.rst:293
msgid "`Libravatar <https://www.libravatar.org/>`_"
msgstr "`Libravatar <https://www.libravatar.org/>`_"

#: admin/optionals.rst:306
msgid ""
"The :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.cdnjs` and :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.files` add-"
"ons write files to :setting:`LOCALIZE_CDN_PATH`; Weblate does not serve "
"them. Configure the web server or CDN serving :setting:`LOCALIZE_CDN_URL` as "
"a public, read-only static file host."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.cdnjs` 和 :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.files` 附加元件會將"
"檔案寫入 :setting:`LOCALIZE_CDN_PATH`；Weblate 不會提供這些檔案。請將提"
"供 :setting:`LOCALIZE_CDN_URL` 的網頁伺服器或 CDN 設定為公開且唯讀的靜態檔案"
"主機。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:311
msgid ""
"Treat every published CDN file as public. The add-on specific UUID in the "
"URL is not an access-control mechanism. Do not enable CDN add-ons for "
"components that contain private strings, unreleased product text, customer "
"data, internal URLs, API examples, repository paths, translator comments, or "
"file-format metadata that should not be exposed."
msgstr ""
"請將每個已發佈的 CDN 檔案視為公開資料。URL 中附加元件專用的 UUID 不是存取控制"
"機制。請勿對包含私人字串、尚未發行的產品文字、客戶資料、內部 URL、API 範例、"
"儲存庫路徑、翻譯者註解，或不應公開的檔案格式中繼資料之元件啟用 CDN 附加元件。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:317
msgid ""
"The :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.files` add-on publishes raw translation files in "
"formats supported by Weblate. Some formats can be interpreted by browsers or "
"other clients as HTML, SVG, XML, JavaScript, YAML, or application-specific "
"configuration. Serve the CDN from a dedicated domain that is separate from "
"Weblate and from the application consuming the translations. Do not share "
"authentication cookies with the CDN domain."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.files` 附加元件會以 Weblate 支援的格式發佈原始翻譯檔"
"案。瀏覽器或其他用戶端可能會將部分格式解讀為 HTML、SVG、XML、JavaScript、"
"YAML 或特定應用程式的設定。請從與 Weblate 及翻譯使用端應用程式分離的專用網域"
"提供 CDN。請勿與 CDN 網域共用驗證 Cookie。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:324
msgid "Recommended server configuration:"
msgstr "建議的伺服器設定："

#: admin/optionals.rst:326
msgid ""
"Serve only the directory configured by :setting:`LOCALIZE_CDN_PATH`; do not "
"expose Weblate repositories, backups, media, configuration, or the whole "
"data directory."
msgstr ""
"只提供 :setting:`LOCALIZE_CDN_PATH` 所設定的目錄；請勿公開 Weblate 儲存庫、備"
"份、媒體、設定或整個資料目錄。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:329
msgid "Disable directory listing."
msgstr "停用目錄列舉。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:330
msgid "Use HTTPS and make the CDN host read-only from the web server."
msgstr "使用 HTTPS 並使網路伺服器對 CDN 主機唯讀。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:331
msgid "Send :http:header:`X-Content-Type-Options` with ``nosniff``."
msgstr "傳送值為 ``nosniff`` 的 :http:header:`X-Content-Type-Options`。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:332
msgid ""
"Configure conservative MIME types. Serve unknown translation formats "
"as :mimetype:`text/plain` or :mimetype:`application/octet-stream`; only "
"serve :file:`weblate.js` as JavaScript."
msgstr ""
"採用保守的 MIME 類型設定。將未知翻譯格式以 :mimetype:`text/plain` "
"或 :mimetype:`application/octet-stream` 提供；只有 :file:`weblate.js` 應以 "
"JavaScript 提供。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:335
msgid ""
"For raw translation formats that are not intended to be rendered in a "
"browser, consider adding :http:header:`Content-Disposition` with "
"``attachment``."
msgstr ""
"對於不應在瀏覽器中轉譯的原始翻譯格式，請考慮新增值為 ``attachment`` "
"的 :http:header:`Content-Disposition`。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:338
msgid ""
"Configure ``Access-Control-Allow-Origin`` only for sites that need browser "
"access to the files."
msgstr "只為需要從瀏覽器存取檔案的網站設定 ``Access-Control-Allow-Origin``。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:340
msgid ""
"Set cache lifetimes that match your update expectations, and purge CDN "
"caches when stale translations must disappear quickly."
msgstr ""
"設定符合更新需求的快取存留時間，並在過時翻譯必須迅速消失時清除 CDN 快取。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:343
msgid ""
"The following nginx snippet serves only the configured CDN directory and "
"applies conservative defaults for raw translation files:"
msgstr ""
"下列 nginx 程式碼片段只提供已設定的 CDN 目錄，並對原始翻譯檔案套用保守的預設"
"值："

#: admin/optionals.rst:359
msgid "Signing Git commits with GnuPG"
msgstr "使用 GnuPG 為 Git 提交簽名"

#: admin/optionals.rst:361
msgid "All commits can be signed by the GnuPG key of the Weblate instance."
msgstr "所有的提交均可由 Weblate 執行個體的 GnuPG 金鑰為其簽名。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:363
msgid ""
"Turn on :setting:`WEBLATE_GPG_IDENTITY`. (Weblate will generate a GnuPG key "
"when needed and will use it to sign all translation commits.)"
msgstr ""
"開啟 :setting:`WEBLATE_GPG_IDENTITY`。（Weblate 將在需要時產生一個 GnuPG 金"
"鑰，並使用它為所有的翻譯提交簽名。）"

#: admin/optionals.rst:366
msgid "This feature needs GnuPG 2.1 or newer installed."
msgstr "這個特性需要安裝 GnuPG 2.1 或更新版。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:368
msgid ""
"You can find the key in the :setting:`DATA_DIR` and the public key is shown "
"on the \"About\" page:"
msgstr ""
"您可以在 :setting:`DATA_DIR` 中找到金鑰，而公開金鑰顯示在“關於”頁面上："

#: admin/optionals.rst:373
msgid ""
"Alternatively you can also import existing keys into Weblate, just set "
"``HOME=$DATA_DIR/home`` when invoking gpg."
msgstr ""
"另外您還可以將現有的金鑰匯入 Weblate 中，當呼叫 pgp 時只設定 "
"``HOME=$DATA_DIR/home``。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:378
msgid ""
"The key material is cached by Weblate for a long period. In case you let "
"Weblate generate a key with :setting:`WEBLATE_GPG_IDENTITY` and then import "
"key with the same identity to use an existing key, purging redis cache is "
"recommended to see the effect of such change."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 會將關鍵材料快取很長一段時間。如果您透"
"過 :setting:`WEBLATE_GPG_IDENTITY` 讓 Weblate 產生一個金鑰，接著用相同身分匯"
"入金鑰來使用現有金鑰的話，建議清空 redis 快取來檢視此類變更的效果。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:386
msgid ""
"When sharing :setting:`DATA_DIR` between multiple hosts, please follow "
"instructions at https://wiki.gnupg.org/NFS to make GnuPG signing work "
"reliably."
msgstr ""
"在多個主機間共享 :setting:`DATA_DIR` 時，請遵照 https://wiki.gnupg.org/NFS 說"
"明讓 GnuPG 簽名可靠地工作。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:396 user/translating.rst:489
msgid "Rate limiting"
msgstr "速率限制"

#: admin/optionals.rst:400
msgid "The rate limiting no longer applies to signed in superusers."
msgstr "速率限制不再適用於已登入的超級使用者。"

#: admin/optionals.rst:402
msgid ""
"Several operations in Weblate are rate limited. Rate limits are evaluated "
"independently for each scope. At most :setting:`RATELIMIT_ATTEMPTS` attempts "
"are allowed within :setting:`RATELIMIT_WINDOW` seconds in one scope. That "
"scope is then blocked for :setting:`RATELIMIT_LOCKOUT`; Weblate does not "
"turn this into a sitewide temporary IP ban. Exceeding one scope, such as "
"``TRANSLATE`` or ``SEARCH``, does not by itself block unrelated scopes such "
"as ``LOGIN`` or ``SECOND_FACTOR``. There are also settings specific to "
"scopes, for example ``RATELIMIT_CONTACT_ATTEMPTS`` or "
"``RATELIMIT_TRANSLATE_ATTEMPTS``. The table below is a full list of "
"available scopes."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 中有幾個操作受速率限制。每個範圍的速率限制單獨評估。一個範圍"
"中，:setting:`RATELIMIT_WINDOW` 秒內最多允許 :setting:`RATELIMIT_ATTEMPTS` 次"
"嘗試。超過這個速率會因 :setting:`RATELIMIT_LOCKOUT` 而封禁那個範圍；Weblate "
"不會將單一範圍的封禁轉變為整個網站的 IP 封鎖。超出單一範圍， 如 "
"``TRANSLATE`` 或 ``SEARCH`` 的限制也不會造成 ``LOGIN`` 或 ``SECOND_FACTOR`` "
"等不相關範圍被封禁。此外，還有適用特定範圍的設定，例如 "
"``RATELIMIT_CONTACT_ATTEMPTS`` 或 ``RATELIMIT_TRANSLATE_ATTEMPTS`` 。下方表格"
"是可用範圍的完整清單。"

