#: admin/projects.rst:2 user/translating.rst:24
msgid "Translation projects"
msgstr "翻譯專案"

#: admin/projects.rst:5
msgid "Translation organization"
msgstr "翻譯組織"

#: admin/projects.rst:7
msgid ""
"Weblate organizes translatable VCS content of project/components into a tree-"
"like structure. You can additionally organize components within a project "
"using categories."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 將專案/元件的可翻譯版本控制系統內容組織成樹狀結構。您還可以使用類別來"
"組織專案內的元件。"

#: admin/projects.rst:11
msgid ""
"The bottom level object is :ref:`project`, which should hold all "
"translations belonging together (for example translation of an application "
"in several versions and/or accompanying documentation)."
msgstr ""
"底層對像是 :ref:`project`，該專案設定應將所有翻譯歸在一起（例如，多個版本的應"
"用程式翻譯和/或隨附的文件）。"

#: admin/projects.rst:15
msgid ""
"The middle level is optionally created by :ref:`category`. The categories "
"can be nested to achieve more complex structure."
msgstr ""
"您可以選擇透過 :ref:`category` 建立該中間層級。可以巢狀類別來達成更復雜的結"
"構。"

#: admin/projects.rst:18
msgid ""
"On the level above, :ref:`component`, which is actually the component to "
"translate, you define the VCS repository to use, and the mask of files to "
"translate."
msgstr ""
"在上面的層級上，即 :ref:`component`，實際上是要翻譯的元件，您定義要使用的版本"
"控制系統儲存庫以及要翻譯的檔案掩碼。"

#: admin/projects.rst:22
msgid ""
"Above :ref:`component` there are individual translations, handled "
"automatically by Weblate as translation files (which match :ref:`component-"
"filemask` defined in :ref:`component`) appear in the VCS repository."
msgstr ""
"在 :ref:`component` 上方有單獨的翻譯，當版本控制系統儲存庫中出現翻譯檔案"
"（與 :ref:`component` 中定義的 :ref:`component-filemask` 相符）時，Weblate 會"
"自動處理這些翻譯。"

#: admin/projects.rst:25
msgid ""
"Weblate supports a wide range of translation formats (both bilingual and "
"monolingual ones) supported by Translate Toolkit, see :ref:`formats`."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 支援 Translate Toolkit 支援的多種翻譯格式（雙語言和單語言），請參"
"閱 :ref:`formats`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:30
msgid ""
"You can share cloned VCS repositories using :ref:`internal-urls`. Using this "
"feature is highly recommended when you have many components sharing the same "
"VCS. It improves performance and decreases required disk space."
msgstr ""
"您可以使用 :ref:`internal-urls` 共享複製的版本控制系統儲存庫。當您有許多共享"
"同一版本控制系統的元件時，強烈建議使用此功能。它提高了效能並減少了所需的磁碟"
"空間。"

#: admin/projects.rst:38
msgid "Adding translation projects and components"
msgstr "新增翻譯專案和元件"

#: admin/projects.rst:40
msgid ""
"Based on your permissions, new translation projects and components can be "
"created. It is always permitted for users with the :guilabel:`Add new "
"projects` permission, and if your instance uses billing (e.g. like https://"
"hosted.weblate.org/ see :ref:`billing`), you can also create those based on "
"your plans allowance from the user account that manages billing. Projects "
"can also be created in a workspace by users who have the :guilabel:`Add "
"projects to workspace` permission in that workspace. Creating a project "
"without selecting a workspace requires the site-wide :guilabel:`Add new "
"projects` permission. See :ref:`workspace-project-creation` for details."
msgstr ""
"使用者能否建立新的翻譯專案及元件取決於其權限。具備 :guilabel:`新增專案` 權限"
"的使用者一律可以建立；如果執行個體使用計費功能（例如 https://"
"hosted.weblate.org/，請參閱 :ref:`billing`），管理計費的使用者帳號也能依方案"
"額度建立。具備工作空間 :guilabel:`新增專案至工作空間` 權限的使用者，也能在該"
"工作空間建立專案。建立不屬於工作空間的專案，則需要全站 :guilabel:`新增專案` "
"權限。詳細資訊請參閱 :ref:`workspace-project-creation`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:53
msgid ""
"To grant every user permission to create new projects create "
"new :ref:`autoteam` for the :guilabel:`Project creators` team."
msgstr ""
"要授予每名使用者建立新專案的權限，請為 :guilabel:`專案建立者` 團隊建立新"
"的 :ref:`autoteam`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:56
msgid "You can view your current billing plan on a separate page:"
msgstr "您可以在單獨的頁面上查看目前的結算方案："

#: admin/projects.rst:60
msgid ""
"The project creation can be initiated from there, or using the menu in the "
"navigation bar, filling in basic info about the translation project to "
"complete addition of it:"
msgstr ""
"您可以從此處開始建立專案，也可以使用導覽條中的選單來填寫翻譯專案的基本資訊以"
"完成新增："

#: admin/projects.rst:65
