#: admin/projects.rst:279
msgid ""
"Enforce :ref:`2fa` for all contributors. Users won’t be allowed to perform "
"any operations within the project without having it configured."
msgstr ""
"強制所有貢獻者使用 :ref:`2fa`。不設定雙因素認證，使用者將不會被允許在專案內執"
"行任何操作。"

#: admin/projects.rst:285 workflows.rst:121 workflows.rst:153 workflows.rst:186
msgid "Enable reviews"
msgstr "啟用檢閱"

#: admin/projects.rst:287
msgid "Enable review workflow for translations, see :ref:`reviews`."
msgstr "允許稽核翻譯的工作流程，請參閱 :ref:`reviews`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:297
msgid "Enable source reviews"
msgstr "啟用來源檢閱"

#: admin/projects.rst:299
msgid "Enable review workflow for source strings, see :ref:`source-reviews`."
msgstr "啟用檢閱來源字串的工作流程，參閱 :ref:`source-reviews`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:310
msgid "Translation quality filter"
msgstr "翻譯品質過濾器"

#: admin/projects.rst:314
msgid ""
"The commit policy determines which translations are included when committing "
"changes to the version control system. This setting is available at the "
"project level and supports the following options:"
msgstr ""
"提交政策決定了提交變更到版本控制系統時會包括哪些譯文。此設定在專案範圍可用並"
"支援以下選項："

#: admin/projects.rst:318
msgid ""
"**Commit all translations regardless of quality**: All translations will be "
"committed, including those marked as needing editing or not reviewed."
msgstr ""
"**不論品質如何提交所有譯文**：所有譯文將被提交，包括那些被標記為需要編輯或未"
"稽核的譯文。"

#: admin/projects.rst:320
msgid ""
"**Skip translations marked as needing editing**: Only translations that "
"don't have the \"needs editing\", \"needs rewriting\" or \"needs checking\" "
"state will be committed."
msgstr ""
"**跳過被標記為需要編輯的譯文**：僅提交沒有“需要編輯“、”需要重寫“或”需要檢查"
"“狀態的譯文。"

#: admin/projects.rst:322
msgid ""
"**Only include approved translations**: Only translations that have been "
"approved by a reviewer will be committed. This option requires :ref:`project-"
"translation_review` to be enabled."
msgstr ""
"**只包括已核准的譯文**：只有稽核者已核准的譯文會被提交。此選項要求啟"
"用 :ref:`project-translation_review`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:330
msgid "Enable hooks"
msgstr "啟用掛勾"

#: admin/projects.rst:332
msgid ""
"Whether unauthenticated :ref:`hooks` are to be used for this repository."
msgstr "是否將未經身分驗證的 :ref:`hooks` 用於此儲存庫。"

#: admin/projects.rst:344
msgid "Language aliases"
msgstr "語言別名"

#: admin/projects.rst:346
msgid ""
"Define language codes mapping when importing translations into Weblate. Use "
"this when language codes are inconsistent in your repositories and you want "
"to get a consistent view in Weblate or in case you want to use non-standard "
"naming of your translation files."
msgstr ""
"將翻譯匯入到 Weblate 時定義語言代碼映射。當您的儲存庫中的語言代碼不一致，並且"
"您希望在 Weblate 中獲得一致的檢視，或者如果您想使用翻譯檔案的非標準命名時，可"
"以使用此方法。"

#: admin/projects.rst:351
msgid ""
"The typical use case might be mapping American English to English: "
"``en_US:en``"
msgstr "典型的使用情況會是將 美國英語映射到英語：``en_US:en``"

#: admin/projects.rst:353
msgid "Multiple mappings to be separated by comma: ``en_GB:en,en_US:en``"
msgstr "由逗號分隔的多個映射：``en_GB:en,en_US:en``"

#: admin/projects.rst:355
msgid "Using non standard code: ``ia_FOO:ia``"
msgstr "使用非標準編碼：``ia_FOO:ia``"

#: admin/projects.rst:359
msgid ""
"The language codes are mapped when matching the translation files and the "
"matches are case sensitive, so ensure you use the source language codes in "
"same form as used in the filenames."
msgstr ""
"當相符翻譯檔案時映射語言代碼，並且映射是大小寫敏感的，所以您確保使用與檔案名"
"稱中使用的形式相同的來源語言代碼。"

#: admin/projects.rst:372 admin/projects.rst:906 admin/workspaces.rst:119
msgid "Adding new translation"
msgstr "加入新翻譯"

#: admin/projects.rst:374
msgid ""
"Default behavior for requests to create new translations in components in "
"this project."
msgstr "在此專案元件中建立新翻譯的請求的預設行為。"

#: admin/projects.rst:385 admin/projects.rst:971 admin/workspaces.rst:132
msgid "Language code style"
msgstr "語言代碼類型"

#: admin/projects.rst:387
msgid ""
"Default language code style for translations created by Weblate in "
"components in this project."
msgstr "Weblate 在此專案元件中建立的翻譯的預設語言程式碼樣式。"

#: admin/projects.rst:398 admin/projects.rst:1224 admin/workspaces.rst:145
msgid "Secondary language"
msgstr "第二語言"

#: admin/projects.rst:402 admin/projects.rst:1228
msgid ""
"Additional language to show together with the source language while "
"translating."
msgstr "翻譯時，在來源語言旁另外顯示的語言。"

#: admin/projects.rst:404 admin/projects.rst:1230
msgid ""
"Optionally, it can be also used as a source for the machine translation."
msgstr "或者，它也可以用作機器翻譯的來源。"

#: admin/projects.rst:415 admin/projects.rst:857 admin/translating.rst:84
#: admin/workspaces.rst:159 formats.rst:105
msgid "Translation flags"
msgstr "翻譯旗標"

#: admin/projects.rst:419 admin/projects.rst:859 admin/translating.rst:86
msgid ""
"Customization of quality checks and other Weblate behavior, see :ref:`custom-"
"checks`."
msgstr "品質檢查和其他 Weblate 行為的自訂，請參閱 :ref:`custom-checks`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:421 admin/projects.rst:861
msgid "Workspace, project, component, and translation flags are merged."
msgstr "合併了工作空間、專案、元件和翻譯標記。"

#: admin/projects.rst:435 admin/projects.rst:1063 admin/workspaces.rst:177
msgid "Commit, add, delete, merge, add-on, and merge request messages"
msgstr "提交、新增、刪除、合併、附加元件與合併請求訊息"

#: admin/projects.rst:437
msgid ""
"Default commit and merge request message templates for components in this "
"project."
msgstr "此專案中各元件的預設提交與合併請求訊息範本。"

#: admin/projects.rst:440
msgid ""
"The default values can be changed "
"by :setting:`DEFAULT_ADD_MESSAGE`, :setting:`DEFAULT_ADDON_MESSAGE`, :setting:`DEFAULT_COMMIT_MESSAGE`, :setting:`DEFAULT_DELETE_MESSAGE`, :setting:`DEFAULT_MERGE_MESSAGE`, :setting:`DEFAULT_PULL_MESSAGE`."
msgstr ""
"預設值可以透"
"過 :setting:`DEFAULT_ADD_MESSAGE` 、 :setting:`DEFAULT_ADDON_MESSAGE` 、 :setting:`DEFAULT_COMMIT_MESSAGE` 、 :setting:`DEFAULT_DELETE_MESSAGE` 、 :setting:`DEFAULT_MERGE_MESSAGE` 、 :setting:`DEFAULT_PULL_MESSAGE` "
"變更。"

#: admin/projects.rst:445 admin/projects.rst:1072
msgid ""
"The built-in defaults follow Conventional Commits and include Weblate links "
"where available. Use :guilabel:`Restore site default` next to a message "
"editor to restore the current installation default for that message; for "
"inherited values, this also disables inheritance for that message."
msgstr ""
"內建預設值遵循 Conventional Commits，並在可用時加入 Weblate 連結。使用訊息編"
"輯器旁的 :guilabel:`還原網站預設值`，可為該訊息還原目前安裝環境的預設值；對於"
"繼承的值，這也會停用該訊息的繼承。"

#: admin/projects.rst:459 devel/sphinx.rst:30
msgid "Component configuration"
msgstr "元件設定"

#: admin/projects.rst:461
msgid ""
"A component is a grouping of something for translation. You enter a VCS "
"repository location and file mask for which files you want translated, and "
"Weblate automatically fetches from this VCS, and finds all matching "
"translatable files."
msgstr ""
"元件是待翻譯內容的群組。您需要輸入 VCS 儲存庫位置，以及指定待翻譯檔案的檔案遮"
"罩；Weblate 會自動從該 VCS 擷取內容，並找出所有相符且可翻譯的檔案。"

#: admin/projects.rst:469
msgid ""
"You can find some examples of typical configurations in the :ref:`formats`."
msgstr "您可以在 :ref:`formats` 中找到一些典型設定範例。"

#: admin/projects.rst:473
msgid ""
"It is recommended to keep translation components to a reasonable size - "
"split the translation by anything that makes sense in your case (individual "
"apps or add-ons, book chapters or websites)."
msgstr ""
"建議將翻譯文件保持在合理的大小——在您的案例中使用任何合理的工具（獨立的 app 或"
"附加元件、書籍的章節或網站）來分割翻譯文件。"

#: admin/projects.rst:477
msgid ""
"Weblate easily handles translations with 10000s of strings, but it is harder "
"to split work and coordinate among translators with such large translation "
"components."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 能夠輕鬆處理 10000 個字串，但大的翻譯元件的分割工作和翻譯者之間的協調"
"更困難。"

#: admin/projects.rst:480
msgid ""
"Should the language definition for a translation be missing, an empty "
"definition is created and named as \"cs_CZ (generated)\". You should adjust "
"the definition and report this back to the Weblate authors, so that the "
"missing languages can be included in next release."
msgstr ""
"如果翻譯的語言定義遺失，會新增一個空的定義，並且命名為 \"cs_CZ (generated)"
"\"。您應該調整定義，並將其回饋給 Weblate 的作者，從而遺失的語言可以包括在下一"
"次的發佈版本中。"

#: admin/projects.rst:485
msgid ""
"The component contains all important parameters for working with the VCS, "
"and for getting translations out of it:"
msgstr "使用版本控制系統工作的所有重要引數都包含在元件中，並且從中取出翻譯："

#: admin/projects.rst:491 admin/projects.rst:1388
msgid "Component name"
msgstr "元件名稱"

#: admin/projects.rst:493
msgid "Verbose component name, used to display the component name."
msgstr "冗長元件名稱，用於顯示元件的名稱。"

#: admin/projects.rst:498 admin/projects.rst:1390
#: snippets/addons-autogenerated.rst:517 snippets/addons-autogenerated.rst:531
msgid "Component slug"
msgstr "元件代稱"

#: admin/projects.rst:500
msgid "Component name suitable for URLs."
msgstr "適用於 URLs 的元件名稱。"

#: admin/projects.rst:505
msgid "Component project"
msgstr "元件專案"

#: admin/projects.rst:507
msgid ":ref:`project` where the component belongs."
msgstr "元件所屬的 :ref:`project`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:512
msgid "Version control system"
msgstr "版本控制系統"

#: admin/projects.rst:514
msgid "VCS to use, see :ref:`vcs` for details."
msgstr "使用的版本控制系統，細節請參閱：:ref:`vcs`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:523 devel/gettext.rst:231
msgid "Source code repository"
msgstr "原始碼儲存庫"

#: admin/projects.rst:525
msgid "VCS repository used to pull changes."
msgstr "版本控制系統儲存庫，用於拉取變更。"

#: admin/projects.rst:529
msgid "See :ref:`vcs-repos` for more details on specifying URLs."
msgstr "指定 URLs 的更多細節請參閱 :ref:`vcs-repos`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:533
msgid ""
"This can either be a real VCS URL or ``weblate://project/component`` "
"indicating that the repository should be shared with another component. "
"See :ref:`internal-urls` for more details."
msgstr ""
"這可以是真實的版本控制系統的 URL，也可以是 ``weblate://project/component``，"
"表示與其他元件共享該儲存庫。更多細節請參閱 :ref:`internal-urls`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:540
msgid "Repository push URL"
msgstr "儲存庫推送 URL"

#: admin/projects.rst:542
msgid ""
"Repository URL used for pushing. The behavior of this depends "
"on :ref:`component-vcs`, and this is in more detail covered in :ref:`code-"
"hosting-push-options`."
msgstr ""
"用於推送的儲存庫 URL，其行為取決於 :ref:`component-vcs`。更多詳細資訊"
"見 :ref:`code-hosting-push-options`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:546
msgid ""
"For linked repositories, this is not used and setting from linked component "
"applies."
msgstr "對於連結的儲存庫，這一點不被使用，連結元件的設定適用。"

#: admin/projects.rst:550
msgid ""
"See :ref:`vcs-repos` for more details on how to specify a repository URL "
"and :ref:`code-hosting-push-options` for more details on pushing changes "
"from Weblate."
msgstr ""
"關於如何指定儲存庫 URL 的更多細節請見 :ref:`vcs-repos`，並且關於從 Weblate 推"
"送變更的更多細節，請參閱 :ref:`code-hosting-push-options`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:557
msgid "Repository browser"
msgstr "儲存庫瀏覽器"

#: admin/projects.rst:559
msgid ""
"URL of repository browser used to display source files (location of used "
"messages). When empty, no such links will be generated. You can "
"use :ref:`markup`."
msgstr ""
"用於顯示來源檔案（已使用訊息的位置）儲存庫瀏覽器的 URL。當它為空白時，將不產"
"生這樣的連結。您可以使用 :ref:`markup`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:562
msgid ""
"For example on GitHub, use something like: ``https://github.com/WeblateOrg/"
"hello/blob/{{branch}}/{{filename}}#L{{line}}``"
msgstr ""
"例如在 GitHub 上，使用像： ``https://github.com/WeblateOrg/hello/blob/"
"{{branch}}/{{filename}}#L{{line}}`` 那樣的一些東西"

#: admin/projects.rst:565
msgid ""
"In case your paths are relative to different folder (path contains ``..``), "
"you might want to strip leading directory by ``parentdir`` filter "
"(see :ref:`markup`): ``https://github.com/WeblateOrg/hello/blob/{{branch}}/"
"{{filename|parentdir}}#L{{line}}``"
msgstr ""
"如果您的路徑是相對於不同資料夾的（路徑包含 ``..``），您可能想使用 "
"``parentdir`` 過濾器（見 :ref:`markup`）來剝除前導資料夾：``https://"
"github.com/WeblateOrg/hello/blob/{{branch}}/{{filename|parentdir}}#L{{line}}"
"``"

#: admin/projects.rst:577
msgid "Exported repository URL"
msgstr "已匯出儲存庫 URL"

#: admin/projects.rst:579
msgid ""
"URL where changes made by Weblate are exported. This is important "
"when :ref:`continuous-translation` is not used, or when there is a need to "
"manually merge changes. You can use :ref:`git-exporter` to automate this for "
"Git repositories."
msgstr ""
"由 Weblate 進行的變更被匯出的 URL。當不使用 :ref:`continuous-translation` "
"時，或者當需要手動合併變更時，這是重要的。您可以為 Git 儲存庫使用 :ref:`git-"
"exporter` 來將其自動化。"

#: admin/projects.rst:587
msgid "Repository branch"
msgstr "儲存庫分支"

#: admin/projects.rst:589
msgid ""
"Which branch to checkout from the VCS, and where to look for translations."
msgstr "要從 VCS 簽出哪個分支，以及要在何處尋找翻譯。"

#: admin/projects.rst:596
msgid "Push branch"
msgstr "推送分支"

#: admin/projects.rst:598
msgid "Branch for pushing changes, leave empty to use :ref:`component-branch`."
msgstr "用於推送變更的分支，留為空白來使用 :ref:`component-branch`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:604
msgid "This setting is ignored for Mercurial and Subversion."
msgstr "Mercurial 和 Subversion 忽略此設定。"

#: admin/projects.rst:606
msgid ""
"For Gerrit, this selects the target branch for the review request. Leave it "
"empty to review against :ref:`component-branch`. Use the short branch name, "
"not ``refs/heads/<branch>`` or ``refs/for/<branch>``. Gerrit push options "
"can be appended after ``%`` in either setting, for example "
"``main%topic=l10n``; Gerrit interprets them as the configured Weblate Gerrit "
"account."
msgstr ""
"對於 Gerrit，此設定會選取審查請求的目標分支。將其留空會針對 :ref:`component-"
"branch` 進行審查。請使用簡短分支名稱，而非 ``refs/heads/<branch>`` 或 ``refs/"
"for/<branch>``。Gerrit 推送選項可以附加在任一設定的 ``%`` 後方，例如 "
"``main%topic=l10n``；Gerrit 會將這些選項解讀為已設定的 Weblate Gerrit 帳號。"

