msgid "File mask"
msgstr "檔案遮罩"

#: admin/projects.rst:622
msgid ""
"Mask of files to translate, including path. It should include one \"*\" "
"replacing language code (see :ref:`languages` for info on how this is "
"processed). In case your repository contains more than one translation file "
"(e.g. more gettext domains), you need to create a component for each of them."
msgstr ""
"要翻譯的檔案的遮罩，包括路徑。它應包含一個 \"*\" 替換語言代碼（有關處理方式的"
"資訊，請參閱 :ref:`languages`）。如果您的儲存庫包含多個翻譯檔案（例如，多個 "
"gettext 定義域），則您需要為每個檔案建立元件。"

#: admin/projects.rst:628
msgid "For example ``po/*.po`` or ``locale/*/LC_MESSAGES/django.po``."
msgstr "例如 ``po/*.po`` 或 ``locale/*/LC_MESSAGES/django.po``。"

#: admin/projects.rst:630
msgid ""
"In case your filename contains special characters such as ``[``, ``]``, "
"these need to be escaped as ``[[]`` or ``[]]``."
msgstr ""
"如果檔名包含特殊字元（例如 ``[`` 或 ``]``），則需要將這些特殊字元逸出為 "
"``[[]`` 或 ``[]]``。"

#: admin/projects.rst:641
msgid "Screenshot file mask"
msgstr "螢幕擷圖檔案遮罩"

#: admin/projects.rst:643
msgid ""
"This feature allows the discovery and updating of screenshots through "
"screenshot file masks, using paths from the VCS repository. This operates at "
"the component level and necessitates the use of an asterisk \"*\" to replace "
"the screenshot file name."
msgstr ""
"此功能使用 VCS 儲存庫路徑透過螢幕擷圖檔案掩碼來發現和更新螢幕擷圖。此功能執行"
"在元件層級且必須使用星號“*”來替換螢幕擷圖檔名。"

#: admin/projects.rst:646
msgid "Allowed formats are WebP, JPEG, PNG, APNG and GIF."
msgstr "允許的格式是 WebP、JPEG、PNG、APNG 和 GIF。"

#: admin/projects.rst:648
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "備註："

#: admin/projects.rst:650
msgid ""
"The file mask and screenshot file mask are not related. Configure them "
"separately."
msgstr "檔案掩碼和螢幕擷圖檔案掩碼並不相關，請分別設定它們。"

#: admin/projects.rst:651
msgid ""
"It is a manual job to link a discovered screenshot in a component to a "
"specific translation key."
msgstr "需要手動將元件中發現的螢幕擷圖連結到特定的翻譯金鑰。"

#: admin/projects.rst:655
msgid "Let's assume your VCS repository has a structure like this:"
msgstr "讓我們假定您的 VCS 儲存庫有一個類似這樣的結構："

#: admin/projects.rst:664
msgid ""
"For component_A, you want to allow discovery and updates of PNG screenshots. "
"You'd set the screenshot file mask for component_A as ``component_A/docs/"
"*.png``. This means any PNG images under docs in component_A can be "
"discovered and updated. So, if you want to update ``image1.png``, the new "
"screenshot you provide should be named ``image1.png``, matching the existing "
"``filename``, and stored under ``component_A/docs/``."
msgstr ""
"對於 A 元件，您想允許 PNG 螢幕擷圖發現和更新。您會把 A 元件的螢幕擷圖檔案掩碼"
"設定為 ``component_A/docs/*.png``。這表示元件 A 中 doc 目錄下的任何 PNG 格式"
"圖片可被發現並更新。因此，若您想更新 ``image1.png``，您提供的新螢幕擷圖應命名"
"為 ``image1.png`` 來相符現有的 ``filename``，並儲存在 ``component_A/docs/`` "
"下。"

#: admin/projects.rst:670
msgid ""
"For Android projects using Fastlane metadata, a source-language screenshot "
"mask can point to the metadata screenshot folder, for example ``fastlane/"
"metadata/android/en-US/images/phoneScreenshots/*.png``. Weblate will "
"discover matching screenshots on repository update. The discovered "
"screenshots still need to be associated with source strings in the "
"screenshot management interface; use OCR or source string search there to "
"assign them in bulk."
msgstr ""
"對於使用 Fastlane 中繼資料的 Android 專案，來源語言螢幕擷圖遮罩可以指向中繼資"
"料螢幕擷圖資料夾，例如 ``fastlane/metadata/android/en-US/images/"
"phoneScreenshots/*.png``。Weblate 會在儲存庫更新時探索相符的螢幕擷圖。探索到"
"的螢幕擷圖仍需在螢幕擷圖管理介面中與來源字串建立關聯；可在該處使用 OCR 或來源"
"字串搜尋來批次指派。"

