msgid "Monolingual base language file"
msgstr "單語言基底語言檔案"

#: admin/projects.rst:682
msgid "Base file containing string definitions for :ref:`monolingual`."
msgstr "包含字串定義的譯文範本檔案，用於 :ref:`monolingual`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:692
msgid "Edit base file"
msgstr "編輯基底檔案"

#: admin/projects.rst:694
msgid "Whether to allow editing strings in the :ref:`component-template`."
msgstr "是否允許編輯 :ref:`component-template` 中的字串。"

#: admin/projects.rst:706 snippets/addons-autogenerated.rst:248
msgid "Intermediate language file"
msgstr "中間語言檔案"

#: admin/projects.rst:708
msgid ""
"Intermediate language file for :ref:`monolingual`. In most cases this is a "
"translation file provided by developers and is used when creating actual "
"source strings."
msgstr ""
"對於 :ref:`monolingual` 的單一語言檔案。在多數情況下，這是開發者提供的翻譯檔"
"案，並且在新增真正的來源字串時使用。"

#: admin/projects.rst:712
msgid ""
"When set, the source strings are based on this file, but all other languages "
"are based on :ref:`component-template`. In case the string is not translated "
"into the source language, translating to other languages is prohibited. This "
"provides :ref:`source-quality-gateway`."
msgstr ""
"設定好後，來源字串將基於此檔案，但所有其他語言都基於 :ref:`component-"
"template`。如果字串沒有被翻譯成來源語言，則禁止翻譯成其他語言。這樣就提供"
"了 :ref:`source-quality-gateway`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:717
msgid ""
"The intermediate file can match an existing language file. While it is "
"configured as intermediate, Weblate does not list it as a regular language "
"in the component language list. Clearing this setting makes the file appear "
"as a regular language again on the next component scan."
msgstr ""
"中繼檔案可以與既有語言檔案相符。將其設定為中繼檔案時，Weblate 不會在元件語言"
"清單中將其列為一般語言。清除此設定後，檔案會在下次掃描元件時再次顯示為一般語"
"言。"

#: admin/projects.rst:722
msgid ""
"Target strings can become read-only while the intermediate file is "
"configured. This happens for strings where the matching source string in "
"the :ref:`component-template` is not translated yet."
msgstr ""
"設定中繼檔案時，目標字串可能變成唯讀。若 :ref:`component-template` 中相符的來"
"源字串尚未翻譯，就會發生這種情況。"

