#: admin/projects.rst:772
msgid ""
"Parameters used to configure how translation files are processed, see "
"also :ref:`file_format_params`."
msgstr "用於設定翻譯檔案處理方式的引數，另見 :ref:`file_format_params`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:777
msgid "Source string bug reporting address"
msgstr "來源字串漏洞報告位址"

#: admin/projects.rst:779
msgid ""
"Email address used for reporting upstream bugs. This address will also "
"receive notification about any source string comments made in Weblate."
msgstr ""
"用於回報上游缺陷的電子郵件地址。 Weblate 中做出的任何字串註解的通知，也由這個"
"地址接收。"

#: admin/projects.rst:782
msgid ""
"With the :ref:`gettext` format, this address is also saved by Weblate in "
"the :mailheader:`Report-Msgid-Bugs-To` header of the file."
msgstr ""
"對於 :ref:`gettext` 格式，此地址同樣由 Weblate 儲存在該檔案"
"的 :mailheader:`Report-Msgid-Bugs-To` 標頭內。"

#: admin/projects.rst:788
msgid "Do not show glossary matches"
msgstr "不要顯示詞彙表符合專案"

#: admin/projects.rst:790
msgid ""
"Hides the glossary panel and its matches in the translation editor for this "
"component. When enabled, glossary suggestions for this component are not "
"computed, and the Glossary panel (including its “Add term to glossary” "
"action) is hidden in the editor."
msgstr ""
"對這個元件隱藏翻譯編輯器中的詞彙表面板及相符項目。啟用後，系統不會計算這個元"
"件的詞彙表建議，編輯器也會隱藏詞彙表面板（包括「新增詞彙至詞彙表」動作）。"

#: admin/projects.rst:796
msgid ""
"Glossary self-references are always excluded from matches even when this "
"option is disabled."
msgstr "詞彙表自參考始終被排除在相符之外，即便停用該選項時也是如此。"

#: admin/projects.rst:806
msgid "Allow translation propagation"
msgstr "允許翻譯重用"

#: admin/projects.rst:808
msgid ""
"You can turn off propagation of translations to this component from other "
"components within same project. This really depends on what you are "
"translating, sometimes it's desirable to have make use of a translation more "
"than once."
msgstr ""
"您可以關閉專案內從其它元件到這個元件的翻譯的傳播。這真正依賴於您在翻譯的是什"
"麼，有時最好多次使用同一個翻譯。"

#: admin/projects.rst:812
msgid ""
"It's usually a good idea to turn this off for monolingual translations, "
"unless you are using the same IDs across the whole project."
msgstr ""
"對於單語言翻譯，除非您跨越整個專案中使用相同的 ID，通常關閉它是個好主意。"

#: admin/projects.rst:815
msgid ""
"The default value can be changed "
"by :setting:`DEFAULT_TRANSLATION_PROPAGATION`."
msgstr "可以透過 :setting:`DEFAULT_TRANSLATION_PROPAGATION` 變更預設值。"

#: admin/projects.rst:824 workflows.rst:123 workflows.rst:155 workflows.rst:188
msgid "Enable suggestions"
msgstr "啟用建議"

#: admin/projects.rst:826
msgid "Whether translation suggestions are accepted for this component."
msgstr "對於這個元件，建議的翻譯是否被接受。"

#: admin/projects.rst:835 admin/translating.rst:7 workflows.rst:126
#: workflows.rst:157 workflows.rst:191
msgid "Suggestion voting"
msgstr "建議投票"

#: admin/projects.rst:837
msgid "Turns on vote casting for suggestions, see :ref:`voting`."
msgstr "為建議打開投票，請參閱 :ref:`voting`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:846 workflows.rst:128 workflows.rst:159 workflows.rst:193
msgid "Automatically accept suggestions"
msgstr "自動接受建議"

#: admin/projects.rst:848
msgid "Automatically accept voted suggestions, see :ref:`voting`."
msgstr "自動接收被投票的建議，請參閱 :ref:`voting`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:870
msgid "Enforced checks"
msgstr "強制檢查"

#: admin/projects.rst:872
msgid "List of checks which can not be dismissed."
msgstr "不能忽略的檢查清單。"

#: admin/projects.rst:883
msgid ""
"License of the translation (does not need to be the same as the source code "
"license)."
msgstr "翻譯的許可（不需要與原始碼的授權相同）。"

#: admin/projects.rst:894
msgid ""
"Contributor license agreement which needs to be approved before a user can "
"translate this component."
msgstr "使用者必須先同意貢獻者授權協議才能翻譯此元件。"

#: admin/projects.rst:897
msgid "Markdown can be used for text formatting or inserting links."
msgstr "Markdown 可被用於調整文字格式或插入連結。"

#: admin/projects.rst:908
msgid ""
"How to handle requests for creation of new languages. Available options:"
msgstr "如何處理建立新語言的請求。可用選項："

#: admin/projects.rst:910
msgid "Contact maintainers"
msgstr "聯絡維護者"

#: admin/projects.rst:911
msgid ""
"User can select desired language and the project maintainers will receive a "
"notification about this. It is up to them to add (or not) the language to "
"the repository."
msgstr ""
"使用者可以選取所需的語言，專案維護者將收到有關該語言的通知。由他們決定是否向"
"儲存庫新增（或不新增）語言。"

#: admin/projects.rst:914
msgid "Point to translation instructions URL"
msgstr "指向翻譯說明 URL"

#: admin/projects.rst:915
msgid ""
"User is presented a link to page which describes process of starting new "
"translations. Use this in case more formal process is desired (for example "
"forming a team of people before starting actual translation)."
msgstr ""
"向使用者顯示的頁面連結描述了開始新翻譯的過程。如果需要更正式的流程（例如，在"
"開始實際翻譯之前組成人員團隊），請使用此選項。"

#: admin/projects.rst:918
msgid "Create new language file"
msgstr "建立新語言檔案"

#: admin/projects.rst:919
msgid ""
"User can select language and Weblate automatically creates the file for it "
"and translation can begin."
msgstr "使用者可以選擇語言，然後 Weblate 會自動為其新增檔案並開始翻譯。"

#: admin/projects.rst:921
msgid "Disable adding new translations"
msgstr "停用新增翻譯"

#: admin/projects.rst:922
msgid "There will be no option for user to start new translation."
msgstr "使用者將無法選擇開始新的翻譯。"

#: admin/projects.rst:926
msgid ""
"The project admins can add new translations even if it is disabled here when "
"it is possible (either :ref:`component-new_base` or the file format supports "
"starting from an empty file)."
msgstr ""
"即使此處已停用新增翻譯，只要可行，專案管理員仍能新增翻譯（可使"
"用 :ref:`component-new_base`，或檔案格式支援從空白檔案開始）。"

#: admin/projects.rst:939
msgid "Manage strings"
msgstr "管理字串"

#: admin/projects.rst:943
msgid ""
"Configures whether users in Weblate will be allowed to add new strings and "
"remove existing ones. Adjust this to match your localization workflow - how "
"the new strings are supposed to be introduced."
msgstr ""
"設定Weblate中的使用者是否被允許新增新字串和刪除現有字串。調整這一點以配合您的"
"在地化工作流程--新字串應該如何被引入。"

#: admin/projects.rst:947
msgid ""
"For bilingual formats, the strings are typically extracted from the source "
"code (for example by using :program:`xgettext`) and adding new strings in "
"Weblate should be disabled (they would be discarded next time you update the "
"translation files). In Weblate you can manage strings for every translation "
"and it does not enforce the strings in all translations to be consistent."
msgstr ""
"對於雙語言格式，通常會從原始碼中提取字串（例如，通過使"
"用 :program:`xgettext`）並停用在 Weblate 中新增字串（在下次更新翻譯檔案時將被"
"丟棄）。在 Weblate 中，您可以為每個翻譯管理字串，並且它不會在所有翻譯中強制執"
"行字串。"

#: admin/projects.rst:953
msgid ""
"For monolingual formats, the strings are managed only on source language and "
"are automatically added or removed in the translations. The strings appear "
"in the translation files once they are translated."
msgstr ""
"對於單晶格式，字串僅在來源語言上管理，並在翻譯中自動新增或刪除。一旦翻譯，字"
"串會在翻譯檔案中出現。"

#: admin/projects.rst:959
msgid ""
"You might want to turn on :ref:`component-edit_template` together "
"with :guilabel:`Manage strings` for monolingual formats."
msgstr ""
"對於單語言格式，您可能想要同時開啟 :ref:`component-edit_template` "
"和 :guilabel:`管理字串`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:966
msgid ""
":http:post:`/api/translations/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"(string:language)/units/`"
msgstr ""
":http:post:`/api/translations/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"(string:language)/units/`"

#: admin/projects.rst:973
msgid ""
"Customize language code used to generate the filename for translations "
"created by Weblate."
msgstr "用來產生使用 Weblate 建立之翻譯檔案名稱的自訂語言代碼。"

#: admin/projects.rst:978
msgid ""
"Weblate recognizes any of the language codes when parsing translation files, "
"following settings only influences how new files are created."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 在解析翻譯檔案時能辨識其中的語言程式碼，以下設定隻影響新檔案的建立方"
"式。"

#: admin/projects.rst:981
msgid "Default based on the file format"
msgstr "預設基於檔案格式"

#: admin/projects.rst:982
msgid "Dependent on file format, for most of them POSIX is used."
msgstr "依賴於檔案格式，對於其中的多數使用 POSIX。"

#: admin/projects.rst:983
msgid "POSIX style using underscore as a separator"
msgstr "POSIX 樣式，使用底線當作分隔符號"

#: admin/projects.rst:984 admin/projects.rst:987
msgid ""
"Typically used by gettext and related tools, produces language codes like "
"``pt_BR``."
msgstr "典型地由 gettext 和相關工具使用，產生像 ``pt_BR`` 那樣的語言代碼。"

#: admin/projects.rst:986
msgid "POSIX style using underscore as a separator, lower cased"
msgstr "POSIX 樣式，使用底線作為分隔符號，小寫"

#: admin/projects.rst:989
msgid "POSIX style using underscore as a separator, including country code"
msgstr "POSIX 樣式，使用底線當作分隔符，包含地區碼"

#: admin/projects.rst:990
msgid ""
"POSIX style language code including the country code even when not necessary "
"(for example ``cs_CZ``)."
msgstr "POSIX 風格的語言代碼即使不必要時也包括國家代碼；例如 ``cs_CZ``）。"

#: admin/projects.rst:992
msgid ""
"POSIX style using underscore as a separator, including country code, lower "
"cased"
msgstr "POSIX 樣式，使用底線作為分隔符號，包括國家代碼，小寫"

#: admin/projects.rst:993
msgid ""
"POSIX style language code including the country code even when not necessary "
"(lowercase) (for example ``cs_cz``)."
msgstr ""
"POSIX 風格的語言程式碼，包含小寫的國家地區程式碼，即使沒有必要（例如 "
"``cs_cz``）。"

#: admin/projects.rst:995
msgid "BCP style using hyphen as a separator"
msgstr "BCP 樣式，使用連字號當作分隔符號"

#: admin/projects.rst:996
msgid ""
"Typically used on web platforms, produces language codes like ``pt-BR``."
msgstr "典型地在 web 平台上使用，產生像 ``pt-BR`` 那樣的語言編碼。"

#: admin/projects.rst:998
msgid "BCP style using hyphen as a separator, including country code"
msgstr "BCP 樣式，使用連字號當作分隔符號，包含地區碼"

#: admin/projects.rst:999
msgid ""
"BCP style language code including the country code even when not necessary "
"(for example ``cs-CZ``)."
msgstr "BCP 風格的語言代碼即使不必要時也包括國家代碼；例如 ``cs-CZ``）。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1001
msgid "BCP style using hyphen as a separator, legacy language codes"
msgstr "BCP 樣式，使用連字號作為分隔符號、舊式語言代碼"

#: admin/projects.rst:1002
msgid "Uses legacy codes for Chinese and BCP style notation."
msgstr "對中文和 BCP 樣式符號使用舊程式碼。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1003
msgid "BCP style using hyphen as a separator, lower cased"
msgstr "BCP 樣式，使用連字號作為分隔符號，小寫"

#: admin/projects.rst:1004
msgid "BCP style notation, all in lower case (for example ``cs-cz``)."
msgstr "BCP 樣式表示法，全部為小寫（例如 ``cs-cz``）。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1005
msgid "Apple App Store metadata style"
msgstr "Apple App Store 詮釋資料樣式"

#: admin/projects.rst:1006
msgid "Style suitable for uploading metadata to Apple App Store."
msgstr "適用於將後設資料上傳到 Apple 應用商店的樣式。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1007
msgid "Google Play metadata style"
msgstr "Google Play 詮釋資料樣式"

#: admin/projects.rst:1008
msgid "Style suitable for uploading metadata to Google Play Store."
msgstr "適用於將後設資料上傳到 Google Play 應用商店的樣式。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1009
msgid "Android style"
msgstr "Android 樣式"

#: admin/projects.rst:1010
msgid "Only used in Android apps, produces language codes like ``pt-rBR``."
msgstr "只在Android apps 中使用，產生像 ``pt-rBR`` 那樣的語言代碼。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1012
msgid "Linux style"
msgstr "Linux 樣式"

#: admin/projects.rst:1013
msgid ""
"Locales as used by Linux, uses legacy codes for Chinese and POSIX style "
"notation."
msgstr "Linux 使用的語言環境，使用中文和 POSIX 樣式符號的遺留程式碼。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1014
msgid "Linux style, lower cased"
msgstr "Linux 樣式，小寫"

#: admin/projects.rst:1015
msgid ""
"Locales as used by Linux, uses legacy codes for Chinese and POSIX style "
"notation. Lower cased."
msgstr "Linux 使用的語言環境，使用老式中文編碼和 POSIX 樣式符號。小寫。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1028
msgid "Merge style"
msgstr "合併類型"

#: admin/projects.rst:1030
msgid ""
"You can configure how updates from the upstream repository are handled. The "
"actual implementation depends on VCS, see :doc:`/vcs`."
msgstr ""
"您可以設定如何處理來自上游儲存庫的更新。實際部署取決於版本控制系統，"
"見 :doc:`/vcs`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1033
msgid "Rebase"
msgstr "衍合"

#: admin/projects.rst:1034
msgid ""
"Rebases Weblate commits on top of upstream repository on update. This "
"provides clean history without extra merge commits."
msgstr ""
"在更新時，將Weblate的提交重新放在上游儲存庫之上。這提供了乾淨的歷史，沒有額外"
"的合併提交。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1037
msgid ""
"Rebasing can cause you trouble in case of complicated merges, so carefully "
"consider whether or not you want to enable them."
msgstr "在複雜融合的情況下，變基可能使您產生麻煩，因此請仔細考慮是否允許它們。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1040
msgid ""
"You might need to enable force pushing by choosing :ref:`vcs-git-force-push` "
"as :ref:`component-vcs`, especially when pushing to a different branch."
msgstr ""
"您可能需要透過選擇 :ref:`vcs-git-force-push` 作為 :ref:`component-vcs` 來啟用"
"強制推送，特別是在推送到不同的分支時。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1043
msgid "Merge"
msgstr "合併"

#: admin/projects.rst:1044
msgid ""
"Upstream repository changes are merged into Weblate one. This setting "
"utilizes fast-forward when possible. This is the safest way, but might "
"produce a lot of merge commits."
msgstr ""
"上游儲存庫變更合併到 Weblate 之一。此設定儘可能使用快進。這是最安全的方式，但"
"可能會產生大量合併提交。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1048
msgid "Merge without fast-forward"
msgstr "不快轉合併"

#: admin/projects.rst:1049
msgid ""
"Upstream repository changes are merged into Weblate one with doing a merge "
"commit every time (even when fast-forward would be possible). Every Weblate "
"change will appear as a merge commit in Weblate repository."
msgstr ""
"上游儲存庫的修改會被合併到Weblate儲存庫中，每次都要做一次合併提交（即使是在可"
"以快進的時候）。每一個Weblate的修改都會在Weblate儲存庫中顯示為合併提交。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1053
msgid "The default value can be changed by :setting:`DEFAULT_MERGE_STYLE`."
msgstr "可以透過 :setting:`DEFAULT_MERGE_STYLE` 變更預設值。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1065
msgid "Message used when committing a translation, see :ref:`markup`."
msgstr "在提交翻譯時使用的說明，請參閱 :ref:`markup`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1067
msgid ""
"The default value can be changed "
"by :setting:`DEFAULT_ADD_MESSAGE`, :setting:`DEFAULT_ADDON_MESSAGE`, :setting:`DEFAULT_COMMIT_MESSAGE`, :setting:`DEFAULT_DELETE_MESSAGE`, :setting:`DEFAULT_MERGE_MESSAGE`, :setting:`DEFAULT_PULL_MESSAGE`."
msgstr ""
"預設值可以透"
"過 :setting:`DEFAULT_ADD_MESSAGE` 、 :setting:`DEFAULT_ADDON_MESSAGE` 、 :setting:`DEFAULT_COMMIT_MESSAGE` 、 :setting:`DEFAULT_DELETE_MESSAGE` 、 :setting:`DEFAULT_MERGE_MESSAGE` 、 :setting:`DEFAULT_PULL_MESSAGE` "
"變更。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1084
msgid "Push on commit"
msgstr "提交時一併推送"

#: admin/projects.rst:1086
msgid ""
"Whether committed changes should be automatically pushed to the upstream "
"repository. When enabled, the push is initiated once Weblate commits changes "
"to its underlying repository (see :ref:`lazy-commit`). To actually enable "
"pushing :guilabel:`Repository push URL` has to be configured as well."
msgstr ""
"是否自動推送已提交的專案到上游儲存庫。啟用時，當 Weblate 將變更提交到其基礎儲"
"存庫中，就會啟動推送。（請參閱 :ref:`lazy-commit`）。為了能真正啟用推送功能，"
"需設定 :guilabel:`Repository push URL`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1097
msgid "Age of changes to commit"
msgstr "變更後提交的經過時間"

#: admin/projects.rst:1099
msgid ""
"Sets how old (in hours) changes have to be before they are committed by "
"background task or the :wladmin:`commit_pending` management command. All "
"changes in a component are committed once there is at least one change older "
"than this period."
msgstr ""
"設定在後臺任務或 :wladmin:`commit_pending` 管理指令提交變更前，這些變更存在的"
"時長（以小時為單位）。一旦存在至少一個比該時長更舊的變更，便會提交元件中的所"
"有變更。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1106
msgid "The default value can be changed by :setting:`COMMIT_PENDING_HOURS`."
msgstr "可以透過 :setting:`COMMIT_PENDING_HOURS` 變更預設值。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1110
msgid ""
"There are other situations where pending changes might be committed, "
"see :ref:`lazy-commit`."
msgstr "還有一些情況下，未提交的修改可能會被提交，見 :ref:`lazy-commit`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1116
msgid "Lock on error"
msgstr "有錯誤時鎖定"

#: admin/projects.rst:1118
msgid ""
"Locks the component (and linked components, see :ref:`internal-urls`) upon "
"the first failed push or merge into its upstream repository, or pull from "
"it. This avoids adding another conflicts, which would have to be resolved "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"鎖定元件 (及關聯的元件，請參閱 :ref:`internal-urls` )，觸發條件是第一個失敗的"
"推送，合併到其上游儲存庫，或從中拉出。這樣可以避免新增其他衝突，這些衝突必須"
"手動解決。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1122
msgid ""
"The component will be automatically unlocked once there are no repository "
"errors left."
msgstr "一旦儲存庫沒有錯誤留下來了，元件將會自動解鎖。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1130 devel/migration.rst:113
msgid "Source language"
msgstr "來源語言"

#: admin/projects.rst:1132
msgid ""
"Language used for source strings. Change this if you are translating from "
"something else than English."
msgstr "用於來源字串的語言。如果您要翻譯的不是英語，請變更此選項。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1137
msgid ""
"In case you are translating bilingual files from English, but want to be "
"able to do fixes in the English translation as well, "
"choose :guilabel:`English (Developer)` as a source language to avoid "
"conflict between the name of the source language and the existing "
"translation."
msgstr ""
"如果您正在從英語翻譯雙語言檔案，但又希望能夠在英語翻譯中進行修復，選"
"擇 :guilabel:`English (Developer)` 作為一種來源語言以避免來源語言和現有翻譯之"
"間名稱上的衝突。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1142
msgid ""
"For monolingual translations, you can use intermediate translation in this "
"case, see :ref:`component-intermediate`."
msgstr ""
"對於單語言翻譯，您可以使用這種情況下的中間翻譯，請參閱 :ref:`component-"
"intermediate`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1149 snippets/addons-autogenerated.rst:250
msgid "Language filter"
msgstr "語言篩選"

#: admin/projects.rst:1151
msgid ""
"Regular expression used to filter the translation when scanning for file "
"mask. It can be used to limit the list of languages managed by Weblate."
msgstr ""
"當掃描檔案掩碼時用於將翻譯過濾的正規表示式。它可以用於限制 Weblate 管理的語言"
"清單。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1156
msgid "You need to list language codes as they appear in the filename."
msgstr "單出現在檔案名稱中時，您需要列出語言代碼。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1158 admin/projects.rst:1186
msgid "Some examples of filtering:"
msgstr "過濾的一些範例："

#: admin/projects.rst:1161 admin/projects.rst:1189
msgid "Filter description"
msgstr "過濾器的描述"

#: admin/projects.rst:1161 admin/projects.rst:1189
#: snippets/checks-autogenerated.rst:1871
msgid "Regular expression"
msgstr "正規表達式"

#: admin/projects.rst:1163
msgid "Selected languages only"
msgstr "僅已選取的語言"

#: admin/projects.rst:1165
msgid "Exclude languages"
msgstr "排除的語言"

#: admin/projects.rst:1167
msgid "Filter two letter codes only"
msgstr "只篩選兩個字母的代碼"

#: admin/projects.rst:1169
msgid "Exclude non language files"
msgstr "排除非語言檔案"

#: admin/projects.rst:1171
msgid "Include all files (default)"
msgstr "包括所有檔案（預設）"

#: admin/projects.rst:1178
msgid "Key filter"
msgstr "鍵值篩選器"

#: admin/projects.rst:1182
msgid ""
"A regular expression that is used to filter units by their keys. It displays "
"only those units whose keys match the regular expression that was set as the "
"value of this field."
msgstr ""
"用於依鍵值篩選翻譯單元的正規表示式。只有鍵值符合此欄位所設定正規表示式的翻譯"
"單元會顯示。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1191
msgid "Selected keys only"
msgstr "僅已選取的金鑰"

#: admin/projects.rst:1193
msgid "Exclude app store changelogs"
msgstr "排除應用商店更新日誌"

#: admin/projects.rst:1195
msgid "Filter prefixed strings"
msgstr "篩選含前置字串的字串"

#: admin/projects.rst:1200
msgid ""
"This filter is only available for components with monolingual file formats."
msgstr "此篩選器只對有單語言檔案格式的元件可用。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1206
msgid "Variants regular expression"
msgstr "變體的正規表達式"

#: admin/projects.rst:1208
msgid ""
"Regular expression used to determine the variants of a string, "
"see :ref:`variants`."
msgstr "用於確定字串變體的正規表達式，請見 :ref:`variants`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1213
msgid ""
"Most of the fields can be edited by project owners or administrators, in the "
"Weblate interface."
msgstr "多數欄位可以由專案所有者或管理員在 Weblate 介面上編輯。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1234
msgid "This setting can be inherited from the project."
msgstr "此設定可從專案繼承。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1245
msgid "Priority"
msgstr "優先度"

#: admin/projects.rst:1247
msgid "Components with higher priority are offered first to translators."
msgstr "較高優先度的元件會優先提供給翻譯者。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1251
msgid "This now also affects ordering of matched glossary terms."
msgstr "這同樣影響相符的詞彙表術語的順序。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1256
msgid "Restricted access"
msgstr "受限制的存取"

#: admin/projects.rst:1260
msgid ""
"On Hosted Weblate, this requires a billing plan which permits private "
"projects."
msgstr "在 Hosted Weblate 上，這需要採用允許私密專案的計費方案。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1263
msgid ""
"By default the component is visible to anybody who has access to the "
"project, even if the person can not perform any changes in the component. "
"This makes it easier to keep translation consistency within the project."
msgstr ""
"元件預設對存取專案的任何人都可見，即使不能在元件中進行任何變更。這會容易地使"
"翻譯在專案內保持一致。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1267
msgid ""
"Restricting access at a component, or component-list level takes over access "
"permission to a component, regardless of project-level permissions. You will "
"have to grant access to it explicitly. This can be done through granting "
"access to a new user group and putting users in it, or using the default "
"`custom` or `private` access control groups."
msgstr ""
"無論專案層級權限如何，限制元件的存取或元件清單層級將接管到元件的存取權限。您"
"必須明確授予對其的存取權限。這可以通過授予對新使用者群組的存取並將使用者放入"
"其中，或使用預設的“自訂”或“私有”存取控制組。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1273
msgid ""
"The default value can be changed in :setting:`DEFAULT_RESTRICTED_COMPONENT`."
msgstr "預設設定可在 :setting:`DEFAULT_RESTRICTED_COMPONENT` 中變更。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1277
msgid ""
"This applies to project admins as well — please ensure you will not lose "
"access to the component after toggling the status."
msgstr "這也適用於專案管理員；請務必確認切換狀態後仍可存取該元件。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1283
msgid "Share in projects"
msgstr "分享專案"

#: admin/projects.rst:1285
msgid ""
"You can choose additional projects where the component will be visible. "
"Useful for shared libraries which you use in several projects."
msgstr "可以選擇元件可見的附加專案。這在分享不同專案間使用的庫時是有用的。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1290
msgid ""
"Sharing a component doesn't change its access control. It only makes it "
"visible when browsing other projects. Users still need access to the actual "
"component to browse or translate it."
msgstr ""
"分享元件不變更其存取控制。這樣做只是讓它在瀏覽其它專案時可見。使用者仍然需要"
"存取實際元件的權限來瀏覽或翻譯它。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1298
msgid "Use as a glossary"
msgstr "當作詞彙表"

#: admin/projects.rst:1302
msgid ""
"Allows using this component as a glossary. Use when you want to manage "
"terminology separately from normal translations."
msgstr "允許將此元件用作詞彙表。當您想分別管理專業術語和一般翻譯時使用。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1305
msgid "Glossaries are best for:"
msgstr "詞彙表的最佳用處："

#: admin/projects.rst:1307
msgid "Ensuring consistent use of terms (e.g., UI labels, product names)."
msgstr "確保術語使用一致性（如 UI 標籤、產品名）。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1308
msgid "Sharing preferred translations across multiple components or projects."
msgstr "在多個元件或專案間共享首選的譯文。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1309
msgid "Supporting translators with definitions and context."
msgstr "用定義和情境支援翻譯者。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1313
msgid ""
"Glossaries are not for regular translations—they are for managing terms only."
msgstr "詞彙表不適用於一般翻譯，而只用於管理術語。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1315
msgid ""
"You can configure how it will be listed using :ref:`component-"
"glossary_color`."
msgstr "您可以用 :ref:`component-glossary_color` 設定如何列舉它。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1317
msgid ""
"The glossary will be accessible in all projects defined by :ref:`component-"
"links`."
msgstr "詞彙表將可以在所有由 :ref:`component-links` 定義的專案中存取。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1319
msgid ""
"It is recommended to enable :ref:`component-manage_units` on glossaries in "
"order to allow adding new words to them."
msgstr "建議在詞彙表上啟用 :ref:`component-manage_units`，以允許新增新詞。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1329
msgid "Glossary color"
msgstr "詞彙表色彩"

#: admin/projects.rst:1331
msgid ""
"Color used when displaying terms from this glossary. Useful to distinguish "
"glossaries when using more of them."
msgstr "展示來自此詞彙表的術語時所用的顏色。有助於在使用多個術語時進行區分。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1340 snippets/machines-autogenerated.rst:672
msgid "Category"
msgstr "類別"

#: admin/projects.rst:1342
msgid ""
"Categories are there to give structure to components within a project. You "
"can nest them to achieve a more complex structure."
msgstr "類別的作用是賦予專案內元件以結構。您可以巢狀它們來達成更復雜的結構。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1348
msgid "Category settings"
msgstr "類別設定"

#: admin/projects.rst:1350
msgid ""
"Categories can override the same inherited settings as projects and "
"components, including translation license, contributor agreement, adding new "
"translations, secondary language, translation flags, and commit messages."
msgstr ""
"分類可以覆寫與專案及元件相同的繼承設定，包括翻譯授權、貢獻者協議、新增翻譯、"
"第二語言、翻譯旗標及提交訊息。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1354
msgid ""
"Nested categories inherit from their parent category by default. Top-level "
"categories inherit from the project. Components in a category inherit from "
"that category by default."
msgstr ""
"巢狀分類預設會繼承其上層分類。最上層分類會繼承專案。分類中的元件預設會繼承該"
"分類。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1367
msgid "Template markup"
msgstr "範本標記"

#: admin/projects.rst:1369
msgid ""
"Weblate uses simple markup language in several places where text rendering "
"is needed. It is based on :doc:`django:ref/templates/language`, so it can be "
"quite powerful."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 在幾個需要進行文字渲染的地方使用了簡單的標記語言。它基"
"於 :doc:`django:ref/templates/language`，所以它可以非常強大。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1373
msgid "Currently it is used in:"
msgstr "目前它用在："

#: admin/projects.rst:1375
msgid "Commit message formatting, see :ref:`component`"
msgstr "提交說明格式，請參閱 :ref:`component`"

#: admin/projects.rst:1376
msgid "Several add-ons"
msgstr "幾個附加元件"

#: admin/projects.rst:1381
msgid "The following variables are available in the component templates:"
msgstr "在元件範本中，有以下變數可用："

#: admin/projects.rst:1394 snippets/addons-autogenerated.rst:515
#: snippets/addons-autogenerated.rst:529
msgid "Project slug"
msgstr "專案 slug"

#: admin/projects.rst:1396
msgid "Translation URL"
msgstr "翻譯 URL"

#: admin/projects.rst:1398
msgid "Translation filename"
msgstr "翻譯檔案名稱"

#: admin/projects.rst:1400
msgid "Translation stats, this has further attributes, examples below."
msgstr "翻譯統計資料，這具有進一步的屬性，範例如下。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1402
msgid "Total strings count"
msgstr "總字串數量"

#: admin/projects.rst:1404
msgid "Count of strings needing review"
msgstr "需要檢閱的字串數量"

#: admin/projects.rst:1406
msgid "Percent of strings needing review"
msgstr "需要檢閱的字串數量百分比"

#: admin/projects.rst:1408
msgid "Translated strings count"
msgstr "已翻譯的字串數量"

#: admin/projects.rst:1410
msgid "Translated strings percent"
msgstr "已翻譯的字串百分比"

#: admin/projects.rst:1412
msgid "Number of strings with failing checks"
msgstr "檢查失敗的字串數量"

#: admin/projects.rst:1414
msgid "Percent of strings with failing checks"
msgstr "檢查失敗的字串百分比"

#: admin/projects.rst:1416
msgid "Author of current commit, available only in the commit scope."
msgstr "目前提交的作者，只在提交範圍可用。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1418
msgid ""
"Name of currently executed add-on, available only in the add-on commit "
"message."
msgstr "目前執行的附加元件名稱，只能用於附加元件提交訊息。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1420
msgid ""
"The following variables are available in the repository browser or editor "
"templates:"
msgstr "下面的變數在儲存庫瀏覽器或編輯器範本中可用："

#: admin/projects.rst:1423
msgid "current branch"
msgstr "目前的分支"

#: admin/projects.rst:1425
msgid "line in file"
msgstr "檔案中的列"

#: admin/projects.rst:1427
msgid ""
"filename, you can also strip leading parts using the ``parentdir`` filter, "
"for example ``{{filename|parentdir}}``"
msgstr ""
"檔案名稱，您也可以使用 ``parentdir`` 過濾器，例如 ``{{filename|parentdir}}"
"``，來剝除前導部分"

#: admin/projects.rst:1431
msgid ""
"In some places additional variables can be available, see :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.discovery.discovery`."
msgstr ""
"某些地方可能有額外的變數可用，見 :ref:`addon-weblate.discovery.discovery`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1433
msgid "You can combine them with filters:"
msgstr "您可以將它們與過濾器結合："

#: admin/projects.rst:1439
msgid "You can use conditions:"
msgstr "您可以使用條件："

#: admin/projects.rst:1445
msgid "There is additional tag available for replacing characters:"
msgstr "有另外的標籤用於替換字元："

#: admin/projects.rst:1451
msgid "You can combine it with filters:"
msgstr "您可以將它與過濾器結合："

#: admin/projects.rst:1457
msgid "There are also additional filter to manipulate with filenames:"
msgstr "還有另外的過濾器來操作檔案名稱："

#: admin/projects.rst:1466
msgid "…and other Django template features."
msgstr "…以及其他 Django 範本特性。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1471
msgid "Importing speed"
msgstr "匯入速度"

#: admin/projects.rst:1473
msgid ""
"Fetching VCS repository and importing translations to Weblate can be a "
"lengthy process, depending on size of your translations. Here are some tips:"
msgstr ""
"從版本控制系統儲存庫取得並將翻譯匯入 Weblate 可能會是漫長的過程，具體取決於您"
"的翻譯的大小。以下是一些提示："

#: admin/projects.rst:1477
msgid "Optimize configuration"
msgstr "最佳化設定"

#: admin/projects.rst:1479
msgid ""
"The default configuration is useful for testing and debugging Weblate, while "
"for a production setup, you should do some adjustments. Many of them have "
"quite a big impact on performance. Please check :ref:`production` for more "
"details, especially:"
msgstr ""
"對於測試並除錯 Weblate，預設的設定是有用的，當用於生產設定時，您應該進行一些"
"調整。它們中的很多都對形成具有巨大的衝擊。特別是，更多細節請查"
"看 :ref:`production` ："

#: admin/projects.rst:1484
msgid "Configure Celery for executing background tasks (see :ref:`celery`)"
msgstr "設定 Celery 來執行背景工作（請參閱 :ref:`celery`）"

#: admin/projects.rst:1490
msgid "Check resource limits"
msgstr "檢查資源限制"

#: admin/projects.rst:1492
msgid ""
"If you are importing huge translations or repositories, you might be hit by "
"resource limitations of your server."
msgstr "如果匯入巨大的翻譯或儲存庫，您會遭到伺服器資源限制的打擊。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1495
msgid ""
"Check the amount of free memory, having translation files cached by the "
"operating system will greatly improve performance."
msgstr "檢查空閒記憶體的量，通過作業系統來快取翻譯，將極大地提高效能。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1496
msgid ""
"Disk operations might be bottleneck if there is a lot of strings to process—"
"the disk is pushed by both Weblate and the database."
msgstr ""
"如果有很多字串需要處理的話，磁碟操作會是瓶頸——磁碟被 Weblate 和資料庫施加壓"
"力。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1497
msgid ""
"Additional CPU cores might help improve performance of background tasks "
"(see :ref:`celery`)."
msgstr "另外的 CPU 核心會幫助提高背景工作的效能（請參閱 :ref:`celery`）。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1500
msgid "Disable unneeded checks"
msgstr "停用不必要的檢查"

#: admin/projects.rst:1502
msgid ""
"Some quality checks can be quite expensive, and if not needed, can save you "
"some time during import if omitted. See :setting:`CHECK_LIST` for info on "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"一些品質檢查可以使非常昂貴的，而如果不需要，在匯入時省略可以節省一些時間。設"
"定的資訊請參閱 :setting:`CHECK_LIST`。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1509
msgid "Automatic creation of components"
msgstr "自動新增元件"

#: admin/projects.rst:1511
msgid ""
"In case your project has dozen of translation files (e.g. for different "
"gettext domains, or parts of Android apps), you might want to import them "
"automatically. This can either be achieved from the command-line by "
"using :wladmin:`import_project` or :wladmin:`import_json`, or by installing "
"the :ref:`addon-weblate.discovery.discovery` add-on."
msgstr ""
"在您的專案有十多個翻譯檔案的情況下（例如不同的 gettext 域，或 Android 應用的"
"一部分），您會想要將它們自動匯入。可以透過使用 :wladmin:`import_project` "
"或 :wladmin:`import_json`，或者透過安裝 :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.discovery.discovery` 附加元件，透過指令列來達成。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1517
msgid ""
"To use the add-on, you first need to create a component for one translation "
"file (choose the one that is the least likely to be renamed or removed in "
"future), and install the add-on on this component."
msgstr ""
"要使用附加元件，首先您需要為一個翻譯檔案（選擇未來最不可能改名或刪除的那個）"
"建立一個元件，然後在該元件上安裝附加元件。"

#: admin/projects.rst:1521
msgid ""
"For the management commands, you need to create a project which will contain "
"all components and then run :wladmin:`import_project` "
"or :wladmin:`import_json`."
msgstr ""
"對於管理指令，您需要建立包含所有元件的專案，然後執"
"行 :wladmin:`import_project` 或 :wladmin:`import_json`。"

#: admin/sample.rst:4
msgid "Sample configuration"
msgstr "範例設定"

#: admin/sample.rst:6
msgid ""
"The following example is shipped as :file:`weblate/settings_example.py` with "
"Weblate:"
msgstr "Weblate 隨附的下列範例位於 :file:`weblate/settings_example.py`："

#: admin/support.rst:2
msgid "Getting support for Weblate"
msgstr "從 Weblate 獲得支援"

#: admin/support.rst:5
msgid ""
"*Weblate* is copylefted libre software with community support. Hosting "
"subscribers receive priority support at no extra charge. Prepaid help "
"packages are available for everyone, including self-hosting users. Find info "
"about current support offerings at https://weblate.org/support."
msgstr ""
"*Weblate* 是由社群支援、採 copyleft 授權的自由軟體。託管訂閱者無須額外付費即"
"可獲得優先支援。所有人都能購買預付協助方案，包括自行託管的使用者。目前的支援"
"方案請參閱 https://weblate.org/support。"

#: admin/support.rst:13
msgid "Integrating support"
msgstr "整合支援"

#: admin/support.rst:15
msgid ""
"Purchased support packages can optionally be integrated into your Weblate "
"`subscription management <https://weblate.org/user/>`_ interface, from where "
"you will find a link to it. Basic instance details about your installation "
"are also reported back to Weblate this way."
msgstr ""
"購買的支援方案可以選用地整合在您的 Weblate的 `subscription management "
"<https://weblate.org/user/>`_ 介面中，您可以在那裡找到它的連結。關於您的安裝"
"的基本事例的細節，也會以這種方式回饋給 Weblate。"

#: admin/support.rst:24
msgid "Info sent to the Weblate"
msgstr "提交給 Weblate 的資訊"

#: admin/support.rst:26
msgid "Your Weblate instance URL"
msgstr "您的 Weblate 執行個體 URL"

#: admin/support.rst:27
msgid "Its site title"
msgstr "網站標題"

#: admin/support.rst:28
msgid "The version you are running"
msgstr "您正在執行的版本"

#: admin/support.rst:29
msgid "Tallies of projects, components, languages, source strings, and users"
msgstr "專案、元件、語言、來源字串和使用者數目"

#: admin/support.rst:30
msgid "The public SSH key of your instance"
msgstr "您事件的 SSH 公開金鑰"

#: admin/support.rst:32
msgid "Additionally, if you turn on :ref:`discover-weblate`:"
msgstr "此外，當 :ref:`discover-weblate` 開啟時："

#: admin/support.rst:34
msgid "List of public and protected projects (name, URL, and website)."
msgstr "公開及受保護專案的清單（名稱、URL 及網站）。"

#: admin/support.rst:37
msgid ""
"Check what *Discover* shows publicly in the :ref:`discover-weblate` "
"description."
msgstr "在 :ref:`discover-weblate` 描述中檢查 *Discover* 公開顯示的內容。"

#: admin/support.rst:39
msgid "No other data is submitted."
msgstr "沒有提交其它資料。"

#: admin/support.rst:42
msgid "Integration services"
msgstr "整合服務"

#: admin/support.rst:44
msgid "See if your support package is still valid"
msgstr "查看您的支援包是否合法"

#: admin/support.rst:51
msgid ""
"Purchased support packages are already activated upon purchase and can be "
"used without integrating them."
msgstr "購買的支援方案在購買後已自動啟用，無需進行任何系統整合即可直接使用。"

#: admin/support.rst:56
msgid "Contacting customer care"
msgstr "聯絡客服"

#: admin/support.rst:60
msgid ""
"If you do not have a support package yet, please refer to the :doc:`/"
"contributing/issues` section for available community resources."
msgstr ""
"如果還沒有支援包，請參考 :doc:`/contributing/issues` 部分取得可用的社群資源。"

#: admin/support.rst:63
msgid ""
"Subscribers can reach Weblate Care directly through the following channels:"
msgstr "訂閱者可透過下列渠道直接聯絡到 Weblate Care："

#: admin/support.rst:65
msgid "Email support at care@weblate.org."
msgstr "電子郵件支援地址 care@weblate.org。"

#: admin/support.rst:66
msgid "The `customer care portal <https://care.weblate.org/>`_"
msgstr "`客服門戶網站 <https://care.weblate.org/>`_"

#: admin/support.rst:67
msgid ""
"The support form is available in the Weblate management interface "
"after :ref:`activate-support`."
msgstr "啟用 :ref:`activate-support` 後可在 Weblate 管理介面中看到支援表單。"

#: admin/support.rst:69
msgid ""
"A subscription ensures timely and reliable help with setup, maintenance, and "
"troubleshooting."
msgstr ""
"訂閱方案能確保您在安裝設定、系統維護及故障排除時，獲得即時且可靠的技術支援。"

#: admin/support.rst:73
msgid "**Sending encrypted content**"
msgstr "**傳送加密內容**"

#: admin/support.rst:75
msgid ""
"If you want to send an encrypted content, please use the public key for "
"care@weblate.org with ID ``0961 62CE 141D 7FE4 B15D A9FA 73D9 298A CB26 "
"03F0``."
msgstr ""
"如果想傳送加密內容，請使用 care@weblate.org 的公開金鑰，ID 為 ``0961 62CE "
"141D 7FE4 B15D A9FA 73D9 298A CB26 03F0``."

#: admin/support.rst:79
msgid ""
"This public key is available on the most commonly used key servers, using "
"WKD or `directly from weblate.org <https://weblate.org/.well-known/"
"openpgpkey/hu/7oq6zfqsndhzsmw94xm1e5yu8me8sjsx?l=care>`_."
msgstr ""
"最常使用的 key 伺服器上有這枚公開金鑰，使用 WKD 或 `直接從 weblate.org "
"<https://weblate.org/.well-known/openpgpkey/hu/"
"7oq6zfqsndhzsmw94xm1e5yu8me8sjsx?l=care>`_."

#: admin/support.rst:86
msgid "Discover Weblate"
msgstr "探索 Weblate"

#: admin/support.rst:90
msgid ""
"*Discover* is an opt-in service making it easier for translators to find "
"other Weblate instances and communities. Users can browse registered sites "
"and find projects to contribute to on https://weblate.org/discover/."
msgstr ""
"*探索* 是一項選用服務，讓譯者更容易找到其他 Weblate 執行個體及社群。使用者可"
"以在 https://weblate.org/discover/ 瀏覽已註冊的網站，尋找可以參與貢獻的專案。"

#: admin/support.rst:96
msgid "Getting listed"
msgstr "列入"

#: admin/support.rst:100
msgid ""
"Discover Weblate registration can be started directly from the management "
"interface without manually copying the activation token."
msgstr "不必手動複製啟用權杖，便可直接從管理介面開始註冊 Discover Weblate。"

#: admin/support.rst:105
msgid ""
"Make sure you are OK with publishing your instance name, URL, tally of "
"projects, components, and users, together with names of public and protected "
"projects for use on *Discover*."
msgstr ""
"請確認您同意在 *Discover* 上公開執行個體名稱、URL、專案、元件及使用者數量，以"
"及公開和受保護專案的名稱。"

#: admin/support.rst:109
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Discover Weblate` panel in the management interface to "
"manage the listing. If you have an activated support package, list your "
"server by clicking :guilabel:`Enable discovery`. If the instance is not "
"connected to weblate.org yet, start the registration by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Enable Discover Weblate`:"
msgstr ""
"使用管理介面中的 :guilabel:`Discover Weblate` 面板管理此清單項目。如果您已啟"
"用支援套件，請按一下 :guilabel:`啟用探索`，將您的伺服器列入清單。如果執行個體"
"尚未連線至 weblate.org，請按一下 :guilabel:`啟用 Discover Weblate` 開始註冊："

#: admin/support.rst:118
msgid ""
"This opens the registration form on weblate.org and returns to your Weblate "
"management interface to complete activation with discovery already enabled. "
"The registration flow can be used from an account that has a support "
"subscription, but it registers the Discover Weblate listing; activating a "
"purchased support package is handled by :ref:`activate-support`. Unlinking "
"the support package disables the Discover Weblate listing."
msgstr ""
"這會在 weblate.org 開啟註冊表單，然後返回您的 Weblate 管理介面完成啟用；此時"
"探索功能已啟用。具備支援訂閱的帳號也可使用此註冊流程，但此流程只會註冊 "
"Discover Weblate 清單項目；若要啟用已購買的支援套件，則由 :ref:`activate-"
"support` 處理。取消支援套件的連結會停用 Discover Weblate 清單項目。"

#: admin/support.rst:125
msgid ""
"All steps for listing a server manually, for example from older Weblate "
"versions:"
msgstr "以下是手動將伺服器列入清單的所有步驟，例如使用舊版 Weblate 時："

#: admin/support.rst:128
msgid "Register yourself at https://weblate.org/user/"
msgstr "在 https://weblate.org/user/ 進行註冊"

#: admin/support.rst:129
msgid ""
"Register your Weblate site at https://weblate.org/subscription/discovery/"
msgstr "在 https://weblate.org/subscription/discovery/ 註冊您的 Weblate 網站"

#: admin/support.rst:130
msgid "Copy the activation token into your Weblate management interface."
msgstr "將啟用權杖複製到 Weblate 管理介面。"

#: admin/support.rst:131
msgid ""
"Confirm you want your Weblate listed by clicking :guilabel:`Enable "
"discovery` from the :guilabel:`Discover Weblate` panel:"
msgstr ""
"在 :guilabel:`Discover Weblate` 面板中按一下 :guilabel:`啟用探索`，確認您要"
"將 Weblate 列入清單："

#: admin/support.rst:139
msgid "Listing customization"
msgstr "清單自訂"

#: admin/support.rst:141
msgid ""
"You are encouraged to provide an image (570 x 260 pixels) and description of "
"your Weblate site at https://weblate.org/user/. This improves your "
"instance’s visibility in the list."
msgstr ""
"建議您在 https://weblate.org/user/ 提供 Weblate 網站的圖片（570 × 260 像素）"
"及說明，讓執行個體在清單中更容易被看見。"

#: admin/translating.rst:2
msgid "Translation process"
msgstr "翻譯過程"

#: admin/translating.rst:9
msgid ""
"Everyone can add suggestions by default, to be accepted by signed in users. "
"Suggestion voting can be used to make use of a string when more than one "
"signed-in user agrees, by setting up the :ref:`component` "
"with :guilabel:`Suggestion voting` to turn on voting, "
"and :guilabel:`Automatically accept suggestions` to set a threshold for "
"accepted suggestions (this includes a vote from the user making the "
"suggestion if it is cast)."
msgstr ""
"依預設，所有人都能新增建議，再由已登入的使用者接受。當多名已登入使用者同意"
"時，可以透過建議投票採用字串：在 :ref:`component` 中啟用 :guilabel:`建議投票"
"`，並以 :guilabel:`自動接受建議` 設定接受建議的門檻（提出建議的使用者若有投"
"票，也會計入）。"

#: admin/translating.rst:18
msgid ""
"Once automatic acceptance is set up, normal users lose the privilege to "
"directly save translations or accept suggestions. This can be overridden "
"with the :guilabel:`Edit string when suggestions are "
"enforced` :ref:`permission <privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"一旦新增了自動接受，那麼普通使用者會失去直接儲存翻譯或接受建議的特權。要繞過"
"這一點，可以通過 :guilabel:`當建議強制時編輯字串` :ref:`permission "
"<privileges>`。"

#: admin/translating.rst:23
msgid ""
"You can combine these with :ref:`access control <access-control>` into one "
"of the following setups:"
msgstr ""
"您可以將這些與 :ref:`存取控制 <access-control>` 結合起來，形成下列設定之一："

#: admin/translating.rst:26
msgid ""
"Users suggest and vote for suggestions and a limited group controls what is "
"accepted."
msgstr "使用者提出建議並對建議進行投票，由一個有限的小組控制採納的內容。"

#: admin/translating.rst:29 admin/translating.rst:36
msgid "Turn on voting."
msgstr "開啟投票。"

#: admin/translating.rst:30
msgid "Turn off automatic acceptance."
msgstr "關閉自動接受"

#: admin/translating.rst:31
msgid "Don't let users save translations."
msgstr "不要讓使用者儲存翻譯。"

#: admin/translating.rst:33
msgid ""
"Users suggest and vote for suggestions with automatic acceptance once the "
"defined number of them agree."
msgstr ""
"使用者提出建議並對建議進行投票，一旦有規定數量的使用者同意，就自動接受。"

#: admin/translating.rst:37
msgid "Set the desired number of votes for automatic acceptance."
msgstr "設定自動接受建議的期望票數。"

#: admin/translating.rst:39
msgid ""
"Optional voting for suggestions. (Can optionally be used by users when they "
"are unsure about a translation by making multiple suggestions.)"
msgstr ""
"選用擇是否對建議投票。（使用者不確定翻譯時，可以提出多個建議，再選擇是否使用"
"投票功能。）"

#: admin/translating.rst:42
msgid "Only turn on voting."
msgstr "只開啟投票。"

#: admin/translating.rst:47
msgid "Additional info on source strings"
msgstr "來源字串的額外資訊"

#: admin/translating.rst:49
msgid ""
"Enhance the translation process by adding additional info to the strings "
"including explanations, string priorities, check flags and visual context. "
"Some of that info may be extracted from the translation files and some may "
"be added by editing the additional string info:"
msgstr ""
"透過向字串新增額外的資訊來增強翻譯過程，這些資訊包括解釋、字串優先順序、檢查"
"標記和視覺化情境。有些資訊可以從翻譯檔案中提取，有些可以透過編輯額外的字串資"
"訊新增："

#: admin/translating.rst:56
msgid ""
"Access this directly from the translation interface by clicking the \"Edit\" "
"icon next to :guilabel:`Screenshot context` or :guilabel:`Flags`."
msgstr ""
"可以通過點選緊鄰 :guilabel:`Screenshot context` 或 :guilabel:`Flags` 的 "
"\"Edit\" 標籤而從翻譯介面直接存取。"

#: admin/translating.rst:68
msgid "Strings prioritization"
msgstr "字串優先順序"

#: admin/translating.rst:70
msgid ""
"String priority can be changed to offer higher priority strings for "
"translation earlier by using the ``priority`` flag."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``priority`` 標記可以變更字串優先順序，更高優先順序的字串會更早地被提供"
"以進行翻譯。"

#: admin/translating.rst:75
msgid "This can be used to order the flow of translation in a logical manner."
msgstr "這可以用於以邏輯的方式將翻譯流程排序。"

#: admin/translating.rst:89
msgid ""
"The string flags are also inherited from the :ref:`component-check_flags` "
"at :ref:`component` and flags from the translation file (see :doc:`/"
"formats`)."
msgstr ""
"字串標記也繼承了 :ref:`component` 中的 :ref:`component-check_flags` 和翻譯檔"
"案中的標記（見 :doc:`/formats`）。"

#: admin/translating.rst:101 formats.rst:84 user/translating.rst:375
msgid "Explanation"
msgstr "解釋"

#: admin/translating.rst:105
msgid "In previous versions this has been called :guilabel:`Extra context`."
msgstr "在以前的版本中這被稱為 :guilabel:`額外情境`。"

#: admin/translating.rst:109
msgid "Support for syncing explanation with a file was introduced."
msgstr "引入了支援使用檔案來同步字串或翻譯的解釋的功能。"

#: admin/translating.rst:111
msgid ""
"Use the explanation to clarify scope or usage of the translation. You can "
"use Markdown to include links and other markup."
msgstr ""
"使用解釋來明確翻譯的範圍或翻譯的使用。您可以使用 Markdown 來包括連結和其它標"
"記。"

#: admin/translating.rst:114
msgid ""
"Some file formats support storing explanation within the file, "
"see :ref:`format-explanation`."
msgstr "某些檔案格式支援在檔案記憶體儲解釋資訊，見 :ref:`format-explanation`。"

#: admin/translating.rst:118
msgid ""
"Weblate can also display description present in the translation file for "
"some formats, see :ref:`format-description`."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 也可以為某些格式展示存在於翻譯檔案中的描述資訊，見 :ref:`format-"
"description`。"

#: admin/translating.rst:124
msgid "Screenshots and visual context"
msgstr "螢幕擷圖和視覺化情境"

#: admin/translating.rst:126
msgid ""
"You can upload a screenshot showing a given source string in use within your "
"program. This helps translators understand where it is used, and how it "
"should be translated."
msgstr ""
"您可以將顯示您程式中使用的給定來源字串的螢幕擷圖上傳。這幫助譯者理解它用在哪"
"裡，並且應該如何翻譯。"

#: admin/translating.rst:130
msgid "The uploaded screenshot is shown in the translation context sidebar:"
msgstr "上傳的螢幕擷圖顯示在翻譯情境側欄中："

#: admin/translating.rst:134
msgid ""
"In addition to :ref:`additional`, screenshots can be managed in the Weblate "
"UI, kept in sync from the repository, or handled through the :ref:`api`."
msgstr ""
"除 :ref:`additional`，也可以在 Weblate 使用者介面管理螢幕擷圖，從儲存庫保持同"
"步，或透過 :ref:`api` 進行處理。"

#: admin/translating.rst:138
msgid "Managing screenshots in the UI"
msgstr "在使用者介面中管理螢幕擷圖"

#: admin/translating.rst:140
msgid ""
"Each screenshot is stored for a specific translation language. In the "
"translate page, screenshots attached to the source language are shown for "
"every translation of the string, while screenshots attached to any other "
"language are shown only for that language. You can add a screenshot directly "
"from the translate page using :guilabel:`Add screenshot` in "
"the :guilabel:`Screenshot context` panel, or open the separate management "
"interface under the :guilabel:`Operations` menu. There you can upload "
"screenshots, assign them to source strings manually, or let Weblate find "
"strings in the image using text recognition (OCR) with the :guilabel:`Find "
"strings in image` button. Matching source strings can be assigned "
"individually, in a selected batch, or all at once."
msgstr ""
"一種翻譯語言儲存一張螢幕擷圖。在翻譯頁面中，來源語言字串每種語言的翻譯都顯示"
"附加到來源語言的螢幕擷圖，而附加到任何其他語言的螢幕擷圖均只在那種語言中顯"
"示。可以用 :guilabel:`螢幕擷圖情境` 中 :guilabel:`新增螢幕擷圖` 直接從翻譯頁"
"面新增螢幕擷圖，或者在 :guilabel:`操作` 選單下開啟單獨的管理介面。您可以在那"
"裡上傳螢幕擷圖，手動將它們分配給來源字串，或者透過 :guilabel:`在圖片中尋找字"
"串` 按鈕讓 Weblate 用文字辨識（OCR）在圖片中尋找字串。可逐一分配相符的字串"
"（按所選批次分配或一次性分配完）。"

#: admin/translating.rst:153
msgid ""
"The screenshot listing summarizes uploaded screenshots and lets you search "
"or filter them:"
msgstr "螢幕擷圖清單會彙整已上傳的螢幕擷圖，並讓您搜尋或篩選："

#: admin/translating.rst:158
msgid ""
"Once a screenshot is uploaded, this interface handles management and source "
"string association:"
msgstr "上傳螢幕擷圖後，就可以在這個介面進行管理以及和來源字串的關聯："

#: admin/translating.rst:163
msgid ""
"Use the screenshot listing search to find screenshots by name, repository "
"path, language, assigned source string, source string context, or source "
"string location. The search accepts plain text as well as advanced "
"screenshot queries, see :ref:`search-screenshots`. For example, use ``NOT "
"has:string`` to find unassigned screenshots, ``has:string`` to find assigned "
"screenshots, or ``repository:fastlane`` to review screenshots discovered "
"from repository paths."
msgstr ""
"使用螢幕擷圖清單搜尋，依名稱、儲存庫路徑、語言、已指派的來源字串、來源字串情"
"境或來源字串位置尋找螢幕擷圖。搜尋接受純文字和進階螢幕擷圖查詢，請參"
"閱 :ref:`search-screenshots`。例如，使用 ``NOT has:string`` 尋找未指派的螢幕"
"擷圖、使用 ``has:string`` 尋找已指派的螢幕擷圖，或使用 "
"``repository:fastlane`` 檢閱從儲存庫路徑探索到的螢幕擷圖。"

#: admin/translating.rst:170
msgid ""
"You can upload a screenshot from a local file, paste it from the clipboard, "
"or provide a URL to download an image from an external source. URL-based "
"uploads may be restricted based on the :setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_DOMAINS` "
"setting, which controls which domains are trusted for downloading external "
"assets, including any redirects followed while fetching the image, "
"and :setting:`ASSET_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, which rejects internal or non-public "
"targets unless they are included in :setting:`ASSET_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST`. "
"The :setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_SIZE` setting limits maximal size for the asset."
msgstr ""
"可以從本機檔案上傳螢幕擷圖，從剪貼簿貼上它，或提供從外部源下載圖片的 URL。根"
"據控制信任哪些網域下載外部資源的 :setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_DOMAINS` 設定，包括"
"取得圖片時跟隨的任何重定向，以及 :setting:`ASSET_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`，用於拒絕"
"未包含在 :setting:`ASSET_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST` 中的內部或非公開目"
"標。:setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_SIZE` 設定限制資源最大大小。"

#: admin/translating.rst:180
msgid "Managing screenshots from the repository"
msgstr "管理來自儲存庫的螢幕擷圖"

#: admin/translating.rst:182
msgid ""
"You can add or update screenshots directly from your Version Control System "
"(VCS) repository."
msgstr "您可以直接從您的版本控制系統儲存庫新增或更新螢幕擷圖。"

#: admin/translating.rst:185
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, you can either set a screenshot file mask when "
"creating a component, which will be monitored for updates in the repository, "
"or you can add or update screenshots when uploading them manually."
msgstr ""
"要開啟此功能，您可以在建立元件時設定螢幕擷圖檔案掩碼，以便在儲存庫中監視該元"
"件的更新。您也可以在手動上傳螢幕擷圖檔案時新增或更新它們。"

#: admin/translating.rst:189
msgid ""
"To connect a manually uploaded screenshot with later repository updates, "
"fill in :guilabel:`Repository path to screenshot` with the path tracked in "
"the repository."
msgstr ""
"要將手動上傳的螢幕擷圖和之後的儲存庫更新連線起來，用儲存庫中跟蹤的路徑填"
"充 :guilabel:`儲存庫的螢幕擷圖路徑`。"

#: admin/translating.rst:193
msgid ""
"When the repository is updated, the system will automatically scan for "
"changes. Existing screenshots in the repository will be updated, and new "
"screenshots matching the specified screenshot file mask will be added to the "
"component."
msgstr ""
"更新儲存庫時，系統會自動掃描變更。儲存庫中的現有螢幕擷圖會被更新，相符指定螢"
"幕擷圖檔案掩碼的新螢幕擷圖會被新增到元件中。"

#: admin/translating.rst:198
msgid "For application projects, a practical workflow is:"
msgstr "對於應用程式專案，實用的工作流程如下："

#: admin/translating.rst:200
msgid ""
"Capture source-language screenshots for the most visible user interface."
msgstr "擷取最醒目使用者介面的來源語言螢幕擷圖。"

#: admin/translating.rst:201
msgid ""
"Store them in a stable repository path, for example below :file:`fastlane/"
"metadata/android/en-US/images/phoneScreenshots/`."
msgstr ""
"將其儲存在固定的儲存庫路徑，例如 :file:`fastlane/metadata/android/en-US/"
"images/phoneScreenshots/` 下方。"

#: admin/translating.rst:203
msgid "Configure :ref:`component-screenshot_filemask` for that path."
msgstr "設定那個路徑的 :ref:`component-screenshot_filemask`。"

#: admin/translating.rst:204
msgid ""
"Update the component repository so Weblate discovers or refreshes the "
"screenshots."
msgstr "更新元件儲存庫，讓 Weblate 探索或重新整理螢幕擷圖。"

#: admin/translating.rst:206
msgid ""
"Use OCR or source string search to assign screenshots to the matching source "
"strings, and review the :guilabel:`Source strings without screenshots` "
"counter for important strings still missing visual context."
msgstr ""
"使用 OCR 或來源字串搜尋，將螢幕擷圖指派給相符的來源字串，並檢閱 :guilabel:`沒"
"有螢幕擷圖的來源字串` 計數器，確認仍缺少視覺內容的重要字串。"

#: admin/translating.rst:217
msgid "Managing screenshots through the API"
msgstr "透過 API 管理螢幕擷圖"

#: admin/translating.rst:219
msgid ""
"Screenshot workflows are also available through the REST API. "
"Use :http:get:`/api/components/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"screenshots/` to list screenshots for one component, :http:post:`/api/"
"screenshots/` to create screenshots, :http:post:`/api/screenshots/(int:id)/"
"file/` to replace the image, :http:post:`/api/screenshots/(int:id)/units/` "
"and :http:delete:`/api/screenshots/(int:id)/units/(int:unit_id)` to manage "
"source string associations, and :http:delete:`/api/screenshots/(int:id)/` to "
"delete screenshots. Screenshot API objects include the related translation "
"and the optional repository path used for repository-based updates."
msgstr ""
"也可透過 REST API 獲得螢幕擷圖工作流。用 :http:get:`/api/components/"
"(string:project)/(string:component)/screenshots/` 列出一個元件的螢幕擷"
"圖，:http:post:`/api/screenshots/` 建立螢幕擷圖，:http:post:`/api/"
"screenshots/(int:id)/file/` 替換圖片，:http:post:`/api/screenshots/(int:id)/"
"units/` 和 :http:delete:`/api/screenshots/(int:id)/units/(int:unit_id)` 管理"
"來源字串關聯，:http:delete:`/api/screenshots/(int:id)/` 來刪除螢幕擷圖。螢幕"
"擷圖 API 物件包括相關翻譯和用於基於儲存庫的更新的選用儲存庫路徑。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:2
msgid "Upgrading Weblate"
msgstr "升級 Weblate"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:5
msgid "Docker image upgrades"
msgstr "Docker 映像升級"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:7
msgid ""
"The official Weblate Docker image (see :doc:`install/docker`) integrates all "
"upgrade steps. Typically, no manual interaction is needed beyond pulling the "
"latest (or at least newer) version."
msgstr ""
"官方 Weblate Docker 映像（請參閱 :doc:`install/docker`）整合了所有升級步驟。"
"通常無需除拉取最新（或至少較新）版本之外的人工互動。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:18
msgid "Generic upgrade instructions"
msgstr "通用升級說明"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:20
msgid ""
"Always look for new changes to :ref:`requirements` before upgrading. Once "
"all requirements are installed or upgraded, ensure your :file:`settings.py` "
"matches the changes in the configuration "
"(consult :file:`settings_example.py` for correct values)."
msgstr ""
"升級前，請始終檢查 :ref:`requirements` 的新變更。安裝或升級所有的必需項後，請"
"確保您的 :file:`settings.py` 相符設定中的變更（正確的值請"
"見 :file:`settings_example.py`）。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:25
msgid ""
"Always check :ref:`version-specific-instructions` before upgrading. If you "
"are skipping any versions, be sure to follow instructions for all versions "
"you are skipping during such upgrade. It's sometimes better to upgrade "
"gradually to an intermediate version to ensure a smooth migration. Upgrading "
"across multiple releases should work, but is not as well tested as single "
"version upgrades!"
msgstr ""
"在升級前務必查看 :ref:`version-specific-instructions`。在您略過一些版本的情況"
"下，請務必遵從在升級中您所略過的所有版本的說明。有時最好升級到一些中間版本以"
"確保順利移轉。跨多個發行版本的升級應該可行，但還沒有像單一版本升級一樣經過充"
"分測試！"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:33
msgid ""
"Always back up the full database before upgrading, so that you can roll back "
"the database if the upgrade fails, see :doc:`backup`."
msgstr ""
"請在升級前始終備份完整資料庫，以便您可以在升級失敗的情況下回復資料庫，參"
"閱 :doc:`backup`。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:36
msgid ""
"Wait for the Celery queues to become empty, then stop the WSGI and Celery "
"processes to avoid old processes running while upgrading. Otherwise "
"incompatible changes in the database might occur."
msgstr ""
"請等待 Celery 佇列變空，然後停止 WSGI 和 Celery 處理程序避免升級時舊處理程序"
"執行。否則可能發生不相容的資料庫變更。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:40
msgid ""
"The Celery task queue is not a stable interface across releases, so queued "
"tasks from the old version are not guaranteed to work after the upgrade. You "
"can monitor queue length in the :ref:`management-interface` or by "
"using :wladmin:`celery_queues`."
msgstr ""
"Celery 任務佇列不是跨版本的穩定介面，因此不保證來自舊版本的佇列任務在升級後能"
"正常工作。可以在 :ref:`management-interface` 中監控佇列長度或使"
"用 :wladmin:`celery_queues` 來監控佇列長度。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:45
msgid "Upgrade Weblate"
msgstr "升級 Weblate"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:47
msgid "For pip installs it can be achieved by:"
msgstr "對於 pip 安裝，可以通過後面的來達成："

#: admin/upgrade.rst:53
msgid "Or, if you just want to get the latest released version:"
msgstr "或者，如果您只想取得最新發佈的版本："

#: admin/upgrade.rst:59
msgid "If you don't want to install all of the optional dependencies do:"
msgstr "如果不想安裝所有選用相依套件，請執行以下操作："

#: admin/upgrade.rst:65
msgid ""
"Using Git checkout, you need to fetch new source code and update your "
"installation:"
msgstr "使用 Git checkout，您需要取回新的原始碼並更新您的安裝："

#: admin/upgrade.rst:78
msgid ""
"New Weblate releases might have new :ref:`python-deps`, check if they cover "
"the features you want."
msgstr ""
"新的 Weblate 發行版本可能加入新的 :ref:`python-deps`，請確認其中是否包含您需"
"要的功能。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:81
msgid ""
"Upgrade the configuration file by following "
"either :file:`settings_example.py`, or :ref:`version-specific-instructions`."
msgstr ""
"升級設定檔案，所需的步驟請參考 :file:`settings_example.py` 或 :ref:`version-"
"specific-instructions`。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:84
msgid "Upgrade the database:"
msgstr "升級資料庫："

#: admin/upgrade.rst:90
msgid ""
"Collect updated static files (see :ref:`server` and :ref:`static-files`):"
msgstr "收集升級的靜態檔案（請參閱 :ref:`server` 和 :ref:`static-files`）："

#: admin/upgrade.rst:96
msgid ""
"If you are running an installation from Git, you should also regenerate "
"locale files every time you upgrade. You can do this by invoking:"
msgstr ""
"如果執行的是從 Git 安裝的版本，每次升級時也應重新產生語系檔案。請執行："

#: admin/upgrade.rst:103
msgid "Verify that your setup is sane (see also :ref:`production`):"
msgstr "驗證您的設定是否合理 （另請參閱 :ref:`production`）："

#: admin/upgrade.rst:109
msgid "Restart the Celery worker (see :ref:`celery`)."
msgstr "重新啟動 Celery worker （請參閱 :ref:`celery`）。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:111
msgid ""
"Some upgrades run translation-memory scope backfill and consolidation in the "
"background using periodic Celery tasks. Keep Celery running after the "
"upgrade and monitor progress in :guilabel:`Administration` "
"> :guilabel:`Performance report`. See :ref:`memory-scopes` for details."
msgstr ""
"部分升級會使用定期 Celery 工作，在背景執行翻譯記憶作用範圍回填及整併。升級後"
"請讓 Celery 保持執行，並在 :guilabel:`管理` > :guilabel:`效能報告` 中監看進"
"度。詳細資訊請參閱 :ref:`memory-scopes`。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:119
msgid "Version-specific instructions"
msgstr "版本特定說明"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:123
msgid ""
"Version specific instructions are now included in the release notes, "
"see :doc:`/changes`."
msgstr "特定版本的操作指南現在包含在發行日志中，見 :doc:`/changes`。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:127
msgid "Upgrade from an older unsupported release"
msgstr "從較舊的不受支援的版本進行升級"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:129
msgid ""
"Direct upgrades are only supported for releases from the current or previous "
"calendar year. If you need to upgrade across this boundary, upgrade first to "
"an intermediate version as listed below. Upgrades skipping this step are not "
"supported and will break."
msgstr ""
"只支援來自目前或上個日曆年的版本進行直接升級。如果您需要跨越這個邊界進行升"
"級，請先升級到下方所列的中間版本。不支援跳過這一步進行升級，這樣升級會出問"
"題。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:134
msgid ""
"If you are upgrading from the 2.x release, always first upgrade to 3.0.1."
msgstr "如果從 2.x 釋出版本升級，請始終先升級到 3.0.1。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:135
msgid ""
"If you are upgrading from the 3.x release, always first upgrade to 4.0.4."
msgstr "如果從 3.x 釋出版本升級，請始終首先升級到 4.0.4。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:136
msgid ""
"If you are upgrading from the 4.x release, always first upgrade to 5.0.2."
msgstr "如果從 4.x 釋出版本升級，請首先升級到 5.0.2。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:137
msgid "If you are upgrading from 5.0.x-5.9.x, always first upgrade to 5.10.4."
msgstr "如果從 5.0.x-5.9.x 升級，請始終先升級到 5.10.4。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:138
msgid "Upgrades from 5.10.x and newer are currently directly supported."
msgstr "目前直接支援從 5.10.x 和更新版本進行升級。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:142
msgid ""
"`Upgrade from 2.20 to 3.0 in Weblate 3.0 documentation <https://"
"docs.weblate.org/en/weblate-3.0.1/admin/upgrade.html#upgrade-3>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Weblate 3.0 文件中從 2.20 升級到 3.0 的內容 <https://docs.weblate.org/en/"
"weblate-3.0.1/admin/upgrade.html#upgrade-3>`_"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:143
msgid ""
"`Upgrade from 3.11 to 4.0 in Weblate 4.0 documentation <https://"
"docs.weblate.org/en/weblate-4.0.4/admin/upgrade.html#upgrade-from-3-11-"
"to-4-0>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Weblate 4.0 文件中從 3.11 升級到 4.0 的內容 <https://docs.weblate.org/en/"
"weblate-4.0.4/admin/upgrade.html#upgrade-from-3-11-to-4-0>`_"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:144
msgid ""
"`Upgrade from 4.x to 5.0.2 in Weblate 5.0 documentation <https://"
"docs.weblate.org/en/weblate-5.0.2/changes.html>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Weblate 5.0 文件中從 4.x 升級到 5.0.2 的內容 <https://docs.weblate.org/en/"
"weblate-5.0.2/changes.html>`_"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:149
msgid "Migrating from other databases to PostgreSQL"
msgstr "從其它資料庫移轉到 PostgreSQL"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:153
msgid ""
"MySQL and MariaDB are no longer supported in Weblate. You must migrate to "
"PostgreSQL before upgrading."
msgstr "Weblate 不再支援 MySQL 與 MariaDB。您必須先移轉至 PostgreSQL 再升級。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:156
msgid ""
"If you are running Weblate with MySQL or MariaDB, consider migrating to "
"PostgreSQL for better performance by doing the following steps. Remember to "
"stop both, the web and Celery servers beforehand, otherwise you might end up "
"with inconsistent data."
msgstr ""
"如果您目前使用 MySQL 或 MariaDB 執行 Weblate，請考慮執行以下步驟移轉到 "
"PostgreSQL，因為 Weblate 與它搭配效能更好。請記住移轉前要停止 Web 和 Celery "
"伺服器，否則會導致不一致的資料。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:164
msgid ""
"It is usually a good idea to run Weblate in a separate database, and a "
"separate user account:"
msgstr "通常來說，用單獨的資料庫中和單獨的使用者帳號執行 Weblate 是個好主意："

#: admin/upgrade.rst:180
msgid "Migrating to PostgreSQL using pgloader"
msgstr "使用 pgloader 移轉到 PostgreSQL"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:182
msgid ""
"The `pgloader`_ is a generic migration tool to migrate data to PostgreSQL. "
"You can use it to migrate your Weblate database."
msgstr ""
"`pgloader`_ 是通用移轉工具，將資料移轉到 PostgreSQL。您可以使用它來移轉您的 "
"Weblate 資料庫。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:185
msgid "Adjust your :file:`settings.py` to use PostgreSQL as database."
msgstr "調整您的 :file:`settings.py` 以使用 PostgreSQL 作為資料庫。"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:187
msgid "Migrate the schema in the PostgreSQL database:"
msgstr "移轉 PostgreSQL 中的模式："

#: admin/upgrade.rst:194
msgid ""
"3. Run the pgloader to transfer the data. The following script can be used "
"to migrate the database, but you might want to learn more about `pgloader`_ "
"to better understand what it does, and tweak it to match your setup:"
msgstr ""
"3. 執行 pgloader 來轉移資料。後面的指令碼可以用於移轉資料庫，但您會想要學習更"
"多關於 `pgloader`_ 的知識，來更好理解它做什麼以及調整它來相符您的設定："

#: admin/upgrade.rst:216
msgid "Migrating from Pootle"
msgstr "從 Pootle 移轉"

#: admin/upgrade.rst:218
msgid ""
"As Weblate was originally written as a replacement for Pootle, it is "
"supported to migrate the user accounts from it. You can dump the users from "
"Pootle and import them using :wladmin:`importusers`."
msgstr ""
"由於 Weblate 最初是作為 Pootle 的替代品而編寫的，因此支援從 Pootle 移轉使用者"
"帳號。您可以從 Pootle 轉儲使用者，並使用 :wladmin:`importusers` 將其匯入。"

#: admin/workspaces.rst:4 snippets/permissions.rst:329
msgid "Workspaces"
msgstr "工作空間"

#: admin/workspaces.rst:6
msgid ""
"Workspaces group related translation projects. They sit above projects and "
"provide a shared place for project listings, workspace-scoped access "
"control, and billing details when the billing module is enabled."
msgstr ""
"工作空間會將相關翻譯專案分組。工作空間位於專案上層，提供共用位置來顯示專案清"
"單、進行工作空間範圍的存取控制，以及在啟用計費模組時顯示計費詳細資料。"

#: admin/workspaces.rst:10
msgid ""
"Workspace membership does not grant access to translate or manage projects "
"in the workspace. Project access is still controlled by the project access "
"control settings and project teams, see :ref:`acl`."
msgstr ""
"工作空間成員資格不會授予翻譯或管理其中專案的存取權。專案存取仍由專案存取控制"
"設定和專案團隊控制，請參閱 :ref:`acl`。"

#: admin/workspaces.rst:14
msgid ""
"The workspace page lists projects in that workspace that you can access."
msgstr "工作區頁面列舉了您可以存取的那個工作區的專案。"

#: admin/workspaces.rst:18
msgid ""
"Signed-in users can also review grouped project and component findings on "
"the workspace :guilabel:`Diagnostics` tab. See :ref:`diagnostics-overviews`."
msgstr ""
"已登入的使用者也可以在工作空間的 :guilabel:`診斷` 分頁中，檢閱依專案與元件分"
"組的診斷結果。請參閱 :ref:`diagnostics-overviews`。"

#: admin/workspaces.rst:21
msgid ""
"You can list all workspaces in the management interface "
"at :guilabel:`Manage` ↓ :guilabel:`Workspaces`."
msgstr ""
