#: api.rst:136
msgid ""
"For the :http:method:`POST` method the parameters can be specified either as "
"form submission (:mimetype:`application/x-www-form-urlencoded`) or as JSON "
"(:mimetype:`application/json`)."
msgstr ""
"對於 :http:method:`POST` 方法，參數可以指定為表格提交"
"（:mimetype:`application/x-www-form-urlencoded`）或 JSON "
"（:mimetype:`application/json`）。"

#: api.rst:140
msgid "**Form request example:**"
msgstr "**表單請求範例：**"

#: api.rst:152
msgid "**JSON request example:**"
msgstr "**JSON 請求範例：**"

#: api.rst:174
msgid "**CURL JSON example:**"
msgstr "**CURL JSON 範例：**"

#: api.rst:187
msgid "Components and categories"
msgstr "元件與類別"

#: api.rst:189
msgid ""
"To access a component which is nested inside a :ref:`category`, you need to "
"URL encode the category name into a component name separated with a slash. "
"For example ``usage`` placed in a ``docs`` category needs to be used as "
"``docs%252Fusage``. Full URL in this case would be for example ``https://"
"example.com/api/components/hello/docs%252Fusage/repository/``."
msgstr ""
"若要存取巢狀於 :ref:`category` 中的元件，您必須將分類名稱進行 URL 編碼，成為"
"以斜線分隔的元件名稱。例如，``docs`` 分類中的 ``usage`` 必須寫成 "
"``docs%252Fusage``；完整 URL 會是 ``https://example.com/api/components/hello/"
"docs%252Fusage/repository/``。"

#: api.rst:198
msgid "API rate limiting"
msgstr "API 速率限制"

#: api.rst:200
msgid ""
"The API requests are rate limited; the default configuration limits it to "
"100 requests per day for anonymous users and 5000 requests per hour for "
"authenticated users."
msgstr ""
"這個 API 請求限制了速率；對於匿名使用者預設設定限制為每天 100 個請求，對於身"
"分驗證的使用者限制為每小時 5000 個請求。"

#: api.rst:204
msgid ""
"Rate limiting can be adjusted in the :file:`settings.py`; see `Throttling in "
"Django REST framework documentation <https://www.django-rest-framework.org/"
"api-guide/throttling/>`_ for more details how to configure it."
msgstr ""
"速率限制可以在 :file:`settings.py` 中調整；如何設定它的更多細節請參閱 "
"`Throttling in Django REST framework documentation <https://www.django-rest-"
"framework.org/api-guide/throttling/>`_。"

#: api.rst:208
msgid ""
"In the Docker container this can be configured "
"using :envvar:`WEBLATE_API_RATELIMIT_ANON` "
"and :envvar:`WEBLATE_API_RATELIMIT_USER`."
msgstr ""
"在 Docker 容器中可使用 :envvar:`WEBLATE_API_RATELIMIT_ANON` "
"和 :envvar:`WEBLATE_API_RATELIMIT_USER` 對此進行設定。"

#: api.rst:211
msgid "The status of rate limiting is reported in following headers:"
msgstr "速率限制在後面的標頭中報告："

#: api.rst:214
msgid "Allowed number of requests to perform"
msgstr "允許執行的請求數"

#: api.rst:216
msgid "Remaining number of requests to perform"
msgstr "剩餘的執行請求數"

#: api.rst:218
msgid "Number of seconds until the rate-limit window resets"
msgstr "直到速率限制視窗重設時的秒數"

#: api.rst:223
msgid "Added ratelimiting status headers."
msgstr "新增了速率限制狀態標頭。"

