msgstr "記憶"

#: api.rst:2586
msgid "Units"
msgstr "單元"

#: api.rst:2588
msgid ""
"A `unit` is a single piece of a translation which pairs a source string with "
"a corresponding translated string and also contains some related metadata. "
"The term is derived from "
"the :py:class:`tt:translate.storage.base.TranslationUnit` in Translate "
"Toolkit and XLIFF."
msgstr ""
