#: changes/v5.rst:2165
msgid "New features"
msgstr "新功能"

#: changes.rst:8
msgid ""
"Workspaces now provide aggregate translation statistics and historical "
"metrics."
msgstr ""

#: changes.rst:9
msgid ""
"Added API endpoints for listing, adding, accepting, rejecting, and voting on "
"translation suggestions."
msgstr "新增了可列出、新增、接受、拒絕翻譯建議及對其投票的 API 端點。"

#: changes.rst:10
msgid ""
":doc:`Translation reports </devel/reporting>` are now generated in the "
"background, stored for later download, available at workspace scope, and "
"include translator work analysis."
msgstr ""
":doc:`翻譯報告 </devel/reporting>` 現在會在背景產生並加以儲存，以供稍後下載；"
"這些報告可在工作空間層級使用，且包含譯者工作分析。"

#: changes.rst:11
msgid ""
"Added :guilabel:`Use keywords exclusively` option to :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.gettext.xgettext`, allowing projects to disable xgettext default "
"keywords and rely only on a custom keyword."
msgstr ""
"為 :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.xgettext` 新增 :guilabel:`僅使用關鍵字` 選項，"
"讓專案能停用 xgettext 預設關鍵字，且僅使用自訂關鍵字。"

