#: changes/v5.rst:2173
msgid "Improvements"
msgstr "改進"

#: changes.rst:15
msgid ""
"Added grouped project and workspace :guilabel:`Diagnostics` views with "
"state, severity, category, and actionable-by-user filters."
msgstr ""
"新增分組顯示的專案與工作空間 :guilabel:`診斷` 檢視，並提供狀態、嚴重程度、類"
"別，以及使用者是否可處理等篩選條件。"

#: changes.rst:16
msgid ""
"Component diagnostics now record dismissal ownership, reopen after relevant "
"changes, and notify only project maintainers who can act on warnings and "
"errors."
msgstr ""
"元件診斷現在會記錄由誰關閉，並在相關變更發生後重新開啟，且僅通知能處理警告與"
"錯誤的專案維護人員。"

#: changes.rst:17
msgid ""
":ref:`Add-on activity logs <addon-activity-logging>` now distinguish "
"pending, successful, failed, and skipped executions and explain why an add-"
"on was skipped."
msgstr ""
":ref:`附加元件活動記錄 <addon-activity-logging>` 現在會區分待處理、成功、失敗"
"及已略過的執行，並說明略過附加元件的原因。"

#: changes.rst:18
msgid ""
"Add-on management now uses separate configuration, logs, and components tabs."
msgstr ""

#: changes.rst:19
msgid ""
"Expanded :ref:`change-actions` documentation with detailed event semantics "
"and improved OpenAPI schema accuracy."
msgstr ""
"擴充 :ref:`change-actions` 說明文件，加入詳細的事件語意，並提升 OpenAPI 結構"
"描述的準確性。"

#: changes.rst:20
msgid ""
"Improved matrix view loading performance when displaying multiple languages."
msgstr "改善矩陣檢視顯示多種語言時的載入效能。"

#: changes.rst:21
msgid ""
"Translation memory management pages now load origin summaries with a single "
"database aggregation."
msgstr "翻譯記憶管理頁面現在僅需一次資料庫彙總，即可載入來源摘要。"

#: changes.rst:22
msgid ""
"Dashboard component list tabs now load without processing unrelated "
"component lists."
msgstr "控制台元件清單的分頁現在無須處理不相關的元件清單即可載入。"

#: changes.rst:23
msgid ""
"Static assets now use content-hashed filenames, and CAPTCHA JavaScript is "
"loaded only when needed."
msgstr ""
"靜態資產現在使用名稱含內容雜湊值的檔案，且僅在需要時載入 CAPTCHA JavaScript。"

#: changes.rst:24
msgid ""
":ref:`Empty workspaces <workspace-removal>` not associated with billing can "
"now be removed from the workspace :guilabel:`Operations` menu."
msgstr ""

#: changes.rst:25
msgid ""
":ref:`mt-aws` machine translation now supports configuring formality, "
"brevity, and profanity masking."
msgstr ":ref:`mt-aws` 機器翻譯現在支援設定正式程度、簡潔程度及不雅字詞遮罩。"

#: changes.rst:26
msgid ""
"Improved :ref:`screenshots` OCR reliability and error reporting when "
"downloading recognition data."
msgstr "改善 :ref:`screenshots` OCR 的可靠性，以及下載辨識資料時的錯誤回報。"

#: changes.rst:27
msgid ""
"Celery workers now prefetch fewer tasks by default to reduce memory usage "
"and improve task distribution."
msgstr ""
"Celery worker 現在預設會預先擷取較少的任務，以降低記憶體用量並改善任務分配。"

#: changes.rst:28
msgid ""
"Improved the recommended :ref:`running-granian` configuration and Docker "
"container worker resilience for Weblate's WSGI workload."
msgstr ""
"改善建議使用的 :ref:`running-granian` 設定，並提高 Docker 容器 worker 執行 "
"Weblate WSGI 工作負載時的韌性。"

#: changes.rst:29
msgid "Deployment checks now detect corrupted PostgreSQL relation statistics."
msgstr "部署檢查現在可偵測損毀的 PostgreSQL 關聯統計資料。"

#: changes.rst:30
msgid ""
":ref:`Community diagnostics <alerts>` now show source-string screenshot "
"coverage, recommend key translation-instruction topics, and distinguish "
"inbound from outbound repository automation."
msgstr ""

