#: changes.rst:34
msgid ""
"Category, project, and comment statistics now stay consistent after "
"component topology and comment changes, and category metrics are collected "
"correctly."
msgstr ""

#: changes.rst:35
msgid ""
"Mercurial repository filenames beginning with a dash are now handled safely."
msgstr ""

#: changes.rst:36
msgid ""
"Self-service REST API e-mail changes are now restricted to verified "
"addresses."
msgstr "透過自助式 REST API 變更電子郵件地址時，現在僅能使用已驗證的地址。"

#: changes.rst:37
msgid ""
"REST API authorization now consistently protects internal accounts, "
"restricted components, add-on configuration, component sharing, repository "
"links, and review states."
msgstr ""
"REST API 授權現在會一致保護內部帳號、受限元件、附加元件設定、元件共用、儲存庫"
"連結及審閱狀態。"

#: changes.rst:38
msgid ""
"Project backup imports now skip repository-linked components when the "
"importer cannot access the target component."
msgstr ""

#: changes.rst:39
msgid ""
"Suggestion submission and rejection now reject excessively long suggestion "
"text and rejection reasons."
msgstr ""

#: changes.rst:40
msgid ""
"Restricted components are now available on Hosted Weblate when the billing "
"plan permits private projects."
msgstr "當計費方案允許私密專案時，Hosted Weblate 現在可使用受限元件。"

#: changes.rst:41
msgid ""
"Machine translation and translation memory AJAX lookups no longer disclose "
"whether inaccessible unit IDs exist."
msgstr ""
"機器翻譯與翻譯記憶的 AJAX 查詢，現在不再洩漏無法存取的單元 ID 是否存在。"

#: changes.rst:42
msgid ""
":ref:`RSS feeds <rss>` no longer disclose change history from inaccessible "
"projects or restricted components."
msgstr ":ref:`RSS 摘要 <rss>` 現在不再洩漏無法存取的專案或受限元件的變更歷程。"

