msgstr "相容性"

#: changes.rst:46
msgid ""
"django-compressor is no longer used, and the ``COMPRESS_*`` settings have "
"been removed."
msgstr "不再使用 django-compressor，並已移除 ``COMPRESS_*`` 設定。"

#: changes.rst:47
msgid ""
"Legal document styling is now provided through an overridable template "
"instead of Weblate's global stylesheet. See :ref:`legal-customization`."
msgstr ""

#: changes.rst:48
msgid ""
"The project and component ``credits`` REST API endpoints and their "
"``credits_url`` response fields have been replaced by scoped ``reports`` "
"endpoints and ``reports_url``. Credits report generation is now "
"asynchronous; clients need to submit a ``credits`` report, follow the "
"returned task URL, and fetch the completed report. See :http:post:`/api/"
"reports/`."
msgstr ""
"專案與元件的 ``credits`` REST API 端點及其 ``credits_url`` 回應欄位，已由限定"
"範圍的 ``reports`` 端點及 ``reports_url`` 取代。譯者名錄報告現在會以非同步方"
"式產生；用戶端必須提交 ``credits`` 報告、前往傳回的工作 URL，然後擷取已完成的"
"報告。請參閱 :http:post:`/api/reports/`。"

