msgid "Contributors"
msgstr "貢獻者"

#: changes.rst:61
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/167?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`所有變更詳情 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/167?"
"closed=1>`__。"

#: changes.rst:64
msgid "Weblate 2026.7.1"
msgstr "Weblate 2026.7.1"

#: changes.rst:66
msgid "*Released on July 10th 2026.*"
msgstr "*發佈於 2026 年 7 月 10 日。*"

#: changes.rst:70
msgid ""
"Added :setting:`INTERNAL_BOT_EMAIL_TEMPLATE` to customize internal bot e-"
"mail addresses."
msgstr ""
"新增 :setting:`INTERNAL_BOT_EMAIL_TEMPLATE`，以自訂內部機器人電子郵件地址。"

#: changes.rst:74
msgid "Restricted components now show a status icon in component listings."
msgstr "受限元件現在在元件清單中顯示狀態圖示。"

#: changes.rst:75
msgid ""
"Permission checks now reuse materialized team membership data from "
"lightweight relation lookups."
msgstr "權限檢查現在會重複使用從輕量關聯查詢取得的具體化團隊成員資格資料。"

#: changes.rst:76
msgid ""
"Documented that intermediate language files are hidden from language "
"listings and can make target strings read-only."
msgstr ""
"檔案現在已說明：中繼語言檔案會從語言清單隱藏，也可能使目標字串變成唯讀。"

#: changes.rst:77
msgid ""
"Component diagnostics now warn when regular :ref:`gettext` PO files are "
"configured as monolingual PO files."
msgstr ""
"元件診斷現在會在一般 :ref:`gettext` PO 檔案被設定為單語 PO 檔案時發出警告。"

#: changes.rst:78
msgid ""
"Translation memory fuzzy lookups are now faster on large translation "
"memories."
msgstr "大型翻譯記憶中進行翻譯記憶模糊查詢的速度更快了。"

#: changes.rst:79
msgid ""
"Permission denied messages when saving translations, editing glossaries, or "
"voting on suggestions now show more specific reasons."
msgstr ""
"儲存翻譯、編輯詞彙表或對建議投票時顯示的權限遭拒訊息，現在會提供更具體的原"
"因。"

#: changes.rst:80
msgid ""
"Comment notifications for strings you translated now also include strings "
"you previously commented on or suggested translations for."
msgstr "您所翻譯字串的留言通知，現在也會包含您先前曾留言或提出翻譯建議的字串。"

#: changes.rst:81
msgid ""
"Comments and suggestions now auto-watch the project "
"when :guilabel:`Automatically watch projects on contribution` is enabled."
msgstr ""
"啟用 :guilabel:`自動關注作出貢獻的專案` 時使用者寫評論和提翻譯建議會讓使用者"
"自動關注該專案。"

#: changes.rst:82
msgid ""
"Clarified Hosted Weblate repository access guidance in :doc:`/admin/code-"
"hosting`."
msgstr "釐清 :doc:`/admin/code-hosting` 中 Hosted Weblate 儲存庫存取操作指南。"

#: changes.rst:83
msgid ""
":ref:`search-strings` now includes filters for comments by the current user "
"and separate source string comment lookups."
msgstr ""
":ref:`search-strings` 現在包含目前使用者所留留言的篩選條件，以及個別查詢來源"
"字串留言的功能。"

#: changes.rst:84
msgid ""
"Code-hosting account pages now consistently use :guilabel:`Code-hosting "
"connections` and provider-neutral connected account wording."
msgstr ""
"程式碼託管帳號頁面現在一致使用 :guilabel:`程式碼託管連線`，並以不限定服務提供"
"者的措辭描述已連結帳號。"

#: changes.rst:85
msgid ""
":ref:`discover-weblate` registration can now be started from the management "
"interface without manually copying the activation token."
msgstr ""
":ref:`discover-weblate` 註冊現在可以直接從管理介面開始，不必手動複製啟用權"
"杖。"

#: changes.rst:86
msgid ""
":ref:`discover-weblate` can now be managed from a dedicated management "
"panel, registration starts with discovery enabled, and protected projects "
"are included in the listing."
msgstr ""
":ref:`discover-weblate` 現在可從專用管理面板進行管理；註冊時會預設啟用探索功"
"能，且清單會包含受保護的專案。"

#: changes.rst:87
msgid ""
"Updated the :ref:`mt-openai`, :ref:`mt-mistral`, and :ref:`mt-anthropic` "
"model lists for currently supported models."
msgstr ""
"更新 :ref:`mt-openai`、:ref:`mt-mistral` 及 :ref:`mt-anthropic` 的模型清單，"
"以納入目前支援的模型。"

#: changes.rst:91
msgid ""
"Filtered translation and zen navigation now reuse a stable session result "
"list, keeping positions and counts stable after translated strings leave the "
"filter."
msgstr ""
"經篩選的翻譯及 Zen 瀏覽功能現在會重複使用固定的工作階段結果清單，在已翻譯字串"
"離開篩選結果後，仍可保持位置和數量穩定。"

#: changes.rst:92
msgid "Component priority icons are no longer shown on translation listings."
msgstr "不再在翻譯清單中顯示元件優先順序圖示。"

#: changes.rst:93
msgid ""
":ref:`check-punctuation-spacing` no longer flags Markdown image markers as "
"French punctuation and now shows which punctuation marks triggered the check."
msgstr ""
":ref:`check-punctuation-spacing` 不再將 Markdown 圖片標記視為法文標點，且現在"
"會顯示觸發檢查的標點符號。"

#: changes.rst:94
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.fedora_messaging.publish` received several reliability "
"fixes."
msgstr ":ref:`addon-weblate.fedora_messaging.publish` 已完成多項可靠性修正。"

#: changes.rst:95
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Things to check` panel no longer uses error highlighting for "
"suggestions and other non-error translation states."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`待檢查項目` 面板不再以錯誤醒目提示顯示建議及其他非錯誤的翻譯狀態。"

#: changes.rst:96
msgid ""
"Translation workflow customization now makes it clearer when per-language "
"workflow settings are disabled until customization is enabled."
msgstr ""
"翻譯工作流程自訂功能現在會更清楚說明：啟用自訂功能前，個別語言的工作流程設定"
"會停用。"

#: changes.rst:97
msgid "Anonymous user permission caches are now isolated between requests."
msgstr "匿名使用者的權限快取現在會在各項要求之間隔離。"

#: changes.rst:98
msgid ""
"GitHub App setup now explains that a workspace is required instead of "
"showing a permission error when no workspace exists."
msgstr ""
"現在沒有工作空間時，GitHub App 設定會說明必須具備工作空間，而非顯示權限錯誤。"

#: changes.rst:99
msgid ""
"LLM automatic suggestion settings no longer show ``null`` for empty language-"
"specific instructions."
msgstr "LLM 自動建議設定不再為空白的特定語言說明顯示 ``null``。"

#: changes.rst:100
msgid ""
"File format feature tables now better match actual format support, including "
"descriptions, context, plural metadata, obsolete string removal, specialized "
"file extensions, and merged variants."
msgstr ""
"各檔案格式的功能對照表現在能更準確反映實際格式支援情形，包括說明、上下文、複"
"數形式中繼資料、淘汰字串移除功能、專用副檔名及合併變體。"

#: changes.rst:101
msgid ""
"Accepting a project invitation now automatically adds the project to the "
"user's watched projects."
msgstr "接受專案邀請時，現在會自動將專案新增至使用者的關注專案。"

#: changes.rst:102
msgid ""
"Dismissing a failing check no longer shows a JSON parsing error in the "
"translation editor."
msgstr "關閉未通過的檢查時，翻譯編輯器不再顯示 JSON 剖析錯誤。"

#: changes.rst:103
msgid ""
"Screenshot searches without an explicit field now match screenshot names "
"only, and the search box links to the full screenshot search documentation."
msgstr ""
"未指定明確欄位的螢幕擷圖搜尋，現在只會比對螢幕擷圖名稱；搜尋方塊也會連結至完"
"整的螢幕擷圖搜尋文件。"

#: changes.rst:104
msgid ""
"Anonymous and internal bot accounts can no longer be edited through generic "
"user management."
msgstr "匿名帳號和內部機器人帳號不再能透過一般使用者管理功能編輯。"

#: changes.rst:105
msgid ""
"LLM machine translation suggestions now recover from more malformed "
"structured JSON replies."
msgstr "LLM 機器翻譯建議現在可以從更多格式錯誤的結構化 JSON 回覆中復原。"

#: changes.rst:106
msgid ""
"Azure AI Translator settings now reject malformed region names before "
"validating service connectivity."
msgstr ""
"Azure AI Translator 設定現在會在驗證服務連線能力前，拒絕格式錯誤的區域名稱。"

#: changes.rst:112
msgid ""
"Weblate now requires the PostgreSQL ``btree_gist`` extension for translation "
"memory lookups. The migration installs it automatically when the database "
"user has sufficient privileges. Installations using a non-superuser database "
"user should pre-create it before upgrading; see :ref:`dbsetup-postgres`."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 現在需要 PostgreSQL ``btree_gist`` 擴充功能用於翻譯記憶查詢。當資料庫"
"使用者具有足夠權限時，移轉過程將會自動安裝它。使用非特權資料庫使用者的安裝應"
"該在升級前建立它；請參閱 :ref:`dbsetup-postgres`。"

#: changes.rst:118
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/170?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`所有變化詳情 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/170?"
"closed=1>`__."

#: changes.rst:121
msgid "Weblate 2026.7"
msgstr "Weblate 2026.7"

#: changes.rst:123
msgid "*Released on July 1st 2026.*"
msgstr "*發佈於 2026 年 7 月 1 日。*"

#: changes.rst:127
msgid ""
"Added :ref:`check-safe-mdx`, :ref:`check-source-max-length`, and :ref:`check-"
"accelerator` quality checks for :ref:`mdx` JSX expressions, source length "
"limits, and accelerator key consistency."
msgstr ""
"新增了 :ref:`check-safe-mdx` 、 :ref:`check-source-max-length` "
"與 :ref:`check-accelerator` 品質檢查用於 :ref:`mdx` JSX 表達式 、 來源長度限"
"制與加速器金鑰一致性。"

#: changes.rst:128
msgid ""
"Added :ref:`mt-mistral` machinery integration for Mistral LLM automatic "
"suggestions."
msgstr "新增供 Mistral LLM 自動建議使用的 :ref:`mt-mistral` 機器翻譯整合。"

#: changes.rst:129
msgid ""
"Added :ref:`code-hosting-github-app-register` for connecting GitHub "
"repositories through a Weblate GitHub App."
msgstr ""
"新增了 :ref:`code-hosting-github-app-register` 用於透過 Weblate GitHub App 連"
"線 GitHub 儲存庫。"

#: changes.rst:130
msgid ""
":ref:`projectbackup` backups can now be created and downloaded via "
"the :ref:`api`."
msgstr ":ref:`projectbackup` 現在可以透過 :ref:`api` 建立或下載。"

#: changes.rst:131
msgid ""
"Added file format parameters for translating individual YAML front matter "
"values in :ref:`markdown` and :ref:`mdx` files and escaping formula-like "
"values in :ref:`csv` files."
msgstr ""
"新增檔案格式參數，以翻譯 :ref:`markdown` 和 :ref:`mdx` 檔案中的個別 YAML 前置"
"資料值，並對 :ref:`csv` 檔案中類似公式的值進行逸出處理。"

#: changes.rst:132
msgid "Added an option to capitalize the text in status badge widgets."
msgstr "新增將狀態徽章小工具中文字改為大寫的選項。"

#: changes.rst:133
msgid ""
"Added :ref:`workspace translation memory <memory-scopes>` with asynchronous "
"scope backfill for existing translation memory entries."
msgstr ""
"新增 :ref:`工作空間翻譯記憶 <memory-scopes>`，並以非同步方式回填既有翻譯記憶"
"項目的作用範圍。"

#: changes.rst:134
msgid ""
"Added :wladmin:`analyze_translator_work` to estimate realistic daily "
"translator throughput from change history."
msgstr ""
"新增了 :wladmin:`analyze_translator_work` 以透過變更歷史紀錄估算每天翻譯者的"
"實際工作量。"

#: changes.rst:138
msgid ""
"RTL editing and translation display now handle bidirectional text better, "
"including Unicode isolate controls in the :ref:`visual-keyboard`."
msgstr ""
"RTL 編輯與翻譯顯示功能現在能更好地處理雙向文字，包含 :ref:`visual-keyboard` "
"中的萬國碼分離控制。"

#: changes.rst:139
msgid ""
"Management interface access control is now more fine-grained with dedicated "
"site-wide permissions."
msgstr "管理介面的存取控制現在透過專用的全站權限提供更細緻的控制。"

#: changes.rst:140
msgid ""
"Default commit and merge request message templates now use Conventional "
"Commits, settings forms can restore installation defaults, and pull request "
"messages use a compact language progress matrix."
msgstr ""
"預設提交及合併請求訊息範本現在使用 Conventional Commits；設定表單可以還原安裝"
"環境預設值；拉取請求訊息則使用精簡的語言進度矩陣。"

#: changes.rst:141
msgid ""
"Documented :ref:`legal` customizations and added options to hide legal pages "
"or disable document numbering."
msgstr "記錄了 :ref:`legal` 自訂並新增了用於隱藏法律頁面或停用文件編號的選項。"

#: changes.rst:142
msgid ""
"Expanded :doc:`security documentation </security/index>` for data residency, "
"EU cloud sovereignty, release artifacts, supported versions, release "
"verification, SBOMs, dependency handling, vulnerability reporting, hosted-"
"service incident response, and self-hosted operator responsibilities."
msgstr ""
"擴充 :doc:`安全性文件 </security/index>`，涵蓋資料駐留、歐盟雲端主權、發行成"
"品、支援的版本、發行版本驗證、SBOM、相依套件處理、弱點回報、託管服務事件回"
"應，以及自行託管維運人員的責任。"

#: changes.rst:143
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.linguas` better detects ``LINGUAS`` file "
"presence."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.linguas` 更好地偵測 ``LINGUAS`` 檔案的存在。"

#: changes.rst:144
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.xgettext` can now leave the xgettext language "
"blank to let xgettext guess it from source file extensions."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.xgettext` 現在可以將 xgettext 語言欄位留空，讓 "
"xgettext 從來源檔案副檔名自行猜測。"

#: changes.rst:145
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.xgettext`, :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.gettext.meson`, :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.django`, and :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.gettext.sphinx` can now keep source locations in generated POT files "
"even when translated PO files omit locations."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.xgettext`、 :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.gettext.meson`、 :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.django` 和 :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.gettext.sphinx` 現在可以在產生的 POT 檔案中保留原文位置，即便翻譯的 "
"PO 檔案省略位置。"

#: changes.rst:146
msgid ""
"Add-ons installed at higher scopes are now shown on lower-scope add-on "
"pages, and broad-scope add-ons can list affected components with "
"compatibility details."
msgstr ""
"安裝在較高作用範圍的附加元件，現在會顯示在較低作用範圍的附加元件頁面；作用範"
"圍較廣的附加元件也可以列出受影響的元件及相容性詳細資料。"

#: changes.rst:147
msgid ""
":envvar:`WEBLATE_ALLOWED_ASSET_SIZE` is now available in Docker container."
msgstr ":envvar:`WEBLATE_ALLOWED_ASSET_SIZE` 現在於 Docker 容器中可用。"

#: changes.rst:148
msgid ""
"LLM automatic suggestions now use translated examples, language-specific "
"instructions, richer glossary context, and structured placeholder context "
"for more reliable output."
msgstr ""
"LLM 自動建議現在會使用已翻譯的範例、特定語言說明、更豐富的詞彙表情境，以及結"
"構化預留位置內容，提供更可靠的輸出。"

#: changes.rst:149
msgid ""
"Meta descriptions now better match single-project and self-hosted "
"installations."
msgstr "Meta 描述現在更符合單一專案及自行託管的安裝環境。"

#: changes.rst:150
msgid ""
"Zen mode, filtered searches, nearby strings, translation form submissions, "
"and add-on management pages now load more efficiently on large sites."
msgstr ""
"Zen 模式、篩選搜尋、附近字串、翻譯表單提交及附加元件管理頁面，現在可在大型網"
"站上更有效率地載入。"

#: changes.rst:151
msgid ""
"Added :ref:`distribution-packaging` guidance for distribution maintainers."
msgstr "新增供發行版維護人員使用的 :ref:`distribution-packaging` 操作指南。"

#: changes.rst:152
msgid ""
"Large component imports now avoid duplicate translation-memory processing."
msgstr "大量匯入元件時，現在會避免重複處理翻譯記憶。"

#: changes.rst:153
msgid ""
":ref:`gettext` files can now be configured to remove obsolete strings on "
"save, including during repository maintenance."
msgstr ""
"現在可以設定 :ref:`gettext` 在儲存時刪除陳舊的字串，包括在儲存庫維護期間。"

#: changes.rst:154
msgid ""
":ref:`Bulk accepting suggestions <suggestions>` now confirms the number of "
"affected suggestions, can approve them for reviewers, and processes the "
"acceptance in the background."
msgstr ""
":ref:`批次接受建議 <suggestions>` 現在會確認受影響的建議數量、可為審閱者核准"
"建議，並在背景處理接受作業。"

#: changes.rst:155
msgid ""
"Committing large numbers of pending translations now queues browser requests "
"in the background and avoids duplicate repository commit tasks."
msgstr ""
"提交大量待處理翻譯時，現在會將瀏覽器要求排入背景佇列，並避免重複的儲存庫提交"
"工作。"

#: changes.rst:156
msgid ""
"Change-event notification add-ons can now use presets for translation "
"content events, all events, or selected individual events."
msgstr ""
"變更事件通知附加元件現在可以使用翻譯內容事件、所有事件，或個別選取事件的預設"
"集。"

#: changes.rst:157
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.fedora_messaging.publish` now validates secure broker "
"connections and exposes delivery timing and topic prefix settings."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.fedora_messaging.publish` 現在驗證安全代理連線並暴露傳輸"
"時間及主題字首設定。"

#: changes.rst:158
msgid ""
"Component diagnostics now sort entries by severity, color-code severity "
"badges, and show the error count on the :guilabel:`Diagnostics` tab."
msgstr ""
"元件診斷現在會依嚴重性排序項目、以色彩標示嚴重性徽章，並在 :guilabel:`診斷` "
"分頁顯示錯誤數量。"

#: changes.rst:159
msgid ""
":ref:`manage-performance` now shows PostgreSQL database disk usage next to "
"server disk usage and warns when the database usage cannot be collected."
msgstr ""
":ref:`manage-performance` 現在會在伺服器磁碟用量旁顯示 PostgreSQL 資料庫磁碟"
"用量，並在無法收集資料庫用量時發出警告。"

#: changes.rst:160
msgid ""
":ref:`manage-performance` now shows PostgreSQL database disk usage next to "
"server disk usage and warns when the database usage cannot be collected or "
"there is not enough free space in the backup destination to store a database "
"dump."
msgstr ""
":ref:`manage-performance` 現在會在伺服器磁碟用量旁顯示 PostgreSQL 資料庫磁碟"
"用量，並在無法收集資料庫用量，或備份目的地沒有足夠可用空間可儲存資料庫傾印時"
"發出警告。"

#: changes.rst:161
msgid ""
"The :ref:`search-replace` preview now keeps the search parameters editable "
"so the query can be refined before applying replacements."
msgstr ""
":ref:`search-replace` 預覽現在會讓搜尋參數保持可編輯，以便在套用取代前調整查"
"詢。"

#: changes.rst:165
msgid ""
":ref:`check-regex` and :ref:`check-placeholders` now enforce regular "
"expression timeouts when evaluating source-string flags "
"(:cve:`2026-62326`, :ghsa:`r52j-4vjp-q949`)."
msgstr ""
":ref:`check-regex` 與 :ref:`check-placeholders` 現在會在評估來源字串旗標時，"
"強制執行正規表示式逾時限制（:cve:`2026-62326`、:ghsa:`r52j-4vjp-q949`）。"

#: changes.rst:166
msgid ""
"Restricted component changes are no longer exposed through nested project, "
"component, or translation API change endpoints "
"(:cve:`2026-62249`, :ghsa:`92m8-wv36-prmx`)."
msgstr ""
"受限元件的變更不再透過巢狀專案、元件或翻譯 API 變更端點公開"
"（:cve:`2026-62249`、:ghsa:`92m8-wv36-prmx`）。"

#: changes.rst:167
msgid ""
"ZIP downloads, including :ref:`appstore` translation bundles, no longer "
"follow child symbolic links outside the downloaded tree "
"(:cve:`2026-61792`, :ghsa:`xwj4-fp82-r2rj`)."
msgstr ""
"ZIP 下載（包括 :ref:`appstore` 翻譯套件）不再跟隨指向下載目錄樹外部的下層符號"
"連結（:cve:`2026-61792`、:ghsa:`xwj4-fp82-r2rj`）。"

#: changes.rst:168
msgid ""
"Teams enforcing two-factor authentication now also withhold site-wide "
"permissions from human members without 2FA configured "
"(:cve:`2026-61790`, :ghsa:`x86c-ff69-cr2m`)."
msgstr ""
"強制執行雙因素身分驗證的團隊，現在也不會向未設定 2FA 的人類成員授予全站權限"
"（:cve:`2026-61790`、:ghsa:`x86c-ff69-cr2m`）。"

#: changes.rst:169
msgid ""
"Globally scoped HTML and AJAX object lookups no longer disclose object "
"existence in private projects (:cve:`2026-55227`, :ghsa:`2p9g-x3cv-5hh4`)."
msgstr ""
"全域範圍的 HTML 與 AJAX 物件查詢不再洩露私人專案中物件是否存在"
"（:cve:`2026-55227`、:ghsa:`2p9g-x3cv-5hh4`）。"

#: changes.rst:170
msgid ""
"Team API access checks now prevent project managers from reading private-"
"project team data or expanding scoped team assignments outside their allowed "
"projects (:cve:`2026-55228`, :ghsa:`2q2q-jr9g-v9rf`)."
msgstr ""
"團隊 API 存取檢查現在會防止專案經理讀取私人專案團隊資料，或在其允許的專案之外"
"展開具作用範圍的團隊指派（:cve:`2026-55228`、:ghsa:`2q2q-jr9g-v9rf`）。"

#: changes.rst:171
msgid "Malformed ``replacements`` flags no longer abort source length checks."
msgstr "格式錯誤的 ``replacements`` 旗標不再中止來源長度檢查。"

#: changes.rst:172
msgid ""
"Empty component lists are no longer exposed to users without component list "
"management permission."
msgstr "空白元件清單不再對沒有元件清單管理權限的使用者公開。"

#: changes.rst:173
msgid ""
"Glossary handling no longer duplicates TBX terms or shows source-language "
"terms in both translation columns."
msgstr "詞彙表處理不再重複 TBX 詞彙，也不再於兩個翻譯欄中顯示來源語言詞彙。"

#: changes.rst:174
msgid ""
"Duplicate string alerts now offer a cleanup action to remove repeated "
"strings from translation files."
msgstr "重複字串警報現在提供從翻譯檔案刪除重複字串的清理選項。"

#: changes.rst:175
msgid ""
":ref:`code-hosting-gerrit` review pushes can again include Gerrit push "
"options in the target branch."
msgstr ""
":ref:`code-hosting-gerrit` 審查推送現在可以再次在目標分支中包含 Gerrit 推送選"
"項。"

#: changes.rst:176
msgid ""
"Webhook target fallback matching is now stricter and reported in component "
"diagnostics."
msgstr "Webhook 目標的備用比對現在更嚴格，且會在元件診斷中回報。"

#: changes.rst:177
msgid ""
"Creating components linked with ``weblate://`` no longer waits on the shared "
"repository lock during the request."
msgstr "建立與 ``weblate://`` 連結的元件在請求期間不再等待共享的儲存庫鎖。"

#: changes.rst:178
msgid ""
"Project and workspace translation license defaults now follow component and "
"project licenses more closely."
msgstr "專案和工作空間的翻譯授權預設值，現在會更貼近元件和專案授權。"

#: changes.rst:179
msgid ""
"Component and category API ``PATCH`` requests no longer remove the category "
"when the field is omitted."
msgstr "省略欄位時，元件和分類 API 的 ``PATCH`` 要求不再移除分類。"

#: changes.rst:180
msgid ""
"Document and translation-memory uploads now "
"enforce :setting:`TRANSLATION_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE`, and API document uploads "
"validate file extensions."
msgstr ""
"檔案及翻譯記憶上傳現在會強制套用 :setting:`TRANSLATION_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE`，而 "
"API 檔案上傳也會驗證副檔名。"

#: changes.rst:181
msgid ""
":ref:`check-rst-syntax` now detects inline roles wrapped in stray backticks."
msgstr ":ref:`check-rst-syntax` 現在檢測不成對反引號包裹的內聯角色。"

#: changes.rst:182
msgid ""
":ref:`check-safe-html` now efficiently detects changed placeholder-only HTML "
"attribute values in translations."
msgstr ""
":ref:`check-safe-html` 現在可以有效偵測翻譯中只有預留位置的 HTML 屬性值變更。"

#: changes.rst:183
msgid ""
":ref:`check-max-size` no longer wraps text configured to fit on one line, "
"checks source strings, and refreshes rendered previews after source edits."
msgstr ""
":ref:`check-max-size` 不再為設定成只顯示一行的文字換行，會檢查來源字串，並在"
"編輯來源後重新整理轉譯預覽。"

#: changes.rst:184
msgid ""
"Bitmap widgets and :ref:`check-max-size` previews now use Matplotlib and no "
"longer require Pango, Cairo, librsvg, or GObject Introspection."
msgstr ""

#: changes.rst:185
msgid ""
"Repository reset and update history now keeps attribution, records remote "
"update failures, and includes follow-up translation-file reconciliation."
msgstr ""
"儲存庫重設及更新歷程現在會保留歸屬資訊、記錄遠端更新失敗，並包含後續翻譯檔案"
"一致化作業。"

#: changes.rst:186
msgid ""
"Updating repository URLs now validates compatible Git history without "
"requiring an immediate successful merge."
msgstr "更新儲存庫 URL 時，現在會驗證相容的 Git 歷程，而不要求立即成功合併。"

#: changes.rst:187
msgid ""
":ref:`auto-translation` no longer validates hidden component fields when "
"using machine translation."
msgstr ":ref:`auto-translation` 使用機器翻譯時不再驗證隱藏的元件欄位。"

#: changes.rst:188
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Strings marked for edit` links now include all strings needing "
"editing, checking, or rewriting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`標示為待編輯的字串` 連結現在包含所有需要編輯、檢查或重寫的字串。"

#: changes.rst:189
msgid ""
"Anonymous permission checks no longer fail when loading teams scoped to "
"projects or workspaces."
msgstr "載入作用範圍限定於專案或工作空間的團隊時，匿名權限檢查不再失敗。"

#: changes.rst:190
msgid ""
"API project creation can again use the user's only eligible workspace when "
"no explicit workspace is supplied."
msgstr ""
"未明確提供工作空間時，透過 API 建立專案現在可以再次使用該使用者唯一符合資格的"
"工作空間。"

#: changes.rst:191
msgid ""
"Git auto-maintenance is now disabled for Weblate-managed repositories to "
"avoid concurrent detached maintenance jobs."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 管理的儲存庫現在會停用 Git 自動維護，以避免同時執行獨立的維護工作。"

#: changes.rst:192
msgid ""
"Interrupted Git repository operations are now either recovered and recorded "
"or surfaced as a repository alert."
msgstr "中斷的 Git 儲存庫操作現在會復原並記錄，或以儲存庫警示呈現。"

#: changes.rst:193
msgid ""
"Watched translations on the dashboard now include category path segments."
msgstr "操作面板上已關注翻譯現在包含類別路徑部分。"

#: changes.rst:194
msgid ""
"Unsupported upload levels now show an upload placeholder pointing to "
"individual translations."
msgstr "不支援的上傳層級現在會顯示指向個別翻譯的上傳預留位置。"

#: changes.rst:195
msgid ""
"Component API responses no longer expose repository export, push branch, or "
"repository browser links to users without repository access."
msgstr ""
"對於沒有儲存庫存取權的使用者，元件 API 回應不再公開儲存庫匯出、推送分支或儲存"
"庫瀏覽器連結。"

#: changes.rst:199
msgid ""
":ref:`mt-deepl` now handles DeepL API versions internally, uses v3 for "
"glossary management and language discovery, and no longer supports DeepL API "
"v1."
msgstr ""
":ref:`mt-deepl` 現在會在內部處理 DeepL API 版本、以 v3 管理詞彙表及探索語言，"
"並不再支援 DeepL API v1。"

#: changes.rst:200
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.fedora_messaging.publish` topics now include category "
"path segments, and broker settings are stored as an AMQP URL with existing "
"host and SSL settings migrated automatically."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.fedora_messaging.publish` 主題現在包含分類路徑區段，而 "
"broker 設定會儲存為 AMQP URL，並自動移轉既有的主機和 SSL 設定。"

#: changes.rst:206
msgid ""
"There are changes in :file:`settings_example.py`, most notably in "
"``SOCIAL_AUTH_PIPELINE`` and ``SOCIAL_AUTH_DISCONNECT_PIPELINE``; please "
"adjust your settings accordingly."
msgstr ""
":file:`settings_example.py` 中有幾項變更，最顯著的變更在 "
"``SOCIAL_AUTH_PIPELINE`` 和 ``SOCIAL_AUTH_DISCONNECT_PIPELINE``，請相應調整您"
"的設定。"

#: changes.rst:207
msgid ""
"Existing translation-memory entries are moved to scoped storage by a "
"periodic Celery background task. Keep Celery running after the upgrade; "
"translation-memory suggestions can be incomplete until the backfill finishes."
msgstr ""
"既有翻譯記憶項目會由定期 Celery 背景工作移至具有作用範圍的儲存空間。升級後請"
"讓 Celery 保持執行；在回填完成前，翻譯記憶建議可能不完整。"

#: changes.rst:213
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/166?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`所有變化詳情 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/166?"
"closed=1>`__."

#: changes.rst:216
msgid "Weblate 2026.6.1"
msgstr "Weblate 2026.6"

#: changes.rst:218 changes.rst:237
msgid "*Released on June 1st 2026.*"
msgstr "*發佈於 2026 年 6 月 1 日。*"

#: changes.rst:222
msgid ""
"Language-wide :doc:`/admin/announcements` no longer break language overview "
"pages."
msgstr "面向所有語言的 :doc:`/admin/announcements` 不再破壞語言概覽頁。"

#: changes.rst:232
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/169?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`所有變化詳情 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/169?"
"closed=1>`__."

#: changes.rst:235
msgid "Weblate 2026.6"
msgstr "Weblate 2026.6"

#: changes.rst:241
msgid ""
":doc:`/admin/announcements` can now also be managed via the :ref:`api` for "
"specific project languages."
msgstr ""
"現在也可透過特定專案語言的 :ref:`api` 管理 :doc:`/admin/announcements`。"

#: changes.rst:242
msgid ""
"Team memberships can now be limited to selected languages for per-user "
"translation permissions."
msgstr "現在可以將團隊成員身分限制為所選語言用於每使用者翻譯權限。"

#: changes.rst:243
msgid "Added :ref:`cost estimates <cost-estimate>` to translation reports."
msgstr "新增了 :ref:`成本估算 <cost-estimate>` 至翻譯報告。"

#: changes.rst:244
msgid ""
"Added optional :ref:`OpenTelemetry tracing <collecting-errors>` for backend "
"requests and tasks, and :ref:`Google Cloud Error Reporting <collecting-"
"errors>` for handled server errors."
msgstr ""
"新增選用的 :ref:`OpenTelemetry 追蹤 <collecting-errors>`，用於後端要求及工"
"作；也新增 :ref:`Google Cloud Error Reporting <collecting-errors>`，用於已處"
"理的伺服器錯誤。"

#: changes.rst:245
msgid ""
"Added :doc:`/admin/workspaces` to group related projects, with workspace "
"project listings, workspace-scoped teams and project creation permissions, "
"inherited workspace, project, and category defaults for selected component "
"settings, and billing details when available."
msgstr ""
"新增 :doc:`/admin/workspaces` 以將相關專案分組，並在可用時提供工作空間專案清"
"單、工作空間範圍的團隊和專案建立權限、供特定元件設定繼承的工作空間、專案及分"
"類預設值，以及計費詳細資料。"

#: changes.rst:249
msgid ""
"Docker containers can now configure :envvar:`WEBLATE_SAML_SECURITY_CONFIG` "
"to customize SAML security settings, and adjust :setting:`WEBLATE_FORMATS` "
"using :envvar:`WEBLATE_ADD_FORMATS` and :envvar:`WEBLATE_REMOVE_FORMATS`."
msgstr ""
"Docker 容器現在可以設定 :envvar:`WEBLATE_SAML_SECURITY_CONFIG` 以自訂 SAML 安"
"全設定，並透過 :envvar:`WEBLATE_ADD_FORMATS` "
"與 :envvar:`WEBLATE_REMOVE_FORMATS` 來調整 :setting:`WEBLATE_FORMATS`。"

#: changes.rst:250
msgid ""
"Improved performance of the :ref:`check-inconsistent` check on large "
"projects."
msgstr "改進了大型專案中的 :ref:`check-inconsistent` 檢查效能。"

#: changes.rst:251
msgid ""
"Translation flag fields now use a tag-based editor with autocompletion and "
"grouped suggestions for all known flags."
msgstr ""
"翻譯旗標欄位現在使用以標籤為基礎的編輯器，並提供自動完成和所有已知旗標的分組"
"建議。"

#: changes.rst:252
msgid ""
":ref:`Contributor stats <stats>` now de-duplicate repeated work on the same "
"string by default, with an option to count all changes."
msgstr ""
":ref:`貢獻者統計資料 <stats>` 現在預設會將同一字串上的重複工作去除重複計算，"
"並提供計算所有變更的選項。"

#: changes.rst:253
msgid ""
":doc:`/admin/code-hosting` now documents HTTPS access-token URLs and "
"dedicated-user SSH URLs for accessing repositories, and :doc:`/admin/"
"continuous` now explains why squash merging Weblate conflict-resolution pull "
"requests can require a repository reset."
msgstr ""
":doc:`/admin/code-hosting` 現在說明用於存取儲存庫的 HTTPS 存取權杖 URL 和專用"
"使用者 SSH URL；:doc:`/admin/continuous` 現在則說明以 squash 方式合併 "
"Weblate 衝突解決拉取請求，為何可能需要重設儲存庫。"

#: changes.rst:254
msgid ""
":ref:`alerts` now include dismissible component diagnostics for community "
"localization."
msgstr ":ref:`alerts` 現在包含可關閉的社群在地化元件診斷。"

#: changes.rst:255
msgid ""
":ref:`screenshots` now support bulk assignment from search or image text "
"recognition results, make finding strings in uploaded images easier to "
"discover, show source string coverage counts, and include advanced listing "
"search."
msgstr ""
":ref:`screenshots` 現在支援從搜尋或圖片文字辨識結果批次指派、讓使用者更容易找"
"到已上傳圖片中的字串、顯示來源字串涵蓋數量，並包含進階清單搜尋。"

#: changes.rst:256
msgid ""
":ref:`sbom` release artifacts now include CISA 2025 document-level metadata."
msgstr ":ref:`sbom` 發行成品現在包含 CISA 2025 文件層級詮釋資料。"

#: changes.rst:260
msgid ""
"Outbound URL validation now rejects additional non-public targets "
"(:cve:`2026-50127`, :ghsa:`vmfc-9982-2m45`)."
msgstr ""
"傳出 URL 驗證現在會拒絕更多非公開目標"
"（:cve:`2026-50127`、:ghsa:`vmfc-9982-2m45`）。"

#: changes.rst:261
msgid ""
"Project-language :doc:`/admin/announcements` no longer appear across the "
"whole project."
msgstr "專案語言 :doc:`/admin/announcements` 不再在整個專案中出現。"

#: changes.rst:262
msgid ""
"Hardened :http:post:`/api/screenshots/` access checks against private "
"project enumeration."
msgstr "加固了 :http:post:`/api/screenshots/` 存取檢查以對抗私人專案列舉。"

#: changes.rst:263
msgid ""
"Registration-attempt account activity e-mails now link to password reset to "
"help users finish account setup."
msgstr ""
"帳號註冊嘗試活動電子郵件現在會連結至密碼重設，以協助使用者完成帳號設定。"

#: changes.rst:264
msgid ""
":ref:`invite-user` links now work for signed-in users whose account owns the "
"invited e-mail address."
msgstr ""
"如果已登入使用者的帳號擁有受邀電子郵件地址，:ref:`invite-user` 連結現在可以正"
"常運作。"

#: changes.rst:265
msgid ""
"Searching for strings with content changes without a recorded author now "
"supports ``changed_by:\"\"``, and combined change filters now apply to the "
"same change event."
msgstr ""
"搜尋內容已有變更但未記錄作者的字串時，現在支援 ``changed_by:\"\"``；合併的變"
"更篩選條件現在也會套用至同一個變更事件。"

#: changes.rst:266
msgid ""
"Gitea and Forgejo pull requests no longer reconfigure existing fork remotes "
"to point to the source repository."
msgstr ""
"Gitea 和 Forgejo 拉取請求不再重新設定既有 fork 遠端，使其指向來源儲存庫。"

#: changes.rst:267
msgid ""
"Project and category language translation sessions now keep strings grouped "
"by component priority and show component switch warnings reliably."
msgstr ""
"專案和分類語言翻譯工作階段現在會依元件優先順序保持字串分組，並可靠顯示元件切"
"換警告。"

#: changes.rst:268
msgid ""
"Engage page task links now stay centered and show the target translation "
"language."
msgstr "Engage 頁面的工作連結現在會保持置中，並顯示目標翻譯語言。"

#: changes.rst:269
msgid ""
"Gettext POT update add-ons now rescan translations after committing updated "
"POT and PO files."
msgstr ""
"Gettext POT 更新附加元件現在會在提交更新後的 POT 和 PO 檔案後，重新掃描翻譯。"

#: changes.rst:270
msgid ""
"Git repositories now update branches correctly when the remote also has a "
"tag with the same name."
msgstr "遠端也有同名標籤時，Git 儲存庫現在可以正確更新分支。"

#: changes.rst:271
msgid ""
"Conflicting repository setup alerts now allow same-branch direct pushes."
msgstr "衝突的儲存庫設定警報現在允許同分支直接推送。"

#: changes.rst:272
msgid ""
"Obsolete cleanup schedules are now removed from Celery beat during upgrade."
msgstr "升級期間，現在會從 Celery beat 移除過時內容清除排程。"

#: changes.rst:273
msgid ""
"Translation pages for workspace projects no longer crash when workspace "
"fields are deferred."
msgstr "延後載入工作空間欄位時，工作空間專案的翻譯頁面不再當機。"

#: changes.rst:279
msgid ""
"There is a change in :setting:`django:INSTALLED_APPS`; "
"``weblate.workspaces`` should be added."
msgstr ""
":setting:`django:INSTALLED_APPS` 有一處變更；應新增 ``weblate.workspaces`` 。"

#: changes.rst:280
msgid "The database migrations might take longer on larger instances."
msgstr "資料庫移轉在較大的執行個體上可能要花更長時間。"

#: changes.rst:286
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/165?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`所有變化詳情 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/165?"
"closed=1>`__."

#: changes.rst:289
msgid "Weblate 2026.5"
msgstr "Weblate 2026.5"

#: changes.rst:291
msgid "*Released on May 15th 2026.*"
msgstr "*發佈於 2024 年 5 月 15 日。*"

#: changes.rst:295
msgid ""
"Added :ref:`mdx` support for translating Markdown text while preserving JSX "
"syntax, with :ref:`file_format_params` shared with :ref:`markdown` for line "
"wrapping, code blocks, front matter, and placeholder handling."
msgstr ""
"新增 :ref:`mdx` 支援，可在保留 JSX 語法的同時翻譯 Markdown 文字；並"
"與 :ref:`markdown` 共用 :ref:`file_format_params`，處理自動換行、程式碼區塊、"
"前置資料及預留位置。"

#: changes.rst:296
msgid ""
"Added extended :ref:`LLM translation context <llm-translation-context>` for "
"automatic suggestions, covering string context, explanations, secondary-"
"language translations, plurals, failing checks, and placeholders."
msgstr ""
"新增供自動建議使用的擴充 :ref:`LLM 翻譯內容 <llm-translation-context>`，涵蓋"
"字串情境、說明、第二語言翻譯、複數形式、未通過的檢查及預留位置。"

#: changes.rst:297
msgid ""
"Added a digest-only translation activity summary notification, "
"see :ref:`notifications`."
msgstr "新增僅以摘要方式傳送的翻譯活動彙整通知，請參閱 :ref:`notifications`。"

#: changes.rst:298
msgid ""
":ref:`CSV <csv>` and :ref:`XLSX <xlsx>` downloads in :ref:`download` now "
"export plural strings as separate plural-form rows that can be imported back."
msgstr ""
":ref:`download` 中的 :ref:`CSV <csv>` 和 :ref:`XLSX <xlsx>` 下載，現在會將複"
"數字串匯出為可重新匯入的個別複數形式資料列。"

#: changes.rst:299
msgid ""
"Added Gettext PO and POT :ref:`file_format_params` to control whether "
"Weblate updates the ``Language-Team``, ``Last-Translator``, ``X-Generator``, "
"and ``Report-Msgid-Bugs-To`` headers."
msgstr ""
"新增 Gettext PO 和 POT :ref:`file_format_params`，以控制 Weblate 是否更新 "
"``Language-Team``、``Last-Translator``、``X-Generator`` 和 ``Report-Msgid-"
"Bugs-To`` 標頭。"

#: changes.rst:300
msgid ""
"Added a :ref:`backup-management-command` to run configured backup services "
"synchronously."
msgstr "新增了 :ref:`backup-management-command` 以同步執行設定的備份服務。"

#: changes.rst:301
msgid ""
"The translation memory lookup API can now skip fuzzy matching with the "
"``exact`` query parameter."
msgstr "翻譯記憶查詢 API 現在可以使用 ``exact`` 查詢參數略過模糊比對。"

#: changes.rst:302
msgid ""
"Added :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.files` to publish translation files to the "
"configured CDN."
msgstr "新增了 :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.files` 以發佈翻譯檔案至設定的 CDN。"

#: changes.rst:306
msgid ""
"Using DOS line endings can now be configured using the "
"``dos_eol`` :ref:`file_format_params`."
msgstr ""
"現在可用 ``dos_eol`` :ref:`file_format_params` 來設定使用 DOS 行結尾符號。"

#: changes.rst:307
msgid ""
":ref:`mt-openai` and :ref:`mt-alibaba` no longer require their vendor Python "
"SDKs."
msgstr ""
":ref:`mt-openai` 與 :ref:`mt-alibaba` 不再需要它們的供應商 Python SDK 了。"

#: changes.rst:308
msgid ""
"Audited project and component setting changes are now recorded in history."
msgstr "現在在歷史記錄中記錄經審計的專案和元件設定。"

#: changes.rst:309
msgid ""
"Gerrit review pushes now use :ref:`component-push_branch` as the target "
"branch."
msgstr "Gerrit 檢閱推送現在使用 :ref:`component-push_branch` 作為目標分支。"

#: changes.rst:310
msgid ""
"Weblate now checks whether :setting:`CACHE_DIR` allows executing generated "
"helper files."
msgstr "Weblate 現在會檢查 :setting:`CACHE_DIR` 是否允許執行產生的輔助檔案。"

#: changes.rst:311
msgid ""
"The :ref:`sbom` is now generated during release and published as a versioned "
"release asset instead of being stored in the source repository."
msgstr ""
":ref:`sbom` 現在會在發行期間產生，並以具有版本的發行資產形式發佈，而非儲存在"
"來源儲存庫中。"

#: changes.rst:312
msgid ""
"The translating page now separates screenshots from string information, "
"collapses rarely used string details, and groups glossary and screenshot "
"actions more consistently."
msgstr ""
"翻譯頁面現在會分開顯示螢幕擷圖和字串資訊、收合不常使用的字串詳細資料，並以更"
"一致的方式將詞彙表和螢幕擷圖動作分組。"

#: changes.rst:313
msgid ""
"Project access management now paginates users and better explains site-wide "
"automatic team assignments."
msgstr "專案存取管理現在會將使用者分頁，並更清楚說明全站自動團隊指派。"

#: changes.rst:314
msgid ""
"Added provider-oriented code-hosting documentation and Gettext-"
"style :ref:`plural-formula` guidance."
msgstr ""
"新增以服務提供者為導向的程式碼託管說明文件，以及 Gettext 風格的 :ref:`plural-"
"formula` 指引。"

#: changes.rst:315
msgid ""
"The Python wheel no longer ships source translation catalogs, test files, or "
"deployment example files, reducing the installed package size."
msgstr ""
"Python wheel 不再隨附來源翻譯目錄、測試檔案或部署範例檔案，以降低安裝套件大"
"小。"

#: changes.rst:316
msgid ""
"The engage page now highlights actionable translation task buckets for "
"newcomers."
msgstr "Engage 頁面現在會為新加入者醒目提示可採取行動的翻譯工作分類。"

#: changes.rst:317
msgid ""
":ref:`RSS feeds <rss>` can now use the same filters as the changes browsing "
"page."
msgstr ":ref:`RSS 資訊提供 <rss>` 現在可以使用與變更瀏覽頁面相同的篩選條件。"

#: changes.rst:318
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.django` now supports gettext PO files used as "
"templates when they are excluded by the language filter."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.django` 現在支援作為範本使用，且由語言篩選條件排"
"除的 Gettext PO 檔案。"

#: changes.rst:319
msgid "Reworked :doc:`/security/threat-model` into a contract-style document."
msgstr "將 :doc:`/security/threat-model` 改寫為契約式文件。"

#: changes.rst:323
msgid ""
"Hardened search previews and :ref:`machine-translation` suggestion origins "
"against XSS, and stopped exposing database error details in upload failures "
"(:cve:`2026-45106` / :ghsa:`6wxc-8mgq-w26m`)."
msgstr ""
"加固了搜尋預覽與 :ref:`machine-translation` 建議源頭以對抗 XSS 攻擊，並停止了"
"在上傳失敗中曝露資料庫錯誤詳細資訊 （:cve:`2026-45106` / :ghsa:`6wxc-8mgq-"
"w26m`）。"

#: changes.rst:324
msgid ""
"Screenshot URL uploads, remote HTML extraction in :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.cdn.cdnjs`, and URL health-check redirects now reject internal or "
"non-public targets by default."
msgstr ""
"螢幕擷圖 URL 上傳、:ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.cdnjs` 中的遠端 HTML 擷取，以及 "
"URL 健全狀態檢查重新導向，現在預設會拒絕內部或非公開目標。"

#: changes.rst:325
msgid ""
"Gerrit review pushes now reject target branches containing push options, "
"track the target branch before invoking ``git-review``, and suggest short "
"branch names when full refs are supplied."
msgstr ""
"Gerrit 審查推送現在會拒絕包含推送選項的目標分支、在叫用 ``git-review`` 前追蹤"
"目標分支，並在提供完整 ref 時建議使用簡短分支名稱。"

#: changes.rst:326
msgid ""
"Category :doc:`/admin/announcements` no longer appear across the whole "
"project, and translation announcement deletion now honors language-scoped "
"permissions."
msgstr ""
":doc:`/admin/announcements` 類別不再出現在整個專案中，翻譯宣告刪除現在遵守語"
"言級的權限。"

#: changes.rst:327
msgid ""
"Merge request pushes now refresh stale fork remotes after changing "
"repository hosting."
msgstr "變更儲存庫託管服務後，合併請求推送現在會重新整理過時的 fork 遠端。"

#: changes.rst:328
msgid ""
"Plural counts parsed from translation file headers are now bounded, and "
"plural formulas are rejected when they can evaluate outside the configured "
"plural form range."
msgstr ""
"現在會限制從翻譯檔案標頭剖析的複數形式數量，並拒絕可能求得超出已設定複數形式"
"範圍之值的複數公式。"

#: changes.rst:329
msgid ""
":ref:`project-api` expiring today now remain valid until the end of the day."
msgstr "今天到期的 :ref:`project-api` 現在會保持有效至當日結束。"

#: changes.rst:330
msgid ""
"Malformed ALTCHA CAPTCHA submissions and repository URLs in webhook payloads "
"no longer cause server errors."
msgstr ""
"格式錯誤的 ALTCHA CAPTCHA 提交內容及 Webhook 承載內容中的儲存庫 URL，不再造成"
"伺服器錯誤。"

#: changes.rst:331
msgid ""
":ref:`check-placeholders` now merges overlapping non-nested spans from "
"multiple flags."
msgstr ":ref:`check-placeholders` 現在會合併多個旗標中彼此重疊但未巢狀的範圍。"

#: changes.rst:332
msgid ""
":ref:`backup` logs no longer include OpenSSH post-quantum key exchange "
"warnings from remote Borg connections."
msgstr ""
":ref:`backup` 紀錄不再包含來自遠端 Borg 連線的 OpenSSH 後量子金鑰交換警告。"

#: changes.rst:333
msgid ""
"Category repository paths are now handled more safely during cleanup and "
"moves."
msgstr "清除和移動期間，現在會更安全地處理分類儲存庫路徑。"

#: changes.rst:334
msgid ""
"Locked component pages now show an unsubscribe action after subscribing to "
"unlock notifications."
msgstr "訂閱解除鎖定通知後，鎖定的元件頁面現在會顯示取消訂閱動作。"

#: changes.rst:335
msgid ""
":ref:`projectbackup` imports now restore in the background to avoid web "
"worker memory limits."
msgstr ""
":ref:`projectbackup` 匯入現在於背景中復原以避免 web worker 記憶體限制。"

#: changes.rst:339
msgid ""
"The ``dos-eol`` flag is no longer supported. Use the "
"``dos_eol`` :ref:`file_format_params` instead."
msgstr ""
"不再支援 ``dos-eol`` 旗標。請改為使用 ``dos_eol`` :ref:`file_format_params`。"

#: changes.rst:340
msgid ""
"The registration CAPTCHA now uses the ALTCHA widget v3 protocol with "
"Argon2id proof-of-work."
msgstr ""
"註冊流程的 CAPTCHA 現在使用 ALTCHA widget v3 協定並搭配 Argon2id 工作量證明機"
"制。"

#: changes.rst:341
msgid ""
"The ``set_language_team`` project attribute has been replaced with the "
"``po_set_language_team`` file format parameter at the component level; "
"see :ref:`file_format_params`."
msgstr ""
"``set_language_team`` 專案屬性已被位於元件層級的 ``po_set_language_team`` 檔"
"案格式參數取代；請參閱 :ref:`file_format_params`。"

#: changes.rst:342
msgid ""
"Weblate now uses calendar versioning for releases, see :ref:`release-cycle`."
msgstr "Weblate 現在使用日曆版本編號發行，請參閱 :ref:`release-cycle`。"

#: changes.rst:343
msgid ""
"Weblate now uses stricter dependency version constraints to better control "
"runtime environment."
msgstr "Weblate 現在使用更嚴格的依賴版本約束以更好地控制執行時期環境。"

#: changes.rst:349
msgid ""
"The ``ALTCHA_MAX_NUMBER`` setting has been replaced "
"by :setting:`ALTCHA_COST`, :setting:`ALTCHA_MEMORY_COST`, "
"and :setting:`ALTCHA_PARALLELISM`; please adjust your settings accordingly."
msgstr ""
"``ALTCHA_MAX_NUMBER`` 設定已"
"被 :setting:`ALTCHA_COST` 、 :setting:`ALTCHA_MEMORY_COST` "
"與 :setting:`ALTCHA_PARALLELISM` 取代；請相應地調整您的設定。"

#: changes.rst:350
msgid ""
"The upgrading policy was changed, and upgrades are only supported from the "
"current or previous calendar year."
msgstr "升級政策已變更，僅支援從目前或前一個日曆年度的版本升級。"

#: changes.rst:351
msgid ""
"The ``COMMENT_CLEANUP_DAYS`` and ``SUGGESTION_CLEANUP_DAYS`` settings are "
"migrated once to site-wide :ref:`addon-weblate.removal.comments` "
"and :ref:`addon-weblate.removal.suggestions` add-ons; configure those add-"
"ons instead."
msgstr ""
"``COMMENT_CLEANUP_DAYS`` 與 ``SUGGESTION_CLEANUP_DAYS`` 設定會一次性移轉至網"
"站層級的 :ref:`addon-weblate.removal.comments` 及 :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.removal.suggestions` 附加元件；之後請改為設定這些附加元件。"

#: changes.rst:357
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/162?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`所有變化詳情 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/162?"
"closed=1>`__."

