#: changes/v4.rst:89
msgid ""
"Migration to rewritten metrics storage might take considerable time on "
"larger Weblate instance (expect around 15 minutes per GB of "
"``metrics_metric`` table). To reduce downtime, you can copy :file:`weblate/"
"metrics/migrations/*.py` from Weblate 4.17 to 4.16 and start the migration "
"in the background. Once it is completed, perform full upgrade as usual."
msgstr ""
"在較大的 Weblate 執行個體上移轉至重寫後的指標儲存空間，可能需要相當長的時間"
"（``metrics_metric`` 資料表每 GB 預計約需 15 分鐘）。為縮短停機時間，您可以"
"將 Weblate 4.17 的 :file:`weblate/metrics/migrations/*.py` 複製到 4.16，並在"
"後台啟動移轉。完成後，再照常執行完整升級。"

#: changes/v4.rst:95
msgid ""
"Docker container now requires PostgreSQL 12 or newer, please "
"see :ref:`docker-postgres-upgrade` for upgrade instructions. Weblate itself "
"supports older versions as well, when appropriate Django version is "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Docker 容器現在需要 PostgreSQL 12 或更新版本，升級說明請見 :ref:`docker-"
"postgres-upgrade`。裝有合適的 Django 版本時，Weblate 自身同樣支援舊版本。"

#: changes/v4.rst:101
msgid ""
"Migration on MySQL will try to load all metrics into memory due to "
"limitation of the Python database driver. You might need to prune metrics "
"prior to migration if you want to continue using MySQL. Please consider "
"switching to PostgreSQL, see :ref:`database-migration`."
msgstr ""
"受限於 Python 資料庫驅動限制，MySQL 移轉會嘗試載入所有指標到記憶體中。如果想"
"要繼續使用 MySQL，您可能需要在移轉前刪減指標。請考慮切換到 PostgreSQL，"
"見 :ref:`database-migration`。"

