msgstr "加入鍵盤快捷建 Alt+Enter 來以建議的方式提交字串。"

#: changes/v4.rst:216
msgid "Added support for placeables in the Fluent format."
msgstr "新增對 Fluent 格式中可置入項目的支援。"

#: changes/v4.rst:217
msgid "Improved performance of translation memory."
msgstr "改進了翻譯記憶的效能。"

#: changes/v4.rst:218
msgid ""
"Autogenerate repoweb browsing links for well known code hosting services."
msgstr "為知名的程式碼託管服務自動產生 repoweb 瀏覽連結。"

#: changes/v4.rst:219
msgid "Improved performance of several views."
msgstr "改進了多個檢視的效能。"

#: changes/v4.rst:220
msgid "Improved listing of strings with plurals."
msgstr "改進了含複數的字串的清單。"

#: changes/v4.rst:221
msgid "Added support for adding custom markup to HTML head."
msgstr "新增對 HTML head 自訂標記的支援。"

#: changes/v4.rst:222
msgid ""
"Fixed generation of MO files in the add-on to include only translated files."
msgstr "修復了附加元件中 MO 檔案產生的問題，現在只包含已翻譯檔案。"

#: changes/v4.rst:223
msgid "Fixed rendering of regular expression flags."
msgstr "修復了正規表達式的繪製問題。"

#: changes/v4.rst:224
msgid "Improved placeholders check behavior with plurals."
msgstr "改進了複數的佔位符檢查行為。"

#: changes/v4.rst:225
msgid "Added support for translation files naming suitable for Google Play."
msgstr "新增對適用於 Google Play 之翻譯檔案命名方式的支援。"

#: changes/v4.rst:226
msgid "Added support for labels in API."
msgstr "新增了在 API 中標籤的支援。"

#: changes/v4.rst:227
msgid ""
"Added support for choosing different e-mail for commits than for "
"notifications."
msgstr "新增支援為提交與通知選擇不同的電子郵件地址。"

#: changes/v4.rst:228
msgid "The Docker image no longer enables debug mode by default."
msgstr "該 Docker 映像不再預設啟用除錯模式。"

#: changes/v4.rst:229
msgid "Order glossary terms based on the glossary component priority."
msgstr "根據詞彙表元件優先順序對詞彙表術語進行排序。"

#: changes/v4.rst:230
msgid "Added team administrators who can add or remove members of the team."
msgstr "新增了可以新增或刪除團隊成員的管理員。"

#: changes/v4.rst:231
msgid "Added a popup confirmation before deleting users."
msgstr "新增了刪除使用者前的彈出視窗確認。"

#: changes/v4.rst:232
msgid "Added add-on to customize XML output."
msgstr "新增了自訂 XML 輸出的附加元件。"

#: changes/v4.rst:234
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/88?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`所有變化詳情 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/88?"
"closed=1>`__ 。"

#: changes/v4.rst:240
msgid ""
"Weblate now requires ``btree_gin`` extension in PostgreSQL. The migration "
"process will install it if it has sufficient privileges. See :ref:`dbsetup-"
"postgres` for manual setup."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 現在需要 PostgreSQL 中的 ``btree_gin`` 擴充套件。如果具有足夠的權限，"
"移轉過程中將安裝它。請參閱 :ref:`dbsetup-postgres` 進行手動設定。"

#: changes/v4.rst:242
msgid ""
"The Docker image no longer enables debug mode by default. In case you want "
"it, enable it in the environment using :envvar:`WEBLATE_DEBUG`."
msgstr ""
"Docker 映像不再預設啟用除錯模式。如有需要，請在環境中使"
"用 :envvar:`WEBLATE_DEBUG` 啟用。"

#: changes/v4.rst:244
msgid ""
"The database migration make take hours on larger instances due to recreating "
"some of the indexes."
msgstr ""
"由於要重新建立一些索引，資料庫移轉在較大的執行個體上可能需要花費數小時。"

#: changes/v4.rst:246
msgid ""
"**Changed in 4.15.1:** The default value for ``DEFAULT_PAGINATION_CLASS`` in "
"rest framework settings was changed."
msgstr ""
"**4.15.1 版變更：**\\ REST framework 設定中 ``DEFAULT_PAGINATION_CLASS`` 的預"
"設值已變更。"

#: changes/v4.rst:251
