msgstr "修正註冊失敗時的 CAPTCHA 輸入問題。"

#: changes/v4.rst:267
msgid "Improved languages support in DeepL."
msgstr "改進了 DeepL 中的語言支援。"

#: changes/v4.rst:268
msgid "Improved webhooks compatibility with authenticated repositories."
msgstr "改進了 webhook 與經身分驗證的儲存庫的相容性。"

#: changes/v4.rst:269
msgid "Added support for Python 3.11."
msgstr "新增了對 Python 3.11 的支援。"

