msgstr "修復了變更連結元件儲存庫時的死鎖。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1220
msgid "Included edit distance in changes listing and CSV and reports."
msgstr "包括了變更清單和 CSV 與 報告中的編輯距離。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1221
msgid "Avoid false positives of punctuation spacing check for Canadian French."
msgstr "避免了對加拿大法語進行符號間隔檢查時的誤報。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1222
msgid "Fixed XLIFF export with placeholders."
msgstr "修復了用佔位符匯出 XLIFF。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1223
msgid "Fixed false positive with zero width check."
msgstr "修復了零寬度檢查的誤報。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1224
msgid "Improved reporting of configuration errors."
msgstr "改進了設定錯誤的報告。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1225
msgid "Fixed bilingual source upload."
msgstr "修復了雙語言來源上傳。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1226
msgid "Automatically detect supported languages for DeepL machine translation."
msgstr "為 DeepL 機器翻譯自動檢測支援的語言。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1227
msgid "Fixed progress bar display in some corner cases."
msgstr "修復了一些極端情況下的進度條顯示問題。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1228
msgid "Fixed some checks triggering on non translated strings."
msgstr "修正部分檢查在未翻譯字串上觸發的問題。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1231
msgid "Weblate 4.0.1"
msgstr "Weblate 4.0.1"

#: changes/v4.rst:1233 changes/v4.rst:1240
msgid "*Released on April 16th 2020.*"
msgstr "*發佈於 2020 年 4 月 16 日。*"

#: changes/v4.rst:1235
msgid "Fixed package installation from PyPI."
msgstr "修正從 PyPI 安裝套件的問題。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1238
msgid "Weblate 4.0"
msgstr "Weblate 4.0"

#: changes/v4.rst:1242
msgid "Weblate now requires Python 3.6 or newer."
msgstr "Weblate 現在需要 Python 3.6 或更新版本。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1243
msgid "Added management overview of component alerts."
msgstr "新增了元件警示的管理概覽。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1244
msgid "Added component alert for broken repository browser URLs."
msgstr "新增了斷裂的儲存庫瀏覽器 URL 的元件警示。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1245
msgid "Improved sign in and registration pages."
msgstr "改進了登陸和註冊頁面。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1246
msgid ""
"Project access control and workflow configuration integrated to project "
"settings."
msgstr "專案存取控制與工作流程設定整合在專案設定中。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1247
msgid "Added check and highlighter for i18next interpolation and nesting."
msgstr "為 i18next 插值和巢狀新增了檢查和醒目顯示標記。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1248
msgid "Added check and highlighter for percent placeholders."
msgstr "為百分號佔位符號新增檢查和醒目顯示標記。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1249
msgid "Display suggestions failing checks."
msgstr "顯示未通過檢查的建議。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1250
msgid "Record source string changes in history."
msgstr "在歷史中記錄來源字串變更。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1251
msgid "Upgraded Microsoft Translator to version 3 API."
msgstr "將 Microsoft Translator 升級為版本 3 的 API。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1252
msgid "Reimplemented translation memory backend."
msgstr "重新應用翻譯記憶後端。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1253
msgid "Added support for several ``is:`` lookups in :doc:`/user/search`."
msgstr "新增支援在 :doc:`/user/search` 中同時使用幾個 ``is:`` 進行查詢。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1254
msgid "Allow to make :ref:`check-same` avoid the built-in words exceptions."
msgstr "允許 :ref:`check-same` 不採用內建字詞例外規則。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1255
msgid "Improved comments extraction from monolingual po files."
msgstr "改進了從單語言 po 檔案中提取註解。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1256
msgid "Renamed whiteboard messages to announcements."
msgstr "將白板訊息（whiteboard message）改名為公告（announcement）。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1257
msgid "Fixed occasional problems with registration mails."
msgstr "修復了註冊電子郵件偶爾出現的問題。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1258
msgid "Improved LINGUAS update add-on to handle more syntax variants."
msgstr "改進了 LINGUAS 更新附加元件來處理更多的語法變數。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1259
msgid "Fixed editing monolingual XLIFF source file."
msgstr "修正編輯單語 XLIFF 來源檔案的問題。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1260
msgid "Added support for exact matching in :doc:`/user/search`."
msgstr "新增支援 :doc:`/user/search` 的精確相符。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1261
msgid ""
"Extended API to cover screenshots, users, groups, componentlists and "
"extended creating projects."
msgstr ""
"擴充了 API 覆寫螢幕擷圖、使用者、使用者群組、元件清單，並擴充了新增專案。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1262
msgid "Add support for source upload on bilingual translations."
msgstr "為雙語言翻譯上傳的來源新增支援。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1263
msgid "Added support for intermediate language from developers."
msgstr "為開發者的中間語言新增支援。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1264
msgid "Added support for source strings review."
msgstr "新增了對來源字串檢閱的支援。"

#: changes/v4.rst:1265
msgid "Extended download options for platform wide translation memory."
msgstr "擴充了平台範圍翻譯記憶的下載選項。"

#: changes/v5.rst:2
msgid "Weblate 5.x series"
msgstr "Weblate 5.x 系列"

#: changes/v5.rst:5
msgid "Weblate 5.17.1"
msgstr "Weblate 5.17.1"

#: changes/v5.rst:7
msgid "*Released on April 30th 2026.*"
msgstr "*發佈於 2026 年 4 月 30 日。*"

#: changes/v5.rst:11
msgid ""
"Add-ons that opt in to manual triggering can now be run from add-on "
"management and the :ref:`addons-api`."
msgstr ""
"選擇手動觸發的附加元件現在可以從附加元件管理和 :ref:`addons-api` 中執行。"

#: changes/v5.rst:12
msgid ""
"Admins can now clean up blocked or abusive users by reverting edits, "
"rejecting pending suggestions, and deleting comments across project or site-"
"wide scopes."
msgstr ""
"管理員現在可以還原編輯、拒絕待處理的建議，以及刪除專案範圍或整個網站範圍內的"
"留言，以清理遭封鎖或濫用服務的使用者。"

#: changes/v5.rst:13
msgid "Admin user management can now find users by audit log IP address."
msgstr "管理員使用者管理現在可以依稽核記錄中的 IP 位址搜尋使用者。"

#: changes/v5.rst:14
msgid ""
":doc:`/admin/announcements` can now also be managed via the :ref:`api` for "
"categories."
msgstr "現在也可透過類別的 :ref:`api` 管理 :doc:`/admin/announcements`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:15
msgid "Added :ref:`mt-ltengine` machine translation service."
msgstr "新增了 :ref:`mt-ltengine` 機器翻譯服務。"

#: changes/v5.rst:19
msgid ""
"Improved documentation for the global ``user.edit`` "
"permission, :ref:`autoclean-tm`, :ref:`glossary-terminology`, and "
"current :ref:`translation-memory` management options in the UI."
msgstr ""
"改進了全域 ``user.edit`` 權限、:ref:`autoclean-tm`、:ref:`glossary-"
"terminology`，以及使用者介面中目前 :ref:`translation-memory` 管理選項的說明文"
"件。"

#: changes/v5.rst:20
msgid ""
"Improved :ref:`screenshots` documentation and linked it from the screenshots "
"UI."
msgstr "改善 :ref:`screenshots` 說明文件，並從螢幕擷圖使用者介面連結至該文件。"

#: changes/v5.rst:21
msgid ""
"Documented restoring Docker-based setups from backups, see :ref:`restore-"
"docker`."
msgstr "補充從備份還原 Docker 環境的說明文件，請參閱 :ref:`restore-docker`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:22
msgid ""
"Clarified :ref:`generic-upgrade-instructions` to state that Celery queues "
"should be empty before upgrading."
msgstr ""
"澄清了 :ref:`generic-upgrade-instructions` 來聲明 Celery 佇列在升級前應該為"
"空。"

#: changes/v5.rst:23
msgid ""
"The OpenAPI schema is cleaner and now describes action endpoints with their "
"actual list, statistics, status, upload, and download response payloads."
msgstr ""
"OpenAPI 結構描述更加簡潔，現在會以操作端點實際使用的清單、統計資料、狀態、上"
"傳與下載回應承載資料加以描述。"

#: changes/v5.rst:24
msgid ""
"The web installation flow for :ref:`addon-weblate.consistency.languages` now "
"shows a preview and requires confirmation before creating missing language "
"files across projects, categories, or site-wide scopes."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.consistency.languages` 的 web 安裝流程現在提供預覽並在專"
"案、類別、或全站範圍建立缺失的語言檔案前要求確認。"

#: changes/v5.rst:25
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.discovery.discovery` now offers guided client-side "
"presets, suggests presets detected from component repository layouts, "
"validates ``{{ component }}`` more clearly, and includes a worked discovery-"
"template example in the docs."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.discovery.discovery` 現在提供引導式用戶端預設設定、依元件"
"儲存庫設定建議偵測到的預設設定、更清楚地驗證 ``{{ component }}``，並在說明文"
"件中加入完整的探索範本範例。"

#: changes/v5.rst:26
msgid ""
"Superuser and site-wide team changes are now tracked in :ref:`audit-log`."
msgstr "現在在 :ref:`audit-log` 中追蹤超級使用者和全站團隊變更。"

#: changes/v5.rst:27
msgid ""
"URL validation alerts now show clearer errors for project website and "
"repository browser URLs, and project-level machine translation validation "
"better explains private or local endpoint restrictions on hosted and self-"
"managed sites."
msgstr ""
"URL 驗證警示現在會針對專案網站及儲存庫瀏覽器 URL 顯示更清楚的錯誤；專案層級的"
"機器翻譯驗證也會更清楚說明 Hosted Weblate 與自行管理網站對私有或本機端點的限"
"制。"

#: changes/v5.rst:28
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.autotranslate.autotranslate` now attributes copied "
"translations to the add-on user and records automatic translation results in "
"the add-on activity log."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.autotranslate.autotranslate` 現在將複製的翻譯歸因到附加元"
"件使用者並在附件元件活動日誌中記錄自動翻譯結果。"

#: changes/v5.rst:29
msgid ""
"Extended the conflicting repository setup alert to direct Git pushes, "
"see :ref:`alerts`."
msgstr "將有衝突的儲存庫設定警報擴充套件到直接 Git 推送，見 :ref:`alerts`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:30
msgid ":ref:`profile` links now show an external-link warning where possible."
msgstr ":ref:`profile` 連結現在會在適當情況下顯示外部連結警告。"

#: changes/v5.rst:31
msgid ""
"Client-side popup notifications triggered by JavaScript now use Bootstrap "
"toasts, with higher-contrast dark theme colors for Bootstrap subtle and "
"emphasis variants."
msgstr ""
"JavaScript 觸發的用戶端彈出通知現已改用 Bootstrap Toasts，並為 Bootstrap 的 "
"subtle 與 emphasis 樣式變體採用對比度更高的深色主題配色。"

#: changes/v5.rst:32
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SSH keys` management page can now remove stored host keys so "
"changed host keys can be replaced there."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`SSH 金鑰` 管理頁面現在可以移除已儲存的主機金鑰，以便在此處替換已變"
"更的主機金鑰。"

#: changes/v5.rst:33
msgid ""
"Project listings now show review progress columns when any listed project "
"has reviews enabled."
msgstr "專案清單現在會在所列專案有任何一個啟用審閱時，顯示審閱進度欄。"

#: changes/v5.rst:37
msgid ""
"Image URLs in Markdown are now escaped before rendering "
"(:cve:`2026-44264` / :ghsa:`5cmv-3rc4-7279`)."
msgstr ""
"Markdown 格式的圖片連結現在在渲染前已逸出"
"（:cve:`2026-44264`/:ghsa:`5cmv-3rc4-7279`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:38
msgid ""
"Tightened :ref:`api` input validation to prevent translation enumeration "
"(:cve:`2026-44263` / :ghsa:`gcg5-86jr-f7jg`)."
msgstr ""
"收緊了 :ref:`api` 輸入驗證防止譯文列舉（:cve:`2026-44263`/:ghsa:`gcg5-86jr-"
"f7jg`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:39
msgid ""
"Project backup imports now revalidate component repository URLs before "
"restoring from backup (:cve:`2026-41654` / :ghsa:`cwcx-382v-8m9g`)."
msgstr ""
"專案備份匯入現在會在從備份檔案復原前重新驗證元件儲存庫 URL。"
"（:cve:`2026-41654`/:ghsa:`cwcx-382v-8m9g`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:40
msgid ""
"Fixed revert links in the translate-view history tab after moving a "
"component to another project."
msgstr "修復了移動元件到另一個專案後在翻譯檢視的歷史記錄標籤中撤銷連結的問題。"

#: changes/v5.rst:41
msgid ""
"Invitation acceptance now verifies the invited e-mail address and invitation "
"expiry before granting team membership."
msgstr ""
"接受邀請時，現在會先驗證受邀的電子郵件地址及邀請是否到期，再授予團隊成員資"
"格。"

#: changes/v5.rst:42
msgid ""
":ref:`check-rst-references` no longer crashes on repeated explicit-link "
"targets."
msgstr ":ref:`check-rst-references` 遇到重複的顯示連結目標時不再崩潰。"

#: changes/v5.rst:43
msgid ""
"The :ref:`addons-api` now validates required add-on configuration when "
"installing add-ons."
msgstr ":ref:`addons-api` 現在會於安裝時驗證其需要的設定。"

#: changes/v5.rst:44
msgid ""
"Component updates no longer time out waiting on their own repository lock "
"during validation."
msgstr "元件更新在驗證期間不再因等待自身儲存庫鎖而超時。"

#: changes/v5.rst:45
msgid ""
":ref:`check-punctuation-spacing` check no longer triggers false positives "
"for placeholders."
msgstr ":ref:`check-punctuation-spacing` 不再對佔位字元觸發誤報。"

#: changes/v5.rst:46
msgid ""
"Repository alerts, history entries, and task messages now preserve multiline "
"Git and SSH backend error output."
msgstr ""
"儲存庫警示、歷史記錄項目與工作訊息，現在會保留 Git 及 SSH 後端的多行錯誤輸"
"出。"

#: changes/v5.rst:47
msgid ""
"Interrupted Git rebases now recover more reliably after worker restarts, and "
"signal-terminated backend commands are reported more clearly."
msgstr ""
"被中斷的 Git 變基操作在工作程序重啟後現在可以更可靠地復原，並且因訊號而終止的"
"後端指令會得到更清晰的報告。"

#: changes/v5.rst:48
msgid ""
"Borg backups that finish with warnings are no longer shown as failed in the "
"management UI, and backup logs now show ``C`` entries for files that changed "
"during the backup."
msgstr ""
"以警告結束的 Borg 備份不再在管理 UI 中顯示為失敗，備份日誌現在會為備份過程中"
"發生變更的檔案顯示 ``C`` 條目。"

#: changes/v5.rst:49
msgid ""
"Git exporter no longer rejects shared-history fetches just because the first "
"negotiated ``have`` revisions are newer than Weblate's local history."
msgstr ""
"Git 匯出器不再因為首次協商的 ``have`` 修訂版本比 Weblate 的本機歷史記錄更新就"
"拒絕共享歷史記錄的取得。"

#: changes/v5.rst:50
msgid ""
":ref:`mt-weblate-translation-memory` automatic translation avoids broad "
"PostgreSQL searches."
msgstr ""
":ref:`mt-weblate-translation-memory` 自動翻譯避免了大範圍 PostgreSQL 搜尋。"

#: changes/v5.rst:51
msgid "Malformed IPv6 repository URLs no longer crash SSH host key detection."
msgstr "錯誤格式的 IPv6 儲存庫 URL 不再導致 SSH 主機金鑰偵測當機。"

#: changes/v5.rst:52
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.xgettext` and related POT update add-ons now "
"replace the standard descriptive-title placeholder in normalized POT headers "
"again."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.xgettext` 與相關 POT 更新附加元件，現在會再次取代"
"正規化 POT 標頭中的標準描述性標題預留位置。"

#: changes/v5.rst:53
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.django` now skips repository ``locale`` trees "
"during preflight validation, fixing components that store ``django.pot`` in "
"a top-level ``locale`` directory."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.django` 現在在飛行前驗證期間跳過儲存庫 "
"``locale`` 樹，修復在頂層 ``locale`` 目錄中儲存 ``django.pot`` 的元件。"

#: changes/v5.rst:54
msgid ""
"Screenshot OCR now skips corrupted or truncated image files instead of "
"failing the request."
msgstr "螢幕擷圖 OCR 現在會略過損壞或截斷的影像檔案而不是導致請求失敗。"

#: changes/v5.rst:55
msgid ""
"Monolingual component validation now honors :ref:`component-source_language` "
"when checking duplicate files alongside a separate :ref:`component-template`."
msgstr ""
"單語言元件驗證檢查重複檔案時現在除了單獨的 :ref:`component-template` 還遵"
"循 :ref:`component-source_language`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:56
msgid ""
":ref:`Translation memory upload <memory-user>` and :wladmin:`import_memory` "
"now report a validation error for TMX files missing the required header "
"instead of failing the request."
msgstr ""
":ref:`翻譯記憶上傳 <memory-user>` 與 :wladmin:`import_memory` 現在會針對缺少"
"必要標頭的 TMX 檔案回報驗證錯誤，而不會讓整個要求失敗。"

#: changes/v5.rst:57
msgid ""
":ref:`mt-weblate-translation-memory` no longer misses boundary similarity "
"matches after stricter lookups."
msgstr ""
":ref:`mt-weblate-translation-memory` 在更嚴格的查詢後不再缺失邊界相似性相符。"

#: changes/v5.rst:58
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The missing file-mask matches :ref:`alert <alerts>` is now restored after "
"rescans that leave only the source translation."
msgstr ""
"在重新掃描後僅留下來源翻譯時，現在會還原「找不到符合檔案遮罩的項目」:ref:`警"
"示 <alerts>`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:59
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.discovery.discovery` now disables inherited string "
"management for discovered formats that do not support adding or removing "
"strings."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.discovery.discovery` 現在會針對不支援新增或移除字串的已探"
"索格式，停用繼承的字串管理功能。"

#: changes/v5.rst:60
msgid ""
"Automatic translation from other components now ignores read-only source "
"candidates with empty translations."
msgstr "來自其他元件的自動翻譯現在忽略有空白翻譯的唯讀原文候選。"

#: changes/v5.rst:61
msgid ""
"Project component pagination now keeps the :guilabel:`Components` tab active "
"when jumping to a typed page number."
msgstr ""
"在輸入頁碼跳至指定頁面時，專案元件分頁現在會讓 :guilabel:`Components` 分頁保"
"持作用中。"

#: changes/v5.rst:62
msgid ""
"Markdown rendering now falls back to escaped plain text when the parser "
"fails."
msgstr "Markdown 渲染現在在 Markdown 解析器故障時退回到逸出的純文字。"

#: changes/v5.rst:63
msgid ""
"Forgejo and Gitea test deliveries with sample loopback repository URLs no "
"longer trigger slow suffix matching against all components."
msgstr ""
"Forgejo 與 Gitea 使用範例迴路儲存庫 URL 的測試傳送，已不會再觸發針對所有元件"
"的緩慢後綴比對。"

#: changes/v5.rst:67
msgid ""
"Password changes now regenerate personal API keys by default "
"(:cve:`2026-41519` / :ghsa:`6j8j-4qp3-36p2`)."
msgstr ""
"密碼變更現在預設重新產生個人 API 金鑰 "
"（:cve:`2026-41519` / :ghsa:`6j8j-4qp3-36p2`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:68
msgid ""
":setting:`VCS_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` and :setting:`WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` now "
"reject URLs whose hostnames cannot be resolved during validation unless the "
"host is explicitly allowed."
msgstr ""
":setting:`VCS_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` 與 :setting:`WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` 現在會"
"拒絕驗證期間無法被解析的主機名稱，除非主機被明確允許。"

#: changes/v5.rst:69
msgid ""
":ref:`profile` URL validation now rejects obvious direct file download URLs "
"and invalid code site or Fediverse profile links."
msgstr ""
":ref:`profile` URL 驗證現在拒絕明顯的直接檔案下載 URL 並讓程式碼站或 "
"Fediverse 個人資料連結失效。"

#: changes/v5.rst:70
msgid ""
"Uploads now "
"enforce :setting:`TRANSLATION_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE`, :setting:`COMPONENT_ZIP_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE`, "
"and :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE` before parsing. Component ZIP "
"imports and project backup restores now share stricter ZIP archive safety "
"checks, including total uncompressed data limits for project backup imports."
msgstr ""
"上傳現在會於解析前強制執"
"行 :setting:`TRANSLATION_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE` 、 :setting:`COMPONENT_ZIP_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE` "
"與 :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE`。元件 ZIP 匯入與專案備份復原功能"
"現在共享更嚴格的 ZIP 存檔安全檢查，包含適用於專案備份匯入的總未壓縮資料限制。"

#: changes/v5.rst:80
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/164?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`所有變化詳情 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/164?"
"closed=1>`__."

#: changes/v5.rst:83
msgid "Weblate 5.17"
msgstr "Weblate 5.17"

#: changes/v5.rst:85
msgid "*Released on April 15th 2026.*"
msgstr "*發佈於 2026 年 4 月 15 日。*"

#: changes/v5.rst:89
msgid ""
"Added :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_ALLOWLIST` to exempt selected project "
"slugs from project website restriction settings."
msgstr ""
"新增 :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_ALLOWLIST` 在專案網站限制設定中豁免選取的"
"專案辨識符號。"

#: changes/v5.rst:90
msgid ""
"Added :setting:`WEBSITE_ALERTS_ENABLED` setting to allow disabling project "
"website availability checks and alerts."
msgstr ""
"新增了 :setting:`WEBSITE_ALERTS_ENABLED` 設定以允許停用專案網站可用性檢查與警"
"示。"

#: changes/v5.rst:91
msgid ""
"Added new management command :wladmin:`list_format_features`, which "
"generates RST documentation snippets describing the supported features for "
"every file format."
msgstr ""
"新增新的管理指令 :wladmin:`list_format_features`，此指令產生描述每個檔案格式"
"的受支援功能的 RST 檔案片段。"

#: changes/v5.rst:92
msgid ""
"Shared components can now be categorized within the target project, "
"including through the :ref:`api` using the ``category_id`` parameter."
msgstr ""
"現在可以在目標專案中對共享元件進行分類，包括用 ``category_id`` 引數透"
"過 :ref:`api` 進行分類。"

#: changes/v5.rst:93
msgid ""
"Added :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.xgettext`, :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.gettext.meson`, :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.django`, and :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.gettext.sphinx` to update POT files with configurable update cadence."
msgstr ""
"新增了 :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.xgettext`、:ref:`addon-"
"weblate.gettext.meson`、:ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.django` 和 :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.gettext.sphinx`，支援按可設定的更新頻率更新 POT 檔案。"

#: changes/v5.rst:94
msgid ""
"Added :setting:`PASSWORD_RESET_URL` to customize the sign-in page password "
"reset link, useful for external identity providers (Docker "
"env: :envvar:`WEBLATE_PASSWORD_RESET_URL`)."
msgstr ""
"新增了 :setting:`PASSWORD_RESET_URL` 以自訂登入頁面的密碼重設連結，對外部身分"
"提供者有用 （Docker 環境變數： :envvar:`WEBLATE_PASSWORD_RESET_URL`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:95
msgid "Added :ref:`bulk user invitations <invite-user>`."
msgstr "新增 :ref:`bulk user invitations <invite-user>`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:96
msgid "Added :ref:`check-objc-format`."
msgstr "新增了 :ref:`check-objc-format`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:97
msgid ""
"Added Forgejo notification webhook, see :ref:`Forgejo notifications <code-"
"hosting-forgejo-notifications>`."
msgstr ""
"新增了 Forgejo 通知 webhook，請參閱 :ref:`Forgejo 通知 <code-hosting-forgejo-"
"notifications>`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:98
msgid ""
"Added translation memory API filtering, scoped access, and bulk lookup "
"support."
msgstr "新增翻譯記憶API過濾，限制性存取和bulk查詢支援。"

#: changes/v5.rst:99
msgid ""
"Added ``from_component`` support to the REST API for creating components "
"from existing component content and for seeding new translations by "
"automatic translation from existing components."
msgstr ""
"REST API 新增支援 ``from_component`` 用於從現有元件內容建立元件並透過來自現有"
"元件的自動翻譯播種新翻譯。"

#: changes/v5.rst:100
msgid ""
":doc:`/admin/announcements` can now be managed via the :ref:`api` for "
"projects, components and translations."
msgstr ""
"現在可透過專案、元件和翻譯的 :ref:`api` 管理 :doc:`/admin/announcements` 了。"

#: changes/v5.rst:101
msgid ""
"Added a ``soft`` mode to :setting:`VERSION_DISPLAY` to hide the Weblate "
"version from prominent UI while keeping it available on "
"the :guilabel:`About` page and :http:get:`/api/metrics/`."
msgstr ""
":setting:`VERSION_DISPLAY` 新增 ``soft`` 模式在顯眼的使用者介面中隱藏 "
"Weblate 版本同時在 :guilabel:`關於` 頁面和 :http:get:`/api/metrics/` 顯示版本"
"號。"

#: changes/v5.rst:105
msgid "Track origin of newly added source strings."
msgstr "追蹤新加入來源字串的出處。"

#: changes/v5.rst:106
msgid ""
"Markdown now uses ``auto-safe-html`` by default, applying :ref:`check-safe-"
"html` and :ref:`autofix-html` only to plain text and source strings that "
"contain standard HTML markup or valid custom elements."
msgstr ""
"Markdown 現在預設使用 ``auto-safe-html``，只對純文字和包含標準 HTML 標記或有"
"效的自訂元素的來源字串應用 :ref:`check-safe-html` 和 :ref:`autofix-html`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:107
msgid "Improved LLM interfaces for better reliability."
msgstr "改進了 LLM 介面以提升可靠性。"

#: changes/v5.rst:108
msgid ""
"Improved logic for adding monolingual plurals in :doc:`/formats/gettext`."
msgstr "改進了在 :doc:`/formats/gettext` 中新增單語言複數形式的邏輯。"

#: changes/v5.rst:109
msgid ""
"Added a component alert for conflicting merge request repository setup, "
"see :ref:`alerts`."
msgstr "新增元件警示，提醒合併請求的儲存庫設定發生衝突；請參閱 :ref:`alerts`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:110
msgid "Improved plural handling in :ref:`auto-translation`."
msgstr "改進了 :ref:`auto-translation` 中的複數處理。"

#: changes/v5.rst:111
msgid "Improved error messages in some :ref:`api` endpoints."
msgstr "改進了某些 :ref:`api` 端點中的錯誤訊息。"

#: changes/v5.rst:112
msgid ""
"Updated Microsoft Entra ID authentication docs and Microsoft sign-in "
"branding while keeping legacy Azure AD backend identifiers and documentation "
"anchors for compatibility."
msgstr ""
"更新 Microsoft Entra ID 身分驗證說明文件與 Microsoft 登入品牌，同時為相容性保"
"留舊版 Azure AD 後端辨識碼及文件錨點。"

#: changes/v5.rst:113
msgid ""
"Improved performance of project and category search result pages with very "
"large match sets."
msgstr "改進了專案和含大量相符集合的類別搜尋結果頁的效能。"

#: changes/v5.rst:114
msgid ""
"Docker now "
"exposes :envvar:`WEBLATE_COMMIT_PENDING_HOURS`, :envvar:`WEBLATE_SOCIAL_AUTH_KEYCLOAK_ID_KEY` "
"for customizing the Keycloak unique user identifier claim, "
"and :envvar:`WEBLATE_NGINX_IPV6` for controlling IPv6 listeners in the "
"bundled NGINX."
msgstr ""
"Docker 現在提供 :envvar:`WEBLATE_COMMIT_PENDING_HOURS`、用於自訂 Keycloak 唯"
"一使用者辨識宣告的 :envvar:`WEBLATE_SOCIAL_AUTH_KEYCLOAK_ID_KEY`，以及用於控"
"制隨附 NGINX 中 IPv6 監聽器的 :envvar:`WEBLATE_NGINX_IPV6`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:115
msgid ""
"Project history now records project backups and project/component restore "
"events."
msgstr "專案歷史記錄現在記錄專案備份和專案/元件還原事件。"

#: changes/v5.rst:116
msgid ""
"Improved documentation with auto-generated snippets "
"for :ref:`addons`, :ref:`fmt_capabs`, :ref:`checks`, and :ref:`machine-"
"translation` machines, and clarified merge-conflict behavior for exported "
"repositories using shallow clones by default."
msgstr ""
"改善說明文件，為 :ref:`addons`、:ref:`fmt_capabs`、:ref:`checks` "
"與 :ref:`machine-translation` 引擎加入自動產生的片段，並釐清預設使用淺層複製"
"之匯出儲存庫的合併衝突行為。"

#: changes/v5.rst:117
msgid ""
"Added :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` to reject project website and "
"repository browser URLs targeting internal or non-public "
"addresses, :setting:`WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` to reject webhook URLs "
"targeting internal or non-public addresses, "
"and :setting:`VCS_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` to reject repository and push URLs "
"targeting internal or non-public addresses. These are exposed in Docker "
"as :envvar:`WEBLATE_PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, :envvar:`WEBLATE_WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, "
"and :envvar:`WEBLATE_VCS_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`."
msgstr ""
"新增 :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` 拒絕指向內部或非公開地址的專案網"
"站和儲存庫瀏覽器 URL，:setting:`WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` 拒絕指向內部或非公"
"開地址的 webhook URL， :setting:`VCS_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` 拒絕指向內部或非公開地"
"址的儲存庫和推送 URL。這些在 Docker 中暴露"
"為 :envvar:`WEBLATE_PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`、:envvar:`WEBLATE_WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`、:envvar:`WEBLATE_VCS_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:118
msgid "Improved performance of :ref:`mt-weblate` lookups."
msgstr "改進了 :ref:`mt-weblate` 查詢的效能。"

#: changes/v5.rst:119
msgid ""
"Screenshot and font upload forms now honor :setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_SIZE` "
"which now defaults to 10 MB."
msgstr ""
"螢幕擷圖和字型上傳表單現在支援 :setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_SIZE`，現在預設為 10 "
"MB。"

#: changes/v5.rst:120
msgid ""
"Expanded :doc:`/security/threat-model` to cover webhook trust boundaries and "
"delegated authorization boundaries, and clarified the instance-wide 2FA "
"enforcement path in :doc:`/admin/auth`."
msgstr ""
"擴充 :doc:`/security/threat-model`，納入 webhook 信任邊界與委派授權邊界，並"
"在 :doc:`/admin/auth` 中釐清整個執行個體強制使用 2FA 的流程。"

#: changes/v5.rst:121
msgid ""
":ref:`manage-vcs-reset-reapply` now recreates missing translation files when "
"possible and otherwise reports a clearer recovery error instead of failing "
"later with a generic parse error."
msgstr ""
":ref:`manage-vcs-reset-reapply` 現在如有可能會重新建立缺失的翻譯檔案，如不可"
"能則報告更清晰的復原錯誤而不是之後以一般性解析錯誤出錯。"

#: changes/v5.rst:122
msgid ""
"Updated :doc:`/contributing/documentation` to describe the current ``make -C "
"docs update-docs`` workflow for generated snippets."
msgstr ""
"更新了 :doc:`/contributing/documentation` 描述已產生片段的目前 ``make -C "
"docs update-docs`` 工作流。"

#: changes/v5.rst:123
msgid ""
"Linked repository components now inherit :ref:`component-"
"push_on_commit`, :ref:`component-commit_pending_age`, and :ref:`component-"
"auto_lock_error` from the linked component that owns the repository."
msgstr ""
"連結的儲存庫元件現在從擁有儲存庫的已連結元件繼承 :ref:`component-"
"push_on_commit`、:ref:`component-commit_pending_age`、:ref:`component-"
"auto_lock_error`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:124
msgid ""
"Git exporter now provides clearer push and missing-revision errors to "
"authorized users."
msgstr "Git 匯出工具現在向已授權使用者提供更清晰的推送和修改缺失錯誤。"

#: changes/v5.rst:125
msgid ""
"Faster category and project removals, and improved performance of project "
"language counting and API listing on projects with shared components."
msgstr ""
"加快分類及專案移除作業，並改善含共享元件之專案的語言計數與 API 清單效能。"

#: changes/v5.rst:126
msgid "Clarified Git LFS limits of :ref:`git-exporter` in the UI and docs."
msgstr "在使用者介面和文件中闡明 :ref:`git-exporter` 的 Git LFS 限制。"

#: changes/v5.rst:127
msgid ""
"Improved :ref:`backup` status reporting while keeping maintenance after "
"failed backup attempts."
msgstr "改進了 :ref:`backup` 狀態報告，同時在備份嘗試失敗後保持維護狀態。"

#: changes/v5.rst:128
msgid ""
"Improved loading speed for comments on the translate page and reduced "
"repeated metric queries when rendering activity charts on overview pages "
"with cold caches."
msgstr ""
"改進了翻譯頁面的評論載入速度，減少了在有冷快取的概覽頁面上渲染活動圖表時的重"
"複指標查詢。"

#: changes/v5.rst:131
msgid "Security fixes"
msgstr "安全修復"

#: changes/v5.rst:132
msgid ""
"Hardened repository boundary checks for symlink targets "
"(:cve:`2026-40256` / :ghsa:`ffgh-3jrf-8wvh`)."
msgstr ""
"強化了符號連結目標的儲存庫邊界檢查"
"（:cve:`2026-40256`/:ghsa:`ffgh-3jrf-8wvh`)。"

#: changes/v5.rst:133
msgid ""
"Hardened component file handling for repository symlinks "
"(:cve:`2026-34242` / :ghsa:`hv99-mxm5-q397`)."
msgstr ""
"強化了儲存庫符號連結的元件檔案處理 (:cve:`2026-34242` / :ghsa:`hv99-mxm5-"
"q397`)。"

#: changes/v5.rst:134
msgid ""
"Tightened :ref:`api` permission enforcement (:cve:`2026-34393` / :ghsa:`3382-"
"gw9x-477v`)."
msgstr ""
"收緊了 :ref:`api` 權限強制執行 （:cve:`2026-34393` / :ghsa:`3382-"
"gw9x-477v`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:135
msgid ""
"Hardened project-level :ref:`machine-translation` against SSRF "
"(:cve:`2026-34244` / :ghsa:`xrwr-fcw6-fmq8`)."
msgstr ""
"加固了專案層級 :ref:`machine-translation` 以對抗 SSRF 攻擊 "
"（:cve:`2026-34244` / :ghsa:`xrwr-fcw6-fmq8`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:136
msgid ""
"Tightened location validation in :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.cdnjs` "
"(:cve:`2026-33220` / :ghsa:`mqph-7h49-hqfm`)."
msgstr ""
"收緊了 :ref:`addon-weblate.cdn.cdnjs` 中的位置驗證"
"（:cve:`2026-33220` / :ghsa:`mqph-7h49-hqfm`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:137
msgid ""
"Enforced :setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_DOMAINS` across redirects for asset "
"downloads (:cve:`2026-33440` / :ghsa:`5fhx-9jwj-867m`)."
msgstr ""
"對資產下載重定向強制 :setting:`ALLOWED_ASSET_DOMAINS` "
"（:cve:`2026-33440` / :ghsa:`5fhx-9jwj-867m`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:138
msgid ""
"Hardened :ref:`addon-weblate.webhook.webhook` "
"(:cve:`2026-39845` / :ghsa:`f8hv-g549-hwg2`)."
msgstr ""
"加固了 :ref:`addon-weblate.webhook.webhook` "
"（:cve:`2026-39845` / :ghsa:`f8hv-g549-hwg2`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:139
msgid ""
"Removed unintended :ref:`translation-memory` API endpoints "
"(:cve:`2026-33214` / :ghsa:`mpf5-3vph-q75r`)."
msgstr ""
"刪除了非預期的 :ref:`translation-memory` API 端點"
"（:cve:`2026-33214` / :ghsa:`mpf5-3vph-q75r`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:140
msgid ""
"Tightened API access control for pending tasks "
"(:cve:`2026-33212` / :ghsa:`vj45-x3pj-f4w4`)."
msgstr ""
"收緊了未完成任務的 API 存取控制（:cve:`2026-33212` / :ghsa:`vj45-x3pj-"
"f4w4`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:141
msgid ""
"Hardened :ref:`projectbackup` restore against repository-local VCS "
"configuration and hooks from uploaded archives "
"(:cve:`2026-33435` / :ghsa:`558g-h753-6m33`)."
msgstr ""
"強化 :ref:`projectbackup` 還原作業，防範上傳封存檔中的儲存庫本機 VCS 設定與掛"
"勾（:cve:`2026-33435` / :ghsa:`558g-h753-6m33`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:145
msgid ""
":ref:`Project backup <projectbackup>` now preserves source translation read-"
"only handling, and source-side pending commits without files are discarded "
"to avoid repeated parse failures."
msgstr ""
":ref:`專案備份 <projectbackup>` 現在會保留來源翻譯的唯讀處理方式，並捨棄來源"
"端沒有檔案的待處理提交，以避免重複解析失敗。"

#: changes/v5.rst:146
msgid ""
"Fixed background failures in :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.autotranslate.autotranslate`."
msgstr "修復了 :ref:`addon-weblate.autotranslate.autotranslate` 中的背景失敗。"

#: changes/v5.rst:147
msgid ""
"Generated SSH wrapper scripts are now stored in :setting:`CACHE_DIR` instead "
"of persistent SSH storage, and obsolete or stale wrappers are cleaned up "
"during upgrade."
msgstr ""
"產生的 SSH 包裝器指令碼現在儲存在 :setting:`CACHE_DIR` 中而不是持久化的 SSH "
"儲存中，廢棄的或陳舊的包裝器將在升級期間被清理。"

#: changes/v5.rst:148
msgid ""
"Hardened Git branch handling to reject invalid branch names before "
"repository operations."
msgstr "加固了 Git 分支處理以在儲存庫操作之前拒絕無效分支名稱。"

#: changes/v5.rst:149
msgid ""
"Sanitized repository and upload backend errors before exposing them in UI "
"and API responses."
msgstr ""
"在使用者介面與 API 回應中顯示儲存庫及上傳後端錯誤前，現在會先清理錯誤內容。"

#: changes/v5.rst:150
msgid "Matching exporters now honor component file format parameters."
msgstr "相符的匯出工具現在會遵循元件檔案格式參數。"

#: changes/v5.rst:151
msgid ""
":ref:`project-api` now clean up stale bot users on project deletion and "
"upgrade, and prevent removing the last assigned team to avoid orphaning the "
"token."
msgstr ""
":ref:`project-api` 現在會在刪除及升級專案時清理過時的 bot 使用者，並防止移除"
"最後一個已指派團隊，以免權杖失去歸屬。"

#: changes/v5.rst:152
msgid ""
"Batch automatic translation now uses project-level machinery configuration "
"instead of only site-wide settings."
msgstr "批次自動翻譯現在使用專案級機器翻譯設定而不再僅使用網站範圍設定。"

#: changes/v5.rst:153
msgid "Fixed sorting by the **Unreviewed** column in listings."
msgstr "修正清單中依 **未審閱** 欄排序的問題。"

#: changes/v5.rst:154
msgid ""
"Fixed false positive in :ref:`check-xml-chars-around-tags` for Arabic letter "
"Waw (\"و\") adjacent to XML tags."
msgstr ""
"修復了 :ref:`check-xml-chars-around-tags` 中與 XML 標籤相鄰的阿拉伯字母 Waw "
"(\"و\") 的誤報問題。"

#: changes/v5.rst:155
msgid ":ref:`addon-weblate.git.squash` better handle commits applied upstream."
msgstr ":ref:`addon-weblate.git.squash` 現在能更妥善地處理已套用至上游的提交。"

#: changes/v5.rst:156
msgid ""
":wladmin:`list_checks` now requires exactly one ``--sections`` value when "
"writing generated documentation to a file using ``--output``."
msgstr ""
":wladmin:`list_checks` 使用 ``--output`` 將產生的說明檔案寫入檔案時，現在要求"
"恰好提供一個 ``--sections`` 值。"

#: changes/v5.rst:157
msgid ""
"Watched translations on the dashboard now use a stable language-aware "
"ordering."
msgstr "控制台上已關注的翻譯，現在會使用穩定且能辨識語言的排序方式。"

#: changes/v5.rst:158
msgid ""
"Reduced error-reporting noise for handled authentication callback failures "
"and clarified password reset confirmation messages."
msgstr ""
"降低已處理身分驗證回呼失敗所產生的錯誤回報雜訊，並釐清密碼重設確認訊息。"

#: changes/v5.rst:159
msgid ""
":doc:`/admin/machine` now falls back to the default API URL when base URL is "
"empty."
msgstr "當基礎 URL 為空時，:doc:`/admin/machine` 現在會回退到預設 API URL。"

#: changes/v5.rst:160
msgid ":ref:`mt-deepl` maps plain Portuguese to European Portuguese."
msgstr ":ref:`mt-deepl` 會將未指定地區的葡萄牙文對應至歐洲葡萄牙文。"

#: changes/v5.rst:161
msgid ""
":ref:`mt-mymemory` now falls back to HTTP status handling when the service "
"returns a non-JSON error response."
msgstr ""
":ref:`mt-mymemory` 現在在服務傳回非 JSON 錯誤回應時退回 HTTP 狀態處理。"

#: changes/v5.rst:162
msgid ""
"Push branches are no longer updated with upstream-only commits in multi-"
"branch workflows."
msgstr "在多分支工作流程中，推送分支不再納入僅存在於上游的提交。"

#: changes/v5.rst:163
msgid ""
"POT update add-ons now fall back to the component URL for the ``Report-Msgid-"
"Bugs-To`` header when the component setting is empty."
msgstr ""
"POT 更新附加元件現在會在元件設定為空時回退到 ``Report-Msgid-Bugs-To`` 標頭的"
"元件 URL。"

#: changes/v5.rst:164
msgid "Improved repository lock error handling when deleting units."
msgstr "改進了刪除單元時的儲存庫鎖定錯誤處理。"

#: changes/v5.rst:165
msgid ""
"Adding new languages now rescans only the newly added languages instead of "
"forcing a full component scan."
msgstr "新增新語言現在只重新掃描新新增的語言而不是強制完整的元件掃描。"

#: changes/v5.rst:166
msgid ""
":ref:`check-max-size` previews now keep the configured text box visible and "
"render overflowing text in red."
msgstr ""
":ref:`check-max-size` 預覽現在會讓設定的文字方塊保持可見，並以紅色轉譯溢出的"
"文字。"

#: changes/v5.rst:167
msgid ""
"Restored documented default encoding fallback for :doc:`/formats/apple` "
"and :doc:`/formats/java` when file format parameters are not explicitly set."
msgstr ""
"未明確設定檔案格式參數時，已還原 :doc:`/formats/apple` 與 :doc:`/formats/"
"java` 檔案記載的預設備用編碼。"

#: changes/v5.rst:168
msgid ""
"Reduced repeated database queries in :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.generate.fill_read_only` during the daily add-on task, and fixed "
"auto-translation progress updates when the queued target disappears before "
"execution."
msgstr ""
"減少每日附加元件工作期間，:ref:`addon-weblate.generate.fill_read_only` 的重複"
"資料庫查詢，並修正佇列中的目標在執行前消失時，自動翻譯進度的更新問題。"

#: changes/v5.rst:169
msgid ""
":doc:`/formats/android` now preserves template-defined escaped markup "
"formatting when saving translations."
msgstr ":doc:`/formats/android` 現在會在儲存翻譯時保留範本定義的逸出標記格式。"

#: changes/v5.rst:170
msgid ""
"REST API component creation now handles temporary uploaded files for "
"``docfile`` and ``zipfile`` uploads."
msgstr ""
"透過 REST API 建立元件時，現在會處理 ``docfile`` 與 ``zipfile`` 上傳所使用的"
"暫存檔案。"

#: changes/v5.rst:171
msgid ""
"SSH repository errors now distinguish changed host keys from missing host "
"keys and avoid automatically trusting host key replacements."
msgstr ""
"SSH 儲存庫錯誤現在能區分已變更與缺少的主機金鑰，並避免自動信任替換後的主機金"
"鑰。"

#: changes/v5.rst:172
msgid ""
":ref:`machine-translation` no longer treats translatable reStructuredText "
"role content as :ref:`placeables-mt`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`machine-translation` 不再將可翻譯的 reStructuredText 角色內容視"
"為 :ref:`placeables-mt`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:173
msgid ""
":ref:`check-end-interrobang` now recognizes Arabic interrobang punctuation "
"such as ``؟!`` and ``!؟``."
msgstr ""
":ref:`check-end-interrobang` 現在辨識 ``؟!`` 和 ``!؟`` 等阿拉伯語問歎號標點符"
"號。"

#: changes/v5.rst:177
msgid ""
"The ``project_scope`` class attribute on add-ons has been removed. Third-"
"party add-ons that used ``project_scope = True`` should override "
"``can_install()`` to return ``False`` when ``component`` is not ``None``."
msgstr ""
"已刪除附加元件的 ``project_scope`` 類屬性。當 ``component`` 不是 ``None`` "
"時，使用 ``project_scope = True`` 的第三方附加元件應該覆蓋 ``can_install()`` "
"傳回 ``False`` 。"

#: changes/v5.rst:178
msgid ""
"The ``daily()`` method signature on add-ons has changed. Add-ons that "
"previously overrode ``daily(component)`` to perform per-component work "
"should now override ``daily_component(component)`` instead. The base "
"``daily()`` method automatically iterates components and calls "
"``daily_component()`` for each. Add-ons that can be optimized to operate at "
"project scope should override ``daily(component, project)`` directly to "
"implement project-level logic."
msgstr ""
"附加元件的 ``daily()`` 方法簽章已變更。先前覆寫 ``daily(component)`` 以執行各"
"元件工作的附加元件，現在應改為覆寫 ``daily_component(component)``。基礎 "
"``daily()`` 方法會自動逐一處理元件，並為每個元件呼叫 ``daily_component()``。"
"若附加元件可最佳化為在專案範圍運作，應直接覆寫 ``daily(component, project)`` "
"以實作專案層級邏輯。"

#: changes/v5.rst:179
msgid "Dropped support for MySQL and MariaDB as the database engine."
msgstr "放棄了對 MySQL 與 MariaDB 作為資料庫引擎的支援。"

#: changes/v5.rst:180
msgid "Weblate now requires Django 6.0."
msgstr "Weblate 現在需要 Django 6.0。"

#: changes/v5.rst:181
msgid "Weblate now requires Git 2.46 or newer."
msgstr "Weblate 現在需要 Git 2.46 或更新版本。"

#: changes/v5.rst:182
msgid ""
"Uploaded project backups are now validated more strictly during import and "
"suspicious ZIP archives can be rejected; see :ref:`projectbackup`."
msgstr ""
"現在會在匯入期間更嚴格地驗證已上傳的專案備份，並可拒絕可疑的 ZIP 封存檔；請參"
"閱 :ref:`projectbackup`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:188
msgid ""
"There are several changes in :file:`settings_example.py`, most "
"notably :setting:`ADMINS` syntax has changed in Django and "
"``SOCIAL_AUTH_PIPELINE`` and ``INSTALLED_APPS`` need adjustments; please "
"adjust your settings accordingly."
msgstr ""
":file:`settings_example.py` 中有幾項變更，最值得注意的是 :setting:`ADMINS` 的"
"語法已變更， ``SOCIAL_AUTH_PIPELINE`` 和 ``INSTALLED_APPS`` 需要調整；請相應"
"地調整您的設定。"

#: changes/v5.rst:189
msgid ""
"If you run Weblate in Docker and rely on IPv6 listeners, "
"review :envvar:`WEBLATE_NGINX_IPV6`. The default ``auto`` enables IPv6 "
"listeners only when IPv6 is available in the container runtime; use ``on`` "
"to always enable them or ``off`` to disable them."
msgstr ""
"若您在 Docker 中執行 Weblate 並依賴 IPv6 監聽器，請檢"
"查 :envvar:`WEBLATE_NGINX_IPV6`。預設值 ``auto`` 只會在容器執行階段可使用 "
"IPv6 時啟用 IPv6 監聽器；使用 ``on`` 可一律啟用，使用 ``off`` 則可停用。"

#: changes/v5.rst:190
msgid ""
"Outbound project links, webhook URLs, and repository or push URLs pointing "
"to internal or non-public addresses are now rejected by default. If your "
"setup intentionally uses internal addresses, adjust the corresponding "
"restriction settings such "
"as :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, :setting:`WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, "
"or :setting:`VCS_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, and the related allowlists such "
"as :setting:`VCS_ALLOW_HOSTS`."
msgstr ""
"預設會拒絕指向內部或非公開位址的外連專案連結、webhook URL，以及儲存庫或推送 "
"URL。若您的環境刻意使用內部位址，請調整相應的限制設定，例"
"如 :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`、:setting:`WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE` "
"或 :setting:`VCS_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`，以及 :setting:`VCS_ALLOW_HOSTS` 等相關允"
"許清單。"

#: changes/v5.rst:196
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/158?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`所有變化詳情 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/158?"
"closed=1>`__."

#: changes/v5.rst:199
msgid "Weblate 5.16.2"
msgstr "Weblate 5.16.2"

#: changes/v5.rst:201
msgid "*Released on March 6th 2026.*"
msgstr "*發佈於 2026 年 3 月 6 日。*"

#: changes/v5.rst:205
msgid ""
"New setting :setting:`PUBLIC_ENGAGE` to make the engage page public even "
"with :setting:`REQUIRE_LOGIN`."
msgstr ""
"新設定 :setting:`PUBLIC_ENGAGE` 可在使用 :setting:`REQUIRE_LOGIN` 設定情況下"
"允許公開存取參與頁面。"

#: changes/v5.rst:209
msgid "Improved matching in :doc:`/admin/memory`."
msgstr "改進了 :doc:`/admin/memory` 中的相符。"

#: changes/v5.rst:210
msgid "Show the number of strings waiting for review in listings."
msgstr "顯示清單中待稽核的字串數量。"

#: changes/v5.rst:214
msgid ""
"Avoid displaying confusing status icons for ghost languages on project or "
"category level."
msgstr "避免在專案或類別層級顯示令人困惑的幽靈語言圖示。"

#: changes/v5.rst:215
msgid ""
"Fixed missing plural source strings when creating new bilingual plural units."
msgstr "修復了建立新的雙語複數單元時缺少複數來源字串的問題。"

#: changes/v5.rst:216
msgid "Crash on certain pages with nested categories."
msgstr "在含巢狀類別的特定頁面上崩潰。"

#: changes/v5.rst:217
msgid "Improved API validation when adding strings."
msgstr "改進了新增字串時的 API 驗證。"

#: changes/v5.rst:218
msgid "Disabled throttling for incoming webhooks."
msgstr "停用了傳入 webhooks 的節流。"

#: changes/v5.rst:219
msgid "Avoid displaying non-actionable ghost languages."
msgstr "避免展示無法操作的幽靈語言。"

#: changes/v5.rst:220
msgid "Fixed highlighting in the translation editor."
msgstr "修復了翻譯編輯器中醒目顯示顯示的問題。"

#: changes/v5.rst:230
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/163?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`所有變化詳情 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/163?"
"closed=1>`__."

#: changes/v5.rst:233
msgid "Weblate 5.16.1"
msgstr "Weblate 5.16.1"

#: changes/v5.rst:235
msgid "*Released on February 26th 2026.*"
msgstr "*發佈於 2026 年 2 月 26 日。*"

#: changes/v5.rst:239
msgid ""
":doc:`/formats/asciidoc`, :doc:`/formats/xliff` with Apple extensions, "
"and :doc:`/formats/wxl` are now supported file formats."
msgstr ""
":doc:`/formats/asciidoc`、有 Apple 擴充套件的 :doc:`/formats/xliff` "
"和 :doc:`/formats/wxl` 現在是受支援的檔案格式。"

#: changes/v5.rst:240
msgid ""
"Added :setting:`REGISTRATION_ALLOW_DISPOSABLE_EMAILS` to optionally allow "
"disposable e-mail domains during registration (Docker "
"env: :envvar:`WEBLATE_REGISTRATION_ALLOW_DISPOSABLE_EMAILS`)."
msgstr ""
"新增選用的 :setting:`REGISTRATION_ALLOW_DISPOSABLE_EMAILS` 設定允許在註冊時使"
"用臨時電子郵件 (Docker "
"env: :envvar:`WEBLATE_REGISTRATION_ALLOW_DISPOSABLE_EMAILS`)。"

#: changes/v5.rst:244
msgid ""
"Improved documentation for translation states to clarify the difference "
"between :guilabel:`Needs editing`, :guilabel:`Needs rewriting`, "
"and :guilabel:`Needs checking` states."
msgstr ""
"改進了翻譯狀態文件闡明 :guilabel:`Needs editing`、:guilabel:`Needs "
"rewriting` 和 :guilabel:`Needs checking` 狀態之間的區別。"

#: changes/v5.rst:245
msgid ""
"Improved initial import of translations for :doc:`/formats/markdown` "
"and :doc:`/formats/html`."
msgstr ""
"改進了 :doc:`/formats/markdown` 和 :doc:`/formats/html` 翻譯的初始匯入。"

#: changes/v5.rst:249
msgid ":ref:`addon-weblate.webhook.slack` properly delivers all events."
msgstr ":ref:`addon-weblate.webhook.slack` 正確傳遞所有事件。"

#: changes/v5.rst:250
msgid ":ref:`check-punctuation-spacing` better handles XML markup."
msgstr ":ref:`check-punctuation-spacing` 更好地處理 XML 標記符號。"

#: changes/v5.rst:251
msgid ":doc:`/formats/stringsdict` better handle some plurals."
msgstr ":doc:`/formats/stringsdict` 更好地處理一些複數。"

#: changes/v5.rst:252
msgid "Improved plurals handling for language variants."
msgstr "改進了語言變體的複數處理。"

#: changes/v5.rst:253
msgid "Fixed API access control."
msgstr "修復了 API 存取控制。"

#: changes/v5.rst:255
msgid "Users can manage their own notification subscriptions via the API."
msgstr "使用者可以透過 API 管理他們自己的通知訂閱。"

#: changes/v5.rst:256
msgid ""
"Project administrators can manage teams in their projects via the API, "
"according to access control rules."
msgstr "專案管理員可按照存取控制規則透過 API 管理專案中的團隊。"

#: changes/v5.rst:257
msgid ""
"The add-ons listing in the API now correctly honors user permissions "
"(:cve:`2026-27457` / :ghsa:`wppc-7cq7-cgfv`)."
msgstr ""
"API 中列舉的附加元件現在正確地遵照使用者權限 "
"(:cve:`2026-27457` / :ghsa:`wppc-7cq7-cgfv`)。"

#: changes/v5.rst:259
msgid ""
"Fixed source column being cleared when translating monolingual :doc:`/"
"formats/csv`."
msgstr "修復了單語言 :doc:`/formats/csv` 時原文列被清除的問題。"

#: changes/v5.rst:269
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/161?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`所有變化詳情 <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/161?"
"closed=1>`__."

#: changes/v5.rst:272
msgid "Weblate 5.16"
msgstr "Weblate 5.16"

#: changes/v5.rst:274
msgid "*Released on February 16th 2026.*"
msgstr "*發佈於 2026 年 2 月 16 日。*"

#: changes/v5.rst:278
msgid ":ref:`check-multiple-capital` quality check."
msgstr ":ref:`check-multiple-capital` 品質檢查。"

#: changes/v5.rst:279
msgid ""
":ref:`check-xml-chars-around-tags` reduce translation errors for strings "
"with XML entities."
msgstr ":ref:`check-xml-chars-around-tags` 減少帶 XML 條目字串的翻譯錯誤。"

#: changes/v5.rst:280
msgid "Bulk accepting suggestions from a specific user in :ref:`suggestions`."
msgstr "在 :ref:`suggestions` 中批次接受來自特定使用者的建議。"

#: changes/v5.rst:281
msgid "Cloning suggestions into translation in :ref:`suggestions`."
msgstr "將建議複製到 :ref:`suggestions` 中的翻譯。"

#: changes/v5.rst:282
msgid ""
":setting:`HIDE_SHARED_GLOSSARY_COMPONENTS` to hide glossaries shared into "
"other projects."
msgstr ""
":setting:`HIDE_SHARED_GLOSSARY_COMPONENTS` 隱藏分享到其他專案的詞彙表。"

#: changes/v5.rst:283
msgid ""
"Added new management command :wladmin:`list_change_events`, which lists all "
"possible change events, :ref:`addon-choice-events`."
msgstr ""
"新增管理指令 :wladmin:`list_change_events`，該指令會列出所有可能的變更事"
"件，:ref:`addon-choice-events`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:284
msgid "Added Anthropic machinery integration, see :ref:`mt-anthropic`."
msgstr "新增了 Anthropic 系統整合，請參閱 :ref:`mt-anthropic`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:285
msgid ""
"Encoding for :ref:`formats` can now be configured "
"using :ref:`file_format_params` (e.g., ``csv_encoding``, "
"``properties_encoding``)."
msgstr ""
":ref:`formats` 的編碼現在可以用 :ref:`file_format_params` (如 "
"``csv_encoding``, ``properties_encoding``) 進行設定。"

#: changes/v5.rst:286
msgid ""
"Added support for anonymous commit names "
"via :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_NAME_TEMPLATE`."
msgstr ""
"透過 :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_NAME_TEMPLATE` 新增了對匿名提交名稱的支援。"

#: changes/v5.rst:287
msgid ""
"Consolidating identical strings in :ref:`markdown`, :ref:`html`, "
"and :ref:`txt` files using ``*merge_duplicates`` parameters "
"in :ref:`file_format_params`."
msgstr ""
"使用 :ref:`file_format_params` 中的 ``*merge_duplicates`` 引數整"
"合 :ref:`markdown`, :ref:`html`, 和 :ref:`txt` 檔案中的相同字串。"

#: changes/v5.rst:291
msgid ""
"Delete announcements permission can be assigned to teams, "
"see :ref:`privileges`."
msgstr "可以將刪除公告權限分配給團隊，見 :ref:`privileges`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:292
msgid ":doc:`/user/search` better reports errors in the query strings."
msgstr ":doc:`/user/search` 更好地報告查詢字串中的錯誤。"

#: changes/v5.rst:293
msgid "Regular repository maintenance is now performed in the background."
msgstr "現在在後臺執行定期儲存庫維護。"

#: changes/v5.rst:294
msgid "Repository cleanup now recovers failed merges or rebases."
msgstr "儲存庫清理現在復原失敗的合併或變基操作。"

#: changes/v5.rst:295
msgid "Better visibility of :ref:`project-commit_policy` to translators."
msgstr "改進對譯者的 :ref:`project-commit_policy` 可見性。"

#: changes/v5.rst:296
msgid ""
"Validation of VCS settings :ref:`code-hosting-push-options` has been "
"extended."
msgstr "擴充套件了 VCS 設定 :ref:`code-hosting-push-options` 的驗證。"

#: changes/v5.rst:297
msgid ""
"The default values for :ref:`project-translation_review` and :ref:`project-"
"source_review` can be configured in settings."
msgstr ""
"可以在設定中設定 :ref:`project-translation_review` 和 :ref:`project-"
"source_review` 的預設值。"

#: changes/v5.rst:298
msgid ""
"The :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_TEMPLATE` now supports the ``{user_id}`` "
"and ``{site_title}`` variables."
msgstr ""
":setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_TEMPLATE` 現在支援 ``{user_id}`` 與 "
"``{site_title}`` 變數。"

#: changes/v5.rst:299
msgid ""
"The default value for personal translation memory contribution is now based "
"on the :setting:`DEFAULT_AUTOCLEAN_TM` configuration."
msgstr ""
"個人翻譯記憶貢獻的預設值現在基於 :setting:`DEFAULT_AUTOCLEAN_TM` 設定。"

#: changes/v5.rst:303
msgid ""
"Argument injection in the management console "
"(:cve:`2026-24126` / :ghsa:`33fm-6gp7-4p47`)."
msgstr ""
"管理控制檯中的變數注入漏洞 (:cve:`2026-24126` / :ghsa:`33fm-6gp7-4p47`)。"

#: changes/v5.rst:304
msgid ""
"Adding plural strings with singular matching existing string is now "
"prohibited for bilingual translations (see :ref:`bimono`)."
msgstr ""
"雙語翻譯現在禁止透過相符單數的現有字串新增複數字串（見 :ref:`bimono`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:305
msgid "Automatic :ref:`component-repoweb` URL for common code hosting sites."
msgstr "對於常見程式碼託管網站的自動 :ref:`component-repoweb` URL。"

#: changes/v5.rst:306
msgid ""
"Improved cache isolation for suggestion checks to avoid interference with "
"the parent unit checks."
msgstr "改進了建議檢查的快取隔離避免干涉主單元檢查。"

#: changes/v5.rst:307
msgid "Gracefully handle invalid check flags in :ref:`custom-checks`."
msgstr "優雅地處理 :ref:`custom-checks` 中的無效檢查標記。"

#: changes/v5.rst:308
msgid ":doc:`/formats/appstore` no longer rewrites unchanged files."
msgstr ":doc:`/formats/appstore` 不再重寫未變更的檔案。"

#: changes/v5.rst:312
msgid ""
":ref:`check-regex` no longer marks matched portions as non-translatable to "
"allow generic regular-expression-based checking of strings. Use :ref:`check-"
"placeholders` for checking regular expression matched placeholders."
msgstr ""
":ref:`check-regex` 不再將相符的部分標記為“不可翻譯”來允許通用的基於正規表示式"
"的字串檢查。用 :ref:`check-placeholders` 檢查相符正規表示式的佔位符。"

#: changes/v5.rst:313
msgid ""
"The default value for :setting:`WEBLATE_FORMATS` changed because of the "
"removal of encoding-specific formats."
msgstr ":setting:`WEBLATE_FORMATS` 的預設值已變更，因為刪除了特定編碼的格式。"

#: changes/v5.rst:314
msgid ""
"File formats that only differed in encoding (CSV, GWT Properties, Java "
"Properties, iOS Strings) have been merged into single formats."
msgstr ""
"只有編碼差異的檔案格式（CSV、GWT 屬性、Java 屬性、iOS 屬性）已被合併到到單一"
"格式群。"

#: changes/v5.rst:315
msgid "Fonts used by Weblate are now shipped in a standalone package."
