#: changes/v5.rst:412
msgid ""
"Added new Ollama machinery tool for local Ollama AI model integration, "
"see :ref:`mt-ollama`."
msgstr ""
"新增了新的 Ollama 機器翻譯工具用於本機 Ollama AI 模型整合，請參閱 :ref:`mt-"
"ollama`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:413
msgid ""
"Added :http:get:`/api/units/(int:id)/comments/` to get a list of comments "
