msgstr ""
"新增 :http:get:`/api/units/(int:id)/comments/`，用於取得指定翻譯單元的留言清"
"單。"

#: changes/v5.rst:414
msgid "Memory contents imported from TMX files include string context."
msgstr "從 TMX 檔案匯入的記憶庫內容包括字串情境。"

#: changes/v5.rst:415
msgid ""
":doc:`/formats/xliff2`, :doc:`/formats/nextcloud-json`, :doc:`/formats/"
"resjson`, and :doc:`/formats/toml` are now supported file formats."
msgstr ""
":doc:`/formats/xliff2` 、 :doc:`/formats/nextcloud-json` 、 :doc:`/formats/"
"resjson` 與 :doc:`/formats/toml` 現在是支援的檔案格式。"

#: changes/v5.rst:416
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.fedora_messaging.publish` integration is now available "
