msgstr ":ref:`addon-weblate.fedora_messaging.publish` 現作為附加元件可用。"

#: changes/v5.rst:417
msgid "Added :ref:`check-laravel-format` quality check."
msgstr "新增了 :ref:`check-laravel-format` 品質檢查。"

