msgstr "現在由專門標記而非標籤來標示自動翻譯的字串。"

#: changes/v5.rst:425
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.discovery.discovery` preserves :ref:`file_format_params`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.discovery.discovery` 保留 :ref:`file_format_params`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:426
msgid ":ref:`mt-cyrtranslit` now supports Belarusian and Greek."
msgstr ":ref:`mt-cyrtranslit` 現支援白俄羅斯語和希臘語。"

#: changes/v5.rst:427
msgid ""
":ref:`block-user` now accepts internal notes that are not visible to the "
"user."
msgstr ":ref:`block-user` 現在接受使用者不可見的內部附註。"

#: changes/v5.rst:428
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.webhook.slack` and :ref:`addon-weblate.webhook.webhook` "
"can be installed multiple times."
msgstr ""
"可多次安裝 :ref:`addon-weblate.webhook.slack` 和 :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.webhook.webhook`。"

#: changes/v5.rst:429
msgid "Compatibility with Git SHA256 repositories."
msgstr "相容 Git SHA256 儲存庫。"

#: changes/v5.rst:430
msgid ""
"The allowed version control URLs can now be configured "
"using :setting:`VCS_ALLOW_SCHEMES` and :setting:`VCS_ALLOW_HOSTS`."
msgstr ""
"現在可以用 :setting:`VCS_ALLOW_SCHEMES` 和 :setting:`VCS_ALLOW_HOSTS` 設定允"
"許的版本控制 URL。"

#: changes/v5.rst:431
msgid ""
"The API timeout for creating pull requests or forking can now be configured "
"via :setting:`VCS_API_TIMEOUT`."
msgstr ""
"現在可透過 :setting:`VCS_API_TIMEOUT` 設定建立 Pull Request 或分叉儲存庫時的 "
"API 逾時時間。"

#: changes/v5.rst:432
msgid ""
"Improved VCS integration documentation to clarify Docker environment "
"variables, commit authorship, hosted vs. self-hosted setup, and "
"authentication options."
msgstr ""
"改善 VCS 整合說明文件，釐清 Docker 環境變數、提交作者身分、託管與自行託管環"
"境，以及身分驗證選項。"

#: changes/v5.rst:433
msgid "Timestamps from past are now shown with more detail."
msgstr "現在更加詳細地展示過往時間戳。"

#: changes/v5.rst:434
msgid ""
"Added two new :ref:`states` to provide more detailed tracking of work-in-"
"progress translations."
msgstr "新增兩個 :ref:`states`，以更詳細地追蹤進行中的翻譯。"

#: changes/v5.rst:438
msgid ""
"Improper invitation validation upon accepting "
"(:cve:`2025-64725` / :ghsa:`m6hq-f4w9-qrjj`)."
msgstr ""
"接受邀請時的不正確的邀請驗證（:cve:`2025-64725`/:ghsa:`m6hq-f4w9-qrjj`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:439
msgid ""
"Server-Side Request Forgery while cloning repository "
"(:cve:`2025-66407` / :ghsa:`hfpv-mc5v-p9mm`)."
msgstr ""
"複製儲存庫時的伺服器端請求偽造（:cve:`2025-66407`/:ghsa:`hfpv-mc5v-p9mm`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:440
msgid ""
"Over‑permissive webhook endpoint enabling mass repository updates plus "
"component enumeration (:cve:`2025-67492` / :ghsa:`pj86-258h-qrvf`)."
msgstr ""
"權限過大的 webhook 端點允許大規模儲存庫更新加元件列舉"
"（:cve:`2025-67492`/:ghsa:`pj86-258h-qrvf`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:441
msgid ""
"Notification settings disclosure via Weblate API "
"(:cve:`2025-67715` / :ghsa:`3pmh-24wp-xpf4`)."
msgstr ""
"透過 Weblate API 的通知設定披露（:cve:`2025-67715`/:ghsa:`3pmh-24wp-xpf4`）。"

#: changes/v5.rst:442
msgid ""
":ref:`mt-deepl` integration now correctly handles translating to Chinese "
"variants."
msgstr ":ref:`mt-deepl` 整合現在能正確處理翻譯成不同中文變體的情況。"

#: changes/v5.rst:443
msgid ""
":doc:`/formats/csv` format saving translations with empty source fields when "
"using monolingual base files."
msgstr ""
"使用單語基礎檔案時，修正 :doc:`/formats/csv` 格式儲存空白來源欄位翻譯的問題。"

#: changes/v5.rst:444
msgid ""
"Tighter validation of user and full names to avoid confusing homoglyphs."
msgstr "更嚴格地驗證使用者和全名避免令人困惑的同形異義字元。"

#: changes/v5.rst:445
msgid "Avoid false positive checks upon committing pending changes."
msgstr "避免提交待處理變更時出現檢查誤報。"

#: changes/v5.rst:446
msgid "Performance improvements for file upload."
msgstr "檔案上傳的效能改進。"

#: changes/v5.rst:447
msgid "Show glossary matches for the source language."
msgstr "顯示來源語言的詞彙表相符項目。"

#: changes/v5.rst:448
msgid "Pull/merge requests are now only created when necessary."
msgstr "拉取/合併請求現在僅於必要時建立。"

#: changes/v5.rst:452
msgid ""
"Replaced custom ``RequireLoginMiddleware`` with Django 5.1's "
"``LoginRequiredMiddleware``. This makes settings ``LOGIN_REQUIRED_URLS`` and "
"``LOGIN_REQUIRED_URLS_EXCEPTIONS`` no longer supported, including their "
"Docker environment variable counterparts."
msgstr ""
"用 Django 5.1 的 ``LoginRequiredMiddleware`` 替換了自訂的 "
"``RequireLoginMiddleware``。這使得 ``LOGIN_REQUIRED_URLS`` 和 "
"``LOGIN_REQUIRED_URLS_EXCEPTIONS`` 不再被支援，包括它們的 Docker 環境變數對應"
"物。"

#: changes/v5.rst:453
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.webhook.webhook` secret length is now validated to match "
"the Standard Webhooks specification."
msgstr ""
"現在會驗證 :ref:`addon-weblate.webhook.webhook` 的 secret 長度是否符合 "
"Standard Webhooks 規範。"

#: changes/v5.rst:454
msgid "Python 3.12 or newer is now required."
msgstr "現在需要 Python 3.12 或更新版本。"

#: changes/v5.rst:455
msgid "GLib 2.80 or newer is now required."
msgstr "現在需要 GLib 2.80 或更新版本。"

#: changes/v5.rst:456
msgid "Dropped support for Web Monetization."
msgstr "不再支援 Web Monetization。"

#: changes/v5.rst:457
msgid ""
":doc:`/formats/laravel` no longer includes ``return`` prefix in the keys."
msgstr ":doc:`/formats/laravel` 在 key 中不再包括 ``return`` 字首。"

#: changes/v5.rst:458
msgid ""
"There are several changes in :file:`settings_example.py`, most notable are "
"changed settings ``CRISPY_ALLOWED_TEMPLATE_PACKS`` and ``INSTALLED_APPS``; "
"please adjust your settings accordingly."
msgstr ""
":file:`settings_example.py` 中有幾項變更，最顯著的是變更了 "
"``CRISPY_ALLOWED_TEMPLATE_PACKS`` 和 ``INSTALLED_APPS`` 設定，請相應調整您的"
"設定。"

