msgid ""
":ref:`component-enforced_checks` are now applied on strings imported from "
"the repository."
msgstr ":ref:`component-enforced_checks` 現在會套用至從儲存庫匯入的字串。"

#: changes/v5.rst:1170
msgid ""
"Reduced false positives in :ref:`check-end-colon` and :ref:`check-end-stop` "
"for CJK languages."
msgstr ""
"降低了 CJK 語言在 :ref:`check-end-colon` 與 :ref:`check-end-stop` 中的誤報。"

