msgstr ""
"用於元件和專案的 ``GET /api/components/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"credits/`` 與 ``GET /api/projects/(string:project)/credits/`` API 端點。"

#: changes/v5.rst:1523
msgid ""
":ref:`glossary-terminology` entries in Glossary can now only be created by "
