msgid "Weblate now uses mistletoe instead of misaka as a Markdown renderer."
msgstr "Weblate 現在使用 mistletoe 取代 misaka 作為 Markdown 轉譯器。"

#: changes/v5.rst:1536
msgid ":ref:`csp` is now stricter what might block third-party customizations."
msgstr ":ref:`csp` 現在更為嚴格，這可能攔截第三方自訂。"

