"應調整您的設定。"

#: changes/v5.rst:1547
msgid ""
":setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS` is now required for WebAuthn support. If you cannot "
"use HTTPS, please silence related check as described "
"in :setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS` documentation."
msgstr ""
"WebAuthn 支援現在需要 :setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS`。若無法使用 HTTPS，請"
"依 :setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS` 說明文件停用相關檢查。"

