"式 <formats>`，讓譯者能輕鬆參與貢獻。"

#: contributing/about.rst:13
msgid "\"Weblate\" is a portmanteau of the words \"web\" and \"translate\"."
msgstr "\"Weblate\" 是由字詞 \"web\" 與 \"translate\"融合而來。"

#: contributing/about.rst:18
msgid ""
"The landing page is https://weblate.org and there is a cloud-hosted service "
