#: devel/alerts.rst:22
msgid "Unused screenshots"
msgstr "未使用的螢幕擷圖"

#: devel/alerts.rst:23
msgid "Ambiguous language code"
msgstr "模稜兩可的語言代碼"

#: devel/alerts.rst:24
msgid "Unused new base in component settings"
msgstr "在元件設定中未使用的新基礎"

#: devel/alerts.rst:25
msgid "Duplicate file mask used for linked components"
msgstr "複製連結元件使用的檔案遮罩"

#: devel/alerts.rst:26
msgid "Conflicting merge request repository setup"
msgstr "衝突合併請求儲存庫設定"

#: devel/alerts.rst:27
msgid "Component seems unused (configurable by :setting:`UNUSED_ALERT_DAYS`)"
msgstr "元件似乎未使用（可透過 :setting:`UNUSED_ALERT_DAYS` 設定）"

#: devel/alerts.rst:28
msgid "Unused glossary languages"
msgstr "未使用的詞彙表語言"

#: devel/alerts.rst:30
msgid ""
"The alerts are updated daily, or on related change (for example "
"when :ref:`component` is changed or when repository is updated)."
msgstr ""
"警報每天更新，或在相關變化時更新（例如，當 :ref:`component` 被改變或當儲存庫"
"被更新）。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:33
msgid ""
"Project website availability checks can be disabled "
"using :setting:`WEBSITE_ALERTS_ENABLED`, in which case Weblate will no "
"longer generate alerts for unreachable project websites."
msgstr ""
"可使用 :setting:`WEBSITE_ALERTS_ENABLED` 停用專案網站可用性檢查，如果停用 "
"Weblate 將不再產生無法連線的專案網站的警報。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:37
msgid ""
"Alerts are listed on each respective component page "
"as :guilabel:`Diagnostics`."
msgstr "各項警示會在相應元件頁面上以 :guilabel:`診斷` 列出。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:43
msgid "Project and workspace diagnostics overviews"
msgstr "專案及工作區診斷概覽"

#: devel/alerts.rst:45
msgid ""
"Signed-in users can open the :guilabel:`Diagnostics` tab on project and "
"workspace pages. The overview is loaded when opened and groups alerts of the "
"same type instead of repeating them for every component."
msgstr ""
"已登入的使用者可以開啟專案及工作區頁面的 :guilabel:`診斷` 分頁。開啟時才會載"
"入概覽，並將相同類型的警示分組，而不會針對每個元件重複顯示。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:49
msgid ""
"The project overview shows project-wide findings once and lists the "
"components affected by component-specific findings:"
msgstr ""
"專案概覽會將專案層級的診斷項目各顯示一次，並列出受元件層級診斷項目影響的元"
"件："

#: devel/alerts.rst:52
msgid "Project diagnostics overview with grouped findings and filters"
msgstr "含分組診斷項目及篩選條件的專案診斷概覽"

#: devel/alerts.rst:55
msgid ""
"The workspace overview groups project-wide findings by project and "
"identifies components using both the project and component name:"
msgstr ""
"工作區概覽會依專案將專案層級的診斷項目分組，並同時使用專案名稱及元件名稱來識"
"別元件："

#: devel/alerts.rst:58
msgid "Workspace diagnostics overview with grouped findings and filters"
msgstr "含分組診斷項目及篩選條件的工作區診斷概覽"

#: devel/alerts.rst:61
msgid ""
"Each finding lists up to 20 affected projects or components. Additional "
"affected objects are shown as a count. Follow a component link to see the "
"complete diagnostic details or dismiss a diagnostic on the component page."
msgstr ""
"每個診斷項目最多會列出 20 個受影響的專案或元件。其他受影響的物件會以數量顯"
"示。請開啟元件連結，以查看完整的診斷詳細資料，或在元件頁面忽略該診斷。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:65
msgid ""
"The summary can be filtered by active or dismissed state, severity, "
"category, or whether the signed-in user can act on the diagnostic. "
"Components shared into a project are listed only in the diagnostics of their "
"owning project."
msgstr ""
"摘要可以依作用中或已忽略狀態、嚴重性、類別，或已登入使用者是否能處理該診斷進"
"行篩選。分享至專案的元件，只會列在其所屬專案的診斷中。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:69
msgid ""
"If it is missing, the component clears all current checks. Problem alerts "
"cannot be ignored, but will disappear once the underlying problem has been "
"fixed."
msgstr ""
"若缺少該項目，元件會清除目前所有檢查。問題警示無法忽略，但在根本問題修正後便"
"會消失。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:72
msgid ""
"Information and warning alerts are used for guidance on improving community "
"localization. These can be dismissed and make the :guilabel:`Diagnostics` "
"tab visible, but they do not indicate a component problem in listings."
msgstr ""
"資訊及警告提示用於提供改善社群在地化的指引。這些提示可以關閉，並會"
"讓 :guilabel:`Diagnostics` 分頁顯示出來，但不代表清單中的元件發生問題。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:77
msgid ""
"Dismissed diagnostics record who dismissed them, when they were dismissed, "
"and an optional reason. A dismissal is automatically reopened when the "
"diagnostic details or the configuration relevant to that diagnostic changes. "
"Dismissal and reopening are both recorded in the component change history."
msgstr ""
"已忽略的診斷會記錄忽略者、忽略時間及選填原因。診斷詳細資料或相關設定變更時，"
"系統會自動重新開啟已忽略的診斷。忽略及重新開啟都會記錄在元件變更記錄中。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:82
msgid ""
"Warning and error notifications are sent only to subscribed project "
"maintainers who have permission to act on the diagnostic. Informational "
"recommendations do not send unsolicited notifications."
msgstr ""
"警告及錯誤通知只會傳送給已訂閱且有權處理該診斷的專案維護者。資訊性建議不會主"
"動傳送通知。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:86
msgid ""
"Custom alerts can override ``BaseAlert.get_dismissal_context(component, "
"details)`` to include stable, JSON-serializable configuration or diagnostic "
"inputs. Changing the returned context reopens a dismissed alert. Incidental "
"values such as evaluation time should not be included."
msgstr ""
"自訂警示可覆寫 ``BaseAlert.get_dismissal_context(component, details)``，以納"
"入穩定且可序列化為 JSON 的設定或診斷輸入。傳回的情境資料若有變更，便會重新開"
"啟已忽略的警示。不應納入評估時間等非固定值。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:92
msgid "A component with both duplicated strings and languages looks like this:"
msgstr "帶有複製的字串和語言的元件看起來像這樣："

#: devel/alerts.rst:97
msgid "Conflicting repository setup"
msgstr "有衝突的儲存庫設定"

#: devel/alerts.rst:99
msgid ""
"This alert is shown when multiple Git components are configured to push to "
"the same repository and push branch without all of them pulling from that "
"branch. This includes pull or merge request workflows, and direct pushes to "
"a separate push branch. Such a setup can overwrite the shared branch."
msgstr ""
"當多個 Git 元件被設定為推送到相同儲存庫和推送分支而這些元件均不從那個分支進行"
"拉取時顯示此警告。這包括拉取或合併請求工作流以及直接推送到單獨推送分支。這樣"
"的設定可以覆蓋共享分支。"

#: devel/alerts.rst:104
msgid ""
"To resolve this, either configure a different :guilabel:`Push branch` for "
"each component or share the repository between components using a "
"``weblate://project/component`` repository URL."
msgstr ""
"要解決這個問題，要麼為每個元件設定不同的 :guilabel:`Push branch`，要麼用 "
"``weblate://project/component`` 儲存庫 URL 在不同元件間共享一個儲存庫。"

#: devel/community.rst:2
msgid "Building a translators community"
msgstr "建立譯者社群"

#: devel/community.rst:4
msgid ""
"Following these recommendations supports the creation of a full, "
"multilingual post-editing tool. Good translations are defined through the "
"systemic-functional model of House which aims at a contextual correct "
"translation. Write your own `post-editing guide <https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Postediting>`_ and alter these recommendations to fit your own "
"definitions. In most cases the `browser-plugin of languageTool <https://"
"languagetool.org/#firefox_chrome>`_ is useful as a proof-reading tool."
msgstr ""
"遵循這些建議支援建立完整的多語言後期編輯工具。好的翻譯是透過 House 的系統功能"
"模型定義的，該模型旨在達成情境正確的翻譯。編寫您自己的 `後期編輯指南 "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Postediting>`_ 並變更這些建議以適合您自己的定"
"義。大多數情況下，languageTool 的 `browser-plugin <https://languagetool.org/"
"#firefox_chrome>`_ 可用作校對工具。"

#: devel/community.rst:6
msgid ""
"Many times translators will find problems with the source strings. Make sure "
"it is easy for them to report such problems. To gather this feedback, you "
"can set up the :ref:`component-repoweb` field on your Weblate component, for "
"translators to propose their changes to the upstream repository. You can "
"also receive translator comments if you set up :ref:`component-"
"report_source_bugs`."
msgstr ""
"譯者經常會發現來源字串的問題。確保譯者可以輕鬆報告這樣的問題。要收集此種意見"
"回饋，您可以在您的 Weblate 元件上設定 :ref:`component-repoweb` 欄位，讓譯者提"
"議對上游儲存庫的變更。如果您設定了 :ref:`component-report_source_bugs`，您也"
"可以收到譯者的評論。"

#: devel/community.rst:11
msgid "Component diagnostics"
msgstr "元件診斷"

#: devel/community.rst:13
msgid ""
"Guidance is shown in the :guilabel:`Diagnostics` tab on each component. "
"These alerts are dismissible and point to the configuration or documentation "
"needed to make your localization process easier for community translators."
msgstr ""
"指引顯示在每個元件的 :guilabel:`診斷` 分頁中。這些警報可忽略並指向讓您的在地"
"化流程對社群譯員更加簡單所需的設定或文件。"

#: devel/community.rst:21
msgid "Terminology management"
msgstr "專有名詞管理"

#: devel/community.rst:22
msgid ""
"Post-editing of MT with terminology assignment influences each level of the "
"translation process. The machine translation system can be adapted to the "
"specific vocabulary and style with a continued training or `neural fuzzy "
"repair <https://aclanthology.org/P19-1175.pdf>`_. `Import <https://"
"docs.weblate.org/en/latest/admin/memory.html#imported-translation-memory>`_ "
"your existing translation memory into weblate or create an initial scope "
"with your basic terminology. In the end the lector should be instructed with "
"additional terminology documents to guarantee a good knowledge and output in "
"the field."
msgstr ""
"帶有術語分配的MT的後期編輯影響著翻譯過程的每個層次。機器翻譯系統可以透過持續"
"訓練或 `神經模糊修復 <https://aclanthology.org/P19-1175.pdf>`_ 來適應特定的詞"
"彙和風格。`匯入 <https://docs.weblate.org/en/latest/admin/"
"memory.html#imported-translation-memory>`_ 您現有的翻譯記憶到 weblate，或者用"
"您的基本術語建立一個初始範圍。最後，應該用額外的術語檔案來指導演講者，以保證"
"在該欄位有良好的知識和產出。"

#: devel/community.rst:26 snippets/addons-autogenerated.rst:38
msgid "Machine translation"
msgstr "機器翻譯"

#: devel/community.rst:27
msgid ""
"The quality of the automatic translation (often measured with the BLEU-"
"score) correlates with editing time [1]. Choose a machine backend which "
"supports the needed languages and domains. Make clear how the translation "
"backend functions and which quality the post-editor has to expect."
msgstr ""
"自動翻譯的品質（通常用BLEU分數衡量）與編輯時間相關[1]。選擇一個支援所需語言和"
"領域的機器後端。明確翻譯後臺的功能以及後期編輯所期望的品質。"

#: devel/community.rst:30
msgid "Review translations"
msgstr "檢閱翻譯"

#: devel/community.rst:31
msgid ""
"The translations should be reviewed by a second person after the post-"
"editing. With an impartial and competent reviewer, the two people rule "
"reduces the errors and improves the quality and consistency of the content. "
"Providing reviewers with previews or alpha translations will make for the "
"best review. Screenshots, explanations also help to review the strings in "
"context."
msgstr ""
"譯文在編輯後應由第二個人進行稽核。有公正且稱職的稽核者，雙人稽核規則可以減少"
"錯誤，提升內容的品質和一致性。向稽核者提供預覽或 alpha 翻譯有助於達成最佳稽核"
"效果。螢幕擷圖、解釋也有助於在情境中稽核字串。"

#: devel/community.rst:36
msgid "Structured feedback"
msgstr "結構化回饋"

#: devel/community.rst:37
msgid ""
"There are many :doc:`/user/checks` in Weblate that provide structured "
"feedback on the quality of the translations. They also give visual feedback "
"during translation. This prevents recurring mistakes, and helps translators "
"to understand how the code works."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 中有許多 :doc:`/user/checks` 為翻譯品質提供結構化回饋，並在翻譯期間給"
"予視覺提示。這些功能有助於避免重複發生的錯誤，並幫助翻譯者理解程式碼的工作方"
"式。"

#: devel/community.rst:41
msgid "Translation definition"
msgstr "翻譯定義"

#: devel/community.rst:42
msgid ""
"In addition to the mentalistic and impact-based definitions which make a "
"strong reduction, the text-based linguistic approach fits best with the "
"implemented translation methods. A well-formulated theory for translation "
"evaluation is House's systemic-functional model, which focuses on the "
"relation between original and translation. The model assumes that "
"translation is an attempt to keep the semantic, pragmatic, and textual "
"meaning of a text equivalent when crossing from one linguistic code to "
"another."
msgstr ""
"除了基於心理和基於影響的定義之外，基於文字的語言學方法最適合實施的翻譯方法。"
"一個精心制定的翻譯評估理論是豪斯的系統功能模型，它側重於原始和翻譯之間的關"
"係。該模型假設翻譯是在從一種語言程式碼交叉到另一種語言程式碼時保持文字等效的"
"語義，語用和文字含義的嘗試。"

#: devel/community.rst:44
msgid ""
"The degree of quality of a translation is based on the degree of "
"equivalence, the correspondence between the text profile and the text "
"function. Because it cannot be calculated automatically, sufficient "
"information should be collected to enable a uniform human evaluation. The "
"two main parameters of agreement in a corresponding model are the macro-"
"context – i.e. embedding in a larger social and literary context – and the "
"micro-context consisting of field, tenor and mode."
msgstr ""
"翻譯的品質程度是基於對等程度，即文字輪廓和文字功能之間的對應關係。因為它不能"
"自動計算，所以應該收集足夠的資訊，以便能夠進行統一的人工評估。相應模型中的兩"
"個主要一致引數是宏觀情境--即嵌入更大的社會和文學背景中--以及由領域、主旨和模"
"式組成的微觀情境。"

#: devel/community.rst:47
msgid "Sources"
msgstr "來源"

#: devel/community.rst:48
msgid ""
"Marina Sanchez-Torron and Philipp Koehn in Machine Translation Quality and "
"Post-Editor Productivity, Figure 1: https://www.cs.jhu.edu/~phi/publications/"
"machine-translation-quality.pdf"
msgstr ""
"Marina Sanchez-Torron 和 Philipp Koehn 在機器翻譯品質和譯後編輯效率方面，圖 "
"1：https://www.cs.jhu.edu/~phi/publications/machine-translation-quality.pdf"

#: devel/community.rst:49
msgid ""
"Joanna Best und Sylvia Kalina. Übersetzen und Dolmetschen: eine "
"Orientierungshilfe. A. Francke Verlag Tübingen und Base, 2002. Möglichkeiten "
"der Übersetzungskritik starting on page number 101"
msgstr ""
"Joanna Best und Sylvia Kalina. Übersetzen und Dolmetschen: eine "
"Orientierungshilfe. A. Francke Verlag Tübingen und Base, 2002. Möglichkeiten "
"der Übersetzungskritik 自 101 頁起"

#: devel/community.rst:50
msgid ""
"neural fuzzy repair, Bram Bulté and Arda Tezcan in Neural Fuzzy Repair: "
"Integrating Fuzzy Matches into Neural Machine Translation, 2019 https://"
"aclanthology.org/P19-1175.pdf"
msgstr ""
"神經模糊修復，Bram Bulté 和 Arda Tezcan 在神經模糊修復：將模糊相符整合到神經"
"機器翻譯中，2019年 https://aclanthology.org/P19-1175.pdf"

#: devel/gettext.rst:2
msgid "Translating software using GNU gettext"
msgstr "使用 GNU gettext 來翻譯軟體"

#: devel/gettext.rst:4
msgid ""
"`GNU gettext`_ is one of the most widely used tool for internationalization "
"of free software. It provides a simple yet flexible way to localize the "
"software. It has great support for plurals, it can add further context to "
"the translated string and there are quite a lot of tools built around it. Of "
"course it has great support in Weblate (see :ref:`gettext` file format "
"description)."
msgstr ""
"`GNU gettext`_ 是自由軟體國際化最廣泛使用的工具之一。它提供了簡單與彈性的方式"
"來進行軟體在地化。它有完善的支援複數格式，可以為翻譯字串增加更多的情境內容與"
"相當多的工具為它所打造。當然它也有 Weblate 的強力支援（參閱 :ref:`gettext` 檔"
"案格式說明）。"

#: devel/gettext.rst:12
msgid ""
"If you are about to use it in proprietary software, please consult licensing "
"first, it might not be suitable for you."
msgstr "如果打算在私有軟體中使用它，那麼請首先諮詢許可，它可能不適合您。"

#: devel/gettext.rst:15
msgid ""
"GNU gettext can be used from a variety of languages (C, Python, PHP, Ruby, "
"JavaScript and many more) and usually the UI frameworks already come with "
"some support for it. The standard usage is through the `gettext()` function "
"call, which is often aliased to `_()` to make the code simpler and easier to "
"read."
msgstr ""
"GNU gettext 可以在大量語言中使用（C、Python、PHP、Ruby、JavaScript 以及更"
"多），並且一些 UI 框架通常已經為它帶有一些支援。標準使用是通過 `gettext()` 函"
"式呼叫，這通常具有 `_()` 別名，使代碼更簡單且更容易閱讀。"

#: devel/gettext.rst:20
msgid ""
"Additionally it provides `pgettext()` call to provide additional context to "
"translators and `ngettext()` which can handle plural types as defined for "
"target language."
msgstr ""
"此外，它提供了 `pgettext()` 呼叫，可用於為譯者提供更多的情境；還提供了 "
"`ngettext()`，可以處理目標語言定義的複數型別。"

#: devel/gettext.rst:24
msgid ""
"As a widely spread tool, it has many wrappers which make its usage really "
"simple, instead of manual invoking of gettext described below, you might "
"want to try one of them, for example `intltool`_."
msgstr ""
"作為廣泛傳播的工具，它具有很多封裝，使其使用相當簡單，您也許會想嘗試其中之"
"一，例如 `intltool`_，而非下面描述的對 gettext 的手動呼叫。"

#: devel/gettext.rst:29
msgid "Workflow overview"
msgstr "工作流程概覽"

#: devel/gettext.rst:31
msgid "The GNU gettext uses several files to manage the localization:"
msgstr "GNU gettext 使用幾個檔案來管理在地化工作："

#: devel/gettext.rst:33
msgid ""
":file:`PACKAGE.pot` contains strings extracted from your source code, "
"typically using `xgettext`_ or some high level wrappers such as `intltool`_."
msgstr ""
":file:`PACKAGE.pot` 包含從您的原始碼中提取的字串，典型地使用 `xgettext`_ 或一"
"些進階包裝器，如 `intltool`_。"

#: devel/gettext.rst:34
msgid ""
":file:`LANGUAGE.po` contains strings with a translation to single language. "
"It has to be updated by `msgmerge`_ once the :file:`PACKAGE.pot` is updated. "
"You can create new language files using `msginit`_ or within Weblate."
msgstr ""
":file:`LANGUAGE.po` 包含翻譯為單一語言的字串。一旦 :file:`PACKAGE.pot` 更新，"
"那麼必須由 `msgmerge`_ 來更新它。您可以使用 `msginit`_ 或在 Weblate 內新增新"
"的語言檔案。"

#: devel/gettext.rst:35
msgid ""
":file:`LANGUAGE.mo` contains binary representation of :file:`LANGUAGE.po` "
"and is used at application runtime. Typically it is not kept under version "
"control, but generated at compilation time using `msgfmt`_. In case you want "
"to have it in the version control, you can generate it in Weblate "
"using :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.mo` add-on."
msgstr ""
":file:`LANGUAGE.mo` 包含 :file:`LANGUAGE.po` 的二進製表達，並且應用執行時使"
"用。基本上它並不保持在版本控制之中，但在編譯時使用 `msgfmt`_ 產生。如果您想要"
"將它放到版本控制中，可以使用 :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.mo` 附加元件在 "
"Weblate 中產生它。"

#: devel/gettext.rst:37
msgid "Overall the GNU gettext workflow looks like this:"
msgstr "GNU gettext 總體工作流程看起來像這樣："

