#: devel/review.rst:4
msgid "Reviewing strings"
msgstr "審查字串"

#: devel/review.rst:9
msgid "Activity reports"
msgstr "活動報告"

#: devel/review.rst:11
msgid ""
"Activity reports check changes of translations, for projects, components or "
"individual users."
msgstr "活動報告檢查專案、元件或獨立使用者的翻譯的變更。"

#: devel/review.rst:13
msgid ""
"The activity reports for a project or component are accessible from its "
"dashboard, on the :guilabel:`Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"一個專案或元件的活動報告可以從其操作面板上的 :guilabel:`資訊` 分頁中取得。"

#: devel/review.rst:18
msgid ""
"More reports are accessible on the :guilabel:`Insights` tab, "
"selecting :guilabel:`Translation reports`."
msgstr ""
"更多報告可以從 :guilabel:`洞察` 分頁中取得，選擇 :guilabel:`翻譯報告`。"

#: devel/review.rst:21
msgid ""
"The activity of the currently signed in user can be seen by clicking on the "
"user name from the user menu on the top right."
msgstr "可以透過點選右上角使用者選單的使用者名稱來檢視目前登入使用者的活動。"

#: devel/review.rst:25
msgid "Source strings checks"
msgstr "來源字串的檢查"

#: devel/review.rst:27
msgid ""
"There are many :ref:`checks`, some of them focus on improving the quality of "
"source strings. Many failing checks suggest a hint to make source strings "
"easier to translate. All types of failing source checks are displayed on the "
"source language of every component."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 提供許多 :ref:`checks`，其中部分著重於改善來源字串品質。許多未通過的"
"檢查會提供提示，協助讓來源字串更容易翻譯。所有未通過的來源檢查類型，都會顯示"
"在各元件的來源語言中。"

#: devel/review.rst:33
msgid "Translation string checks"
msgstr "翻譯字串的檢查"

#: devel/review.rst:35
msgid ""
"Erroneous failing translation string checks indicate the problem is with the "
"source string. Translators sometimes fix mistakes in the translation instead "
"of reporting it - a typical example is a missing full stop at the end of a "
"sentence."
msgstr ""
"翻譯字串檢查失敗錯誤地說明問題在來源字串。翻譯者有時在翻譯中更正錯誤而不是將"
"其回報——典型範例是在句子的末尾丟掉句號。"

#: devel/review.rst:40
msgid ""
"Reviewing all failing checks can provide valuable feedback to improve its "
"source strings. To make source strings review easier, Weblate automatically "
"creates a translation for the source language and shows you source level "
"checks there:"
msgstr ""
"審查所有失敗的檢查可以提供有價值的回饋，進而改善其來源字串。為了使來源字串審"
"查更容易，Weblate 為來源語言自動建立了翻譯，並在那裡向您顯示來源語層級的檢"
"查："

#: devel/review.rst:47
msgid ""
"One of the most interesting checks here is the :ref:`check-multiple-"
"failures` - it is triggered whenever there is failure on multiple "
"translations of a given string. Usually this is something to look for, as "
"this is a string which translators have problems translating properly."
msgstr ""
"這裡一個最有趣的檢查是 :ref:`check-multiple-failures` ——無論何時給定字串的多"
"個翻譯失敗時會觸發它。通常這是要尋找的東西，因為這是翻譯者正常翻譯有問題的字"
"串。"

#: devel/review.rst:52
msgid "The detailed listing is a per language overview:"
msgstr "具體清單是每種語言的概覽："

#: devel/review.rst:59
msgid "Receiving source string feedback"
msgstr "接收來源字串回饋"

#: devel/review.rst:61
msgid ""
"Translators can comment on both translation and source strings. "
"Each :ref:`component` can be configured to receive such comments to an e-"
"mail address (see :ref:`component-report_source_bugs`), and using the "
"developers mailing list is usually the best approach. This way you can keep "
"an eye on when problems arise in translation, take care of them, and fix "
"them quickly."
msgstr ""
"翻譯者可以為翻譯和來源字串新增註解。每個 :ref:`component` 都可以設定電子郵件"
"地址來接收這樣的註解（請參閱 :ref:`component-report_source_bugs`），並且使用"
"開發者電子郵件清單通常是最佳方式。可以以這種方式關注翻譯中出現的問題，處理它"
"們，並迅速修復。"

#: devel/share.rst:4
msgid "Building the translation community"
msgstr "建立翻譯社群"

#: devel/share.rst:6
msgid ""
"Weblate provides you content to share on your website or other channels to "
"promote your translation project. A nice welcome page called Engage is "
"available to attract new contributors and provide them basic information "
"about the translation. Additionally, you can share information about the "
"efforts using social networks. All these possibilities can be found on "
"the :guilabel:`Community` tab:"
msgstr ""
"Weblate 提供可在網站或其他管道分享的內容，用來推廣翻譯專案。名為 Engage 的歡"
"迎頁面可吸引新貢獻者，並提供翻譯的基本資訊；也可以透過社群網路分享相關成果。"
"這些功能都位於 :guilabel:`社群` 分頁："

#: devel/share.rst:14
msgid ""
"All these badges are provided with a link to simple page which explains "
"users how to translate using Weblate:"
msgstr ""
"所有這些徽章都附有簡易頁面的連結，向使用者說明如何使用 Weblate 進行翻譯："

#: devel/sphinx.rst:2
msgid "Translating documentation using Sphinx"
msgstr "使用 Sphinx 翻譯說明文件"

#: devel/sphinx.rst:4
msgid ""
"`Sphinx`_ is a tool for creating beautiful documentation. It uses simple "
"reStructuredText syntax and can generate output in many formats. If you're "
"looking for an example, this documentation is also built using it. The very "
"useful companion for using Sphinx is the `Read the Docs`_ service, which "
"will build and publish your documentation for free."
msgstr ""
"`Sphinx`_ 是用來建立漂亮文件的工具。它使用了簡單的 reStructuredText 語法，並"
"以多種格式輸出。如果要找個範例，那麼本文件也是用它來建置的。使用 Sphinx 的非"
"常有用的夥伴是 `Read the Docs`_ 服務，它會免費建置並發佈您的文件。"

#: devel/sphinx.rst:10
msgid ""
"I will not focus on writing documentation itself, if you need guidance with "
"that, just follow instructions on the `Sphinx`_ website. Once you have "
"documentation ready, translating it is quite easy as Sphinx comes with "
"support for this and it is quite nicely covered in their :ref:`sphinx:intl`. "
"It's matter of a few configuration directives and invoking the ``sphinx-"
"intl`` tool."
msgstr ""
"本文不著重說明如何撰寫說明文件；若需要相關指引，請依照 `Sphinx`_ 網站的說明操"
"作。完成說明文件後，翻譯相當容易，因為 Sphinx 本身支援此功"
"能，:ref:`sphinx:intl` 也有完整說明。只需要設定少數指令，並呼叫 ``sphinx-"
"intl`` 工具。"

#: devel/sphinx.rst:17
msgid ""
"If you are using Read the Docs service, you can start building translated "
"documentation on Read the Docs. Their :doc:`rtd:localization` covers pretty "
"much everything you need - creating another project, setting its language, "
"and linking it from the main project as a translation."
msgstr ""
"若使用 Read the Docs 服務，可以開始在 Read the Docs 上建置翻譯後的說明文件。"
"其 :doc:`rtd:localization` 涵蓋幾乎所有必要步驟，包括建立另一個專案、設定語"
"言，以及從主要專案連結該專案作為翻譯。"

#: devel/sphinx.rst:22
msgid ""
"Now all you need is translating the documentation content. Sphinx generates "
"PO file for each directory or top-level file, which can lead to quite a lot "
"of files to translate (depending on :confval:`sphinx:gettext_compact` "
"settings). You can import the :file:`index.po` into Weblate as an initial "
"component and then configure :ref:`addon-weblate.discovery.discovery` add-on "
"to automatically discover all others."
msgstr ""
"接下來只需翻譯說明檔案內容。Sphinx 會為每個目錄或頂層檔案產生 PO 檔案，因此可"
"能產生大量待翻譯檔案（取決於 :confval:`sphinx:gettext_compact` 設定）。您可以"
"先將 :file:`index.po` 匯入 Weblate 作為初始元件，再設定 :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.discovery.discovery` 附加元件，自動探索其他所有元件。"

