#: devel/translations.rst:2
msgid "Managing translations"
msgstr "管理翻譯"

#: devel/translations.rst:9
msgid ""
"New strings can be made available for translation when they appear in the "
"base file, called :ref:`component-new_base` (see :ref:`component`). If your "
"file format doesn't require such a file, as is the case with most "
"monolingual translation flows, you can start with empty files."
msgstr ""
"當新字串出現在被稱為 :ref:`component-new_base` 的翻譯範本檔案中時，就可以對其"
"進行翻譯（請參閱 :ref:`component`）。如果您的檔案格式不需要這樣的檔案，那麼和"
"大多數單語翻譯流程一樣，您可以從空檔案開始。"

#: devel/translations.rst:14
msgid ""
"Weblate can add new strings to existing files for most of the file formats. "
"You can also specify :guilabel:`Context` for bilingual formats to "
"distinguish same strings used in different context. :guilabel:`Auto-adjust "
"context when an identical string already exists.` can be used to "
"automatically adjust :guilabel:`Context` by adding a numeric suffix in case "
"such a string already exist in the translation."
msgstr ""
"對於大多數檔案格式，Weblate 可以新增新字串到現有檔案。對於雙語格式，您還可以"
"指定 :guilabel:`情境` 來區分不同情境中使用的相同字串。如果翻譯中已存在相同字"
"串，則可以透過 :guilabel:`當已存在相同的字串時自動調整情境。` 新增數字字尾來"
"自動調整 :guilabel:`情境`。"

#: devel/translations.rst:28
msgid "Adding new translations"
msgstr "新增新的翻譯"

#: devel/translations.rst:30
msgid ""
"New languages can be added right away when requested by a user in Weblate, "
"or a notification will be sent to project admins for approval and manual "
"addition. This can be done using :ref:`component-new_lang` "
"in :ref:`component`."
msgstr ""
"在 Weblate 中，當使用者要求時新的語言可以立刻加入，或者新的通知會傳送給專案管"
"理員來同一或手動新增。這可以使用 :ref:`component` 中的 :ref:`component-"
"new_lang` 來達成。"

#: devel/translations.rst:34
msgid ""
"Some formats expect to start with an empty file and only translated strings "
"to be included (for example :ref:`aresource`), while others expect to have "
"all keys present (for example :ref:`gettext`). The document-based formats "
"(for example :ref:`odf`) start with a copy of the source document and all "
"strings marked as needing editing. In some situations this really doesn't "
"depend on the format, but rather on the framework you use to handle the "
"translation (for example with :ref:`json`)."
msgstr ""
"部分格式預期從空白檔案開始，且只包含已翻譯字串（例如 :ref:`aresource`）；其他"
"格式則預期所有鍵都存在（例如 :ref:`gettext`）。檔案型格式（例如 :ref:`odf`）"
"會從來源檔案的副本開始，並將所有字串標記為需要編輯。有些情況其實不是由格式決"
"定，而是取決於處理翻譯的框架（例如 :ref:`json`）。"

#: devel/translations.rst:42
msgid ""
"When you specify :ref:`component-new_base` in :ref:`component`, Weblate uses "
"this file to start new translations. Any existing translations is removed "
"from the file when doing so."
msgstr ""
"在 :ref:`component` 中指定 :ref:`component-new_base` 後，Weblate 會使用此檔案"
"建立新翻譯，並移除檔案中所有既有翻譯。"

#: devel/translations.rst:46
msgid ""
"When :ref:`component-new_base` is empty and the file format supports it, an "
"empty file is created where new strings are added once they are translated."
msgstr ""
"若 :ref:`component-new_base` 為空白且檔案格式支援，Weblate 會建立空白檔案，並"
"在新字串翻譯完成後加入其中。"

#: devel/translations.rst:50
msgid ""
"The :ref:`component-language_code_style` allows you to customize language "
"code used in generated filenames. Additionally, any mappings defined "
"in :ref:`project-language_aliases` are applied in reverse."
msgstr ""
":ref:`component-language_code_style` 允許您自訂用在產生的檔名的語言程式碼。此"
"外，任何在 :ref:`project-language_aliases` 中定義的對映會被反向應用。"

#: devel/translations.rst:65
msgid ""
"If you add a language file in connected remote repository, respective "
"translation is added to the component when Weblate updates local repository."
msgstr ""
"如果您在連線的遠端儲存庫中新增語言檔案，則當 Weblate 更新本機儲存庫時，相應的"
"翻譯會被新增到元件中。"

#: devel/translations.rst:68 devel/translations.rst:98
msgid ""
"More info on the repository update settings can be found on the :ref:`update-"
"vcs`."
msgstr "有關儲存庫更新設定的更多資訊可以在 :ref:`update-vcs` 中找到。"

#: devel/translations.rst:73
msgid "Removing existing translations"
msgstr "移除現有的翻譯"

#: devel/translations.rst:75
msgid ""
"Languages, components, or the projects they are in, can be removed (deleted "
"from Weblate and remote repository if used) from the "
"menu :guilabel:`Operations` ↓ :guilabel:`Removal` of each project, "
"component, or language."
msgstr ""
"可以從每個專案、元件或語言的選單 :guilabel:`操作` ↓ :guilabel:`移除` 中刪除語"
"言、元件或它們所在的專案（如果使用，則從 Weblate 和遠端儲存庫中刪除）。"

#: devel/translations.rst:79
msgid ""
"Initiating the :guilabel:`Removal` action shows the list of components to be "
"removed. You have to enter the object's `slug` to confirm the removal. The "
"`slug` is the project's, language's, or component's pathname as it can be "
"seen in the URL."
msgstr ""
"啟動 :guilabel:`移除` 操作後，會顯示待移除元件的清單。您必須輸入物件的 "
"`slug` 以確認移除。`slug` 是專案、語言或元件的路徑名稱，可在 URL 中看到。"

#: devel/translations.rst:83
msgid ""
"If you want to remove just some specific strings, there are following ways:"
msgstr "如果要刪除一些特定字串，則有以下方法："

#: devel/translations.rst:85
msgid ""
"Manually in the source file. They will be removed from the translation "
"project as well upon Weblate's repository update."
msgstr "手動在來源檔案中。他們將從翻譯專案中刪除，以及 Weblate 的儲存庫更新。"

#: devel/translations.rst:90
msgid ""
"In Weblate’s UI via button :guilabel:`Operations` ↓ :guilabel:`Remove` while "
"editing the string. This has differences between file formats, "
"see: :ref:`component-manage_units`"
msgstr ""
"在 Weblate 使用者介面編輯字串時，可透過 :guilabel:`操作` ↓ :guilabel:`移除` "
"按鈕執行。不同檔案格式的行為有所差異，請參閱 :ref:`component-manage_units`。"

#: devel/translations.rst:95
msgid ""
"If you delete a language file in connected remote repository, respective "
"translation will be removed from the component when Weblate updates local "
"repository."
msgstr ""
"如果刪除已連線的遠端儲存庫中的語言檔案，則當 Weblate 更新本機儲存庫時將從元件"
"中刪除相應的轉換。"

#: devel/translations.rst:104
msgid "String variants"
msgstr "字串變數"

#: devel/translations.rst:106
msgid ""
"Variants are useful to group several strings together so that translators "
"can see all variants of the string at one place."
msgstr ""
"變體可以將幾個字串組合在一起，這樣翻譯人員就可以在一個地方看到字串的所有變"
"體。"

#: devel/translations.rst:111
msgid ""
"Abbreviations (shortened forms, contractions) are a good example of variants."
msgstr "縮寫（縮短表格，收縮）是變體的一個很好範例。"

#: devel/translations.rst:114
msgid "Automated key based variants"
msgstr "自動化的鍵值變體"

#: devel/translations.rst:116
msgid ""
"You can define regular expression to group the strings based on the key of "
"monolingual translations in the :ref:`component`:"
msgstr "可以定義正規表達式，基於 :ref:`component` 的單語言翻譯的鍵將字串分組："

#: devel/translations.rst:121
msgid ""
"In case the :guilabel:`Key` matches the expression, the matching part is "
"removed to generate root key of the variant. Then all the strings with the "
"same root key become part of a single variant group, also including the "
"string with the key exactly matching the root key."
msgstr ""
"如果 :guilabel:`金鑰` 相符表達式，那麼相符部分被刪除以產生變體的根鍵。然後，"
"具有相同根鍵的所有字串將成為單一變體群組的一部分，也包括具有與根鍵完全相符的"
"鍵的字串。"

#: devel/translations.rst:126
msgid "The following table lists some usage examples:"
msgstr "後面的表格列出了一些使用範例："

