msgstr "``dial#S.key``、``dial#M.key``、``dial.key``"

#: devel/translations.rst:137
msgid "Manual variants"
msgstr "手動變化"

#: devel/translations.rst:141
msgid ""
"You can manually link specific strings using ``variant:SOURCE`` flag. This "
"can be useful for bilingual translations which do not have keys to group "
"strings automatically, or to group strings which keys are not matching, but "
"should be considered together when translating."
msgstr ""
"可以使用 ``variant:SOURCE`` 標記手動連接特定字串。對於沒有鍵將字串自動分組，"
"或將鍵不相符的字串分組的雙語言翻譯，這是有用的，但應在翻譯時一起考慮。"

#: devel/translations.rst:146
msgid ""
"The additional variant for a string can also be added using "
"the :guilabel:`Tools` while translating (when :ref:`component-manage_units` "
"is turned on):"
msgstr ""
"字串的附加變體也可以在翻譯時使用 :guilabel:`工具` 新增（當 :ref:`component-"
"manage_units` 開啟時）："

#: devel/translations.rst:153
msgid "The variant source string has to be at most 768 characters long."
msgstr "變體的來源字串長度至多為 768 個字元。"

#: devel/translations.rst:161
msgid "Variants while translating"
msgstr "翻譯時的變體"

#: devel/translations.rst:163
msgid "The variant is later grouped when translating:"
msgstr "當翻譯時變數在後面分組："

#: devel/translations.rst:170
msgid "String labels"
msgstr "字串標籤"

#: devel/translations.rst:172
msgid ""
"Split component translation strings into categories by text and colour in "
"the project configuration."
msgstr "在專案設定中透過文字和顏色將元件翻譯字串分為不同的類別。"

#: devel/translations.rst:178
msgid ""
"Labels can be assigned to units in :ref:`additional` by bulk editing, or "
"using the :ref:`addon-weblate.flags.bulk` add-on."
msgstr ""
"標籤可以透過批次編輯或使用 :ref:`addon-weblate.flags.bulk` 附加元件分配"
