msgstr ""
"非常相似的格式是 :doc:`/formats/compose-multiplatform-resources` 和 :doc:`/"
"formats/moko-resources`。"

#: formats/android.rst:17
msgid ""
"Android string resources are monolingual, the :ref:`component-template` is "
"stored in a different location from the other files -- :file:`res/values/"
"strings.xml`."
msgstr ""
"Android 字串資源是單語格式；:ref:`component-template` 儲存在與其他檔案不同的"
"位置：:file:`res/values/strings.xml`。"

#: formats/android.rst:20
msgid "Weblate does following escaping of strings:"
msgstr "Weblate 會依照下列方式逸出字串："

#: formats/android.rst:22
msgid "If a strings is valid XML, it is inserted as XML to translation."
msgstr "若字串是有效的 XML，會以 XML 形式插入翻譯。"

#: formats/android.rst:23
msgid ""
"``?`` and ``@`` are escaped with a ``\\\\`` at the beginning of the string "
"to avoid interpreting them as style or resource references."
msgstr ""
"若 ``?`` 或 ``@`` 位於字串開頭，會使用 ``\\\\`` 逸出，以免被解讀為樣式或資源"
"參照。"

#: formats/android.rst:24
msgid ""
"In case string contains multiple spaces, it is quoted with double quotes "
"(``\"``)."
msgstr "若字串包含多個空格，會以雙引號（``\"``）括住。"

#: formats/android.rst:25
msgid ""
"Newlines are escaped as ``\\\\n``, but the actual newline is kept for "
"readability as well."
msgstr "換行會逸出為 ``\\\\n``，同時保留實際換行以方便閱讀。"

#: formats/android.rst:29
msgid ""
"Android `string-array` structures are not currently supported. To work "
"around this, you can break your string arrays apart:"
msgstr ""
