#: formats/gettext.rst:29
msgid "Showing source string change"
msgstr "顯示來源字串變更"

#: formats/gettext.rst:31
msgid ""
"Weblate can extract previous source strings from the PO files if present and "
"show the string difference for strings needing editing based on that. To "
"include these, :program:`msgmerge` has to be executed with ``--previous`` "
"and the resulting PO file then contains lines such as:"
msgstr ""
"如果 PO 檔案中包含先前的來源字串，Weblate 可以擷取這些字串，並以此顯示需要編"
"輯之字串的差異。若要納入這些資訊，執行 :program:`msgmerge` 時必須加上 ``--"
"previous`` 引數；產生的 PO 檔案會包含如下的特殊資料列："

#: formats/gettext.rst:43
msgid ""
"This is controlled by the ``po_keep_previous`` :ref:`file_format_params` "
"parameter. It does not affect obsolete entries marked with ``#~``."
msgstr ""
"這由 ``po_keep_previous`` :ref:`file_format_params` 參數控制，不會影響以 "
"``#~`` 標示的過時項目。"

#: formats/gettext.rst:47
msgid "Obsolete strings"
msgstr "過時字串"

#: formats/gettext.rst:49
msgid ""
":program:`msgmerge` keeps strings removed from the POT file as obsolete "
"``#~`` entries by default. Enable the "
"``po_remove_obsolete`` :ref:`file_format_params` parameter to remove "
"obsolete entries when Weblate saves PO files."
msgstr ""
":program:`msgmerge` 預設會將已從 POT 檔案移除的字串保留為過時的 ``#~`` 項目。"
"啟用 ``po_remove_obsolete`` :ref:`file_format_params` 參數，可在 Weblate 儲"
"存 PO 檔案時移除過時項目。"

#: formats/gettext.rst:54
msgid "PO file header"
msgstr "PO 檔案標頭"

#: formats/gettext.rst:56
msgid ""
"The header of the PO file is automatically maintained by Weblate. It can be "
"configured to include the ``Language-Team``, ``Last-Translator``, ``X-"
"Generator`` and ``Report-Msgid-Bugs-To`` headers using "
"the :ref:`file_format_params`."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 會自動維護 PO 檔案的標頭。可使用 :ref:`file_format_params` 將 "
"``Language-Team``、``Last-Translator``、``X-Generator`` 及 ``Report-Msgid-"
"Bugs-To`` 標頭納入設定。"

#: formats/gettext.rst:60
msgid ""
"The header comments also can be updated to contain author names "
"using :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.authors`."
msgstr ""
"也可以使用 :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.authors` 更新標頭註解，使其包含作者名"
"稱。"

#: formats/gettext.rst:63
msgid "Line wrapping"
msgstr "換行"

#: formats/gettext.rst:65
msgid ""
"The line wrapping mostly matches GNU gettext behavior. Both the wrapping "
"algorithm in the GNU gettext and the Unicode data the wrapping is based on "
"evolve which might cause differences in some corner cases."
msgstr ""
"換行方式大致符合 GNU gettext 的行為。GNU gettext 的換行演算法及其所依據的 "
"Unicode 資料都會持續演進，因此少數情況下可能出現差異。"

#: formats/gettext.rst:69
msgid ""
"The wrapping width can be configured using the ``po_line_wrap`` parameter, "
"see :ref:`file_format_params`."
msgstr ""
"可以用 ``po_line_wrap`` 引數設定換行寬度，見 :ref:`file_format_params`。"

#: formats/gettext.rst:72
msgid "Generating matching MO files"
msgstr "產生相符的 MO 檔案"

#: formats/gettext.rst:74
msgid ""
"In case MO files are kept in the repository together with PO "
"files, :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.mo` can be used to keep them up-to-date "
"with PO files."
msgstr ""
"如果 MO 與 PO 檔案一同保留在儲存庫中，可以使用 :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.gettext.mo` 讓 MO 檔案與 PO 檔案保持同步。"

