#: formats/markdown.rst:4
msgid "Markdown files"
msgstr "Markdown 檔案"

#: formats/markdown.rst:10
msgid ""
"The translatable content is extracted from the Markdown files and offered "
"for the translation. For Markdown files with JSX syntax, use :ref:`mdx`."
msgstr ""
"從 Markdown 檔案中提取可翻譯內容並供翻譯。對於含 JSX 語法的 Markdown 檔案，使"
"用 :ref:`mdx`。"

#: formats/markdown.rst:13
msgid ""
"Markdown units automatically get the ``md-text``, ``auto-safe-html`` and "
"``strict-same`` flags. This keeps the unsafe HTML check active for plain "
"text, standard HTML, and custom elements while avoiding HTML cleanup on non-"
"HTML angle-bracket syntax such as MDX or JSX-like components. Use the "
"explicit ``safe-html`` flag for strings that are known to contain HTML and "
"should always be sanitized, including SVG or MathML snippets."
msgstr ""
"Markdown 單元會自動取得 ``md-text``、``auto-safe-html`` 及 ``strict-same`` 旗"
"標。這能讓純文字、標準 HTML 及自訂元素繼續接受不安全 HTML 檢查，同時避免清理 "
"MDX 或類 JSX 元件等非 HTML 的尖括號語法。已知含有 HTML 且應一律清理的字串（包"
"括 SVG 或 MathML 片段），請明確加上 ``safe-html`` 旗標。"

#: formats/markdown.rst:45
msgid "`Markdown file`"
msgstr "`Markdown file`"

#: formats/markdown.rst:55
msgid ""
"By default, Weblate treats each occurrence of a string as a separate "
"translation unit to provide line-based context. This can be problematic in "
"Markdown tables, where reordering rows changes the context and can lead to "
"translation loss."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 預設將字串的每次出現視為不同的翻譯單元來提供基於行的情境。在 "
"Markdown 表格中這可能有問題，因為調整行順序會改變情境，導致譯文丟失。"

#: formats/markdown.rst:72
msgid "Translating front matter values"
msgstr "翻譯前置內容值"

#: formats/markdown.rst:74
msgid ""
"By default, YAML front matter is extracted as a single translatable block. "
"Enable :guilabel:`Translate front matter values` in :ref:`component-"
"file_format_params` to parse YAML front matter and translate only scalar "
"string values while preserving keys, structure, comments, and formatting "
"when possible. The same setting is available for :ref:`mdx` files."
msgstr ""
"根據預設，YAML 前置內容會擷取為單一可翻譯區塊。在 :ref:`component-"
"file_format_params` 中啟用 :guilabel:`Translate front matter values`，即可剖"
"析 YAML 前置內容並僅翻譯純量字串值，同時盡可能保留鍵、結構、註解及格"
"式。:ref:`mdx` 檔案也可使用相同設定。"

#: formats/mdx.rst:4
msgid "MDX files"
msgstr "MDX 檔案"

#: formats/mdx.rst:10
msgid ""
"MDX files are Markdown files with JSX syntax. Weblate extracts translatable "
"Markdown text and preserves imports, exports, JSX components, and "
"expressions."
msgstr ""
"MDX 檔案是使用 JSX 語法的 Markdown 檔案。Weblate 會擷取可翻譯的 Markdown 文"
"字，並保留匯入、匯出、JSX 元件及運算式。"

#: formats/mdx.rst:13
msgid ""
"MDX units automatically get the ``md-text``, ``auto-safe-html``, ``strict-"
"same`` and ``safe-mdx`` flags. This keeps the unsafe HTML check active for "
"plain text, standard HTML, and custom elements while avoiding HTML cleanup "
"on MDX and JSX-like syntax. Use the explicit ``safe-html`` flag for strings "
"that are known to contain HTML and should always be sanitized, including SVG "
"or MathML snippets."
msgstr ""
"MDX 單元自動獲得 ``md-text``、``auto-safe-html``、``strict-same`` 和 ``safe-"
"mdx`` 標記。這使不安全 HTML 勾選對純文字、標準 HTML 和自訂元素生效，同時避免"
"對 MDX 或類 JSX 語法的 HTML 清理。對已知包含 HTML 和應始終被淨化的字串使用明"
"確 ``safe-html`` 標記，包括 SVG 或 MathML 片段。"

#: formats/mdx.rst:44
msgid "`MDX file`"
msgstr "`MDX 檔案`"

#: formats/mdx.rst:54
msgid ""
"By default, Weblate treats each occurrence of a string as a separate "
"translation unit to provide line-based context. This can be problematic in "
"MDX tables or repeated component content, where reordering changes the "
"context and can lead to translation loss."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 預設將字串的每次出現視為不同的翻譯單元來提供基於行的情境。在 MDX 表格"
"或重複的元件內容中可能會有問題，因為調整行順序會改變情境，導致譯文丟失。"

