msgstr "Weblate 會從 TBX 檔案載入及儲存說明，並顯示於 :ref:`glossary`。"

#: formats/tbx.rst:25
msgid ""
"Translation explanation is stored as ``<note from=\"translator\"></note>`` "
"tag."
msgstr "翻譯說明儲存於 ``<note from=\"translator\"></note>`` 標籤中。"

#: formats/tbx.rst:26
