#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:2
msgid "Disaster recovery plan"
msgstr "災難復原計畫"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:5 security/incident-response-plan.rst:5
msgid "Scope and objectives"
msgstr "範圍及目標"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:7
msgid ""
"This plan addresses recovery from catastrophic events impacting Weblate "
"service availability, data integrity, or operational continuity."
msgstr ""
"此計畫涵蓋會影響 Weblate 服務可用性、資料完整性或營運持續性的重大災難事件復"
"原。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:11
msgid ""
"The plan is specifically designed for deployments of Weblate by Weblate "
"s.r.o., but it can be applied to other deployments similarly."
msgstr ""
"此計畫專為 Weblate s.r.o. 營運的 Weblate 部署環境設計，但也能以類似方式套用至"
"其他部署環境。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:14
msgid "Definitions"
msgstr "定義"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:16
msgid ""
"**Disaster:** Any unplanned event causing complete or significant loss of "
"service, data, or system functionality. Examples include hardware failure, "
"data corruption, infrastructure outage, or malicious attack."
msgstr ""
"**災難：**\\ 任何導致服務、資料、或系統功能完全或重大喪失的計劃外事件，例如硬"
"體故障、資料損壞、基礎設施中斷，或惡意攻擊。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:17
msgid ""
"**Recovery Point Objective (RPO):** Maximum acceptable data loss interval: "
"**24 hours**."
msgstr "**復原點目標 (RPO)：** 可接受的資料遺失間隔上限為 **24 小時**。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:18
msgid ""
"**Recovery Time Objective (RTO):** Maximum acceptable time to restore full "
"service: **8 hours**."
msgstr "**復原時間目標 (RTO)：** 完整復原服務的可接受時間上限為 **8 小時**。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:21
msgid "Critical components"
msgstr "關鍵元件"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Application Layer:** Weblate Python/Django application, background workers "
"(Celery), and scheduled tasks."
msgstr ""
"**應用程式層：** Weblate Python/Django 應用程式、背景工作程式 (Celery) 及排程"
"工作。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:24
msgid ""
"**Data Layer:** PostgreSQL database, translation repositories (Git), and "
"logs."
msgstr "**資料層：**\\ PostgreSQL 資料庫、翻譯儲存庫 (Git) 和日誌。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:25
msgid ""
"**Infrastructure:** Web server (NGINX/Apache), reverse proxy, storage "
"volumes, SSL/TLS configuration, and optional SIEM logging system."
msgstr ""
"**基礎設施：**\\ Web 伺服器 (NGINX/Apache)、反向代理、儲存磁碟區、SSL/TLS 設"
"定，及選用的 SIEM 日誌系統。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:28
msgid "Backup policy"
msgstr "備份政策"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:30
msgid ""
":ref:`automated-backup` process guarantees that all essential components "
"(database, data, and configuration) are backed up daily. The backups are "
"stored in two geographically different locations. The backup retention "
"policy ensures that recent backups are available daily and keeps six months "
"of backups."
msgstr ""
":ref:`automated-backup` 處理程序可確保所有必要元件（資料庫、資料及設定）每天"
"都會備份。備份會儲存在兩個不同的地理位置。備份保留政策可確保每日備份近期均可"
"使用，並保留 6 個月。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:36
msgid "Recovery Procedures"
msgstr "復原步驟"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:41
msgid "Failure scenario: full host/system loss"
msgstr "故障情境：整台主機／整套系統遺失"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:43
msgid "Provision new host."
msgstr "開通新主機。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:44
msgid "Bootstrap Weblate using provisioning software."
msgstr "使用佈建軟體啟動 Weblate。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:45
#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:53
msgid "Restore Weblate backup following :ref:`restore-borg`."
msgstr "遵循 :ref:`restore-borg` 還原 Weblate 備份。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:46
msgid "Restart Weblate container."
msgstr "重啟 Weblate 容器。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:47
msgid "Verify functionality and perform consistency checks."
msgstr "驗證功能並執行一致性檢查。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:50
msgid "Failure scenario: database corruption or data volume loss"
msgstr "故障情境：資料庫損毀或資料磁碟區遺失"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:52
msgid "Stop Weblate to prevent further write operations."
msgstr "停止 Weblate，以防止進一步的寫入作業。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:54
msgid "Restart services and verify translation and user data consistency."
msgstr "重新啟動服務，並驗證翻譯與使用者資料的一致性。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:57
msgid "Failure scenario: malicious tampering or ransomware"
msgstr "故障情境：惡意竄改或勒索軟體"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:59
msgid "Isolate affected host from the network."
msgstr "將受影響的主機與網路隔離。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:60
msgid "Identify last known-good backup (pre-infection)."
msgstr "找出最近一份已知正常的備份（感染前）。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:61
msgid "Follow steps from :ref:`drp-host` to deploy the system on a new host."
msgstr "依照 :ref:`drp-host` 的步驟，在新主機上部署系統。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:64
msgid "Validation and testing"
msgstr "認證與測試"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:66
msgid "**Backup Verification:** Monthly restore test of Weblate backups."
msgstr "**備份驗證：**\\ Weblate 備份的每月還原測試。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:67
msgid ""
"**Disaster Recovery Drill:** Conduct at least annually, involving full "
"restoration to a staging environment."
msgstr "**災難復原演練：** 至少每年執行一次，包括完整還原至預備環境。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:68
msgid ""
"**Automated Integrity Checks:** BorgBackup ensures integrity of backup "
"archives."
msgstr "**自動完整性檢查：** BorgBackup 可確保備份封存檔的完整性。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:71
msgid "Post-recovery steps"
msgstr "復原後的步驟"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:73
msgid "Confirm all services are operational and accessible."
msgstr "確認所有服務執行正常且可存取。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:74
msgid "Notify users and stakeholders of the recovery status."
msgstr "將復原狀態通知使用者及利害關係人。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:75
msgid "Document timeline, root cause, and lessons learned."
msgstr "記錄事件時序、根本原因及經驗教訓。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:76
msgid "Apply updates or infrastructure changes to prevent recurrence."
msgstr "套用更新或變更基礎架構，以避免再次發生。"

#: security/disaster-recovery-plan.rst:77
msgid ""
"Follow :ref:`vulnerability-disclosure-policy` in case vulnerability was "
"involved."
msgstr "若涉及弱點，請遵循 :ref:`vulnerability-disclosure-policy`。"

#: security/governance.rst:2
msgid "Security governance and assessment status"
msgstr "安全治理與評估狀態"

#: security/governance.rst:4
msgid ""
"This page summarizes where Weblate publishes security governance information "
"and records the current formal assessment status. It is a factual "
"documentation index and does not claim certification, audit completion, or "
"regulatory compliance."
msgstr ""
"本頁摘要說明 Weblate 公開安全治理資訊的位置，並記錄目前的正式評估狀態。這是事"
"實性的說明文件索引，不代表已取得認證、完成稽核或符合法規。"

#: security/governance.rst:9
msgid ""
"For product identity, contact, support, release, and SBOM identity, "
"see :doc:`product-information`."
msgstr ""
"產品辨識資訊、聯絡方式、支援、發行版本及 SBOM 辨識資訊，請參閱 :doc:`product-"
"information`。"

#: security/governance.rst:13
msgid "Governance documentation"
msgstr "治理說明文件"

#: security/governance.rst:15
msgid ""
"Weblate publishes security governance information in these documentation "
"areas:"
msgstr "Weblate 會在下列說明文件區域公開安全治理資訊："

#: security/governance.rst:18
msgid ""
"Contribution rules, code review expectations, and project participation are "
"documented in :doc:`/contributing/index`, :doc:`/contributing/code`, "
"and :doc:`/contributing/code_of_conduct`."
msgstr ""
"貢獻規則、程式碼審查要求及專案參與方式，記載於 :doc:`/contributing/"
"index`、:doc:`/contributing/code` 及 :doc:`/contributing/code_of_conduct`。"

#: security/governance.rst:21
msgid ""
"Release lifecycle, security update coverage, and upgrade support are "
"documented in :doc:`releases`."
msgstr ""
"發行版本生命週期、安全性更新涵蓋範圍及升級支援，記載於 :doc:`releases`。"

#: security/governance.rst:23
msgid ""
"Vulnerability reporting, disclosure handling, and service incident reporting "
"are documented in :doc:`issues`."
msgstr "弱點回報、揭露處理及服務事件回報，記載於 :doc:`issues`。"

#: security/governance.rst:25
msgid ""
"Dependency inventory, vulnerability triage, update automation, and container "
"scanning are documented in :doc:`dependencies`."
msgstr ""
"相依套件清冊、弱點分流處理、更新自動化及容器掃描，記載"
"於 :doc:`dependencies`。"

#: security/governance.rst:27
msgid ""
"Security assumptions and boundaries are documented in :doc:`threat-model`."
msgstr "安全性假設及界線，記載於 :doc:`threat-model`。"

#: security/governance.rst:28
msgid ""
"Release artifact inventory, SBOMs, signatures, attestations, and "
"verification are documented in :doc:`release-artifacts`."
msgstr ""
"發行產物清冊、SBOM、簽章、證明及驗證方式，記載於 :doc:`release-artifacts`。"

#: security/governance.rst:32
msgid "Formal assessment status"
msgstr "正式評估狀態"

#: security/governance.rst:34
msgid ""
"This repository does not currently record a formal third-party security "
"assessment, certification, audit report, penetration-test report, or formal "
"self-assessment for Weblate."
msgstr ""
"此儲存庫目前未記錄 Weblate 的正式第三方安全評估、認證、稽核報告、滲透測試報告"
"或正式自我評估。"

#: security/governance.rst:38
msgid ""
"Automated security checks and compliance tools such as CodeQL, GitHub "
"dependency review, FOSSA, OpenSSF Scorecard, and container vulnerability "
"scans are security evidence and automation signals. They are not formal "
"assessments, certifications, or audit reports."
msgstr ""
"CodeQL、GitHub 相依套件審查、FOSSA、OpenSSF Scorecard 及容器弱點掃描等自動安"
"全檢查與合規工具，屬於安全性證據及自動化訊號，並非正式評估、認證或稽核報告。"

#: security/governance.rst:43
msgid ""
"If Weblate publishes formal assessment evidence in the future, this page and "
"the repository security metadata should be updated with the assessment "
"reference and date."
msgstr ""
"如果 Weblate 日後公開正式評估證據，應在本頁及儲存庫安全性中繼資料中加入評估參"
"考資料與日期。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:2
msgid "Incident response plan for Weblate"
msgstr "Weblate 事件回應計畫"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:7
msgid ""
"This IRP covers incidents impacting the confidentiality, integrity, or "
"availability of Weblate-operated deployments."
msgstr ""
"此事件回應計畫涵蓋會影響 Weblate 營運部署環境之機密性、完整性或可用性的事件。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:12
msgid ""
"This plan is specifically designed for deployments operated by Weblate "
"s.r.o. Other deployments need to adapt provider-specific and organizational "
"steps to their own environment."
msgstr ""
"此計畫專為 Weblate s.r.o. 營運的部署環境設計。其他部署環境需依自身環境調整服"
"務提供者及組織專用步驟。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:17
msgid "Roles and responsibilities"
msgstr "角色和責任"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:19
msgid ""
"**Incident Response Lead (IRL):** Coordinates all phases of the response "
"process."
msgstr "**事件回應負責人 (IRL)：**\\ 協調回應過程的所有階段。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:20
msgid "**System Administrator:** Executes containment and recovery measures."
msgstr "**系統管理員：** 執行圍堵及復原措施。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:21
msgid ""
"**Security Officer:** Evaluates security impact and regulatory consequences."
msgstr "**安全主管：** 評估安全性影響及法規後果。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:22
msgid ""
"**Data Protection Officer (DPO):** Evaluates if personal data (PII) was "
"compromised and manages mandatory GDPR notifications."
msgstr ""
"**資料保護長 (DPO)：** 評估個人資料 (PII) 是否遭到危害，並管理 GDPR 強制通"
"知。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Communications Lead:** Manages notifications to internal stakeholders and "
"external parties if required."
msgstr "**溝通負責人：** 視需要管理對內部利害關係人及外部當事方的通知。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:26
msgid "Communication logistics"
msgstr "溝通工作"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:28
msgid "**Internal Communication:**"
msgstr "**內部通訊：**"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:29
msgid "Primary channel is **Signal** for human-to-human coordination."
msgstr "人員間協調的主要管道為 **Signal**。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:30
msgid "Technical alerts remain outside of Signal to avoid noise."
msgstr "技術警示仍留在 Signal 之外，以避免產生雜訊。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:31
msgid "**External Communication:**"
msgstr "**外部通訊：**"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:32
msgid "**E-mail** is used to reach customers."
msgstr "**電子郵件** 用於聯絡客戶。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:33
msgid ""
"Customer contact lists are maintained in several locations to ensure access "
"during service outages."
msgstr "客戶聯絡清單會維護於數個位置，以確保服務中斷時仍可存取。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:34
msgid "**Public Disclosure:**"
msgstr "**公開披露：**"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:35
msgid ""
"If an incident includes a Weblate product vulnerability, follow the product "
"vulnerability reporting process and :ref:`vulnerability-disclosure-policy` "
"in :doc:`/security/issues`."
msgstr ""
"如果事件包含 Weblate 產品弱點，請依循產品弱點回報處理程序，以及 :doc:`/"
"security/issues` 中的 :ref:`vulnerability-disclosure-policy`。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:40
msgid "Incident categories and severity"
msgstr "事件類別與嚴重程度"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:43
msgid "Incident activation"
msgstr "事件啟動"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:45
msgid ""
"Declare an incident when an event is confirmed or strongly suspected to "
"affect the confidentiality, integrity, or availability of the service beyond "
"routine operational noise."
msgstr ""
"確認或高度懷疑某事件對服務的機密性、完整性或可用性造成超出日常營運雜訊的影響"
"時，即應宣布事件。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:48
msgid ""
"The **Security Officer** declares the incident, assigns the initial "
"severity, and appoints the **Incident Response Lead (IRL)**."
msgstr ""
"**安全主管** 會宣布事件、指定初始嚴重程度，並任命 **事件回應負責人 (IRL)**。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:50
msgid ""
"If the Security Officer is unavailable, any available senior operator may "
"declare the incident and hand over ownership as soon as practical."
msgstr ""
"若安全主管無法處理，任何可聯絡的資深營運人員均可宣布事件，並在可行時盡快移交"
"責任。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:52
msgid ""
"Reclassify the incident if the scope or impact changes during investigation."
msgstr "若事件範圍或影響在調查期間發生變化，請重新分類事件。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:55
msgid "Incident categories"
msgstr "事件類型"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:57
msgid "Category 1 – Unauthorized Access"
msgstr "類別 1 – 未經授權的存取"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:58
msgid "Category 2 – Data Integrity Violation"
msgstr "類別 2 – 資料完整性破壞"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:59
msgid "Category 3 – Service Outage or Degradation"
msgstr "類別 3 – 服務中斷或效能降低"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:60
msgid "Category 4 – Misconfiguration or Deployment Error"
msgstr "類別 4 – 設定錯誤或部署錯誤"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:63
msgid "Severity levels and SLAs"
msgstr "嚴重程度層級與 SLA"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:66
msgid "Severity"
msgstr "嚴重程度"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:66
msgid "Definition"
msgstr "定義"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:66
msgid "Target Acknowledge"
msgstr "目標知悉"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:66
msgid "Target Initial Action"
msgstr "目標初始動作"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:68
msgid "Critical"
msgstr "重大"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:68
msgid ""
"Total outage; Admin compromise; Active data breach; requires immediate "
"containment."
msgstr "全面中斷；管理員帳號遭入侵；持續發生資料外洩；需要立即圍堵。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:68
msgid "< 30 Minutes"
msgstr "< 30 分鐘"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:68
msgid "< 4 Hours"
msgstr "< 4 小時"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:71
msgid "High"
msgstr "高"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:71
msgid "Core feature failure; PII leak of single user."
msgstr "核心功能故障；單一使用者的個人辨識資訊外洩。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:71
msgid "< 2 Hours"
msgstr "< 2 小時"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:71
msgid "12 Hours"
msgstr "12 小時"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:73
msgid "Medium"
msgstr "中"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:73
msgid "Performance degradation; Minor security issue."
msgstr "效能降低；輕微安全性問題。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:73
msgid "1 Business Day"
msgstr "1 個工作天"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:73
msgid "3 Business Days"
msgstr "3 個工作天"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:75
msgid "Low"
msgstr "低"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:75
msgid "UI bugs; Staging issues; Non-security errors."
msgstr "使用者介面錯誤；預備環境問題；非安全性錯誤。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:75
msgid "Best Effort"
msgstr "最佳結果"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:79
msgid "Incident response lifecycle"
msgstr "事件回應生命週期"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:82
msgid "Preparation"
msgstr "準備"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:84
msgid ""
"Ensure regular daily backups of the PostgreSQL database and the data "
"directory using Weblate's built-in backup with rotation, see :ref:`backup`."
msgstr ""
"請使用 Weblate 內建的輪替備份功能，確保每天定期備份 PostgreSQL 資料庫及資料目"
"錄；請參閱 :ref:`backup`。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:85
msgid ""
"Ensure Weblate uses a properly configured reverse proxy (e.g., NGINX) with "
"HTTPS (TLS 1.2+)."
msgstr ""
"確保 Weblate 使用已正確設定 HTTPS (TLS 1.2+) 的反向 Proxy（例如 NGINX）。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:86
msgid "Enable 2FA for all admin-level accounts."
msgstr "為所有管理員層級帳號啟用 2FA。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:87
msgid ""
"Keep the Weblate instance and its dependencies (Python, Django, Celery, "
"database, etc.) up to date."
msgstr ""
"保持 Weblate 執行個體及其相依套件（Python、Django、Celery、資料庫等）為最新"
"版。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:88
msgid ""
"Integrate with SIEM systems using the GELF protocol for audit and "
"application log forwarding."
msgstr "使用 GELF 通訊協定與 SIEM 系統整合，以轉送稽核記錄及應用程式記錄。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:91
msgid "Identification"
msgstr "辨識"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:93
msgid ""
"Monitor system and application logs (``journalctl``, reverse proxy logs, "
"Weblate application and audit logs)."
msgstr ""
"監控系統及應用程式記錄（``journalctl``、反向 Proxy 記錄、Weblate 應用程式記錄"
"及稽核記錄）。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:94
msgid "Analyze login events, webhook executions, and push/pull failures."
msgstr "分析登入事件、Webhook 執行及推送／拉取失敗。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:95
msgid ""
"Configure alerting (via Prometheus, Zabbix, or SIEM) for multiple login "
"failures, unexpected restarts, or irregular VCS actions."
msgstr ""
"針對多次登入失敗、非預期重新啟動或異常 VCS 動作設定警示（透過 Prometheus、"
"Zabbix 或 SIEM）。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:98
msgid "Containment"
msgstr "抑制"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:100
msgid ""
"Create an incident record with a case ID and record timeline updates as "
"actions are taken."
msgstr "建立含有案件 ID 的事件記錄，並在採取動作時記下事件時序更新。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:102
msgid ""
"Coordinate human response in **Signal** and keep technical alerting in the "
"existing monitoring systems."
msgstr "在 **Signal** 中協調人員回應，並將技術警示保留於現有監控系統。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:104
msgid ""
"For Category 1 or 2 incidents, create a manual **Hetzner Cloud Snapshot** "
"before taking disruptive action when it is safe to do so."
msgstr ""
"對於類別 1 或 2 的事件，若情況安全，請先手動建立 **Hetzner Cloud Snapshot**，"
"再採取可能造成中斷的動作。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:107
msgid "Name format: ``IRP-[CaseID]-[YYYYMMDD]-Evidence``."
msgstr "名稱格式： ``IRP-[CaseID]-[YYYYMMDD]-Evidence``。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:108
msgid ""
"These are separate from standard rotating backups and must be preserved for "
"analysis."
msgstr "這些快照與標準輪替備份分開，必須保留以供分析。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:111
msgid ""
"Isolate the affected host or service as needed (for example by firewall "
"rules or service isolation)."
msgstr "視需要隔離受影響的主機或服務（例如透過防火牆規則或服務隔離）。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:113
msgid ""
"Disable external integrations (Git/webhooks) if they are part of the attack "
"vector."
msgstr "若外部整合 (Git/Webhook) 屬於攻擊途徑的一部分，請將其停用。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:115
msgid "Suspend affected user accounts immediately."
msgstr "立即凍結受影響的使用者帳號。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:116
msgid ""
"Revoke or rotate affected administrative, API, VCS, and webhook credentials "
"as applicable."
msgstr "視情況撤銷或輪替受影響的管理員、API、VCS 及 Webhook 認證資訊。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:118
msgid ""
"Preserve relevant evidence, including system logs, reverse proxy logs, "
"Weblate application and audit logs, affected configuration state, and the "
"list of impacted credentials or integrations."
msgstr ""
"保留相關證據，包括系統記錄、反向 Proxy 記錄、Weblate 應用程式與稽核記錄、受影"
"響的設定狀態，以及受影響認證資訊或整合的清單。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:123
msgid "Eradication"
msgstr "根除"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:125
msgid "Remove any unauthorized code or data."
msgstr "刪除任何未經授權的程式碼或資料。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:126
msgid "Patch known vulnerabilities by upgrading Weblate or server components."
msgstr "升級 Weblate 或伺服器元件，以修補已知弱點。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:127
msgid ""
"Validate binary and repository integrity using SHA-256 checksums or Git logs."
msgstr "使用 SHA-256 檢查碼或 Git 記錄，驗證二進位檔案及儲存庫的完整性。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:130
msgid "Recovery"
msgstr "復原"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:132
msgid ""
"Restore affected services or data from the latest known-good Weblate backups."
msgstr "從最近一份已知正常的 Weblate 備份還原受影響的服務或資料。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:133
msgid ""
"**PII Assessment:** DPO determines if the breach requires a 72-hour GDPR "
"notification."
msgstr "**PII 評估：** DPO 會判斷資料外洩是否需要在 72 小時內發出 GDPR 通知。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:134
msgid "Reintroduce services in a phased approach."
msgstr "分階段重新啟用服務。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:135
msgid ""
"Confirm the root cause has been removed or a compensating control is in "
"place before restoring normal traffic."
msgstr "還原正常流量前，請確認已排除根本原因，或已採取補償性控制措施。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:137
msgid ""
"Rotate affected credentials and verify integrity of the restored system, "
"repositories, and configuration."
msgstr "輪換受影響的憑證並驗證已還原系統、儲存庫和設定的完整性。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:139
msgid "The Security Officer and IRL approve returning to normal operations."
msgstr "安全主管及 IRL 會核准回復正常營運。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:140
msgid ""
"Monitor logs and system behavior continuously for at least 72 hours post-"
"recovery."
msgstr "復原後至少 72 小時持續監控日誌和系統行為。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:143
msgid "Post-incident review"
msgstr "事件後審查"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:145
msgid ""
"**Timeline:** Hold a review meeting within **5 business days** of incident "
"closure."
msgstr "**時程：** 在事件結案後 **5 個工作天** 內召開檢討會議。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:146
msgid "Compile a full incident timeline and actions taken."
msgstr "彙整完整的事件時序及已採取的動作。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:147
msgid ""
"Perform Root Cause Analysis (RCA) and document it within **10 business "
"days**."
msgstr "執行根本原因分析（RCA），並於 **10 個工作天** 內完成記錄。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:148
msgid "Update security policies and IRP documentation based on findings."
msgstr "依調查結果更新安全性原則及 IRP 說明文件。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:149
msgid "Review the effectiveness of detection and containment mechanisms."
msgstr "審查偵測及圍堵機制的有效性。"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:150
msgid ""
"Verify whether escalation, alerting, and external communication "
"followed :doc:`/security/issues` as expected."
msgstr "確認呈報、警示及對外溝通是否如預期遵循 :doc:`/security/issues`。"

#: security/index.rst:2
msgid "Security, privacy and compliance"
msgstr "安全 、 隱私與法規遵循"

#: security/index.rst:6
msgid ""
"At Weblate, security maintains an environment that values the privacy of our "
"users."
msgstr "Weblate 致力於維護安全，打造重視使用者隱私的環境。"

#: security/index.rst:8
msgid ""
"Development of Weblate adheres to the `Best Practices of the Open Source "
"Security Foundation <https://www.bestpractices.dev/en/projects/552>`_."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 的開發遵循 `開源安全基金會的最佳實踐 <https://www.bestpractices.dev/"
"en/projects/552>`_。"

#: security/index.rst:12
msgid "Discovered a security issue in Weblate? Please read :ref:`security`."
msgstr "在 Weblate 中發現了安全問題？請閱讀 :ref:`security`。"

#: security/index.rst:15
msgid "Security updates and releases"
msgstr "安全更新和釋出"

#: security/index.rst:17
msgid ""
"Only the latest Weblate release is guaranteed to receive security updates. "
"Learn more about :doc:`Weblate releases and supported versions <releases>`."
msgstr ""
"只有最新的 Weblate 發行版本保證能取得安全性更新。深入瞭解 :doc:`Weblate 發行"
"版本與支援版本 <releases>`。"

#: security/index.rst:20
msgid ""
"Release artifacts can be checked using published signatures, attestations, "
"and SBOMs. See :doc:`release-artifacts`."
msgstr ""
"可使用已公開的簽章、證明及 SBOM 檢查發行產物。請參閱 :doc:`release-"
"artifacts`。"

#: security/index.rst:24
msgid "Security policies"
msgstr "安全政策"

#: security/index.rst:26
msgid ""
":doc:`product-information` - product identity, contact, support, release, "
"and SBOM metadata."
msgstr ""
":doc:`product-information` — 產品辨識資訊、聯絡方式、支援、發行版本及 SBOM 中"
"繼資料。"

#: security/index.rst:28
msgid ""
":doc:`governance` - security governance documentation and assessment status."
msgstr ":doc:`governance` — 安全治理說明文件及評估狀態。"

#: security/index.rst:29
msgid ""
":doc:`releases` - release cycle, security update coverage, and upgrade "
"support."
msgstr ":doc:`releases` — 發行週期、安全性更新涵蓋範圍及升級支援。"

#: security/index.rst:31
msgid ""
":doc:`release-artifacts` - release artifact inventory, SBOMs, signatures, "
"attestations, and verification."
msgstr ":doc:`release-artifacts` — 發行產物清冊、SBOM、簽章、證明及驗證。"

#: security/index.rst:33
msgid ""
":doc:`dependencies` - dependency inventory, vulnerability triage, update "
"automation, and container scanning."
msgstr ""
":doc:`dependencies` — 相依套件清冊、弱點分流處理、更新自動化及容器掃描。"

#: security/index.rst:35
msgid ":doc:`issues` - vulnerability reporting and disclosure."
msgstr ":doc:`issues` — 弱點回報及揭露。"

#: security/index.rst:42
msgid "Compliance"
msgstr "法規遵循"

#: security/index.rst:52
msgid "Terms of service and privacy policy"
msgstr "服務條款與隱私政策"

#: security/index.rst:58
msgid "Guidelines"
msgstr "指導原則"

#: security/issues.rst:2
msgid "Vulnerability and incident handling"
msgstr "漏洞與事件處理"

#: security/issues.rst:7
msgid "Product vulnerability reports"
msgstr "產品漏洞報告"

#: security/issues.rst:11
msgid ""
"Please read :ref:`ai-issues` in case you have used AI to discover a security "
"issue in Weblate."
msgstr "如果您曾使用 AI 發現 Weblate 的安全問題，請閱讀 :ref:`ai-issues`。"

#: security/issues.rst:13
msgid ""
"Weblate’s development team is strongly committed to responsible reporting "
"and disclosure of security-related issues. We have adopted and follow "
"policies that are geared toward delivering timely security updates to "
"Weblate."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 開發團隊堅定致力於以負責任的方式回報及揭露安全性相關問題。我們採用並"
"遵循旨在及時提供 Weblate 安全性更新的原則。"

#: security/issues.rst:17
msgid ""
"Product vulnerability reports cover security issues in Weblate source code, "
"release artifacts, and documented Weblate security properties. They do not "
"replace operational incident response for a particular deployment."
msgstr ""
"產品弱點回報涵蓋 Weblate 原始碼、發行產物及已記載的 Weblate 安全性特性中所發"
"生的安全性問題，無法取代特定部署環境的營運事件回應。"

#: security/issues.rst:21
msgid ""
"Most normal bugs in Weblate are reported to our public `GitHub issues "
"tracker <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/issues>`_, but due to the "
"sensitive nature of security issues, we ask them not to be publicly reported "
"in this fashion."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 的一般錯誤大多會回報至公開的 `GitHub 問題追蹤器 <https://github.com/"
"WeblateOrg/weblate/issues>`_；但由於安全性問題十分敏感，請勿以這種方式公開回"
"報。"

#: security/issues.rst:26
msgid ""
"Instead, if you believe you’ve found something in Weblate that has security "
"implications, please submit a description of the issue to "
"security@weblate.org, `GitHub <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/"
"security/advisories/new>`_, or using `HackerOne <https://hackerone.com/"
"weblate>`_."
msgstr ""
"如果您認為在 Weblate 中發現可能影響安全性的問題，請將問題說明寄至 "
"security@weblate.org、使用 `GitHub <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/"
"security/advisories/new>`_，或透過 `HackerOne <https://hackerone.com/"
"weblate>`_ 提交。"

#: security/issues.rst:31
msgid ""
"Self-hosted operators should use this process when they believe an incident "
"in their own deployment is caused by a Weblate product vulnerability. Local "
"containment, recovery, customer notification, provider escalation, and other "
"deployment-specific incident response remain the operator's responsibility."
msgstr ""
"自行託管環境的營運者若認為其部署環境中的事件是由 Weblate 產品弱點所致，應採用"
"此處理程序。部署環境的圍堵、復原、客戶通知、提供者呈報及其他部署環境專用的事"
"件回應，仍由營運者負責。"

#: security/issues.rst:36
msgid ""
"A member of the security team will respond to you within 48 hours, and "
"depending on what action is taken, you may get more follow-up emails."
msgstr ""
"安全團隊成員會在 48 小時內回覆您；視採取的處理方式而定，您可能會收到更多後續"
"電子郵件。"

#: security/issues.rst:41
msgid "**Sending encrypted reports**"
msgstr "**傳送加密的報告**"

#: security/issues.rst:43
msgid ""
"If you want to send an encrypted email (*optional*), please use the public "
"key for security@weblate.org with ID ``8EA7 6E43 0976 3323 C2E3 D5A0 C472 "
"9F23 8A80 EA93``."
msgstr ""
"如果想傳送加密電子郵件（*選用*），請使用 security@weblate.org 的公開金鑰，ID "
"為 ``8EA7 6E43 0976 3323 C2E3 D5A0 C472 9F23 8A80 EA93``."

#: security/issues.rst:46
msgid ""
"This public key is available on the most commonly used key servers, using "
"WKD or `directly from weblate.org <https://weblate.org/.well-known/"
"openpgpkey/hu/t5s8ztdbon8yzntexy6oz5y48etqsnbb?l=security>`_."
msgstr ""
"這把公開金鑰可透過常用金鑰伺服器、WKD 或 `直接從 weblate.org <https://"
"weblate.org/.well-known/openpgpkey/hu/t5s8ztdbon8yzntexy6oz5y48etqsnbb?"
"l=security>`_ 取得。"

#: security/issues.rst:52
msgid ""
"Weblate depends on third-party components for many things. In case you find "
"a vulnerability affecting one of those components in general, please report "
"it directly to the respective project."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 在很多事情上依賴於第三方元件。如果您發現一個影響這些元件的漏洞，請直"
"接報告給相應的專案。"

#: security/issues.rst:56
msgid "Some of these are:"
msgstr "其中包括："

#: security/issues.rst:58
msgid ":doc:`Django <django:internals/security>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Django <django:internals/security>`"

#: security/issues.rst:59
msgid ""
"`Django REST framework <https://www.django-rest-framework.org/#security>`_"
msgstr "`Django REST 框架 <https://www.django-rest-framework.org/#security>`_"

#: security/issues.rst:60
msgid "`Python Social Auth <https://github.com/python-social-auth>`_"
msgstr "`Python Social Auth <https://github.com/python-social-auth>`_"

#: security/issues.rst:67
msgid "Weblate-operated service incidents"
msgstr "Weblate 營運服務的事件"

#: security/issues.rst:69
msgid ""
"Operational incidents affecting Hosted Weblate, Dedicated Weblate, or other "
"deployments operated by Weblate s.r.o. are handled using :doc:`/security/"
"incident-response-plan`."
msgstr ""
"影響 Hosted Weblate、Dedicated Weblate 或其他由 Weblate s.r.o. 營運之部署環境"
"的營運事件，會依 :doc:`/security/incident-response-plan` 處理。"

#: security/issues.rst:73
msgid ""
"When such an incident also involves a Weblate product vulnerability, the "
"vulnerability report and public advisory follow the product vulnerability "
"reporting process and :ref:`vulnerability-disclosure-policy` on this page."
msgstr ""
"若這類事件同時涉及 Weblate 產品弱點，弱點回報及公開公告會依本頁的產品弱點回報"
"處理程序與 :ref:`vulnerability-disclosure-policy` 處理。"

#: security/issues.rst:78
msgid "Self-hosted deployment incidents"
msgstr "自託管部署事件"

#: security/issues.rst:80
msgid ""
"Operators of self-hosted Weblate deployments are responsible for their local "
"incident response process, including containment, recovery, notification, "
"and provider-specific escalation. The Weblate-operated :doc:`/security/"
"incident-response-plan` can be used as a reference, but it is not a "
"maintained incident response plan for third-party deployments."
msgstr ""
"自行託管 Weblate 部署環境的營運者，須負責其部署環境的事件回應處理程序，包括圍"
"堵、復原、通知及提供者專用的呈報。由 Weblate 營運的 :doc:`/security/incident-"
"response-plan` 可作為參考，但不是針對第三方部署環境維護的事件回應計畫。"

#: security/issues.rst:86
msgid ""
"If a self-hosted incident appears to be caused by a Weblate product "
"vulnerability, report it using the product vulnerability reporting process "
"above."
msgstr ""
"如果自行託管環境中的事件疑似由 Weblate 產品弱點所致，請使用上述產品弱點回報處"
"理程序加以回報。"

#: security/issues.rst:93
msgid "Vulnerability disclosure policy"
msgstr "漏洞揭露政策"

#: security/issues.rst:95
msgid ""
"For Weblate product vulnerabilities, within 30 days following a release "
"containing a vulnerability fix, a security advisory is published at https://"
"github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/security/advisories. The advisory is available "
"immediately with a release when possible."
msgstr ""
"對於 Weblate 產品弱點，含有弱點修正的版本發行後 30 天內，會在 https://"
"github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/security/advisories 發佈安全性公告。如有可能，"
"公告會在版本發行後立即提供。"

#: security/issues.rst:100
msgid ""
"Any actively exploited Weblate vulnerability, or any severe incident "
"affecting Weblate-operated services, is notified to CSIRT within 24 hours, "
"general info is provided to CSIRT within 72 hours, and a full report is "
"provided within 14 days."
msgstr ""
"任何遭到積極利用的 Weblate 弱點，或影響 Weblate 營運服務的嚴重事件，都會在 "
"24 小時內通知 CSIRT、在 72 小時內向 CSIRT 提供一般資訊，並在 14 天內提供完整"
"報告。"

#: security/issues.rst:105
msgid ""
"All users of Hosted or Dedicated Weblate impacted by a severe incident or an "
"actively exploited vulnerability are notified within 7 days."
msgstr ""
"所有受活躍利用漏洞或嚴重事件影響的託管或專用 Weblate 的使用者會在 7 天內收到"
"通知。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:2
msgid "Localization Threat Model"
msgstr "在地化威脅模型"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:4
msgid ""
"Outsourcing or crowdsourcing translation tasks to third parties introduces "
"additional security and privacy risks. Unlike internal development teams, "
"translators may have limited trust relationships with the organization and "
"may operate from various jurisdictions. This model identifies and classifies "
"threats associated with external translation contributors."
msgstr ""
"將翻譯工作外包或眾包給第三方，會引入額外的安全性及隱私權風險。譯者與組織的信"
"任關係可能不如內部開發團隊緊密，也可能在不同司法管轄區工作。本模型會辨識並分"
"類與外部翻譯貢獻者相關的威脅。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:7
msgid "Key Assumptions"
msgstr "關鍵假設"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:8
msgid ""
"Translators may be contractors, volunteers, or agencies with varying levels "
"of vetting."
msgstr "譯者可能是承包人員、志工或機構，且審查程度各不相同。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:9
msgid "Translators require access to Weblate."
msgstr "譯者需要 Weblate 存取權限。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:10
msgid ""
"Translation strings may contain sensitive content such as unreleased "
"features, legal terms, or security messages."
msgstr "翻譯字串可能包含未釋出的功能、法律條款或安全資訊等敏感內容。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:11
msgid ""
"The organization has limited control over translators' local environments."
msgstr "組織對譯者的本機環境控制有限。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:14
msgid "Threat Categories (STRIDE)"
msgstr "威脅類別 (STRIDE)"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:17
msgid "1. Spoofing"
msgstr "1. 欺騙"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:19
msgid "**S1. Fake translator accounts impersonating legitimate contributors.**"
msgstr "**S1. 偽裝成真實貢獻者的虛假譯者帳號。**"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:21
msgid ""
"Risk: Unauthorized access to projects or injection of malicious strings."
msgstr "風險：未經授權存取專案，或插入惡意字串。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:22 security/localization-threat.rst:34
#: security/localization-threat.rst:43 security/localization-threat.rst:54
#: security/localization-threat.rst:65 security/localization-threat.rst:74
#: security/localization-threat.rst:85 security/localization-threat.rst:96
msgid "Mitigations:"
msgstr "緩解措施："

#: security/localization-threat.rst:24
msgid "Enforce strong authentication (2FA); see :ref:`project-enforced_2fa`."
msgstr "強制採用高強度身分驗證 (2FA)；請參閱 :ref:`project-enforced_2fa`。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:25
msgid "Verify identities of contracted translators."
msgstr "驗證簽約譯者的身分。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:26
msgid "Use role-based access to limit project scope; see :ref:`acl`."
msgstr "使用基於角色的存取控制來限制專案範圍；請參閱 :ref:`acl`。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:29
msgid "2. Tampering"
msgstr "2. 竄改"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:31
msgid "**T1. Malicious translations embedding harmful payloads.**"
msgstr "**T1. 內嵌有害承載內容的惡意譯文。**"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:33
msgid ""
"Risk: Injection of JavaScript, HTML, or format-string attacks if "
"translations are not properly escaped."
msgstr "風險：若翻譯未正確逸出，可能遭到 JavaScript、HTML 或格式字串插入攻擊。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:36
msgid ""
"Apply strict input validation in Weblate. Enforcing quality checks "
"like :ref:`check-safe-html` might help. See :ref:`checks` "
"and :ref:`component-enforced_checks`."
msgstr ""
"在 Weblate 中套用嚴格的輸入驗證。強制執行 :ref:`check-safe-html` 等品質檢查可"
"能有所幫助。請參閱 :ref:`checks` 及 :ref:`component-enforced_checks`。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:37
msgid "Use automated security scanning for translation files in your CI."
msgstr "在 CI 中使用自動化的翻譯檔案安全掃描。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:38
msgid ""
"Limit usage of dangerous markup from translation files. Depending on the "
"used localization framework, this might be implicit, opt-in, or require a "
"third-party library."
msgstr ""
"限制翻譯檔案使用危險標記。依所用在地化框架而定，這可能是內建行為、需選擇啟"
"用，或需要第三方程式庫。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:40
msgid "**T2. Insertion of misleading translations.**"
msgstr "**T2. 插入誤導性譯文。**"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:42
msgid ""
"Risk: Users misled about application behavior (e.g., consent dialogs "
"mistranslated)."
msgstr "風險：使用者可能誤解應用程式行為（例如同意對話方塊翻譯錯誤）。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:45 security/localization-threat.rst:123
msgid ""
"Perform peer review of critical strings; see :ref:`peer-review` "
"or :ref:`reviews`."
msgstr "對重要字串進行同儕審閱；請參閱 :ref:`peer-review` 或 :ref:`reviews`。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:46
msgid "Maintain style guides and :ref:`glossary` to prevent manipulation."
msgstr "維護風格指南及 :ref:`glossary`，以防止操弄。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:49
msgid "3. Repudiation"
msgstr "3. 否認"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:51
msgid "**R1. Disputes over malicious or poor-quality translations.**"
msgstr "**R1. 惡意或低品質譯文的爭論。**"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:53
msgid "Risk: Translators deny responsibility for injected issues."
msgstr "風險：譯者否認應對所插入的問題負責。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:56
msgid "All changes in Weblate are logged."
msgstr "Weblate 中的所有變更都有記錄。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:57
msgid "Use Weblate with version control for immutable history."
msgstr "搭配版本控制使用 Weblate，以保留不可變更的歷程記錄。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:60
msgid "4. Information Disclosure"
msgstr "4. 資訊披露"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:62
msgid "**I1. Leakage of unreleased product details.**"
msgstr "**I1. 洩露未釋出產品的細節。**"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:64
msgid ""
"Risk: Translators gain early access to unreleased features or confidential "
"terminology."
msgstr "風險：譯者獲得未釋出功能或機密術語的提早存取權。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:67
msgid "Segment projects to limit access to sensitive strings."
msgstr "分割專案，以限制敏感字串的存取權。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:68
msgid "Apply non-disclosure agreements with external agencies."
msgstr "與外部機構簽訂保密協議。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:69
msgid "Delay translation of highly confidential strings until public release."
msgstr "延後高度機密字串的翻譯至公開發佈為止。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:71
msgid "**I2. Exposure of personal data within strings.**"
msgstr "**I2. 暴露字串內個人資料。**"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:73
msgid "Risk: Translators might access or misuse embedded user data."
msgstr "風險：譯者可能存取或濫用內嵌的使用者資料。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:76
msgid "Avoid exposing real user data in source strings."
msgstr "避免在來源字串中曝露真實使用者資料。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:77
msgid "Use placeholders for sensitive fields."
msgstr "敏感欄位請使用預留位置。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:80
msgid "5. Denial of Service"
msgstr "5. 阻斷服務"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:82
msgid "**D1. Bulk submission of junk translations.**"
msgstr "**D1. 批次提交垃圾譯文。**"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:84
msgid "Risk: Review queues overwhelmed; release timelines disrupted."
msgstr "風險：審閱佇列不堪負荷；發行時程遭到干擾。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:87
msgid ""
"Choose an appropriate workflow to match your team capacity. :ref:`workflow-"
"customization` can allow you to tweak this on a language basis."
msgstr ""
"選取符合團隊處理量的適當工作流程。:ref:`workflow-customization` 可讓您依語言"
"進行調整。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:88
msgid "Configure automated translation quality checks; see :ref:`checks`."
msgstr "設定自動化譯文品質檢查；見 :ref:`checks`。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:91
msgid "6. Elevation of Privilege"
msgstr "6. 權限提升"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:93
msgid ""
"**E1. The translator gains unauthorized project-wide or administrative "
"rights.**"
msgstr "**E1. 譯者獲得未經授權的專案層級權限或管理權限。**"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:95
msgid "Risk: Escalation leading to tampering or data exposure."
msgstr "風險：權限提升導致竄改或資料暴露。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:98
msgid "Apply the principle of least privilege."
msgstr "採用最小權限原則。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:99
msgid "Regularly review access rights and group memberships."
msgstr "定期審閱存取權及群組成員資格。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:102
msgid "Asset Inventory"
msgstr "資產清冊"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:104
msgid ""
"**Source Strings:** May contain unreleased product features or legal text."
msgstr "**來源字串：**\\ 可能包含未釋出的產品功能或法律文字。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:105
msgid "**Translated Strings:** Output presented directly to end users."
msgstr "**已翻譯字串：**\\ 輸出直接呈現給終端使用者。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:106
msgid ""
"**User Data Placeholders:** Names, emails, or IDs referenced in strings."
msgstr "**使用者資料預留位置：** 字串中參照的姓名、電子郵件或 ID。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:107
msgid "**Access Credentials:** Accounts for translators, agencies, or bots."
msgstr "**存取憑證：**\\ 譯者、機構或機器人的帳號。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:110
msgid "Trust Boundaries"
msgstr "信任邊界"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:112
msgid ""
"**Organization ↔ Translators:** Authentication and role-based access must be "
"enforced."
msgstr "**組織 ↔ 譯者：**\\ 必須強制身分驗證和基於角色的存取。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:113
msgid ""
"**Translation Platform ↔ Source Control:** Synchronization requires secured "
"tokens/keys."
msgstr "**翻譯平台 ↔ 版本控制：** 同步需要安全的權杖／金鑰。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:114
msgid ""
"**Translators ↔ Translation Platform:** All input must be sanitized before "
"integration into builds."
msgstr "**譯者 ↔ 翻譯平台：** 所有輸入都必須先清理，才能整合至建置版本中。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:115
msgid ""
"**Platform ↔ End Users:** Translations must be validated to prevent code "
"injection."
msgstr "**平台 ↔ 終端使用者：** 必須驗證翻譯，以防止程式碼插入。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:118
msgid "Mitigation Summary"
msgstr "緩解摘要"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:120
msgid ""
"Enforce 2FA and RBAC for translator accounts; see :ref:`project-"
"enforced_2fa`."
msgstr "對譯者帳號強制執行 2FA 和 RBAC；見 :ref:`project-enforced_2fa`。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:121
msgid ""
"Require non-disclosure agreements or contracts for professional translators."
msgstr "要求專業譯者簽訂保密協議或合約。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:122
msgid ""
"Use automated quality/security scanning for translations; see :ref:`checks`."
msgstr "為翻譯使用自動化品質/安全掃描；請參閱 :ref:`checks`。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:124
msgid ""
"Limit project visibility to reduce exposure of sensitive content; "
"see :ref:`acl`."
msgstr "限制專案可見度，以降低敏感內容暴露的風險；請參閱 :ref:`acl`。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:125
msgid ""
"Regularly patch and harden your Weblate server. You might also "
"consider :doc:`/admin/support`."
msgstr ""
"定期修補與強化您的 Weblate 伺服器。您可能也需要考慮 :doc:`/admin/support`。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:126
msgid ""
"Retain immutable version history for all translation changes in the version "
"control system."
msgstr "保留版本控制系統中所有翻譯變更的不可變版本歷史記錄。"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:129
msgid "Conclusion"
msgstr "結論"

#: security/localization-threat.rst:131
msgid ""
"Third-party translators introduce unique risks compared to internal "
"contributors. With proper technical, organizational, and contractual "
"controls, organizations can mitigate these risks and safely integrate "
"external translation services while maintaining product integrity and "
"compliance."
msgstr ""
"相較於內部貢獻者，第三方譯者會引入特有風險。透過適當的技術、組織及合約控制措"
"施，組織可以降低這些風險，並安全地整合外部翻譯服務，同時維護產品完整性及法規"
"遵循。"

#: security/passwords.rst:2
msgid "Password security"
msgstr "密碼安全"

#: security/passwords.rst:5
msgid "How Weblate stores passwords"
msgstr "Weblate 如何儲存密碼"

#: security/passwords.rst:7
msgid ""
"Weblate uses a Django implementation to store hashed passwords; "
"see :ref:`django:auth_password_storage`."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 使用 Django 的實作來儲存雜湊處理過的密碼；請參"
"閱 :ref:`django:auth_password_storage`。"

#: security/passwords.rst:9
msgid ""
"The recommended Weblate configuration uses Argon2 with time_cost = 2, "
"memory_cost = 102400, and parallelism = 8."
msgstr ""
"建議的 Weblate 設定使用 Argon2 搭配 time_cost = 2 、 memory_cost = 102400 與 "
"parallelism = 8。"

#: security/passwords.rst:13
msgid ""
"The password hashing can be customized "
"using :setting:`django:PASSWORD_HASHERS`."
msgstr "密碼雜湊可以使用 :setting:`django:PASSWORD_HASHERS` 進行自訂。"

#: security/passwords.rst:16
msgid "Password validation"
msgstr "密碼驗證"

#: security/passwords.rst:18
msgid ""
"When a user is configuring a password, it is validated to reduce the risk of "
"using weak passwords."
msgstr "使用者設定密碼時，系統會進行驗證，以降低使用弱密碼的風險。"

#: security/passwords.rst:20
msgid "The recommended Weblate configuration verifies:"
msgstr "建議的 Weblate 設定驗證："

#: security/passwords.rst:22
msgid ""
"The password has to be at least 10 characters long, and at most 72 "
"characters long."
msgstr "密碼長度至少 10 個字元，最長 72 個字元。"

#: security/passwords.rst:23
msgid "Password similar to username and other attributes is rejected."
msgstr "與使用者名稱或其他屬性相似的密碼會遭到拒絕。"

#: security/passwords.rst:24
msgid "A common or overly simple password is rejected."
msgstr "拒絕常用或過於簡單的密碼。"

#: security/passwords.rst:25
msgid "Any password user used recently is rejected."
msgstr "使用者近期使用過的密碼都會遭到拒絕。"

#: security/passwords.rst:26
msgid "Password strength is optionally checked using the zxcvbn algorithm."
msgstr "使用 zxcvbn 演算法檢查密碼強度（選用）。"

#: security/passwords.rst:30
msgid ""
"The password validation can be customized "
"using :setting:`django:AUTH_PASSWORD_VALIDATORS`."
msgstr "密碼驗證可以使用 :setting:`django:AUTH_PASSWORD_VALIDATORS` 進行自訂。"

#: security/passwords.rst:33
msgid "Social or third-party authentication"
msgstr "社群登入或第三方身分驗證"

#: security/passwords.rst:35
msgid ""
"Weblate does not store any passwords or enforce any password policy when "
"social or third-party authentication is configured. The passwords are, in "
"such a case, fully managed externally."
msgstr ""
"設定社群登入或第三方身分驗證時，Weblate 不會儲存任何密碼，也不會強制執行任何"
"密碼原則。在這種情況下，密碼完全由外部服務管理。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:2
msgid "Privacy regulations compliance"
msgstr "隱私法規遵循"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:8
msgid ""
"Weblate provides features that help organizations operate within privacy "
"frameworks such as GDPR, DPDPA, PIPL, and others. Hosting, legal basis, "
"retention, notices, and compliance responsibilities remain under the "
"deploying organization's control."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 提供幫助組織在 GDPR、DPDPA、PIPL 及其他隱私框架內運作的特性。託管、法"
"律依據、留存、通知和合規職責仍在部署機構的控制下。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:13
msgid ""
"This document outlines Weblate features that can support compliance with:"
msgstr "本文件概述可支援下列隱私法規架構的 Weblate 特性："

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:15
msgid "EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)"
msgstr "歐盟通用資料保護條例（GDPR）"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:16
msgid "California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)"
msgstr "加利福利亞消費者隱私法案（CCPA）"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:17
msgid "Brazilian Lei Geral de Proteção de Dados (LGPD)"
msgstr "巴西通用資料保護法（LGPD）"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:18
msgid "Swiss Federal Act on Data Protection (nFADP)"
msgstr "瑞士聯邦資料保護法（nFADP）"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:19
msgid ""
"Canadian Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act "
"(PIPEDA)"
msgstr "加拿大個人資訊保護和電子文件法案（PIPEDA）"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:20
msgid "Indian Digital Personal Data Protection Act (DPDPA)"
msgstr "印度數位個人資料保護法案 (DPDPA)"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:21
msgid "China’s Personal Information Protection Law (PIPL)"
msgstr "中華人民共和國個人資訊保護法（PIPL）"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:24
msgid "Privacy principles"
msgstr "隱私指導原則"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:27
msgid "Data minimization"
msgstr "資料最小化"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:29
msgid ""
"Weblate processes account and activity data needed to provide translation "
"workflows, authentication, notifications, access control, and auditability. "
"Depending on enabled features, the following personal data can be stored or "
"processed:"
msgstr ""
"Weblate 會處理提供翻譯工作流程、驗證、通知、存取控制及可稽核性所需的帳號與活"
"動資料。依啟用的功能而定，可能會儲存或處理下列個人資料："

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:34
msgid ""
"Account identifiers such as username, full name, primary e-mail address, "
"verified e-mail addresses, and social-authentication associations."
msgstr ""
"帳號辨識資訊，例如使用者名稱、全名、主要電子郵件地址、已驗證的電子郵件地址及"
"社群登入驗證關聯。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:36
msgid ""
"Optional profile fields such as public e-mail, website, profile links, "
"location, company, language preferences, and dashboard preferences."
msgstr ""
"選用的個人資料欄位，例如公開電子郵件地址、網站、個人資料連結、所在地、公司、"
"語言偏好及控制台偏好設定。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:38
msgid ""
"Translation activity, suggestions, comments, watched projects, notification "
"settings, and contribution statistics."
msgstr "翻譯活動、建議、留言、關注的專案、通知設定及貢獻統計資料。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:40
msgid ""
"Operational records such as audit-log entries, IP addresses, user agents, "
"timestamps, and security-related events."
msgstr ""
"營運記錄，例如稽核記錄項目、IP 位址、使用者代理程式、時間戳記及安全性相關事"
"件。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:43
msgid ""
"External analytics, crash reporting, remote logging, and avatar providers "
"are optional integrations controlled by the site operator."
msgstr ""
"外部分析、當機回報、遠端記錄及個人頭像提供者，均為由網站營運者控制的選用整合"
"功能。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:47
msgid "User consent and transparency"
msgstr "使用者同意與透明度"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:49
msgid ""
"Users can review and update their account and profile data in :ref:`user-"
"profile`."
msgstr "使用者可以在 :ref:`user-profile` 中檢閱及更新帳號與個人資料。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:51
msgid ""
"Administrators can publish privacy policy, terms, cookie information, and "
"subcontractor information using :ref:`legal`, or link externally "
"using :setting:`LEGAL_URL` and :setting:`PRIVACY_URL`."
msgstr ""
"管理員可以使用 :ref:`legal` 公開隱私權政策、條款、Cookie 資訊及分包商資訊，或"
"使用 :setting:`LEGAL_URL` 與 :setting:`PRIVACY_URL` 連結至外部文件。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:54
msgid ""
"Terms of service confirmation can be enforced using the legal app, "
"and :setting:`LEGAL_TOS_DATE` can require users to accept updated terms."
msgstr ""
"可以使用 legal 應用程式強制使用者確認服務條款，並可透"
"過 :setting:`LEGAL_TOS_DATE` 要求使用者接受更新後的條款。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:56
msgid ""
"Data processing depends on user interaction and on integrations enabled by "
"the site operator."
msgstr "資料處理方式取決於使用者互動及網站營運者啟用的整合功能。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:60
msgid "Data access and portability"
msgstr "資料存取與可攜性"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:62
msgid ""
"Users can download a JSON export of their user data from "
"the :guilabel:`Account` tab in :ref:`user-profile`; the export format is "
"documented in :ref:`schema-userdata`."
msgstr ""
"使用者可以從 :ref:`user-profile` 的 :guilabel:`帳號` 分頁下載使用者資料的 "
"JSON 匯出檔；匯出格式記載於 :ref:`schema-userdata`。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:65
msgid ""
"Administrators can export active non-bot user data "
"with :wladmin:`dumpuserdata`."
msgstr ""
"管理員可以使用 :wladmin:`dumpuserdata` 匯出作用中且非機器人的使用者資料。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:67
msgid ""
"Project translations and translation files can be exported separately using "
"Weblate's project and file export features."
msgstr "可以使用 Weblate 的專案及檔案匯出功能，分別匯出專案翻譯及翻譯檔案。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:71
msgid "Right to erasure and correction"
msgstr "清除權及更正權"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:73
msgid ""
"Users can correct account and profile information from the profile interface."
msgstr "使用者可以透過個人資料介面更正帳號和個人資料資訊。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:75
msgid ""
"Users can request account removal from the :guilabel:`Account` tab. The "
"removal flow requires confirmation and then deactivates and anonymizes the "
"account."
msgstr ""
"使用者可以從 :guilabel:`Account` 分頁要求移除帳號。移除流程需經過確認，接著會"
"停用帳號並將其匿名化。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:78
msgid ""
"Account removal clears private profile fields, API tokens, social-auth "
"associations, group memberships, notification subscriptions, watched "
"projects, and user translation memory."
msgstr ""
"移除帳號會清除私人個人資料欄位、API 權杖、社群登入驗證關聯、群組成員資格、通"
"知訂閱、關注的專案及使用者翻譯記憶。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:81
msgid ""
"Historical project records can remain associated with an anonymized deleted "
"account where needed to preserve translation history and auditability."
msgstr ""
"為保留翻譯歷程及可稽核性，歷史專案記錄可視需要繼續與已匿名化的刪除帳號關聯。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:85
msgid "Data retention and deletion"
msgstr "資料駐留與刪除"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:87
msgid "Audit-log retention is configured using :setting:`AUDITLOG_EXPIRY`."
msgstr "稽核記錄的保留期間可使用 :setting:`AUDITLOG_EXPIRY` 設定。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:88
msgid ""
"Backups, reverse-proxy logs, mail server logs, and database retention are "
"controlled by the site operator."
msgstr ""
"備份、反向 Proxy 記錄、電子郵件伺服器記錄及資料庫保留政策，均由網站營運者控"
"制。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:90
msgid ""
"Third-party services receive data only when configured or used by the "
"operator, for example external authentication providers, avatar providers, "
"Matomo, Sentry, OpenTelemetry, remote logging, machine translation services, "
"or repository integrations."
msgstr ""
"只有在營運者設定或使用第三方服務時，這些服務才會收到資料，例如外部驗證提供"
"者、個人頭像提供者、Matomo、Sentry、OpenTelemetry、遠端記錄、機器翻譯服務或儲"
"存庫整合。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:96
msgid "Security and confidentiality"
msgstr "安全與保密性"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:98
msgid ""
"Weblate supports HTTPS deployments and secure cookie settings; operators "
"should configure TLS and trusted proxy headers correctly."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 支援 HTTPS 部署與安全 cookie 設定；操作者應正確設定 TLS 與信任的代理"
"標頭。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:100
msgid ""
"Failed sign-ins, permission changes, two-factor changes, account removal "
"requests, and other security events are recorded in the audit log."
msgstr ""
"登入失敗、權限變更、雙因素驗證變更、帳號移除要求及其他安全性事件，都會記錄於"
"稽核記錄中。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:102
msgid "Optional GELF logging can forward logs to systems such as Graylog."
msgstr "選用的 GELF 記錄功能可將記錄轉送至 Graylog 等系統。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:103
msgid ""
"Access control is enforced through users, teams, roles, project access "
"settings, and component permissions."
msgstr "存取控制會透過使用者、團隊、角色、專案存取設定及元件權限強制執行。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:105
msgid ""
"Commit identity privacy can be improved "
"with :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_OPT_IN`, :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_TEMPLATE`, :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_NAME_OPT_IN`, "
"and :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_NAME_TEMPLATE`."
msgstr ""
"提交身分隱私可以透"
"過 :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_OPT_IN` 、 :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_TEMPLATE` 、 :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_NAME_OPT_IN` "
"與 :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_NAME_TEMPLATE` 改進。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:110
msgid ""
"Avatar fetching can be disabled with :setting:`ENABLE_AVATARS`; when "
"enabled, avatars are downloaded and cached server-side as described "
"in :ref:`avatars`."
msgstr ""
"可以使用 :setting:`ENABLE_AVATARS` 停用個人頭像擷取功能；啟用時，會"
"依 :ref:`avatars` 所述，在伺服器端下載及快取個人頭像。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:114
msgid "International transfers"
msgstr "國際傳輸"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:116
msgid "Weblate itself does not require a specific hosting region."
msgstr "Weblate 本身不要求特定的託管區域。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:117
msgid ""
"Hosting location, backups, e-mail delivery, repository hosting, external "
"authentication, analytics, error reporting, and machine translation services "
"determine where data is processed."
msgstr ""
"託管位置、備份、電子郵件傳送、儲存庫託管、外部驗證、分析、錯誤回報及機器翻譯"
"服務，會決定資料的處理位置。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:120
msgid ""
"Organizations can self-host Weblate in the required jurisdiction, or use a "
"dedicated deployment with suitable infrastructure controls."
msgstr ""
"組織可以在所需的司法管轄區內自行託管 Weblate，或使用具備適當基礎架構控制措施"
"的專用部署環境。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:124
msgid "Regulatory mapping"
msgstr "法規對應"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:130
msgid "Framework"
msgstr "框架"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:131
msgid "Supporting Weblate features"
msgstr "支援的 Weblate 功能"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:132
msgid "GDPR (EU)"
msgstr "GDPR (歐盟)"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:133
msgid ""
"Data export, correction, account removal, audit logs, privacy notices, "
"configurable retention, self-hosting"
msgstr ""
"資料匯出、更正、帳號移除、稽核記錄、隱私權聲明、可設定的保留政策、自行託管"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:135
msgid "CCPA (California)"
msgstr "CCPA (加州)"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:136
msgid ""
"Data access, deletion workflow, user control, no built-in sale of personal "
"data"
msgstr "資料存取、刪除工作流程、使用者控制、不內建個人資料銷售功能"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:138
msgid "LGPD (Brazil)"
msgstr "LGPD (巴西)"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:139
msgid ""
"Transparency, access, correction, deletion workflow, operator-defined legal "
"basis"
msgstr "透明度、存取、更正、刪除工作流程、由營運者定義的法律依據"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:141
msgid "nFADP (Switzerland)"
msgstr "nFADP (瑞士)"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:142
msgid ""
"Transparency, purpose limitation by configuration, account controls, "
"auditability"
msgstr "透明度、透過設定限制用途、帳號控制、可稽核性"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:144
msgid "PIPEDA (Canada)"
msgstr "PIPEDA (加拿大)"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:145
msgid "Notice, consent workflow, access, correction, deletion"
msgstr "通知、同意工作流程、存取、修正、刪除"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:146
msgid "DPDPA (India)"
msgstr "DPDPA (印度)"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:147
msgid ""
"Notice, consent workflow, user rights handling, hosting locality controlled "
"by operator"
msgstr "通知、同意工作流程、使用者權利處理、由營運者控制託管位置"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:149
msgid "PIPL (China)"
msgstr "PIPL (中國)"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:150
msgid ""
"Purpose limitation by configuration, data minimization, self-hosted locality "
"controls"
msgstr "透過設定限制用途、資料最小化、自行託管的位置控制"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:154
msgid "Recommendations for compliance"
msgstr "合規建議"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:156
msgid ""
"**Notices and consent:** Provide privacy, cookie, subcontractor, and terms "
"information through :ref:`legal`, and update :setting:`LEGAL_TOS_DATE` when "
"users must accept changed terms."
msgstr ""
"**通知與同意：** 透過 :ref:`legal` 提供隱私權、Cookie、分包商及條款資訊；當使"
"用者必須接受變更後的條款時，請更新 :setting:`LEGAL_TOS_DATE`。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:159
msgid ""
"**Policy links:** Link external privacy and legal documents "
"with :setting:`PRIVACY_URL` and :setting:`LEGAL_URL` when the documents are "
"hosted outside Weblate."
msgstr ""
"**政策連結：** 隱私權及法律文件託管於 Weblate 以外的位置時，請使"
"用 :setting:`PRIVACY_URL` 與 :setting:`LEGAL_URL` 連結至外部文件。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:162
msgid ""
"**Data subject requests:** Define an operational process for user-data "
"export, correction, account removal, backup handling, and historical "
"contribution review."
msgstr ""
"**資料主體要求：** 定義使用者資料匯出、更正、帳號移除、備份處理及歷史貢獻審查"
"的營運處理程序。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:165
msgid ""
"**Retention:** Configure :setting:`AUDITLOG_EXPIRY` and document retention "
"periods for database backups, log aggregation, mail systems, repositories, "
"and external integrations."
msgstr ""
"**保留政策：** 設定 :setting:`AUDITLOG_EXPIRY`，並記載資料庫備份、記錄彙整、"
"電子郵件系統、儲存庫及外部整合功能的保留期間。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:168
msgid ""
"**External services:** Review configured authentication providers, avatar "
"providers, analytics, Sentry, OpenTelemetry, GELF logging, machine "
"translation, e-mail, and repository integrations for transfer and processor "
"obligations."
msgstr ""
"**外部服務：** 檢閱已設定的驗證提供者、個人頭像提供者、分析、Sentry、"
"OpenTelemetry、GELF 記錄、機器翻譯、電子郵件及儲存庫整合，確認其資料傳輸及處"
"理者義務。"

#: security/privacy-compliance.rst:172
msgid ""
"**Locality:** Ensure application hosting, backups, logs, repositories, and "
"external processors are located in permitted jurisdictions."
msgstr ""
"**位置：** 確認應用程式託管、備份、記錄、儲存庫及外部處理者位於允許的司法管轄"
"區內。"

