msgstr "使用 CycloneDX 述詞類型，驗證附加至相同套件產物的 SBOM 證明："

#: security/release-artifacts.rst:187
msgid "SBOM and checksums"
msgstr "SBOM 與驗證和"

#: security/release-artifacts.rst:189
msgid ""
"The release SBOM is a CycloneDX JSON file named ``weblate-<version>-"
"sbom.cdx.json`` and is attached to GitHub release assets. The SBOM "
"attestation is attached to the package archives, not to the SBOM file as a "
"separate release artifact."
msgstr ""
"發行 SBOM 是名為 ``weblate-<version>-sbom.cdx.json`` 的 CycloneDX JSON 檔案，"
"並附加至 GitHub 發行資產。SBOM 證明附加至套件封存檔，而不是將 SBOM 檔案視為獨"
"立發行產物加以附加。"

#: security/release-artifacts.rst:194
msgid ""
"Weblate does not currently publish a separate checksum manifest such "
"as :file:`SHA256SUMS` for release artifacts."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 目前不會另行為發行產物公開 :file:`SHA256SUMS` 之類的檢查碼清單。"

#: security/release-artifacts.rst:198
msgid "Other release channels"
msgstr "其他發行管道"

#: security/release-artifacts.rst:200
msgid ""
"The release artifact inventory does not currently identify signatures, "
"SBOMs, or provenance attestations for Helm charts. The verification "
"instructions in this section apply to the Weblate Python release artifacts "
"published by this repository. Docker image and Weblate Client supply-chain "
"metadata is published by their owning repositories."
msgstr ""
"發行產物清冊目前未列出 Helm 圖表的簽章、SBOM 或來源證明。本節驗證說明適用於此"
"儲存庫發佈的 Weblate Python 發行產物。Docker 映像及 Weblate Client 的供應鏈中"
"繼資料由其所屬儲存庫公開。"

#: security/releases.rst:2
msgid "Releases and supported versions"
msgstr "發行版本與支援的版本"

#: security/releases.rst:4
msgid ""
"This page summarizes the public release, security-update, and upgrade "
"support policies for Weblate. For maintainer release steps, see :doc:`/"
"contributing/release`. For upgrade commands, see :doc:`/admin/upgrade`. For "
"published release artifacts, SBOMs, signatures, and provenance attestations, "
"see :doc:`release-artifacts`."
msgstr ""
"本頁摘要說明 Weblate 的公開發行、安全性更新及升級支援政策。維護者的發行步驟請"
"參閱 :doc:`/contributing/release`。升級指令請參閱 :doc:`/admin/upgrade`。已公"
"開的發行產物、SBOM、簽章及來源證明請參閱 :doc:`release-artifacts`。"

#: security/releases.rst:15
msgid ""
"Weblate uses calendar versioning with monthly releases. The version format "
"is ``<YEAR>.<MONTH>.<PATCH>`` with a numeric, non-zero-padded month. The "
"``<PATCH>`` part is omitted for the first release in a month when it would "
"be ``0``, for example ``2026.5``. Patch releases use the full version "
"number, for example ``2026.5.1``."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 採用每月發行的日曆版本編號。版本格式為 ``<YEAR>.<MONTH>.<PATCH>``，月"
"份以不補零的數字表示。每月第一個版本的 ``<PATCH>`` 若為 ``0``，則會省略，例"
"如 ``2026.5``。修補版本會使用完整版本號，例如 ``2026.5.1``。"

#: security/releases.rst:21
msgid ""
"Monthly releases are usually published at the beginning of the month. Patch "
"releases include bug fixes, security fixes, and dependency updates which "
"should not wait for the next monthly release."
msgstr ""
"每月版本通常會在月初發佈。修補版本包含不應等到下個每月版本才處理的錯誤修正、"
"安全性修正及相依套件更新。"

#: security/releases.rst:25
msgid ""
"The Docker container includes an additional version component to track "
"changes in the container itself, such as dependencies. Fixed Docker image "
"tags include the patch component together with this build component, even "
"when the Weblate version omits a ``0`` patch component. These updates may "
"include security updates."
msgstr ""
"Docker 容器包含額外的版本元件來跟蹤容器本身變化，例如相依套件。即便在 "
"Weblate 版本省略 ``0`` 補丁元件時，固定的 Docker 映像標籤仍同時包含補丁元件和"
"這個建置元件。這些更新可能包含安全更新。"

#: security/releases.rst:34
msgid "Security updates"
msgstr "安全更新"

#: security/releases.rst:36
msgid ""
"Weblate provides security updates to address vulnerabilities and enhance the "
"application's security posture. Only the latest release is guaranteed to "
"receive security updates. Users are encouraged to keep Weblate up to date to "
"benefit from the latest security improvements."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 提供安全更新，以修復漏洞並增強應用程式的安全狀況。只有最新版本才保證"
"收到安全更新。我們鼓勵使用者及時更新 Weblate，以便從最新的安全改進中獲益。"

#: security/releases.rst:41
msgid ""
"Security update coverage and direct upgrade support are separate policies."
msgstr "安全性更新涵蓋範圍及直接升級支援是兩項不同的政策。"

