msgstr "支援。"

#: security/releases.rst:55
msgid "Older releases from the current or previous calendar year"
msgstr "目前或前一個日曆年度的舊版"

#: security/releases.rst:56
msgid ""
"Not guaranteed. Upgrade to the latest release to receive guaranteed security "
"updates."
msgstr "不保證。請升級到最新版本以獲得有保證的安全更新。"

#: security/releases.rst:58 security/releases.rst:62
msgid "Ended when a newer Weblate release was published."
msgstr "較新的 Weblate 版本發佈時即終止。"

#: security/releases.rst:59
msgid "Direct upgrades are supported."
msgstr "支援直接升級。"

#: security/releases.rst:60
