msgstr "透過 :ref:`version-specific-instructions` 所列中間版本進行升級。"

#: security/releases.rst:66
msgid ""
"Direct upgrades are supported from releases in the current or previous "
"calendar year. The first release in a new year drops direct upgrade support "
"for releases from the year before the previous year."
msgstr ""
"支援從目前或前一個日曆年度的發行版本直接升級。新年度的第一個發行版本，會終止"
"對前一年度再前一年度之發行版本的直接升級支援。"

