#: security/us-compliance.rst:2
msgid "US controls compliance"
msgstr "美國出口管制遵守"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:7
msgid "ITAR and other export controls"
msgstr "ITAR 與其他出口管制"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:9
msgid ""
"Weblate can be run within your own datacenter or virtual private cloud. As "
"such, it can be used to store ITAR or other export-controlled information, "
"however, end users are responsible for ensuring such compliance."
msgstr ""
"Weblate可以在您自己的資料中心或虛擬私有雲中執行。因此，它可用於儲存ITAR或其他"
"匯出控制資訊，但是，最終使用者負責確保這種合規性。"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:13
msgid ""
"The Hosted Weblate service has not been audited for compliance with ITAR or "
"other export controls, and does not currently offer the ability to restrict "
"translations access by country."
msgstr ""
"Hosted Weblate 服務尚未遵守符合 ITAR 或其他出口管制，目前尚未提供限制國家/地"
"區存取權限的能力。"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:18
msgid "US encryption controls"
msgstr "美國加密技術管制"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:20
msgid ""
"Weblate does not contain any cryptographic code, but might be subject to "
"export controls as it uses third party components utilizing cryptography for "
"authentication, data-integrity and -confidentiality."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 不包含任何加密程式碼，但由於它使用了第三方元件，而這些元件在身分驗"
"證、資料完整性與機密性方面運用了加密技術，因此可能會受到出口管制的影響。"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:24
msgid ""
"Weblate and all its dependencies have publicly available source code meaning "
"it can usually be exported and reexported without restriction."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 及其所有相依套件的原始碼皆可公開取得，因此通常可以不受限制地匯出及再"
"匯出。"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:28
msgid "Export control classification number"
msgstr "出口控制分類號"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:30
msgid ""
"Weblate has not received a Commodity Classification Automated Tracking "
"System (CCATS) determination from the Bureau of Industry and Security (BIS). "
"Based on the cryptographic functionality used through its dependencies, "
"Weblate should generally be treated as encryption software under ECCN "
"``5D002.c.1``. A mass-market distribution can instead be classified as ECCN "
"``5D992.c`` after the applicable BIS classification or self-classification "
"process."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 尚未取得美國商務部工業暨安全事務局 (BIS) 的商品分類自動追蹤系統 "
"(CCATS) 判定。依其相依套件所使用的密碼學功能，Weblate 通常應視為 ECCN "
"``5D002.c.1`` 所涵蓋的加密軟體。針對大眾市場散布的版本在完成適用的 BIS 分類或"
"自我分類處理程序後，可歸類為 ECCN ``5D992.c``。"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:37
msgid ""
"Weblate source code and release artifacts are publicly available. Under BIS "
"guidance and 15 CFR 742.15(b), publicly available encryption source code "
"classified under ECCN ``5D002`` is not subject to the EAR when the "
"applicable conditions are met, and corresponding object code can also be "
"outside the EAR. Custom builds, hosted services, bundled distributions, and "
"downstream deployments should be evaluated as a whole by the exporting party."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 原始碼及發行產物均可公開取得。依 BIS 指引及 15 CFR 742.15(b)，歸類為 "
"ECCN ``5D002`` 的公開加密原始碼，在符合適用條件時不受 EAR 規範；相關目的碼也"
"可能不受 EAR 規範。自訂建置、託管服務、套裝散布版本及下游部署環境，應由出口方"
"整體評估。"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:46
msgid ""
"`BIS encryption controls <https://www.bis.gov/learn-support/encryption-"
"controls>`_"
msgstr ""
"`BIS 加密控制 <https://www.bis.gov/learn-support/encryption-controls>`_"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:47
msgid ""
"`Encryption items not subject to the EAR <https://www.bis.gov/learn-support/"
"encryption-controls/encryption-items-not-subject-to-ear>`_"
msgstr ""
"`不受 EAR 規範的加密項目 <https://www.bis.gov/learn-support/encryption-"
"controls/encryption-items-not-subject-to-ear>`_"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:49
msgid ""
"`BIS mass market guidance <https://www.bis.gov/learn-support/encryption-"
"controls/mass-market>`_"
msgstr ""
"`BIS 大眾市場指引 <https://www.bis.gov/learn-support/encryption-controls/"
"mass-market>`_"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:51
