"範本更新本身不會更新翻譯 PO 檔案。翻譯檔案需要自動跟隨範本變更時，請保持安"
"裝 :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.msgmerge`。此附加元件的安裝表單可一併安裝該附"
"加元件，但現有附加元件的設定不會再次顯示該安裝選項。"

#: snippets/basics.rst:2
msgid "Weblate basics"
msgstr "Weblate 基礎"

#: snippets/basics.rst:5
msgid "Project and component structure"
msgstr "專案和元件結構"

#: snippets/basics.rst:7
msgid ""
"In Weblate translations are organized into projects and components. Each "
"project can contain number of components and those contain translations into "
"individual languages. The component corresponds to one translatable file "
"(for example :ref:`gettext` or :ref:`aresource`). The projects are there to "
"help you organize component into logical sets (for example to group all "
"translations used within one application)."
msgstr ""
"在 Weblate 中，翻譯被組織成專案和元件。每個專案可以包含多個元件，這些元件又包"
"含各個語言的翻譯。元件對應的是一個可翻譯的檔案（例如 :ref:`gettext` "
"或 :ref:`aresource`）。專案可以幫助您將元件組織成邏輯集合（例如，將一個應用中"
"用到的所有翻譯集合在一起）。"

#: snippets/basics.rst:14
msgid ""
"Additionally, components within projects can be structured using categories. "
"Components can belong to a category, and categories can be nested."
msgstr ""
"此外，也可以使用類別來組織專案內的元件。元件可屬於某個類別，類別也可以巢狀排"
"列。"

#: snippets/basics.rst:17
msgid ""
"Internally, each project has translations to common strings propagated "
"across other components within it by default. This lightens the burden of "
"repetitive and multi version translation. The translation propagation can be "
"disabled per :ref:`component` using :ref:`component-"
"allow_translation_propagation` in case the translations should diverge."
msgstr ""
"預設情況下，每個專案內都有對跨元件傳播的公共字串的翻譯。這減輕了重複和多版本"
"翻譯的負擔。但假如翻譯應有所不同，可以使用 :ref:`component-"
"allow_translation_propagation` 通過 :ref:`component` 停用翻譯傳播。"

#: snippets/basics.rst:24
msgid "Repository integration"
msgstr "儲存庫整合"

#: snippets/basics.rst:26
msgid ""
"Weblate is built to integrate with upstream version control "
"repository, :doc:`/admin/continuous` describes building blocks and how the "
"changes flow between them."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 的設計可與上游版本控制儲存庫整合；:doc:`/admin/continuous` 說明其組成"
"部分，以及變更如何在兩者之間流動。"

#: snippets/basics.rst:32
msgid ":ref:`architecture` describes how Weblate works internally."
msgstr ":ref:`architecture` 描述了 Weblate 內部如何運作。"

#: snippets/basics.rst:35
msgid "User attribution"
msgstr "使用者歸屬"

#: snippets/basics.rst:37
msgid ""
"Weblate keeps the translations properly authored by translators in the "
"version control repository by using name and e-mail. Having a real e-mail "
"attached to the commit follows the distributed version control spirits and "
"allows services like GitHub to associate your contributions done in Weblate "
"with your GitHub profile."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 會使用姓名及電子郵件，讓版本控制儲存庫中的翻譯正確歸屬於譯者。將真實"
"電子郵件附加至提交符合分散式版本控制的精神，也能讓 GitHub 等服務將您在 "
"Weblate 中的貢獻與 GitHub 帳號建立關聯。"

#: snippets/basics.rst:43
msgid ""
"This feature also brings in risk of misusing e-mail published in the version "
"control commits. Moreover, once such a commit is published on public hosting "
"(such as GitHub), there is effectively no way to redact it. Weblate allows "
"choosing a private commit e-mail in :ref:`profile-account` to avoid this."
msgstr ""
"不過，此功能也會帶來風險，公佈在版本控制提交中的電子郵件地址可能會被濫用。此"
"外，一旦此類提交公佈在公開的程式碼託管平台（例如 GitHub），實際上將無法撤回。"
"為了避免這種情況，Weblate 允許在 :ref:`profile-account` 中選擇私密提交電子郵"
"件。"

#: snippets/basics.rst:48
msgid "Therefore, admins should consider this while configuring Weblate:"
msgstr "因此，管理員在設定 Weblate 時應考慮到這一點："

#: snippets/basics.rst:50
msgid ""
"Such a usage of e-mail should be clearly described in service terms in case "
"such document is needed. :ref:`legal` can help with that."
msgstr ""
"若服務需要服務條款文件，應在其中清楚說明電子郵件的這種用途。:ref:`legal` 可協"
"助您完成此設定。"

#: snippets/basics.rst:51
msgid ""
":setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_OPT_IN` can make e-mails private by default."
msgstr ":setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_OPT_IN` 可以讓電子郵件預設隱藏。"

#: snippets/check-flags-autogenerated.rst:2
