"語意。"

#: snippets/checks-autogenerated.rst:2598
msgid ""
"For English source strings, including English variants, the check reports "
"strings using more than 85% of the configured ``max-length``. For other "
"source languages, it reports source strings longer than the configured ``max-"
"length``."
msgstr ""
"對於英文來源字串（包括英文變體），此檢查會回報長度超過設定 ``max-length`` 之 "
"85% 的字串。對其他來源語言，則回報長度超過設定 ``max-length`` 的來源字串。"

#: snippets/checks-autogenerated.rst:2603
