#: snippets/vcs-credentials.rst:1
msgid ""
"The configuration dictionary consists of credentials defined for each API "
"host. The layout is same for almost all version control integrations and is "
"described at :ref:`settings-credentials`."
msgstr ""
"設定字典包含為每個 API 主機定義的認證資訊。幾乎所有版本控制整合的結構都相同，"
"詳見 :ref:`settings-credentials`。"

#: user/checks.rst:4
msgid ""
"The quality checks help catch common translator errors, ensuring the "
"translation is in good shape. The checks can be ignored in case of false "
"positives. For practical translation guidance around placeholders, markup, "
"punctuation, and plural forms, see :ref:`translating-special-text`."
msgstr ""
"品質檢查有助於發現常見的翻譯錯誤，確保翻譯品質良好。如果出現誤報，則可以忽略"
"這些檢查。關於佔位符、標記、標點符號和複數形式的實際翻譯指南，"
"見 :ref:`translating-special-text`。"

#: user/checks.rst:9
msgid ""
"Once submitting a translation with a failing check, this is immediately "
"shown to the user:"
msgstr "提交未通過檢查的翻譯後，將立刻向使用者顯示："

#: user/checks.rst:18
msgid "Automatic fixups"
msgstr "自動修正"

#: user/checks.rst:20
msgid ""
"In addition to :ref:`checks`, Weblate can fix some common errors in "
"translated strings automatically. Use it with caution to not have it add "
"errors."
msgstr ""
"除了 :ref:`checks` 外，Weblate 還可以自動修復翻譯字串中的一些常見錯誤。謹慎使"
"用它，不要使其增加翻譯錯誤。"

#: user/checks.rst:29
msgid "Trailing ellipsis replacer"
msgstr "拖尾省略號替換"

#: user/checks.rst:0
msgid "Class name"
msgstr "類別名稱"

#: user/checks.rst:33
msgid ""
"Replace trailing dots (``...``) with an ellipsis (``…``) to make it "
"consistent with the source string."
msgstr "用省略號 (``…``) 替換拖尾點 (``...``) 來保持和來源字串的一致。"

#: user/checks.rst:37
msgid "Zero-width space removal"
msgstr "零寬度空格移除"

#: user/checks.rst:41
msgid ""
"Zero width space is typically not desired in the translation. This fix will "
"remove it unless it is present in the source string as well."
msgstr ""
"譯文中通常不希望出現零寬空格。此修補會刪除它，除非來源字串中也存在零寬空格。"

#: user/checks.rst:45
msgid "Control characters removal"
msgstr "控制字元移除"

#: user/checks.rst:49
msgid "Removes control characters if the source does not contain any."
msgstr "去掉控制字元，如果來源字串不包含的話。"

#: user/checks.rst:52
msgid "Devanagari danda"
msgstr "天城文短豎線"

#: user/checks.rst:56
msgid ""
"Replaces sentence full stop in Bangla by the Devanagari danda character (``।"
"``)."
msgstr "用天城體 danda 字元 (``।``) 替換孟加拉語中的句號。"

#: user/checks.rst:67
msgid "Ensures French uses correct punctuation spacing."
msgstr "確保法語使用正確的標點符號空格。"

#: user/checks.rst:69
msgid ""
"This fixup can be disabled via ``ignore-punctuation-spacing`` flag (which "
"also disables :ref:`check-punctuation-spacing`)."
msgstr ""
"可透過 ``ignore-punctuation-spacing`` 標記停用此修正（此標記同樣會停"
"用 :ref:`check-punctuation-spacing`）。"

#: user/checks.rst:75
msgid "Unsafe HTML cleanup"
msgstr "不安全 HTML 清理"

#: user/checks.rst:79
msgid "Removes unsafe HTML markup from strings flagged as ``safe-html``."
msgstr "從標記為 ``safe-html`` 的字串中移除不安全的 HTML 標記。"

#: user/checks.rst:86
msgid "Trailing and leading whitespace fixer"
msgstr "修復首尾空白"

#: user/checks.rst:90
msgid ""
"Makes leading and trailing whitespace consistent with the source string. The "
"behavior can be fine-tuned using ``ignore-begin-space`` and ``ignore-end-"
"space`` flags to skip processing parts of the string."
msgstr ""
"使首尾空白和來源字串保持一致。可使用 ``ignore-begin-space`` 和 ``ignore-end-"
"space`` 標記精確調整行為以跳過字串的處理部分。"

#: user/checks.rst:97
msgid "Quality checks"
msgstr "品質檢查"

#: user/checks.rst:99
msgid ""
"Weblate employs a wide range of quality checks on strings. The following "
"section describes them all in further detail. There are also language "
"specific checks. Please file a bug if anything is reported in error."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 對字串進行了廣泛的品質檢查。以下部分將對它們進行更詳細的描述。還有針"
"對特定語言的檢查。如果有錯誤報告，請將缺陷提交。"

#: user/files.rst:2
msgid "Downloading and uploading translations"
msgstr "下載與上傳翻譯"

#: user/files.rst:4
msgid ""
"You can export files from a translation, make changes, and import them "
"again. This allows working offline, and then merging changes back into the "
"existing translation. This works even if it has been changed in the meantime."
msgstr ""
"您可以從轉換中匯出檔案，進行變更，並再次匯入它們。這允許脫機工作，然後將變更"
"合併回現有翻譯。這也有效，即使它在此期間已變更。"

#: user/files.rst:10
msgid ""
"Available options might be limited by :ref:`access control <access-control>` "
"settings."
msgstr "可用選項可能受限於 :ref:`存取控制 <access-control>`。"

#: user/files.rst:16
msgid "Downloading translations"
msgstr "下載翻譯"

#: user/files.rst:18
msgid ""
"From the project or component dashboard, translatable files can be "
"downloaded in the :guilabel:`Files` menu."
msgstr "從專案或元件儀表板，可翻譯檔案可以在 :guilabel:`檔案` 選單中下載。"

#: user/files.rst:21
msgid ""
"The first option is to download the file in the original format as it is "
"stored in the repository. In this case, any pending changes in the "
"translation are getting committed and the up-to-date file is yield without "
"any conversions."
msgstr ""
"第一個選項是以原始格式下載檔案，因為它儲存在儲存庫中。在這種情況下，翻譯中的"
"任何掛起變更都會被提交，最新檔案是不帶任何轉換的產量。"

#: user/files.rst:25
msgid ""
"You can also download the translation converted into one of the widely used "
"localization formats. The converted files will be enriched with data "
"provided in Weblate; such as additional context, comments or flags. Several "
"file formats are available via the :guilabel:`Files` ↓ :guilabel:`Customize "
"download` menu:"
msgstr ""
"您還可以下載轉換為一種廣泛使用的在地化格式的翻譯。轉換後的檔案將使用 Weblate "
"中提供的資料進行豐富；例如附加情境、評論或標記。以下各種檔案格式可透"
"過 :guilabel:`檔案` ↓ :guilabel:`自訂下載` 選單獲得："

#: user/files.rst:30
msgid "gettext PO (``po``)"
msgstr "gettext PO (``po``)"

#: user/files.rst:31
msgid "XLIFF 1.1 with gettext extensions (``xliff``)"
msgstr "XLIFF 1.1 附帶 gettext 擴充 (``xliff``)"

#: user/files.rst:32
msgid "XLIFF 1.1 (``xliff11``)"
msgstr "XLIFF 1.1 (``xliff11``)"

#: user/files.rst:33
msgid "TermBase eXchange (``tbx``)"
msgstr "TermBase eXchange (``tbx``)"

#: user/files.rst:34
msgid "Translation Memory eXchange (``tmx``)"
msgstr "Translation Memory eXchange (``tmx``)"

#: user/files.rst:35
msgid ""
"gettext MO (only available when translation is using gettext PO) (``mo``)"
msgstr "gettext MO（僅當翻譯使用 gettext PO 時可用）(``mo``)"

#: user/files.rst:36
msgid "CSV (``csv``)"
msgstr "CSV (``csv``)"

#: user/files.rst:37
msgid "Excel Open XML (``xlsx``)"
msgstr "Excel Open XML (``xlsx``)"

#: user/files.rst:38
msgid "JSON (only available for monolingual translations) (``json``)"
msgstr "JSON（僅可用於單語言翻譯）(``json``)"

#: user/files.rst:39
msgid ""
"JSON nested structure file (only available for monolingual translations) "
"(``json-nested``)"
msgstr "JSON 巢狀結構檔案（僅適用於單語翻譯） (``json-nested``)"

#: user/files.rst:40
msgid ""
"Android String Resource (only available for monolingual translations) "
"(``aresource``)"
msgstr "Android 字串資源（僅適用於單語翻譯）(``aresource``)"

#: user/files.rst:41
msgid "iOS strings (only available for monolingual translations) (``strings``)"
msgstr "iOS 字串（僅可用於單語言翻譯）(``strings``)"

#: user/files.rst:45
msgid ""
"The content available in the converted files differs based on file format "
"features, you can find overview in :ref:`fmt_capabs`."
msgstr ""
"轉換後的檔案中可用的內容因檔案格式特性而異，您可以在 :ref:`fmt_capabs` 中找到"
"概述。"

#: user/files.rst:52
msgid ""
":http:get:`/api/translations/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"(string:language)/file/`"
msgstr ""
":http:get:`/api/translations/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"(string:language)/file/`"

#: user/files.rst:58
msgid "Downloading components, categories or projects"
msgstr "下載元件、類別或專案"

#: user/files.rst:60
msgid ""
"Translation files for a component, category or project can be downloaded at "
"once via the :guilabel:`Files` menu. The download is always served as a ZIP "
"file, and you can choose original or converted formats similarly as "
"in :ref:`download`."
msgstr ""
"可以透過 :guilabel:`檔案` 選單，一次下載元件、分類或專案的翻譯檔案。下載內容"
"一律以 ZIP 檔案提供，且可比照 :ref:`download` 選擇原始格式或轉換後的格式。"

#: user/files.rst:67
msgid ":http:get:`/api/components/(string:project)/(string:component)/file/`"
msgstr ":http:get:`/api/components/(string:project)/(string:component)/file/`"

#: user/files.rst:72
msgid "Uploading translations"
msgstr "上傳翻譯"

#: user/files.rst:74
msgid ""
"When you have made your changes, use :guilabel:`Upload translation` in "
"the :guilabel:`Files` menu."
msgstr "進行變更後，請使用 :guilabel:`檔案` 選單中的 :guilabel:`上傳譯文`。"

#: user/files.rst:82
msgid "Supported file formats"
msgstr "支援的檔案格式"

#: user/files.rst:84
msgid ""
"Any file in a supported file format can be uploaded, but it is still "
"recommended to use the same file format as the one used for translation, "
"otherwise some features might not be translated properly."
msgstr ""
"可以上傳任何受支援檔案格式的檔案，但仍建議使用與用於翻譯的檔案格式相同的檔案"
"格式，否則某些功能可能無法正確翻譯。"

#: user/files.rst:96
msgid "Import methods"
msgstr "匯入方法"

#: user/files.rst:98
msgid "These are the choices presented when uploading translation files:"
msgstr "這些是上傳翻譯檔案時提供的選項："

#: user/files.rst:102
msgid "Add as translation (``translate``)"
msgstr "新增為翻譯 (``translate``)"

#: user/files.rst:103
msgid ""
"Imported strings are added as translations to existing strings. This is the "
"most common usecase, and the default behavior."
msgstr ""
"匯入的字串會被加入為現有字串的翻譯。這是最常見的使用情境，也是預設行為。"

#: user/files.rst:106 user/files.rst:113 user/files.rst:120 user/files.rst:127
msgid ""
"Only translations are used from the uploaded file and no additional content."
msgstr "只能從上傳的檔案中使用翻譯，而且沒有其他內容。"

#: user/files.rst:108 user/files.rst:129
msgid ""
"This option is available only if the user has the :ref:`\"Edit strings\" "
"permission <privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"僅當使用者擁有 :ref:`「編輯字串」權限 <privileges>` 時，才能使用此選項。"

#: user/files.rst:109
msgid "Add as suggestion (``suggest``)"
msgstr "新增為建議 (``suggest``)"

#: user/files.rst:110
msgid ""
"Imported strings are added as suggestions. Do this when you want to have "
"your uploaded strings reviewed."
msgstr "匯入的字串會以建議形式加入。如果您想檢閱上傳的字串，請選擇此選項。"

#: user/files.rst:115
msgid ""
"This option is available only if the user has the :ref:`\"Add suggestion\" "
"permission <privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"僅當使用者擁有 :ref:`「新增建議」權限 <privileges>` 時，才能使用此選項。"

#: user/files.rst:116
msgid "Add as approved translation (``approve``)"
msgstr "以已核准翻譯新增 (``approve``)"

#: user/files.rst:117
msgid ""
"Imported strings are added as approved translations. Do this when you "
"already reviewed your translations before uploading them."
msgstr ""
"匯入的字串會以核可翻譯形式加入。如果您在上傳翻譯前已事先檢閱過翻譯，請選擇此"
"選項。"

#: user/files.rst:122
msgid ""
"This option is available only if the user has the :ref:`\"Review strings\" "
"permission <privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"僅當使用者擁有 :ref:`「審閱字串」權限 <privileges>` 時，才能使用此選項。"

#: user/files.rst:123
msgid "Add as translation needing edit (``fuzzy``)"
msgstr "新增為需要編輯的翻譯 (``fuzzy``)"

#: user/files.rst:124
msgid ""
"Imported strings are added as translations needing edit. This can be useful "
"when you want translations to be used, but also reviewed."
msgstr ""
"匯入的字串會標上需要編輯的標籤。如果您想要先使用翻譯，但也想讓人檢閱時，這個"
"選項會很有幫助。"

#: user/files.rst:130
msgid "Replace existing translation file (``replace``)"
msgstr "取代既有翻譯檔案 (``replace``)"

#: user/files.rst:131
msgid ""
"Existing file is replaced with new content. This can lead to loss of "
"existing translations, use with caution."
msgstr "現有檔案被取代為新內容。這可能導致現有翻譯遺失，請謹慎使用。"

#: user/files.rst:134
msgid ""
"This option is available only if the user has the :ref:`\"Edit component "
"settings\" permission or \"Add new string\", \"Remove a string\" and \"Edit "
"strings\" permissions <privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"僅當使用者擁有 :ref:`「編輯元件設定」權限，或同時擁有「新增字串」、「移除字"
"串」及「編輯字串」權限 <privileges>` 時，才能使用此選項。"

#: user/files.rst:136
msgid "Update source strings (``source``)"
msgstr "更新來源字串 (``source``)"

#: user/files.rst:137
msgid ""
"Updates source strings in bilingual translation file. This is similar to "
"what :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.msgmerge` does."
msgstr ""
"更新雙語言翻譯檔案中的來源字串。這類似於什麼 :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.gettext.msgmerge` 。"

#: user/files.rst:140
msgid ""
"This option is available only for some file formats and only if the user has "
"the :ref:`\"Upload translations\" permission <privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"此選項僅適用於部分檔案格式，而且只有在使用者擁有 :ref:`「上傳翻譯」權限 "
"<privileges>` 時才能使用。"

#: user/files.rst:142
msgid "Add new strings (``add``)"
msgstr "新增字串 (``add``)"

#: user/files.rst:143
msgid ""
"Adds new strings to the translation. It skips the ones which already exist."
msgstr "將新字串加入為翻譯，略過現有的字串。"

#: user/files.rst:145
msgid ""
"In case you want to both add new strings and update existing translations, "
"upload the file second time with :guilabel:`Add as translation`."
msgstr ""
"如果您想新增新字串並更新現有譯文，請使用 :guilabel:`新增為譯文` 第二次上傳檔"
"案。"

#: user/files.rst:148
msgid ""
"Only source, translation and key (context) are used from the uploaded file."
msgstr "僅使用上傳檔案中的原文、譯文和鍵（情境）。"

#: user/files.rst:150
msgid ""
"This option is available only with :ref:`component-manage_units` turned on "
"and only if the user has the :ref:`\"Add new string\" permission "
"<privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"此選項僅在 :ref:`component-manage_units` 開啟且使用者有 :ref:`“新增字串”權限 "
"<privileges>` 時可用。"

#: user/files.rst:155
msgid ""
":http:post:`/api/translations/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"(string:language)/file/`"
msgstr ""
":http:post:`/api/translations/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"(string:language)/file/`"

#: user/files.rst:160
msgid "Conflicts handling"
msgstr "衝突處理"

#: user/files.rst:162
msgid "Defines how to deal with uploaded strings which are already translated:"
msgstr "定義如何處理已翻譯的已上傳字串："

#: user/files.rst:164
msgid "Change only untranslated strings (``ignore``)"
msgstr "僅變更未翻譯的字串 (``ignore``)"

#: user/files.rst:165
msgid "Ignore uploaded translations which are already translated."
msgstr "忽略翻譯過的已上傳譯文。"

#: user/files.rst:166
msgid "Change translated strings (``replace-translated``)"
msgstr "變更已翻譯的字串 (``replace-translated``)"

#: user/files.rst:167
msgid ""
"Replace existing translations with uploaded ones, but keep approved ones."
msgstr "用已上傳的翻譯替換現有的翻譯，但保留已獲批准的翻譯。"

#: user/files.rst:168
msgid "Change translated and approved strings (``replace-approved``)"
msgstr "變更已翻譯的和已核准的字串 (``replace-approved``)"

#: user/files.rst:169
msgid ""
"Replace existing translations with uploaded ones, including approved ones."
msgstr "使用已上傳的翻譯替換現有翻譯，包括那些已核准的翻譯。"

#: user/files.rst:174
msgid "Strings needing edit"
msgstr "需要編輯的字串"

#: user/files.rst:176
msgid ""
"There is also an option for how to handle strings needing edit in the "
"imported file. Such strings can be handle in one of the three following "
"ways: \"Do not import\", \"Import as string needing edit\", or \"Import as "
"translated\"."
msgstr ""
"還有一個選項可用於處理匯入檔案中需要編輯的字串。可以透過以下三種方式之一處理"
"此類字串：“不匯入”、“匯入為‘需要編輯’”或“匯入為已翻譯”。"

#: user/files.rst:184
msgid "Overriding authorship"
msgstr "覆寫作者資訊"

#: user/files.rst:186
msgid ""
"With admin permissions, you can also specify authorship of uploaded file. "
"This can be useful in case you've received the file in another way and want "
"to merge it into existing translations while properly crediting the actual "
"author."
msgstr ""
"使用管理員權限，您還可以指定上傳檔案的作者身分。如果您以其他方式收到檔案並希"
"望將其合併到現有翻譯中，同時正確註明實際作者，這可能很有用。"

#: user/glossary.rst:6
msgid ""
"Each project can include one or more glossaries for storing terms and their "
"preferred translations. Glossaries help keep translations consistent by "
"showing matching terms in the translation editor."
msgstr ""
"每個專案都可以包含一個或多個詞彙表，用於儲存術語和它們偏好的譯文。詞彙表透過"
"在翻譯編輯器中顯示相符的術語幫助保持譯文一致性。"

#: user/glossary.rst:10
msgid ""
"Glossaries are regular translation components with special behavior. The "
"source language stores the terms Weblate searches for in source strings. "
"Each glossary translation stores the preferred term, forbidden term, or "
"untranslatable entry for one target language."
msgstr ""
"詞彙表是具有特殊行為的一般翻譯元件。來源語言會儲存 Weblate 在來源字串中搜尋的"
"詞彙。每個詞彙表翻譯會針對一種目標語言，儲存偏好詞彙、停用詞彙或不翻譯項目。"

#: user/glossary.rst:15
msgid ""
"Terms from the glossary containing words from the currently translated "
"source string are displayed in the sidebar of the translation editor."
msgstr ""
"詞彙表中包含目前所翻譯來源字串內文字的詞彙，會顯示在翻譯編輯器的側邊欄。"

#: user/glossary.rst:20
msgid ""
"The glossary terms are not used in quality checks unless you enable that, "
"see :ref:`check-check-glossary` for more information."
msgstr ""
"除非啟用，否則不會在品質檢查中使用詞彙表術語，請參閱 :ref:`check-check-"
"glossary` 瞭解更多資訊。"

#: user/glossary.rst:24
msgid "How glossary matching works"
msgstr "詞彙表相符如何工作"

#: user/glossary.rst:26
msgid ""
"When you translate a regular component, Weblate searches the source string "
"for terms from the source language of the project glossaries. When a term "
"matches, Weblate looks up the corresponding glossary entry for the language "
"currently being translated and shows it in the editor."
msgstr ""
"翻譯一般元件時，Weblate 會在來源字串中搜尋專案詞彙表來源語言內的詞彙。找到相"
"符詞彙時，Weblate 會查詢目前所翻譯語言的對應詞彙表項目，並在編輯器中顯示。"

#: user/glossary.rst:31
msgid ""
"This means glossary entries need to exist in the target glossary language to "
"be shown while translating that target language. A source-language-only "
"glossary can still store definitions and context, but it will not provide "
"target-language matches for languages that do not have glossary entries."
msgstr ""
"這表示詞彙表項目必須存在於目標詞彙表語言中，才會在翻譯該目標語言時顯示。僅含"
"來源語言的詞彙表仍可儲存定義及情境，但若某種語言沒有詞彙表項目，就無法提供該"
"目標語言的相符詞彙。"

#: user/glossary.rst:36
msgid ""
"If you want a term to be present in every glossary language, mark the source "
"entry as :ref:`glossary-terminology`. If the term should stay unchanged in "
"every language, use :ref:`glossary-untranslatable`; combine it with "
"terminology only when you want Weblate to create and maintain entries for "
"all glossary languages."
msgstr ""
"若要讓詞彙存在於每個詞彙表語言中，請將來源項目標記為 :ref:`glossary-"
"terminology`。若詞彙在每種語言中都應保持不變，請使用 :ref:`glossary-"
"untranslatable`；只有在希望 Weblate 為所有詞彙表語言建立並維護項目時，才同時"
"套用術語標記。"

#: user/glossary.rst:42
msgid "Managing glossaries"
msgstr "管理詞彙表"

#: user/glossary.rst:46
msgid ""
"Glossaries are now regular translation components and you can use all "
"Weblate features on them — commenting, storing in a remote repository, or "
"adding explanations."
msgstr ""
"詞彙表現在是一般的翻譯元件，您可以在其中使用所有 Weblate 功能——評論、儲存在遠"
"端儲存庫中或新增解釋。"

#: user/glossary.rst:50
msgid ""
"Use any component as a glossary by turning on :ref:`component-is_glossary`. "
"You can create multiple glossaries for one project."
msgstr ""
"使用任何元件作為詞彙表，方法是開啟 :ref:`component-is_glossary`。您可以為一個"
"專案建立多個詞彙表。"

#: user/glossary.rst:53
msgid ""
"An empty glossary for a given project is automatically created with the "
"project. Glossaries are shared among all components of the same project, and "
"optionally with other projects using :ref:`component-links` from the "
"respective glossary component."
msgstr ""
"給定專案的空詞彙表會隨專案自動建立。詞彙表在同一個專案的所有元件之間共享，並"
"且可以選擇使用來自相應詞彙表元件的 :ref:`component-links` 與其他專案共享。"

#: user/glossary.rst:58
msgid ""
"The glossary component looks like any other component in Weblate with added "
"colored label:"
msgstr "詞彙表元件看起來與 Weblate 中的其他元件一樣，只是多了個彩色標籤："

#: user/glossary.rst:63
msgid "You can browse all glossary terms:"
msgstr "您可以瀏覽所有詞彙表術語："

#: user/glossary.rst:67
msgid "or edit them as any translations."
msgstr "或將它們當作任何翻譯進行編輯。"

#: user/glossary.rst:70
msgid "Glossary terms"
msgstr "詞彙表術語"

#: user/glossary.rst:72
msgid ""
"Glossary terms are translated the same way regular strings are. You can "
"toggle additional features using the :guilabel:`Tools` menu for each term."
msgstr ""
"詞彙表的翻譯方式與普通字串的翻譯方式相同。您可以使用每個術語的 :guilabel:`工"
"具` 選單為每個術語切換附加功能。"

#: user/glossary.rst:81
msgid "Glossary entry types"
msgstr "詞彙表條目類型"

#: user/glossary.rst:84
msgid "Type"
msgstr "類型"

#: user/glossary.rst:85
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "目的"

#: user/glossary.rst:87
msgid "Regular glossary term"
msgstr "一般的詞彙表術語"

#: user/glossary.rst:88
msgid ""
"Preferred translation or explanation for a term in one or more languages."
msgstr "一或多種語言中詞彙的偏好翻譯或說明。"

#: user/glossary.rst:92
msgid ""
"Source term Weblate keeps present in every glossary language so missing "
"translations can be tracked and filled."
msgstr "Weblate 會在每個詞彙表語言中保留的來源詞彙，以便追蹤及補上缺少的翻譯。"

#: user/glossary.rst:96
msgid "Term that should stay unchanged or should not be translated."
msgstr "應保持不變或不應翻譯的詞彙。"

#: user/glossary.rst:99
msgid "Translation that should not be used for the source term."
msgstr "不應用於源術語的譯文。"

#: user/glossary.rst:102
msgid ""
"Alternative wording, abbreviation, or shorter form grouped with another "
"glossary term."
msgstr "與另一個詞彙表詞彙歸為同一組的替代用語、縮寫或簡稱。"

#: user/glossary.rst:108
msgid "Choosing glossary terms"
msgstr "選擇詞彙表術語"

#: user/glossary.rst:110
msgid ""
"Choose glossary terms for meaning and audience, not only for literal word "
"shape. If a source term is ambiguous, add an explanation so translators know "
"which meaning applies in the project."
msgstr ""
"選擇詞彙表詞彙時，應考量語意及目標讀者，不應只看字面形式。若來源詞彙可能有多"
"種意思，請加入說明，讓翻譯者知道專案採用的語意。"

#: user/glossary.rst:114
msgid ""
"Glossary entries are especially useful for brand names, acronyms, product "
"features, technical terms, and newly coined or transliterated words. Use "
"variants for abbreviations or shorter wording, mark important cross-language "
"terms as :ref:`glossary-terminology`, mark terms that should stay unchanged "
"as :ref:`glossary-untranslatable`, and mark misleading translations "
"as :ref:`glossary-forbidden`."
msgstr ""
"詞彙表項目特別適合品牌名稱、縮寫、產品功能、技術詞彙，以及新創或音譯詞。請將"
"縮寫或較短用語設為變體、將重要的跨語言詞彙標記為 :ref:`glossary-"
"terminology`、將應保持不變的詞彙標記為 :ref:`glossary-untranslatable`，並將容"
"易造成誤解的翻譯標記為 :ref:`glossary-forbidden`。"

#: user/glossary.rst:124
msgid "Untranslatable terms"
msgstr "不可翻譯的術語"

#: user/glossary.rst:128
msgid ""
"Flagging certain glossary term translations ``read-only`` by bulk-editing, "
"typing in the flag, or by using :guilabel:`Tools` ↓ :guilabel:`Mark as "
"untranslatable` means they can not be translated. Use this for brand names, "
"product names, domains, technology names, or other terms that should not be "
"changed in other languages. Such terms are visually highlighted in the "
"glossary sidebar."
msgstr ""
"透過批次編輯、輸入標記或使用 :guilabel:`工具` ↓ :guilabel:`標記為不可翻譯` 來"
"標記某些術語的譯文為 ``read-only`` 意味著它們不能被翻譯。對於品牌名、產品名、"
"網域、技術名、或其他不應該在其他語言中被改變的術語，可以使用這個方法。這樣的"
"術語會在詞彙表側邊欄中直觀地突出顯示。"

#: user/glossary.rst:135
msgid ""
"The ``read-only`` flag is enough when the glossary entry already exists in "
"the languages where it should be shown. Add the :ref:`glossary-terminology` "
"flag as well only when Weblate should create and maintain the untranslatable "
"entry in every glossary language."
msgstr ""
"當詞彙表項目已存在於應顯示的語言中時，只使用 ``read-only`` 旗標即可。只有在 "
"Weblate 應於每個詞彙表語言中建立並維護不翻譯項目時，才另行加"
"入 :ref:`glossary-terminology` 旗標。"

#: user/glossary.rst:147 user/glossary.rst:276
msgid "Forbidden translations"
msgstr "禁止的翻譯"

#: user/glossary.rst:151
msgid ""
"Flagging certain glossary term translations as ``forbidden`` by bulk-"
"editing, typing in the flag, or by using :guilabel:`Tools` ↓ :guilabel:`Mark "
"as forbidden translation` means they are **not** to be used. Use this to "
"clarify translation when some words are ambiguous or could have unexpected "
"meanings."
msgstr ""
"透過批次編輯、輸入標記或使用 :guilabel:`工具` ↓ :guilabel:`標記為禁止的譯文` "
"來將某些詞彙表術語譯文標記為 ``forbidden`` 意味著它們 **不能** 被使用。當某些"
"字詞模稜兩可或可能具有意想不到的含義時，使用它來澄清譯文。"

#: user/glossary.rst:157
msgid ""
"Use forbidden entries for translations that should be avoided. Use regular "
"glossary entries for preferred translations."
msgstr "應避免使用的翻譯請設為停用項目；偏好的翻譯則使用一般詞彙表項目。"

#: user/glossary.rst:167
msgid "Terminology"
msgstr "專有名詞"

#: user/glossary.rst:171
msgid ""
"Flagging certain source-language glossary terms as ``terminology`` by bulk-"
"editing, typing in the flag, or by using :guilabel:`Tools` ↓ :guilabel:`Mark "
"as terminology` adds entries for them to all languages in the glossary. Use "
"this for important terms that should be well thought out, and retain a "
"consistent meaning across all languages."
msgstr ""
"透過批次編輯、鍵入標誌或使用 :guilabel:`工具` ↓ :guilabel:`標記為專業術語` 來"
"將某些來源語言詞彙表術語標記為 ``terminology`` 以將條目新增到所有語言的詞彙表"
"中。將此用於應該經過深思熟慮的重要術語，並在所有語言中保持一致的含義。"

#: user/glossary.rst:177
msgid ""
"The terminology flag is ongoing state, not just a one-time action. While the "
"flag remains on the source term, Weblate treats it as terminology and keeps "
"an entry for it in every glossary language. If a language entry is removed, "
"the next glossary synchronization creates it again."
msgstr ""
"術語標記是持續的狀態，非一次性動作。當標記保留在源術語上時，Weblate 將其視為"
"專業術語並在每個詞彙表語言中為它保留一個條目。如果刪除了一個語言條目，那麼下"
"次詞彙表同步會再建立它。"

#: user/glossary.rst:182
msgid ""
"Removing the ``terminology`` flag stops this automatic maintenance, but it "
"does not remove or otherwise revert entries that were already created. They "
"remain regular glossary entries."
msgstr ""
"刪除 ``terminology`` 標記停止自動維護，但不刪除或撤銷已建立的條目。它們仍為一"
"般詞彙表條目。"

#: user/glossary.rst:186
msgid ""
"A regular glossary term can also have translations in every language. The "
"difference is that Weblate does not recreate missing language entries for a "
"regular term after they are removed."
msgstr ""
"一般詞彙表詞彙也可以在每種語言中都有翻譯。差別在於，一般詞彙的語言項目遭移除"
"後，Weblate 不會重新建立缺少的項目。"

#: user/glossary.rst:197 user/translating.rst:107
msgid "Variants"
msgstr "變體"

#: user/glossary.rst:199
msgid ""
"Variants are a generic way to group strings together. All term variants are "
"listed in the glossary sidebar when translating."
msgstr ""
"變體是將字串組合在一起的通用方式。在翻譯時，所有術語變體都列在詞彙表側邊條"
"中。"

#: user/glossary.rst:204
msgid ""
"You can use this to add abbreviations or shorter expressions for a term."
msgstr "您可以使用它來新增縮寫或縮短表達式。"

#: user/glossary.rst:211
msgid "Glossary import"
msgstr "詞彙表匯入"

#: user/glossary.rst:213
msgid ""
"Similar to regular translation components, you can upload existing "
"glossaries to Weblate. Formats like :doc:`/formats/csv` or :doc:`/formats/"
"tbx` are supported and can be uploaded, see :ref:`upload`."
msgstr ""
"和一般的翻譯元件類似，您可以將現有的詞彙表上傳到 Weblate。:doc:`/formats/"
"csv` 或 :doc:`/formats/tbx` 等格式受支援，可以被上傳，見 :ref:`upload`。"

#: user/glossary.rst:217
msgid ""
"TBX files can include explanations, read-only metadata, and glossary flags; "
"see :ref:`tbx` for the exact metadata mapping."
msgstr ""
"TBX 檔案可包含說明、唯讀中繼資料及詞彙表旗標；如需確切的中繼資料對應方式，請"
"參閱 :ref:`tbx`。"

#: user/glossary.rst:220
msgid ""
"Even though TBX can contain multiple languages, Weblate still maps component "
"files to languages using the component file mask and language settings. For "
"a TBX glossary component, keep the component source language as the source "
"term language and name translation files for the target language they "
"represent. Avoid naming a translation file with the same language as the "
"component source language, because the source language already exists in "
"Weblate and this can lead to duplicate language detection."
msgstr ""
"即使 TBX 可以包含多種語言，Weblate 仍會使用元件檔案遮罩及語言設定，將元件檔案"
"對應至語言。對 TBX 詞彙表元件而言，請將元件來源語言設為來源詞彙的語言，並依翻"
"譯檔案所代表的目標語言命名。請勿以元件來源語言命名翻譯檔案，因為該來源語言已"
"存在於 Weblate 中，這可能導致偵測到重複語言。"

#: user/glossary.rst:236
msgid "Language files and synchronization"
msgstr "語言檔案和同步"

#: user/glossary.rst:238
msgid ""
"Glossary components follow the languages used by the regular components in "
"the same project. When a language is added to a regular component, Weblate "
"adds the missing glossary language as well so glossary matches can be shown "
"for that language."
msgstr ""
"詞彙表元件會跟隨同一專案內一般元件所使用的語言。一般元件加入某種語言時，"
"Weblate 也會加入缺少的詞彙表語言，以便顯示該語言的相符詞彙。"

#: user/glossary.rst:243
msgid ""
"This automatic language synchronization is intentional. Filtering glossary "
"language files with :ref:`component-language_regex` can reduce the number of "
"managed files, but it also means Weblate has no glossary entries to show for "
"filtered-out target languages."
msgstr ""
"這項自動語言同步是刻意設計的行為。使用 :ref:`component-language_regex` 過濾詞"
"彙表語言檔案可減少受管理的檔案數，但也表示 Weblate 沒有詞彙表項目可向遭過濾的"
"目標語言顯示。"

#: user/glossary.rst:248
msgid ""
"Terminology entries are also synchronized. When a source glossary term is "
"marked as terminology, Weblate creates missing entries in all glossary "
"languages and recreates them if they are removed while the flag is still set."
msgstr ""
"術語項目也會同步。來源詞彙表詞彙標記為術語時，Weblate 會在所有詞彙表語言中建"
"立缺少的項目；只要該旗標仍在，即使項目遭到移除也會重新建立。"

#: user/glossary.rst:252
msgid ""
"Weblate can clean up stale glossary translations only for Weblate-managed "
"glossaries, only when no regular component in the project still uses that "
"language, and only when the stale glossary translation has no translated "
"terms. If the stale glossary language still contains terms, Weblate keeps it "
"and reports it as an unused glossary language."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 只有在詞彙表由 Weblate 管理、專案中沒有一般元件仍使用該語言，且過時的"
"詞彙表翻譯不含已翻譯詞彙時，才能清理該翻譯。若過時的詞彙表語言仍包含詞彙，"
"Weblate 會予以保留，並回報為未使用的詞彙表語言。"

#: user/glossary.rst:259
msgid "Common setup patterns"
msgstr "常見設定模式"

#: user/glossary.rst:261
msgid "English-only explanatory glossary"
msgstr "僅含英文說明的詞彙表"

#: user/glossary.rst:262
msgid ""
"Add source-language glossary terms with explanations. This works as a "
"maintained term list, but it will not show target-language glossary matches "
"unless you also create entries in the target glossary languages."
msgstr ""
"加入含有說明的來源語言詞彙表詞彙。這可作為持續維護的詞彙清單，但除非也在目標"
"詞彙表語言中建立項目，否則不會顯示目標語言的相符詞彙。"

#: user/glossary.rst:266
msgid "Required terminology"
msgstr "必需的術語"

#: user/glossary.rst:267
msgid ""
"Add terms in the source glossary language, mark them as :ref:`glossary-"
"terminology`, and let translators fill the created entries in each target "
"language. Use explanations to document the intended meaning."
msgstr ""
"在詞彙表來源語言中加入詞彙、將其標記為 :ref:`glossary-terminology`，再由翻譯"
"者填寫各目標語言中建立的項目。請使用說明記錄預期語意。"

#: user/glossary.rst:271
msgid "Non-translatable terms"
msgstr "不可翻譯的術語"

#: user/glossary.rst:272
msgid ""
"Mark terms as :ref:`glossary-untranslatable` when they should stay "
"unchanged. Add :ref:`glossary-terminology` only when the term should be "
"present in every glossary language for matching and review."
msgstr ""
"詞彙應保持不變時，請標記為 :ref:`glossary-untranslatable`。只有在詞彙應存在於"
"每個詞彙表語言中，以供比對及審閱時，才加入 :ref:`glossary-terminology`。"

#: user/glossary.rst:277
msgid ""
"Add the misleading translation as a :ref:`glossary-forbidden` entry. Add the "
"preferred wording as a separate regular glossary entry when translators "
"should use a specific translation instead."
msgstr ""
"將容易造成誤解的翻譯加入為 :ref:`glossary-forbidden` 項目。若翻譯者應改用特定"
"譯法，請另行將偏好用語加入為一般詞彙表項目。"

#: user/glossary.rst:284
msgid "Glossaries in automatic suggestion"
msgstr "自動建議中的詞彙表"

#: user/glossary.rst:288
msgid ""
"Some automatic suggestion services utilize glossaries during the "
"translation, please consult their documentation in :doc:`/admin/machine` to "
"see the support."
msgstr ""
"一些自動建議服務在翻譯時使用詞彙表，具體支援情況請檢視 :doc:`/admin/machine` "
"中相關內容。"

#: user/glossary.rst:291
msgid "The glossary is processed before exposed to the service:"
msgstr "在被匯出到服務前，會先處理詞彙表："

#: user/glossary.rst:293
msgid ""
"Duplicate source entries are skipped for services that require unique source "
"terms. LLM-based services can receive duplicates with explanations to "
"disambiguate them."
msgstr ""
"需要唯一來源詞彙的服務會略過重複的來源項目。以 LLM 為基礎的服務則可接收含有說"
"明的重複項目，以釐清其中差異。"

#: user/glossary.rst:296
msgid ""
"Any control characters and leading and trailing whitespace are stripped."
msgstr "所有控制字元，以及開頭與結尾的空白字元都會被移除。"

#: user/glossary.rst:297
msgid ":ref:`glossary-forbidden` are skipped."
msgstr ":ref:`glossary-forbidden` 被跳過。"

#: user/glossary.rst:301
msgid ""
"Many services store glossaries server-side and enforce limit on the number "
"of saved glossaries. Weblate always deletes the oldest glossary if it runs "
"out of space."
msgstr ""
"許多服務會將詞彙表儲存在伺服器端，並限制可儲存的詞彙表數量。空間用盡時，"
"Weblate 一律會刪除最舊的詞彙表。"

#: user/profile.rst:2
msgid "Registration and user profile"
msgstr "註冊與使用者設定檔"

#: user/profile.rst:7
msgid ""
"Everybody can browse projects, view translations or suggest translations by "
"default. Only registered users are allowed to actually save changes, and are "
"credited for every translation made."
msgstr ""
"預設情況下，每個人都可以瀏覽專案，查看翻譯或建議翻譯。只允許註冊使用者實際儲"
"存變更，並為每種翻譯歸功於所做的。"

#: user/profile.rst:11
msgid "You can register by following a few simple steps:"
msgstr "您可以透過以下幾個簡單的步驟註冊："

#: user/profile.rst:13
msgid "Fill out the registration form with your credentials."
msgstr "使用憑證填寫註冊表格。"

#: user/profile.rst:14
msgid "Activate registration by following the link in the e-mail you receive."
msgstr "透過您收到的電子郵件中的連結啟用註冊。"

#: user/profile.rst:15
msgid "Optionally adjust your profile to choose which languages you know."
msgstr "可以選擇調整您的個人資料以選擇您知道的語言。"

#: user/profile.rst:20
msgid "Dashboard"
msgstr "儀表板"

#: user/profile.rst:22
msgid ""
"When you sign in, you will see an overview of projects and components, as "
"well as their respective translation progression."
msgstr "登入時，您將看到專案和元件的概覽，以及各自的翻譯進度。"

#: user/profile.rst:25
msgid ""
"Components of projects you are watching are shown by default, and cross-"
"referenced with your preferred languages."
msgstr "預設顯示您正在關注的專案元件，並通過您的首選語言交叉引用。"

#: user/profile.rst:30
msgid "You can switch to different views using the navigation tabs."
msgstr "您可以使用導覽列中的分頁切換到不同的檢視方式。"

#: user/profile.rst:34
msgid "The menu has these options:"
msgstr "選單有這些選項："

#: user/profile.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Projects` > :guilabel:`Browse all projects` in the main menu "
"showing translation status for each project on the Weblate instance."
msgstr ""
"主選單的 :guilabel:`專案` > :guilabel:`瀏覽所有專案` 會顯示 Weblate 執行個體"
"上每個專案的翻譯狀態。"

#: user/profile.rst:38
msgid ""
"Selecting a language in the main menu :guilabel:`Languages` will show "
"translation status of all projects, filtered by one of your primary "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"在主選單的 :guilabel:`語言` 中選取語言，即會顯示所有專案的翻譯狀態，並以您的"
"某個主要語言篩選。"

#: user/profile.rst:40
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Watched translations` in the Dashboard will show translation "
"status of only those projects you are watching, filtered by your primary "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"控制台中的 :guilabel:`已監看翻譯` 只會顯示您正在監看之專案的翻譯狀態，並以您"
"的主要語言篩選。"

#: user/profile.rst:43
msgid ""
"In addition, the drop-down can also show any number of *component lists*, "
"sets of project components preconfigured by the Weblate administrator, "
"see :ref:`componentlists`."
msgstr ""
"此外，下拉選單還可以顯示任何數量的 *元件清單*，由 Weblate 管理員預先設定的專"
"案元件集，請參閱 :ref:`componentlists`。"

#: user/profile.rst:47
msgid ""
"You can configure your personal default dashboard view in "
"the :guilabel:`Preferences` section of your user profile settings."
msgstr ""
"您可在使用者資料設定的 :guilabel:`偏好設定` 區段中，設定個人預設控制台檢視。"

#: user/profile.rst:52
msgid ""
"When Weblate is configured for a single project "
"using :setting:`SINGLE_PROJECT` in the :file:`settings.py` file "
"(see :ref:`config`), the dashboard will not be shown, as the user will be "
"redirected to a single project or component instead."
msgstr ""
"當使用以下專案設定 Weblate 時 :setting:`SINGLE_PROJECT` "
"在 :file:`settings.py` 檔案（請參閱 :ref:`config`），儀表板將不會顯示，當使用"
"者將被重新導向到單一專案或元件。"

#: user/profile.rst:59
msgid "User profile"
msgstr "使用者設定檔"

#: user/profile.rst:60
msgid ""
"The user profile is accessible by clicking your user icon in the top-right "
"of the top menu, then the :guilabel:`Settings` menu."
msgstr ""
"按下頂端選單右上角的使用者圖示，再選取 :guilabel:`設定` 選單，即可存取使用者"
"資料。"

#: user/profile.rst:63
msgid ""
"The user profile contains your preferences. Name and e-mail address are used "
"in VCS commits, so keep this info accurate."
msgstr ""
"使用者資料包含您的偏好設定。姓名與電子郵件地址會用於 VCS 提交，因此請確保這些"
"資訊正確。"

#: user/profile.rst:68
msgid "All language selections only offer currently translated languages."
msgstr "所有語言選取僅提供目前翻譯的語言。"

#: user/profile.rst:72
msgid ""
"Request or add other languages you want to translate by clicking the button "
"to make them available too."
msgstr "請求或新增要通過點選按鈕來翻譯的其他語言，以使其成為可用。"

#: user/profile.rst:79
msgid "Interface language"
msgstr "介面語言"

#: user/profile.rst:81
msgid "Choose the language you want to display the UI in."
msgstr "選擇您想要顯示使用者介面的語言。"

#: user/profile.rst:86
msgid "Translated languages"
msgstr "想翻譯成哪些語言"

#: user/profile.rst:88
msgid ""
"Choose which languages you prefer to translate, and they will be offered on "
"the main page of watched projects, so that you have easier access to all "
"these translations in each of those languages."
msgstr ""
"選擇您喜歡翻譯的語言，它們將在已關注專案的主頁上提供，以便您可以更輕鬆地存取"
"每種語言的所有翻譯。"

#: user/profile.rst:97
msgid "Secondary languages"
msgstr "第二語言"

#: user/profile.rst:99
msgid ""
"You can define which secondary languages are shown to you as a guide while "
"translating. An example can be seen in the following image, where the Hebrew "
"language is shown as secondarily:"
msgstr ""
"您可以在翻譯時將哪些輔助語言作為指南顯示為指南。在以下圖像中可以看到一個範"
"例，其中希伯來語如下所示："

#: user/profile.rst:107
msgid ""
"This can be also configured in the project (:ref:`project-"
"secondary_language`) or component (:ref:`component-secondary_language`). In "
"that case it can be used for :ref:`secondary-language-workflow`."
msgstr ""
"也可以在專案 (:ref:`project-secondary_language`) 或元件 (:ref:`component-"
"secondary_language`) 對此進行設定。如果是這種情況，它可以被用"
"於 :ref:`secondary-language-workflow`。"

#: user/profile.rst:115
msgid "Preferences"
msgstr "偏好設定"

#: user/profile.rst:118
msgid "Theme"
msgstr "主題"

#: user/profile.rst:120
msgid ""
"Choose whether Weblate follows system settings for dark or light theme, or "
"choose one of them manually."
msgstr ""
"選擇 Weblate 是跟隨系統設定來設定深色或淺色主題，還是讓使用者手動選擇其中的一"
"個。"

#: user/profile.rst:123
msgid "Default dashboard view"
msgstr "預設儀表板檢視"

#: user/profile.rst:125
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Preferences` tab, you can pick which of the available "
"dashboard views to present by default. If you pick the :guilabel:`Component "
"list`, you have to select which component list will be displayed from "
"the :guilabel:`Default component list` drop-down."
msgstr ""
"在 :guilabel:`首選項` 分頁，您可以選擇預設顯示的操作面板檢視。如果您選"
"擇 :guilabel:`元件清單`，您必須從 :guilabel:`預設元件清單` 下拉選單中選擇要顯"
"示哪個元件清單。"

#: user/profile.rst:135
msgid "Editor link"
msgstr "編輯器連結"

#: user/profile.rst:137
msgid ""
"A source code link is shown in the web-browser configured in "
"the :ref:`component` by default."
msgstr ""
"在預設情況下，原始碼連結會顯示在 :ref:`component` 中設定的 Web 瀏覽器中。"

#: user/profile.rst:142
msgid ""
"By setting the :guilabel:`Editor link`, you use your local editor to open "
"the VCS source code file of translated strings. You can use :ref:`markup`."
msgstr ""
"通過設定 :guilabel:`編輯器連結`，您可以使用本機編輯器開啟翻譯字串的 VCS 來源"
"檔案。您可以使用 :ref:`markup`。"

#: user/profile.rst:145
msgid ""
"Usually something like ``editor://open/?file={{filename}}&line={{line}}`` is "
"a good option."
msgstr ""
"通常像 ``editor://open/?file={{filename}}&line={{line}}`` 是一個不錯的選擇。"

#: user/profile.rst:149
msgid ""
"You can find more info on registering custom URL protocols for the editor in "
"the `Nette documentation <https://tracy.nette.org/en/open-files-in-ide>`_."
msgstr ""
"您可以在 `Nette 檔案 <https://tracy.nette.org/en/open-files-in-ide>`_ 中找到"
"更多關於註冊編輯器自訂 URL 協定的資訊。"

#: user/profile.rst:155
msgid "Special characters"
msgstr "特殊字元"

#: user/profile.rst:157
msgid "Additional special characters to include in the :ref:`visual-keyboard`."
msgstr "要包含在 :ref:`visual-keyboard` 的額外特殊字元。"

#: user/profile.rst:162
msgid "Notifications"
msgstr "通知"

#: user/profile.rst:164
msgid ""
"Subscribe to various notifications from the :guilabel:`Notifications` tab. "
"Notifications for selected events on watched or administered projects will "
"be sent to you per e-mail."
msgstr ""
"從 :guilabel:`通知` 分頁訂閱各種通知。有關已關注或管理的專案的選取事件的通知"
"將透過電子郵件傳送給您。"

#: user/profile.rst:168
msgid ""
"Some of the notifications are sent only for events in your languages (for "
"example about new strings to translate), while some trigger at component "
"level (for example merge errors). These two groups of notifications are "
"visually separated in the settings."
msgstr ""
"其中一些通知僅用於語言中的事件（例如，關於要轉換的新字串），而元件層級的某些"
"觸發（例如合併錯誤）。這兩種通知在設定中可視化。"

#: user/profile.rst:173
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Translation activity summary` notification is digest-only and "
"summarizes added, updated, translated, approved, needs editing, and "
"unfinished strings."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`翻譯活動摘要` 通知只會收錄於摘要，並彙整已加入、已更新、已翻譯、已"
"核准、需要編輯及未完成的字串。"

#: user/profile.rst:177
msgid ""
"You can toggle notifications for watched projects and administered projects "
"and it can be further tweaked (or muted) per project and component. Visit "
"the component overview page and select appropriate choice from "
"the :guilabel:`Watching` menu."
msgstr ""
"您可以切換監視專案和管理專案的通知，每個專案和元件都可以進一步調整（或靜"
"音）。存取「元件概覽」頁面，然後選取以下選項 :guilabel:`觀看` 選單。"

#: user/profile.rst:181
msgid ""
"In case :guilabel:`Automatically watch projects on contribution` is enabled "
"you will automatically start watching projects upon contributing to them. "
"The default value depends on :setting:`DEFAULT_AUTO_WATCH`."
msgstr ""
"如果啟用了 :guilabel:`自動關注作出貢獻的專案`，您將在給專案作貢獻後自動開始關"
"注專案。預設值取決於 :setting:`DEFAULT_AUTO_WATCH`。"

#: user/profile.rst:187
msgid "You will not receive notifications for your own actions."
msgstr "您將不會收到自身動作的通知。"

#: user/profile.rst:191
msgid ""
"Sending out notifications is limited, you will not receive more than 1000 e-"
"mails per day. Any further notifications for you will be discarded."
msgstr ""
"傳送通知的數量是有限制的，您每天收到的電子郵件不會超過 1000 封。第 1001 封及"
"之後發給您的電子郵件通知都將被丟棄。"

#: user/profile.rst:199
msgid "Account"
msgstr "帳號"

#: user/profile.rst:201
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Account` tab lets you set up basic account details, connect "
"various services you can use to sign in into Weblate, completely remove your "
"account, or download your user data (see :ref:`schema-userdata`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`帳號` 分頁讓您設定基本帳號資訊、連線其他登入服務並可透過它們來登"
"入 Weblate、完整移除您的帳號或下載您的使用者資料（請參閱 :ref:`schema-"
"userdata`）。"

#: user/profile.rst:205
msgid ""
"The private commit e-mail will be used instead of your account e-mail in "
"version control commits. Use this to avoid leaking your real e-mail there. "
"Be aware that using different e-mail can disconnect your contributions on "
"other servers (for example your contributions will no longer link to your "
"profile on GitHub). The private e-mail can be turned on site-wide "
"using :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_OPT_IN`."
msgstr ""
"在版本控制提交中，將使用私密提交電子郵件而不是您的帳號電子郵件。使用此功能可"
"以避免您的真實電子郵件地址洩露。請注意，使用不同的電子郵件地址可能會斷開您在"
"其他伺服器上的做出的貢獻關聯（例如您的貢獻將不再連結到您的 GitHub 個人資"
"料）。可使用 :setting:`PRIVATE_COMMIT_EMAIL_OPT_IN` 在全站範圍內啟用私密電子"
"郵件功能。"

#: user/profile.rst:215
msgid ""
"The list of services depends on your Weblate configuration, but can be made "
"to include popular sites such as GitLab, GitHub, Google, Facebook, or "
"Bitbucket or other OAuth 2.0 providers."
msgstr ""
"服務清單取決於您的 Weblate 設定，但可設定為包含 Gitlab、Github、Google、"
"Facebook 或 Bitbucket 等流行網站，或是其他 OAuth 2.0 提供者。"

#: user/profile.rst:224
msgid "Profile"
msgstr "個人檔案"

#: user/profile.rst:226
msgid ""
"All of the fields on this page are optional and can be deleted at any time, "
"and by filling them out, you're giving us consent to share this data "
"wherever your user profile appears."
msgstr ""
"此頁面上的所有欄位皆為選填，且可隨時刪除。一旦填入這些資訊，即表示您同意我們"
"在您的個人檔案出現時分享這些資料。"

#: user/profile.rst:230
msgid ""
"Public profile URLs, such as :guilabel:`Website URL`, :guilabel:`Contact "
"URL`, :guilabel:`Fediverse URL`, and :guilabel:`Code site URL`, should point "
"to a website, contact, or profile page. Obvious direct file download links "
"can be rejected, and public profile links show a warning before leaving "
"Weblate where possible."
msgstr ""
"公開的個人資料 URL，如 :guilabel:`網站 URL`、:guilabel:`聯絡 "
"URL`、:guilabel:`Fediverse URL` 和 :guilabel:`程式碼站 URL` 應該指向網站、聯"
"絡人或個人資料頁。明顯的直接檔案下載連結可能會被拒絕，在可能情況下離開 "
"Weblate 存取公開資料頁連結前會顯示警告。"

#: user/profile.rst:236
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Code site URL` should use common code-hosting profile paths, "
"such as ``/username`` or ``/~username``; existing repository-style links "
"such as ``/username/project`` or ``/group/subgroup/project`` are also "
"accepted. The :guilabel:`Fediverse URL` should use common profile paths, "
"such as ``/username``, ``/@username``, ``/web/@username``, ``/users/"
"username``, ``/accounts/username``, ``/channel/username``, ``/profile/"
"username``, ``/u/username``, or ``/people/identifier``."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`程式碼站 URL` 應使用常見的程式碼託管網站個人檔案路徑，例如 ``/"
"username`` 或 ``/~username``；也接受現有的儲存庫形式連結，例如 ``/username/"
"project`` 或 ``/group/subgroup/project``。:guilabel:`Fediverse URL` 應使用常"
"見的個人檔案路徑，例如 ``/username``、``/@username``、``/web/@username``、``/"
"users/username``、``/accounts/username``、``/channel/username``、``/profile/"
"username``、``/u/username`` 或 ``/people/identifier``。"

#: user/profile.rst:245
msgid ""
"Avatar can be shown for each user (depending on :setting:`ENABLE_AVATARS`). "
"These images are obtained using https://gravatar.com/."
msgstr ""
"可以為每個使用者顯示頭像（取決於 :setting:`ENABLE_AVATARS`）。這些圖片是使用 "
"https://gravatar.com/ 獲得的。"

#: user/profile.rst:249
msgid "Licenses"
msgstr "授權"

#: user/profile.rst:252
msgid "API access"
msgstr "API 存取"

#: user/profile.rst:254
msgid "You can get or reset your API access token here."
msgstr "您可以在此處取得或重設 API 存取權杖。"

#: user/profile.rst:259
msgid "Audit log"
msgstr "稽核紀錄"

#: user/profile.rst:261
msgid ""
"Audit log keeps track of the actions performed with your account. It logs IP "
"address and browser for every important action with your account. The "
"critical actions also trigger a notification to a primary e-mail address."
msgstr ""
"稽核紀錄會追蹤您的帳號執行的操作。它會針對您的帳號的每個重要操作記錄 IP 位址"
"與瀏覽器資訊。關鍵操作還會觸發通知，寄送至主要電子郵件位址。"

#: user/search.rst:2
msgid "Searching"
msgstr "搜尋"

#: user/search.rst:5
msgid "Search query syntax"
msgstr "搜尋查詢語法"

#: user/search.rst:7
msgid ""
"Advanced searches support boolean operations, parentheses, field-specific "
"lookup, field operators, exact match, date values, and regular expressions. "
"The available fields depend on what kind of object is being searched."
msgstr ""
"進階搜尋支援布林運算、括號、特定欄位查詢、欄位運算子、完全相符、日期值及正規"
"表示式。可用欄位取決於搜尋的物件類型。"

#: user/search.rst:14
msgid "Boolean operators"
msgstr "布林運算子"

#: user/search.rst:16
msgid ""
"You can combine lookups using ``AND``, ``OR``, ``NOT`` and parentheses to "
"form complex queries. Boolean operators are case-insensitive, so ``and``, "
"``And`` and ``AND`` are equivalent."
msgstr ""
"您可以使用 ``AND``, ``OR``, ``NOT`` 和括號組合查詢，形成複雜的查詢語句。布林"
"運算子不區分大小寫，所以 ``and`` 、 ``And`` 和 ``AND`` 等效。"

#: user/search.rst:20
msgid ""
"The ``NOT`` operator has higher precedence than the ``AND`` operator; the "
"``AND`` operator has higher precedence than the ``OR`` operator. You can add "
"parenthesis to define a precedence of your own."
msgstr ""
"``NOT`` 運算子的優先順序高於 ``AND`` 而 ``AND`` 運算子的優先順序高於 "
"``OR`` 。您可以新增英文圓括號來定義您自己的優先順序。"

#: user/search.rst:24
msgid ""
"Omitting the operator will make the query behave like the ``AND`` operator "
"was used."
msgstr "省略運算子時，查詢會如同使用了 ``AND`` 運算子。"

#: user/search.rst:27
msgid "Equivalent expressions"
msgstr "相等表達式"

#: user/search.rst:30
msgid "Parenthesized expression to clearly show the precedence."
msgstr "加圓括號的表示式來清晰地顯示優先順序。"

#: user/search.rst:32
msgid "The ``AND`` operator has higher precedence than the ``OR`` operator."
msgstr "``AND`` 運算子的優先順序高於 ``OR``。"

#: user/search.rst:34
msgid "Query using an implicit ``AND`` operator."
msgstr "使用隱含的 ``AND`` 運算子進行查詢。"

#: user/search.rst:39
msgid "Field operators"
msgstr "欄位運算子"

#: user/search.rst:41
msgid ""
"You can specify operators, ranges or partial lookups for date or numeric "
"searches:"
msgstr "您可以為日期或數字搜尋指定運算子，範圍或部分尋找："

#: user/search.rst:45
msgid "State is ``translated`` or better (``approved``)."
msgstr "狀態是 ``translated`` 或更好 (``approved``)."

#: user/search.rst:47 user/search.rst:77
msgid "Changed between two given dates (inclusive)."
msgstr "在兩個給定的日期之間發生的變更（包括這兩個日期）。"

#: user/search.rst:49
msgid "Strings with position between 10 and 100 (inclusive)."
msgstr "位次在 10 和 100 之間（包括 10 和 100）的字串。"

#: user/search.rst:54
msgid "Searching for DATETIME fields"
msgstr "搜尋 DATETIME 欄位"

#: user/search.rst:56
msgid ""
"Timestamp searching supports multiple ways to specify the value. It supports "
"wide range of ways to specify date and time."
msgstr "時間戳搜尋支援多種方式來指定數值，也支援各種不同的日期與時間格式。"

#: user/search.rst:59
msgid "ISO 8601 formatted like :samp:`2025-09-08T12:16:55.336146+00:00`."
msgstr "ISO 8601 格式，如 :samp:`2025-09-08T12:16:55.336146+00:00`。"

#: user/search.rst:60
msgid "English written date and time like :samp:`July 4, 2013 PST`."
msgstr "英語書寫的日期和時間，如 :samp:`July 4, 2013 PST`。"

#: user/search.rst:61
msgid ""
"English adverbs of time like :samp:`yesterday`, :samp:`last month`, "
"and :samp:`2 days ago`."
msgstr ""
"英語時間副詞，如 :samp:`yesterday`、:samp:`last month` 和 :samp:`2 days "
"ago`。"

#: user/search.rst:63
msgid ""
"Whenever only the date is specified, it is always used as inclusive and "
"covers that date. Specify the exact timestamp if you need to override this "
"behavior."
msgstr ""
"每當僅明確日期時，始終以包括方式使用並涵蓋那個日期。如需覆蓋此行為，您需要明"
"確精確的時間戳。"

#: user/search.rst:69
msgid "Changed on 1st March 2019 and later (inclusive)."
msgstr "2019 年 3 月 1 日及之後變更（包含 2019 年 3 月 1 日）。"

#: user/search.rst:71
msgid "Changed 2 weeks ago from the current date and time."
msgstr "目前日期和時間 2 周前的變更。"

#: user/search.rst:73
msgid "Changed starting yesterday."
msgstr "自昨天起的變更。"

#: user/search.rst:75
msgid "Changed in the year 2019."
msgstr "2019 年的變更。"

#: user/search.rst:79
msgid "Changed between two relative dates (inclusive)."
msgstr "兩個相對日期間的變更（包括這兩個日期）。"

#: user/search.rst:82
msgid "Exact operators"
msgstr "精確運算子"

#: user/search.rst:84
msgid ""
"You can do an exact match query on different string fields using ``=`` "
"operator. For example, to search for all source strings exactly matching "
"``hello world``, use: ``source:=\"hello world\"``. For searching single word "
"expressions, you can skip quotes. For example, to search for all source "
"strings matching ``hello``, you can use: ``source:=hello``."
msgstr ""
"您可使用 ``=`` 運算子對不同字串欄位進行完全相符查詢。例如，若要搜尋完全符合 "
"``hello world`` 的所有來源字串，請使用 ``source:=\"hello world\"``。搜尋單字"
"運算式時可省略引號。例如，若要搜尋符合 ``hello`` 的所有來源字串，可使用 "
"``source:=hello``。"

#: user/search.rst:91
msgid "Regular expressions"
msgstr "正規表達式"

#: user/search.rst:93
msgid ""
"Anywhere text is accepted you can also specify a regular expression as "
"``r\"regexp\"``."
msgstr "任何已接受的內文，您也可以指定使用一般表示法如 ``r\"regexp\"`` 。"

#: user/search.rst:96
msgid ""
"For example, to search for all source strings which contain any digit "
"between 2 and 5, use ``source:r\"[2-5]\"``."
msgstr ""
"例如，要搜尋包含 2 和 5 之間的任何數字的所有來源字串，請使用 "
"``source:r\"[2-5]\"`` 。"

#: user/search.rst:101
msgid ""
"The regular expressions are evaluated by the database backend and might use "
"different extensions, please consult the database documentation for more "
"details:"
msgstr ""
"正規表示式由資料庫後端評估，所使用的擴充功能可能各不相同；詳細資訊請參閱資料"
"庫說明文件："

#: user/search.rst:105
msgid ""
"`PostgreSQL Regular Expressions Details <https://www.postgresql.org/docs/"
"current/functions-matching.html#POSIX-SYNTAX-DETAILS>`_"
msgstr ""
"`PostgreSQL 正規表達式詳細資訊 <https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/"
"functions-matching.html#POSIX-SYNTAX-DETAILS>`_"

#: user/search.rst:110
msgid "Searching for strings"
msgstr "搜尋字串"

#: user/search.rst:112
msgid "String search supports the shared query syntax above."
msgstr "字串搜尋支援上方共用的查詢語法。"

#: user/search.rst:114
msgid ""
"When no field is defined, the lookup happens on source, target, and context "
"strings."
msgstr "當沒有定義任何欄位時，尋找發生在來源、翻譯和情境字串。"

#: user/search.rst:119
msgid "Simple search"
msgstr "簡易搜尋"

#: user/search.rst:121
msgid ""
"Any phrase typed into the search box is split into words. Strings containing "
"all of them are shown. To look for an exact phrase, put \"the searchphrase\" "
"into quotes (both single (``'``) and double (``\"``) quotes will work): "
"``\"this is a quoted string\"`` or ``'another quoted string'``."
msgstr ""
"在搜尋框中輸入的任何詞句都會被分割成字詞。包含所有字詞的字串才會顯示。要精確"
"查詢詞句，請把“要搜尋的詞句”放入引號中（單引號 ``'`` 和雙引號 ``\"`` 都可"
"以）：``\"this is a quoted string\"`` 或 ``'another quoted string'``。"

#: user/search.rst:127
msgid "Fields"
msgstr "欄位"

#: user/search.rst:130
msgid "Source string case-insensitive search."
msgstr "不區分大小寫的來源字串搜尋。"

#: user/search.rst:132
msgid "Target string case-insensitive search."
msgstr "目標字串不區分大小寫的搜尋。"

#: user/search.rst:134
msgid "Context string case-insensitive search."
msgstr "情境字串不區分大小寫的搜尋。"

#: user/search.rst:136
msgid "Key string case-insensitive search."
msgstr "鍵字串不區分大小寫搜尋。"

#: user/search.rst:138
msgid "Source string description case-insensitive search."
msgstr "不區分大小寫的來源字串描述搜尋。"

#: user/search.rst:140
msgid "Location string case-insensitive search."
msgstr "位置字串不區分大小寫的搜尋。"

#: user/search.rst:142
msgid "String priority."
msgstr "字串優先順序。"

#: user/search.rst:144
msgid "String unique identifier."
msgstr "字串唯一辨識碼。"

#: user/search.rst:146
msgid "String position in the translation file."
msgstr "翻譯檔案中的字串位置。"

#: user/search.rst:148
msgid "Timestamp for when the string was added to Weblate."
msgstr "將字串新增到Weblate時的時間戳。"

#: user/search.rst:150
msgid ""
"Search for string states (``approved``, ``translated``, ``needs-editing``, "
"``needs-rewriting``, ``needs-checking``, ``empty``, ``read-only``)."
msgstr ""
"搜尋字串狀態 (``approved``, ``translated``, ``needs-editing``, ``needs-"
"rewriting``, ``needs-checking``, ``empty``, ``read-only``)。"

#: user/search.rst:152
msgid ""
"This field also supports :ref:`search-operators`, so searching for completed "
"strings can be performed as ``state:>=translated``, searching for strings "
"needing translation as ``state:<translated``."
msgstr ""
"此欄位同樣支援 :ref:`search-operators`，因此搜尋已完成字串可以作為 "
"``state:>=translated`` 執行，搜尋需要翻譯的字串可以作為 ``state:"
"<translated`` 執行。"

#: user/search.rst:154
msgid "Search for source string states, see above for more info."
msgstr "搜尋來源字串狀態，更多資訊請見上方。"

#: user/search.rst:156
msgid "String pending for flushing to VCS."
msgstr "等待寫入 VCS 的字串。"

#: user/search.rst:158
msgid ""
"Search for string having attributes - ``plural``, ``context``, "
"``suggestion``, ``comment``, ``source-comment``, ``check``, ``dismissed-"
"check``, ``translation``, ``variant``, ``screenshot``, ``flags``, "
"``explanation``, ``glossary``, ``note``, ``label``, ``location``."
msgstr ""
"搜尋有屬性的字串—— ``plural``, ``context``, ``suggestion``, ``comment``, "
"``source-comment``, ``check``, ``dismissed-check``, ``translation``, "
"``variant``, ``screenshot``, ``flags``, ``explanation``, ``glossary``, "
"``note``, ``label``, ``location``."

#: user/search.rst:160
msgid "Filters string on a condition:"
msgstr "按條件篩選字串："

#: user/search.rst:162
msgid "``read-only`` or ``readonly``"
msgstr "``read-only`` 或 ``readonly``"

#: user/search.rst:163
msgid "Read-only strings, same as ``state:read-only``."
msgstr "唯讀字串，同 ``state:read-only``。"

#: user/search.rst:165
msgid "Approved strings, same as ``state:approved``."
msgstr "已核准的字串，同 ``state:approved``。"

