#: user/translating.rst:2
msgid "Translating using Weblate"
msgstr "使用 Weblate 進行翻譯"

#: user/translating.rst:4
msgid "Thank you for your interest in translating with Weblate!"
msgstr "感謝您有興趣用 Weblate 進行翻譯！"

#: user/translating.rst:6
msgid "Generally, there are two most used modes of translation:"
msgstr "總體而言，有兩種最常用的翻譯模式："

#: user/translating.rst:8
msgid "Project accepts direct translations"
msgstr "該專案接受直接翻譯"

#: user/translating.rst:9
msgid "Project accepts the suggestions made by users."
msgstr "專案接受使用者的建議。"

#: user/translating.rst:11
msgid "Sometimes, anonymous suggestions are accepted as well."
msgstr "匿名建議有時也被接受。"

#: user/translating.rst:13
msgid "There are more translation workflows detailed in :ref:`workflows`."
msgstr "更多翻譯流程詳情見 :ref:`workflows`。"

#: user/translating.rst:15
msgid ""
"Projects, or the components in them are either visible to everyone, or only "
"to a certain group of translators."
msgstr "專案或其中的元件要麼對所有人可見，要麼只對某些翻譯者可見。"

#: user/translating.rst:26
msgid ""
"Translation projects hold related components; resources for the same "
"software, book, or project."
msgstr "翻譯專案包含相關元件；同一軟體、書籍或專案的資源。"

#: user/translating.rst:33
msgid "Translation links"
msgstr "翻譯連結"

#: user/translating.rst:35
msgid ""
"Having navigated to a component, a set of links lead to its actual "
"translation. The translation is further divided into individual checks, "
"like :guilabel:`Untranslated strings` or :guilabel:`Unfinished strings`. If "
"the whole project is already translated without any errors, :guilabel:`All "
"strings` is still available. Alternatively you can use the :doc:`Search </"
"user/search>` feature to find a specific string or term."
msgstr ""
"導覽到一個元件後，一組連結會指向它的實際翻譯。翻譯進一步分為單獨的檢查，"
"如 :guilabel:`未翻譯的字串` 或 :guilabel:`未提交的字串`。如果整個專案已被翻"
"譯，且沒有任何錯誤，:guilabel:`所有字串` 仍然可用。或者，您可以使用 :doc:`搜"
"尋 </user/search>` 功能來查詢特定的字串或術語。"

#: user/translating.rst:52
msgid "Actual permissions might vary depending on your Weblate configuration."
msgstr "實際權限可能因 Weblate 設定而異。"

#: user/translating.rst:54
msgid ""
"Anonymous users (by default) can only forward suggestions. Doing so is still "
"available to signed-in users, in cases where uncertainty about a translation "
"arises, prompting other translators to review it. Any user can clone an "
"existing suggestion into the translation fields, including plural forms, and "
"use it as the basis for a new suggestion or translation."
msgstr ""
"匿名使用者預設只能提交建議。登入的使用者若對某翻譯有疑慮，也可提交建議，請其"
"他譯者進行審閱。任何使用者都可將現有建議（包括複數形式）複製到翻譯欄位，作為"
"新的建議或翻譯基礎。"

#: user/translating.rst:60
msgid ""
"All suggestions are scanned on a daily basis to remove duplicates and those "
"matching current translations."
msgstr "會每天掃描所有建議，以刪除重複建議以及與目前翻譯相符的建議。"

#: user/translating.rst:63
msgid ""
"If you have the :guilabel:`Accept suggestions` permission, you can bulk "
"accept all suggestions from a specific user by clicking the account check "
"icon next to their suggestion. This is useful for quickly processing "
"suggestions from trusted contributors. Suggestions failing quality checks "
"are skipped and remain for manual review. Weblate shows the number of "
"matching suggestions for confirmation and processes the acceptance in the "
"background. If you can review the translation, you can accept and approve "
"the suggestions in the same step."
msgstr ""
"如果您擁有 :guilabel:`接受建議` 權限，可按下某位使用者建議旁的帳號核取圖示，"
"批次接受該使用者的所有建議。此功能適合用來快速處理來自可信任貢獻者的建議。未"
"通過品質檢查的建議會被略過，並留待人工審閱。Weblate 會顯示相符建議的數量以供"
"確認，並在背景執行接受作業。如果您可審閱翻譯，也可在同一步驟中接受並核准這些"
"建議。"

#: user/translating.rst:76
msgid "Three types of comments can be posted:"
msgstr "可以發表三類評論："

#: user/translating.rst:78
msgid "for translations"
msgstr "對於翻譯"

#: user/translating.rst:79
msgid "for source strings"
msgstr "對於來源字串"

#: user/translating.rst:80
msgid ""
"for reporting source string bugs when this functionality is turned on "
"using :ref:`project-source_review`."
msgstr ""
"報告來源字串的錯誤，前提是透過 :ref:`project-source_review` 開啟了此功能。"

#: user/translating.rst:82
msgid ""
"Choose the suitable type for the topic you want to discuss. Source string "
"comments are in any event good for providing feedback on the original "
"string, for example that it should be rephrased, or to ask questions about "
"it."
msgstr ""
"請為您想討論的主題選擇合適類型。不論任何情況，來源字串註解都很適合用來提供來"
"源字串的意見，例如建議改寫，或對內容提問。"

#: user/translating.rst:87
msgid ""
"Markdown syntax can be used in all comments, as well as mentioning other "
"users by using ``@username``. Mention a maintainer or another translator "
"when you need them to see a follow-up question; they can reply in the "
"same :guilabel:`Comments` tab."
msgstr ""
"所有註解都可以使用 Markdown 語法，也可以使用 ``@username`` 提及其他使用者。需"
"要維護者或其他翻譯者查看後續問題時，請提及對方；他們可以在同一個 :guilabel:`"
"註解` 分頁中回覆。"

#: user/translating.rst:92
msgid ""
"To find comments again, open your :ref:`user-profile`; the comment count "
"links to your comment activity. To find strings with comments by a specific "
"user, use :doc:`/user/search`. For example, ``comment_author:USERNAME`` "
"finds strings with comments by that user, and "
"``source_comment_author:USERNAME`` finds strings with source string comments "
"by that user. When you are signed in, the search filter menu also includes "
"shortcuts for comments by you and source comments by you."
msgstr ""
"若要再次尋找註解，請開啟您的 :ref:`user-profile`；註解數會連結至您的註解活"
"動。若要尋找特定使用者留下註解的字串，請使用 :doc:`/user/search`。例如，"
"``comment_author:USERNAME`` 會找出該使用者留下註解的字串，而 "
"``source_comment_author:USERNAME`` 會找出該使用者留下來源字串註解的字串。登入"
"後，搜尋過濾選單也會提供您的註解及您的來源註解捷徑。"

#: user/translating.rst:109
msgid ""
"Variants are used to group different-length variants of a string. The "
"frontend of your project can then utilize different strings depending on the "
"size of a screen or window."
msgstr ""
"變體用於對字串的不同長度變體進行分組。專案的前端可以根據螢幕或視窗大小使用不"
"同的字串。"

#: user/translating.rst:119
msgid "Labels"
msgstr "標籤"

#: user/translating.rst:121
msgid ""
"Labels are used to categorize strings within a project to further customize "
"the localization workflow (for example to define categories of strings)."
msgstr ""
"標籤用於對專案中的字串進行分類，以進一步自訂在地化工作流程（例如定義字串的類"
"別）。"

#: user/translating.rst:124
msgid "Following labels are used by Weblate:"
msgstr "Weblate 使用以下標籤："

#: user/translating.rst:127
msgid "String translated using :ref:`auto-translation`."
msgstr "字串是使用 :ref:`auto-translation` 翻譯的。"

#: user/translating.rst:128
msgid "Source needs review"
msgstr "來源需要檢閱"

#: user/translating.rst:129
msgid "String marked for review using :ref:`source-reviews`."
msgstr "使用 :ref:`source-reviews` 將字串標記為需要稽核。"

#: user/translating.rst:140
msgid ""
"On the translation page, the source string and an editing area for its "
"translation are shown. Should the translation be plural, multiple source "
"strings and editing areas are shown, each described and labeled in the "
"amount of plural forms the translated language has."
msgstr ""
"在翻譯頁面上，將顯示來源字串及其譯文的編輯區域。如果譯文是複數的，則會顯示多"
"個來源字串和編輯區域，每個來源字串和編輯區域都以翻譯語言具有的複數形式的數量"
"進行描述和標記。"

#: user/translating.rst:144
msgid ""
"All special whitespace characters are underlined in red and indicated with "
"grey symbols. More than one subsequent space is also underlined in red to "
"alert the translator to a potential formatting issue."
msgstr ""
"所有特殊空白字元都會新增紅色下劃線，並用灰色符號表示。多個接續的空格也會新增"
"紅色下劃線，以提醒譯者潛在的格式問題。"

#: user/translating.rst:148
msgid ""
"Various bits of extra info can be shown on this page, most of which coming "
"from the project source code (like context, comments or where the message is "
"being used). Translation fields for any secondary languages translators "
"select in the preferences will be shown (see :ref:`secondary-languages`) "
"above the source string."
msgstr ""
"此頁面上可以顯示各種額外資訊，其中大部分來自專案原始碼（如情境、註解或訊息的"
"使用位置）。譯者在首選項中選擇的任何第二語言的翻譯欄位都將顯示在來源字串上方"
"（參閱 :ref:`secondary-languages`）。"

#: user/translating.rst:153
msgid ""
"Below the translation, translators will find suggestions made by others, to "
"be accepted (✓), accepted with changes (✏️), bulk accepted for a specific "
"user (👤✓), cloned into the translation fields (📑) or deleted (🗑)."
msgstr ""
"在譯文下方，譯者會看到他人的建議，可進行的操作有接受（✓）、接受但進行修改"
"（✏️）、批次接受特定使用者的建議（👤✓）、複製到翻譯框內（📑）或刪除 （🗑）。"

#: user/translating.rst:160
msgid "Translating special text safely"
msgstr "安全地翻譯特殊文字"

#: user/translating.rst:162
msgid ""
"Some source strings contain text that the application interprets at runtime. "
"Translate the human-readable parts, but keep technical markers intact unless "
"the project instructions say otherwise."
msgstr ""
"部分來源字串包含應用程式會在執行階段解讀的文字。請翻譯一般使用者可閱讀的部"
"分，但除非專案說明另有說明，否則應完整保留技術標記。"

#: user/translating.rst:166
msgid "Placeholders and format strings"
msgstr "預留位置及格式字串"

#: user/translating.rst:167
msgid ""
"Keep variables such as ``%s``, ``%1$d``, ``%(name)s``, ``{count}``, "
"``{{ value }}``, or similar markers in the translation. Named placeholders "
"describe the inserted value, but the names themselves are not translated. "
"You can usually reorder numbered or named placeholders to fit the target "
"language. Use the placeable copy shortcuts to insert them without typing "
"mistakes."
msgstr ""
"請在翻譯中保留 ``%s``、``%1$d``、``%(name)s``、``{count}``、``{{ value }}`` "
"等變數或類似標記。具名預留位置會說明插入的值，但名稱本身不應翻譯。通常可以重"
"新排列編號或具名預留位置，使其符合目標語言。請使用可置入項目的複製捷徑插入，"
"以免輸入錯誤。"

#: user/translating.rst:173
msgid "Markup"
msgstr "標記"

#: user/translating.rst:174
msgid ""
"Keep HTML and XML tags, tag names, and attribute names unchanged. Translate "
"the visible text between tags and any attribute value that is meant for "
"users, for example alternative text or a tooltip, when it appears as part of "
"the translatable string. Make sure opening and closing tags still match "
"after reordering the sentence."
msgstr ""
"請保持 HTML 及 XML 標籤、標籤名稱及屬性名稱不變。請翻譯標籤之間可見的文字，以"
"及翻譯字串中供使用者閱讀的屬性值，例如替代文字或工具提示。重新排列句子後，請"
"確認開始與結束標籤仍然相符。"

#: user/translating.rst:179
msgid "Program syntax"
msgstr "程式語法"

#: user/translating.rst:180
msgid ""
"Leave function names, commands, environment variables, spreadsheet "
"functions, SQL keywords, and similar program syntax untranslated unless the "
"project explicitly documents a localized form."
msgstr ""
"除非專案明確記載在地化形式，否則函式名稱、指令、環境變數、試算表函式、SQL 關"
"鍵字及類似程式語法應保持不翻譯。"

#: user/translating.rst:183
msgid "Punctuation and whitespace"
msgstr "標點符號與空格"

#: user/translating.rst:184
msgid ""
"Preserve punctuation and spaces that affect the interface, such as trailing "
"colons, ellipses, leading or trailing spaces, and punctuation next to "
"placeholders. Follow the target language's typography when it differs from "
"the source, and use comments when a source punctuation choice looks wrong."
msgstr ""
"請保留會影響介面的標點及空格，例如結尾冒號、省略符號、開頭或結尾空格，以及預"
"留位置旁的標點。目標語言的排版與來源不同時，請遵循目標語言排版；若來源標點看"
"似有誤，請使用註解反映。"

#: user/translating.rst:189
msgid "Accelerators"
msgstr "加速器"

#: user/translating.rst:190
msgid ""
"Menu labels can mark keyboard accelerators with characters such as ``&``, "
"``_``, or ``~``. When the source has an accelerator, keep one in the "
"translation. Choose a readable key in the translated label and avoid obvious "
"conflicts with nearby menu items or buttons."
msgstr ""
"選單標籤可使用 ``&``、``_`` 或 ``~`` 等字元標示鍵盤快速鍵。來源含有快速鍵時，"
"翻譯也應保留 1 個。請在翻譯後的標籤中選取容易辨識的按鍵，並避免與鄰近選單項目"
"或按鈕發生明顯衝突。"

#: user/translating.rst:194
msgid "Plural forms"
msgstr "複數形式"

#: user/translating.rst:195
msgid ""
"Translate each plural field Weblate shows. Do not combine forms into a "
"single construction such as ``file(s)`` unless that is correct for the "
"target language and project. If the source string uses an ambiguous plural, "
"report it with a source string comment or review."
msgstr ""
"請翻譯 Weblate 顯示的每個複數欄位。除非這種寫法符合目標語言及專案規範，否則請"
"勿將各形式合併為 ``file(s)`` 之類的單一寫法。若來源字串使用語意不明的複數形"
"式，請透過來源字串註解或審閱加以回報。"

#: user/translating.rst:200
msgid ""
"Weblate quality checks catch many technical mistakes in placeholders, "
"markup, punctuation, whitespace, and plural forms. They do not replace "
"translator judgment, so use :ref:`source-context`, :doc:`/user/glossary`, "
"and :ref:`user-comments` when the source text needs clarification."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 品質檢查可以找出許多預留位置、標記、標點、空白及複數形式的技術錯誤，"
"但不能取代翻譯者的判斷。因此，來源文字需要釐清時，請使用 :ref:`source-"
"context`、:doc:`/user/glossary` 及 :ref:`user-comments`。"

#: user/translating.rst:215
msgid "Plurals"
msgstr "複數"

#: user/translating.rst:217
msgid ""
"Words changing form to account for their numeric designation are called "
"plurals. Each language has its own definition of them. English, for example, "
"supports one. In the singular definition of an example \"car\", implicitly "
"one car is referenced, in the plural definition of \"cars\", two or more "
"cars are referenced (or the concept of cars as a noun). Languages like, for "
"example, Czech or Arabic have more forms of plurals, and their rules for "
"plurals are different as well."
msgstr ""
"為了表示數量而改變形態的字詞稱為複數，每種語言的定義都不相同。例如英文支援一"
"種複數形式：範例「car」的單數形式隱含指一輛車；複數形式「cars」則指兩輛以上的"
"車（或作為名詞的車輛概念）。捷克文或阿拉伯文等語言擁有更多複數形式，複數規則"
"也不相同。"

#: user/translating.rst:224
msgid ""
"Weblate has full support for each of these forms, in each respective "
"language. Each grammatical number is translated in a separate field for a "
"pre-defined set of cardinal numbers specific to the translation language. "
"The number of fields and how they are in turn used in the translated "
"application or project, depends on the configured plural formula. Weblate "
"shows the basic information and the `Language Plural Rules`_ by the Unicode "
"Consortium is a more detailed description."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 完整支援各語言的每種形式。每種文法數都會根據翻譯語言特定的預設基數集"
"合，在個別欄位中翻譯。欄位數量及它們在翻譯後的應用程式或專案中如何使用，取決"
"於設定的複數公式。Weblate 會顯示基本資訊；Unicode 聯盟的 `Language Plural "
"Rules`_ 則提供更詳細的說明。"

#: user/translating.rst:243
msgid "Alternative translations"
msgstr "替代翻譯"

#: user/translating.rst:249
msgid "This is currently only supported with :ref:`multivalue-csv`."
msgstr "目前只有 :ref:`multivalue-csv` 支援。"

#: user/translating.rst:251
msgid ""
"With some formats, it is possible to have more translations for a single "
"string. You can add more alternative translations using "
"the :guilabel:`Tools` menu. Any blank alternative translations will be "
"automatically removed upon saving."
msgstr ""
"對於某些格式，單條字串可以有多種翻譯。您可以使用 :guilabel:`工具` 選單新增更"
"多替代翻譯。儲存後將自動刪除任何空白的替代翻譯。"

