"Weblate also stores the host key fingerprint upon first connection, and "
"fails to connect to the host should it be changed later (see :ref:`verify-"
"ssh`)."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 還會在首次連線時儲存主機金鑰指紋，並且在以後進行變更時將無法連線到主"
"機（請參閱 :ref:`verify-ssh`）。"

