msgid ""
"Weblate expects you to have accepted the certificate up-front (and your "
"credentials if needed). It will look to insert them into "
"the :setting:`DATA_DIR` directory. Accept the certificate by using `svn` "
"once with the `$HOME` environment variable set to the :setting:`DATA_DIR`:"
msgstr ""
"Weblate 預期您已事先接受憑證（必要時也包括認證資訊），並會嘗試將它們加"
"入 :setting:`DATA_DIR` 目錄。請將 `$HOME` 環境變數設為 :setting:`DATA_DIR`，"
"再執行一次 `svn` 以接受憑證："

#: vcs.rst:463
msgid "Local files"
msgstr "本機檔案"

#: vcs.rst:467
msgid ""
"Underneath, this uses :ref:`vcs-git`. It requires Git installed and allows "
"you to switch to using Git natively with full history of your translations."
msgstr ""
"下面，它使用 :ref:`vcs-git`。它需要安裝 Git，並允許您切換到本機使用 Git，並提"
"供完整的翻譯歷史記錄。"

#: vcs.rst:470
msgid ""
"Weblate can also operate without a remote VCS. The initial translations are "
"imported by uploading them. Later you can replace individual files by file "
"upload, or add translation strings directly from Weblate (currently "
"available only for monolingual translations)."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 也可以在沒有遠端 VCS 的情況下執行。透過上傳匯入初始翻譯。稍後您可以通"
"過上傳取代個別檔案，或從 Weblate 直接新增翻譯字串 （目前僅對單語言翻譯可"
"用）。"

#: vcs.rst:475
msgid ""
"In the background Weblate creates a Git repository for you and all changes "
"are tracked in. In case you later decide to use a VCS to store the "
"translations, you already have a repository within Weblate can base your "
"integration on."
msgstr ""
"Weblate 在背景為您建立 Git 儲存庫並追蹤所有變更。如果您之後決定使用 VCS 儲存"
"翻譯，其內建儲存庫可作為整合基礎。"

