#: wlc.rst:48
msgid ""
"The Docker container uses Weblate Client defaults and connects to the API "
"deployed on localhost. Configure the API URL and API key using the "
"normal :program:`wlc` arguments or environment variables, for "
"example :option:`--url`, :option:`--key`, :envvar:`WLC_URL`, "
"and :envvar:`WLC_KEY`. API keys are rejected over non-local ``http://`` URLs "
"by default; use HTTPS, loopback HTTP for local development, or explicitly "
"opt in to insecure HTTP."
msgstr ""
"Docker 容器會使用 Weblate Client 預設值，並連線至部署在 localhost 的 API。請"
"使用一般的 :program:`wlc` 引數或環境變數設定 API URL 及 API 金鑰，例"
"如 :option:`--url`、:option:`--key`、:envvar:`WLC_URL` 及 :envvar:`WLC_KEY`。"
"預設會拒絕透過非本機 ``http://`` URL 傳送 API 金鑰；請使用 HTTPS、本機開發用"
"的 Loopback HTTP，或明確選擇允許不安全的 HTTP。"

