msgid ""
"You might want to pass your :ref:`wlc-config` to the Docker container. When "
"your repository contains a project configuration such as :file:`.weblate`, "
"the easiest approach is to add your current directory as the :file:`/home/"
"weblate` volume:"
msgstr ""
"您可能希望將 :ref:`wlc-config` 傳遞給 Docker 容器。儲存庫包含專案設定，"
"如 :file:`.weblate` 時，最簡單的方法是將目前目錄新增為 :file:`/home/weblate` "
"磁碟區："

#: wlc.rst:76
msgid ""
"When the mounted repository provides the API URL in project configuration "
"and you pass an unscoped API key to the container, also pin the URL "
"explicitly: :envvar:`WLC_KEY` requires :envvar:`WLC_URL`, and :option:`--"
"key` requires :option:`--url`."
msgstr ""
"當掛載的儲存庫在專案設定中提供 API URL，而您將未限定範圍的 API 金鑰傳入容器"
"時，也必須明確固定 URL：:envvar:`WLC_KEY` 需要搭"
"配 :envvar:`WLC_URL`，:option:`--key` 則需要搭配 :option:`--url`。"

#: wlc.rst:81
msgid ""
"If the configured API URL uses non-local ``http://`` and an API key is "
"provided, the container refuses to send the key unless insecure HTTP is "
"explicitly enabled. Prefer HTTPS; for legacy deployments, pass :option:`--"
"allow-insecure-http` or set :envvar:`WLC_ALLOW_INSECURE_HTTP`."
msgstr ""
"若已設定的 API URL 使用非本機 ``http://``，且提供了 API 金鑰，除非明確啟用不"
"安全的 HTTP，否則容器會拒絕傳送金鑰。請優先使用 HTTPS；舊版部署環境可傳"
"入 :option:`--allow-insecure-http` 或設定 :envvar:`WLC_ALLOW_INSECURE_HTTP`。"

