"上。"

#: wlc.rst:158
msgid "Arguments"
msgstr "引數"

#: wlc.rst:160
msgid ""
"The program accepts the following arguments which define output format or "
"which Weblate instance to use. These must be entered before any command."
msgstr ""
"程式接受以下參數來定義輸出格式或使用哪個Weblate執行個體。這些參數必須位於任何"
"指令之前。"

#: wlc.rst:165
msgid "Specify the output format."
msgstr "指定輸出格式。"

#: wlc.rst:169
msgid ""
"Specify the API URL. Overrides any value found in the configuration file, "
"see :ref:`wlc-config`. The URL should end with ``/api/``, for example "
"``https://hosted.weblate.org/api/``."
msgstr ""
"指定 API URL。覆寫在設定檔案中找到的任何值，請參閱 :ref:`wlc-config`。該 URL "
"應以 ``/api/`` 結尾，例如 ``https://hosted.weblate.org/api/``。"

#: wlc.rst:174
msgid ""
"Specify the API user key to use. Overrides any value found in the "
"configuration file, see :ref:`wlc-config`. You can find your key in your "
"profile on Weblate. When the API URL is loaded from automatically discovered "
"project configuration, :option:`--key` must be used together with :option:`--"
"url`. API keys are rejected over non-local ``http://`` URLs by default."
msgstr ""
"指定要使用的 API 使用者金鑰。這會覆寫設定檔中的任何值；請參閱 :ref:`wlc-"
"config`。您可在 Weblate 的個人資料中找到金鑰。API URL 從自動探查的專案設定載"
"入時，:option:`--key` 必須與 :option:`--url` 一併使用。預設會拒絕透過非本機 "
"``http://`` URL 傳送 API 金鑰。"

#: wlc.rst:182
msgid ""
"Allow sending API keys over non-local ``http://`` URLs. Prefer HTTPS or "
"loopback HTTP instead; this option is intended only for legacy deployments "
"where HTTPS is not available. This option only enables insecure HTTP for the "
"current run; omitting it does not disable ``allow_insecure_http`` from "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"允許透過非本機 ``http://`` URL 傳送 API 金鑰。請優先改用 HTTPS 或 Loopback "
"HTTP；此選項僅供無法使用 HTTPS 的舊版部署環境使用。此選項只會為目前這次執行啟"
"用不安全的 HTTP；省略此選項不會停用設定中的 ``allow_insecure_http``。"

#: wlc.rst:190
msgid ""
"Load configuration only from ``PATH`` instead of the discovered global and "
"project configuration files, see :ref:`wlc-config`."
msgstr ""
"只從 ``PATH`` 而不是從發現的全域和專案設定檔案載入設定，見 :ref:`wlc-"
"config`。"

#: wlc.rst:195
msgid "Overrides configuration file section in use, see :ref:`wlc-config`."
msgstr "覆寫使用中的設定檔案部分，請參閱 :ref:`wlc-config`。"

