msgstr ""
"傳給 ``urllib3`` 的選用 HTTP 重試及逾時設定。使用 ``allowed_methods`` 列出可"
"重試的要求方法。目前的 :program:`wlc` 發行版本使用此設定名稱，取代較舊的 "
"``method_whitelist`` 選項。"

#: wlc.rst:392
msgid "The configuration file is an INI file, for example:"
msgstr "設定檔案是個 INI 檔案，例如："

#: wlc.rst:406
msgid "The API keys are stored in the ``[keys]`` section:"
msgstr "API 金鑰儲存在 ``[keys]`` 部分中："

#: wlc.rst:413
msgid ""
"This allows you to store keys in your personal settings, while using "
"the :file:`.weblate` configuration in the VCS repository so "
"that :program:`wlc` knows which server it should talk to. The ``[keys]`` "
"lookup is scoped to the exact API URL."
msgstr ""
"這樣，您就可以在版本控制系統儲存庫中使用 :file:`.weblate` 設定時，將金鑰儲存"
