"範圍限定於精確的 API URL。"

#: wlc.rst:418
msgid ""
"In CI, unscoped keys must pin the API URL explicitly: set "
"both :envvar:`WLC_URL` and :envvar:`WLC_KEY`, or use :option:`--url` "
"together with :option:`--key`."
msgstr ""
"在 CI 中，未限定範圍的金鑰必須明確固定 API URL：同時設定 :envvar:`WLC_URL` "
"及 :envvar:`WLC_KEY`，或將 :option:`--url` 與 :option:`--key` 搭配使用。"

#: wlc.rst:424
msgid "Environment variables"
msgstr "環境變數"

#: wlc.rst:430
msgid ""
"Unscoped API keys require an explicit API URL when project configuration is "
"discovered automatically. API keys are rejected over non-local ``http://`` "
"URLs unless insecure HTTP is explicitly enabled."
msgstr ""
"自動探索專案設定時，未限定範圍的 API 金鑰需要明確指定 API URL。除非明確啟用不"
"安全的 HTTP，否則會拒絕透過非本機 ``http://`` URL 傳送 API 金鑰。"

#: wlc.rst:434
msgid ""
"The API URL and key can also be configured using environment variables. This "
"is especially useful for CI workflows where :envvar:`WLC_URL` pins the "
"destination and :envvar:`WLC_KEY` is injected as a secret:"
msgstr ""
"API URL 及金鑰也可使用環境變數設定。這對 CI 工作流程特別有用，其"
"中 :envvar:`WLC_URL` 會鎖定目的地，:envvar:`WLC_KEY` 則以機密資料注入："

#: wlc.rst:444
msgid ""
"API key. When the API URL would otherwise come from automatically discovered "
"project configuration, :envvar:`WLC_KEY` is accepted only together "
"with :envvar:`WLC_URL`. API keys are rejected over non-local ``http://`` "
"URLs by default."
msgstr ""
"API 金鑰。若 API URL 原本會來自自動探索的專案設定，只有同時提"
"供 :envvar:`WLC_URL` 時，才會接受 :envvar:`WLC_KEY`。預設會拒絕透過非本機 "
"``http://`` URL 傳送 API 金鑰。"

#: wlc.rst:451
msgid ""
"Set to ``1``, ``true``, ``yes``, or ``on`` to allow API keys over non-local "
"``http://`` URLs. Prefer HTTPS or loopback HTTP instead. Other values, such "
"as ``0`` or ``false``, are treated as unset and do not disable "
"``allow_insecure_http`` from configuration."
msgstr ""
"設為 ``1``、``true``、``yes`` 或 ``on``，即可允許透過非本機 ``http://`` URL "
"傳送 API 金鑰。請優先改用 HTTPS 或 Loopback HTTP。``0`` 或 ``false`` 等其他值"
"會視為未設定，且不會停用設定中的 ``allow_insecure_http``。"

#: wlc.rst:456
msgid ""
"The same protection applies to command-line arguments: :option:`--key` is "
"accepted with automatically discovered project configuration only "
"when :option:`--url` is provided."
msgstr ""
"同一項保護也適用於指令列引數：自動探索專案設定時，只有提供 :option:`--url` 才"
"會接受 :option:`--key`。"

#: wlc.rst:460
msgid "The API URL and key configuration precedence (highest to lowest) is:"
msgstr "API URL 及金鑰的設定優先順序如下（由高至低）："

#: wlc.rst:462
msgid "Command-line arguments (:option:`--url`, :option:`--key`)."
msgstr "指令列引數 （:option:`--url`、:option:`--key`）。"

#: wlc.rst:463
msgid "Environment variables (:envvar:`WLC_URL`, :envvar:`WLC_KEY`)."
msgstr "環境變數 （:envvar:`WLC_URL`、:envvar:`WLC_KEY`）。"

#: wlc.rst:464
msgid ""
"Configuration loaded from :option:`--config`, or from the discovered global "
"configuration plus the nearest project configuration when :option:`--config` "
"is not used."
msgstr ""
"從 :option:`--config` 載入的設定；未使用 :option:`--config` 時，則為探查到的"
"全域設定及最接近的專案設定。"

#: wlc.rst:468
msgid ""
"The insecure HTTP opt-in is enable-only rather than a normal precedence "
"setting. It is enabled when :option:`--allow-insecure-http` is passed, "
"when :envvar:`WLC_ALLOW_INSECURE_HTTP` has a true value, or when "
"``allow_insecure_http`` is enabled in trusted configuration. Automatically "
"discovered project configuration cannot enable it; set it in user "
"configuration or pass an explicit :option:`--config` file instead."
msgstr ""
"選擇允許不安全 HTTP 的設定只能用來啟用功能，並非一般的優先順序設定。傳"
"入 :option:`--allow-insecure-http`、:envvar:`WLC_ALLOW_INSECURE_HTTP` 為 "
"true 值，或受信任設定中的 ``allow_insecure_http`` 已啟用時，便會啟用此功能。"
"自動探索的專案設定無法啟用此功能；請改在使用者設定中設定，或傳入明確指定"
"的 :option:`--config` 檔案。"

#: wlc.rst:476
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "範例"

#: wlc.rst:478
msgid "Print current program version:"
msgstr "列印目前程式版本："

#: wlc.rst:485
msgid "List all projects:"
msgstr "列出所有專案："

#: wlc.rst:496
msgid "Upload translation file:"
msgstr "上傳翻譯檔案："

#: wlc.rst:502
msgid "You can also designate what project :program:`wlc` should work on:"
msgstr "您還可以指定 :program:`wlc` 應該從事的專案："

#: wlc.rst:530
msgid ""
"With this setup it is easy to commit pending changes in the current project:"
msgstr "通過此設定，可以輕鬆地提交目前專案中待定的變更："

#: workflows.rst:4
msgid "Translation workflows"
msgstr "翻譯工作流程"

#: workflows.rst:6
msgid ""
"Using Weblate raises quality, reduces manual work, and brings everyone "
"involved in the localization process closer to each other. It is up to you "
"to decide how many of Weblate features you want to make use of."
msgstr ""
"使用 Weblate 提升品質、減少人工作業並讓參與到在地化過程中的每個人更靠近彼此。"
"要使用多少 Weblate 功能的決定權在您。"

#: workflows.rst:10
msgid ""
"The following is not a complete list of ways to configure Weblate. You can "
"base other workflows on the examples listed here."
msgstr ""
"以下不是設定 Weblate 方法的完整清單。您可以此處列出的範例為基礎制定其他工作流"
"程。"

#: workflows.rst:16
msgid "Workflow customization"
msgstr "工作流程自訂"

#: workflows.rst:18
msgid ""
"In addition to configuration at :ref:`project` and :ref:`component` "
"(as :ref:`project-translation_review`, :ref:`component-"
"enable_suggestions`, :ref:`component-suggestion_voting`, and :ref:`component-"
"suggestion_autoaccept`), the translation workflow can be customized per "
"language."
msgstr ""
"您可以在 :ref:`project` 和 :ref:`component` 層級設定各種選項"
"（如 :ref:`project-translation_review`、:ref:`component-"
"enable_suggestions`、:ref:`component-suggestion_voting` 和 :ref:`component-"
"suggestion_autoaccept`），也可以自訂每種語言的翻譯工作流程。"

#: workflows.rst:24
msgid ""
"Site-wide workflow customization can be done while :ref:`changing-languages`."
msgstr "可以在 :ref:`changing-languages` 時自訂網站層級的工作流程。"

#: workflows.rst:26
msgid ""
"Per-project customization can be done on each language page of the project."
msgstr "可以在專案的每個語言頁面內完成不同專案的自訂。"

#: workflows.rst:28
msgid ""
"All workflow settings can be overridden, the only limitation is "
"that :ref:`project-translation_review` needs to be turned on and can only be "
"disabled in the per-language customization."
msgstr ""
"所有的工作流程均可被覆蓋，唯一的限制是需要開啟 :ref:`project-"
"translation_review`，且只能在每種語言的自訂中停用它。"

#: workflows.rst:32
msgid "The first existing setting applies:"
msgstr "首個現有設定適用於："

#: workflows.rst:34
msgid "Project-language customization"
msgstr "專案語言自訂"

#: workflows.rst:35
msgid "Language customization"
msgstr "語言自訂"

#: workflows.rst:36
msgid "The project/component settings"
msgstr "專案/元件設定"

#: workflows.rst:40
msgid ""
"Please be careful when using site-wide override as that applies to all "
"projects (unless they have own overrides for a given language)."
msgstr ""
"請小心使用網站級覆蓋，因其會應用到所有專案（除非專案自身為給定語言設定了覆"
"蓋）。"

#: workflows.rst:45
msgid "Translation access"
msgstr "翻譯存取"

#: workflows.rst:47
msgid ""
"The :ref:`access control <access-control>` is not discussed in detail as a "
"whole in the workflows, as most of its options can be applied to any "
"workflow. Please consult the respective documentation on how to manage "
"access to translations."
msgstr ""
":ref:`存取控制 <access-control>` 並沒有作為一個整體在工作流程中被詳細討論，因"
"它的大多數選項都可以應用於任何工作流。請參考有關如何管理對翻譯的存取的相關文"
"件。"

#: workflows.rst:52
msgid ""
"In the following chapters, *any user* means a user who has access to the "
"translation. It can be any authenticated user if the project is public, or a "
"user with :guilabel:`Translate` permission to the project."
msgstr ""
"在以下各章中，*任何使用者* 是指有權存取翻譯的使用者。如果專案是公開的，則可以"
"是任何經過身分驗證的使用者，或者是對專案有 :guilabel:`翻譯` 權限的使用者。"

#: workflows.rst:61
msgid "Each translated string can be in one of the following states:"
msgstr "每個已翻譯的字串可以處於以下狀態之一："

#: workflows.rst:63
msgid "Untranslated"
msgstr "未翻譯"

#: workflows.rst:64
msgid ""
"Translation is empty, it might or not be stored in the file, depending on "
"the file format."
msgstr "翻譯是空的，取決於檔案格式，翻譯是否可能儲存在檔案中。"

#: workflows.rst:67
msgid ""
"Translation needs editing, this is usually the result of fuzzy matching or "
"translator action. Depending on the file format it might be marked as "
"needing edit (for example as it gets a ``fuzzy`` flag in the gettext file)."
msgstr ""
"翻譯需要編輯，這通常是模糊相符或譯者操作的結果。根據檔案格式不同，它可能被標"
"記為需要編輯（例如，當它在 gettext 檔案中獲得一個 ``fuzzy`` 標記）。"

#: workflows.rst:69
msgid "Needs rewriting"
msgstr "需要重寫"

#: workflows.rst:70
msgid "Translation needs to be rewritten because of a source string change."
msgstr "因來源字串變更需要重寫翻譯。"

#: workflows.rst:71
msgid "Needs checking"
msgstr "需要檢查"

#: workflows.rst:72
msgid ""
"State used for source/template strings that need developer review. It is "
"typically set for new source strings imported from the VCS when the Source "
"edit addon is enabled, or when a source string is reported for checking."
msgstr ""
"用於需要開發者稽核的源/範本字串的狀態。通常在啟用原文編輯附加元件或者在來源字"
"串被報告需要檢查時對從 VCS 匯入的新的來源字串設定。"

#: workflows.rst:76
msgid "Translated / Waiting for review"
msgstr "已翻譯/待稽核"

#: workflows.rst:77
msgid ""
"Translation is made. The translated state is shown as \"Waiting for review\" "
"if reviews are enabled."
msgstr "進行了翻譯。如果啟用了稽核則翻譯狀態顯示為“等待稽核”。"

#: workflows.rst:79
msgid ""
"Translation has been approved in the review. It can no longer be changed by "
"translators, but only by reviewers. Translators can only add suggestions to "
"it."
msgstr ""
"翻譯已在檢閱中得到批准。翻譯者不能再變更它，只能由檢閱者變更。譯者只能向其中"
"新增建議。"

#: workflows.rst:83
msgid "This state is only available when reviews are enabled."
msgstr "此狀態僅在啟用稽核時可用。"

#: workflows.rst:84
msgid "Read-only"
msgstr "唯讀"

#: workflows.rst:85
msgid ""
"String is read-only as a result of having ``read-only`` :ref:`flag <custom-"
"checks>`, being a non-editable source string, or marked such in the "
"translation file."
msgstr ""
"字串唯讀的原因包括有 ``read-only`` :ref:`標記 <custom-checks>`、是不可編輯的"
"來源字串，或者在翻譯檔案中被標為唯讀。"

#: workflows.rst:89
msgid "Suggestions are stored in Weblate only and not in the translation file."
msgstr "建議僅儲存在 Weblate 中，而不儲存在翻譯檔案中。"

#: workflows.rst:91
msgid "The states are represented in the translation files when possible."
msgstr "狀態在可能的情況下會呈現在翻譯檔案中。"

#: workflows.rst:95
msgid ""
"If the file format you use does not support storing states, you might want "
"to use the :ref:`addon-weblate.flags.same_edit` add-on to flag unchanged "
"strings as needing rewriting."
msgstr ""
"如果您使用的檔案格式不支援儲存狀態，您可能需要使用 :ref:`addon-"
"weblate.flags.same_edit` 附加元件將未變更的字串標記為需要重寫。"

#: workflows.rst:101
msgid ""
"The :ref:`project-commit_policy` determines which translation states are "
"stored in the file."
msgstr "新增 :ref:`project-commit_policy` 確定在檔案中儲存哪些翻譯狀態。"

#: workflows.rst:110
msgid "Direct translation"
msgstr "直接翻譯"

#: workflows.rst:111
msgid ""
"The most common setup for smaller teams, where anybody can translate "
"directly. This is also the default setup in Weblate."
msgstr ""
"這是小型團隊最常用的設定，其中的任何人都可以直接翻譯。這也是 Weblate 的預設設"
"定。"

#: workflows.rst:114
msgid "*Any user* can edit translations."
msgstr "*任何使用者* 都可以編輯翻譯。"

#: workflows.rst:115
msgid ""
"Suggestions are optional ways to suggest changes, when translators are not "
"sure about the change."
msgstr "當翻譯者不確定變更時，建議是建議變更的選用方法。"

#: workflows.rst:119 workflows.rst:151 workflows.rst:184
msgid "Setting"
msgstr "設定"

#: workflows.rst:119 workflows.rst:151 workflows.rst:184
msgid "Note"
msgstr "備註"

#: workflows.rst:121 workflows.rst:126 workflows.rst:153 workflows.rst:191
msgid "off"
msgstr "關閉"

#: workflows.rst:121 workflows.rst:153 workflows.rst:186
msgid "Configured at project level."
msgstr "已在專案層級中設定。"

#: workflows.rst:123 workflows.rst:155 workflows.rst:157 workflows.rst:186
#: workflows.rst:188
msgid "on"
msgstr "開啟"

#: workflows.rst:123 workflows.rst:188
msgid "Useful for users to be able to suggest when they are not sure."
msgstr "讓使用者能在不確定時提出建議會很有幫助。"

#: workflows.rst:130 workflows.rst:162 workflows.rst:195
msgid "Translators group"
msgstr "翻譯群組"

#: workflows.rst:130 workflows.rst:162 workflows.rst:195
msgid "Or `Translate` with :ref:`per-project access control <manage-acl>`."
msgstr "或者透過 :ref:`每個專案的存取控制 <manage-acl>` 進行 `翻譯`。"

#: workflows.rst:134 workflows.rst:166 workflows.rst:199
msgid "Reviewers group"
msgstr "檢閱者群組"

#: workflows.rst:134 workflows.rst:166
msgid "N/A"
msgstr "N/A"

#: workflows.rst:134
msgid "Not used."
msgstr "尚未使用。"

#: workflows.rst:141
msgid "Peer review"
msgstr "同行評審"

#: workflows.rst:143
msgid ""
"With this workflow, anybody can add a suggestion, which needs approval from "
"additional members before it is accepted as a translation."
msgstr ""
"使用此流程，任何人都可以新增建議，但需要其他多名成員的核準才能被接受為翻譯。"

#: workflows.rst:146
msgid "*Any user* can add suggestions."
msgstr "*任何使用者* 都可以新增建議。"

#: workflows.rst:147
msgid "*Any user* can vote for suggestions."
msgstr "*任何使用者* 都可以對建議投票。"

#: workflows.rst:148
msgid ""
"Suggestions become translations when given a predetermined number of votes."
msgstr "當給定預定數量的投票時，建議就變成翻譯。"

#: workflows.rst:159
msgid "You can set higher value to require more peer reviews."
msgstr "您可以設定較高的值，以要求更多同儕審查。"

#: workflows.rst:166
msgid "Not used, all translators review."
msgstr "未使用，所有翻譯員都檢閱。"

#: workflows.rst:172
msgid "Dedicated reviewers"
msgstr "專門的檢閱者"

#: workflows.rst:174
msgid ""
"With dedicated reviewers you have two groups of users, one able to submit "
"translations, and one able to review them to ensure translations are "
"consistent and that the quality is good."
msgstr ""
"啟用專門的檢閱者後，您會有兩組使用者：一組可以提交翻譯；而另一組可以檢閱翻"
"譯，以確保翻譯一致且品質良好。"

#: workflows.rst:178
msgid "*Any user* can edit unapproved translations."
msgstr "*任何使用者* 都可以編輯未批准的翻譯。"

#: workflows.rst:179
msgid "*Reviewer* can approve / unapprove strings."
msgstr "*檢閱者* 能核可或不核可翻譯字串。"

#: workflows.rst:180
msgid "*Reviewer* can edit all translations (including approved ones)."
msgstr "*檢閱者* 可以編輯所有翻譯（包括批准的翻譯）。"

#: workflows.rst:181
msgid "Suggestions can also be used to suggest changes for approved strings."
msgstr "建議還可以用於建議變更已批准的字串。"

#: workflows.rst:199
msgid "Or `Review` with :ref:`per-project access control <manage-acl>`."
msgstr ""
"或使用 :ref:`per-project access control <manage-acl>` 的權限進行 `審查`。"

#: workflows.rst:205
msgid "Turning on reviews"
msgstr "開啟檢閱"

#: workflows.rst:207
msgid ""
"Reviews can be turned on in the project configuration, from "
"the :guilabel:`Workflow` subpage of project settings (to be found in "
"the :guilabel:`Operations` → :guilabel:`Settings` menu):"
msgstr ""
"可以在專案設定的 :guilabel:`工作流` 子頁面中的專案設定中開啟稽核（位"
"於 :guilabel:`操作` → :guilabel:`設定` 選單中）："

#: workflows.rst:214
msgid "Per-language reviews"
msgstr "每種語言的稽核"

#: workflows.rst:216
msgid ""
"To require review only for selected languages, first turn on :ref:`project-"
"translation_review` for the whole project. Then open each project language "
"page that should use different behavior, enable :guilabel:`Customize "
"translation workflow for this language in this project`, and "
"turn :guilabel:`Enable reviews` off for languages that should not require "
"review."
msgstr ""
"若只要求選取的語言接受審閱，請先為整個專案開啟 :ref:`project-"
"translation_review`。接著開啟每個需要不同作法的專案語言頁面、啟用 :guilabel:`"
"在此專案中自訂此語言的翻譯工作流程`，再為不需要審閱的語言關閉 :guilabel:`啟用"
"審閱`。"

#: workflows.rst:223
msgid ""
"Reviewers also need review access for the same language. Add them to a team "
"whose roles include :guilabel:`Review strings`, and limit that team or the "
"user membership to the language they should review. See :ref:`manage-acl` "
"and :ref:`custom-acl` for language-scoped access setup."
msgstr ""
"審閱者也必須具備相同語言的審閱存取權。請將其加入角色包含 :guilabel:`審閱字串"
"` 的團隊，並將該團隊或使用者成員資格限制為應審閱的語言。如需設定語言範圍存取"
"權，請參閱 :ref:`manage-acl` 及 :ref:`custom-acl`。"

#: workflows.rst:228
msgid ""
"If approval buttons are not visible, check both parts of the setup: reviews "
"have to be enabled for that translation, and the signed-in user has to have "
"review permission for that language."
msgstr ""
"若看不到核准按鈕，請檢查兩項設定：該翻譯必須啟用審閱，且已登入的使用者必須具"
"備該語言的審閱權限。"

#: workflows.rst:235
msgid "Quality gateway for the source strings"
msgstr "來源字串的品質閘道"

#: workflows.rst:237
msgid ""
"The original source language strings usually come from developers, since "
"they write the code and provide the initial strings. However, developers are "
"often not native speakers of the source language and do not provide the "
"desired quality of the source strings. The intermediate translation can help "
"you address this - there is an additional quality gateway for the strings "
"between developers and translators."
msgstr ""
"原始來源語言字串通常來自開發者，因為他們編寫程式碼並提供初始字串。但是，開發"
"者通常並非來源語言的母語者，並且提供的來源字串品質通常達不到預期標準。中間翻"
"譯可以幫助您解決這個問題——它在開發者和譯者之間為字串設定了額外的品質把關環"
"節。"

#: workflows.rst:244
msgid ""
"By setting the :ref:`component-intermediate`, this file is used for "
"translating strings to the source language by translators/editors while it "
"is owned by the developers (often using arbitrary languages such as "
"``en_devel``). Once this stage is done, strings are available for "
"translations to target languages, based on what is now a polished source "
"language stored in the :ref:`component-template`."
msgstr ""
"設定 :ref:`component-intermediate` 後，此檔案會供譯者／編輯人員將字串翻譯為來"
"源語言，同時由開發人員擁有（通常使用 ``en_devel`` 之類的任何語言）。此階段完"
"成後，便可以 :ref:`component-template` 中儲存的已潤飾來源語言為基礎，將字串翻"
"譯為目標語言。"

#: workflows.rst:297
msgid "String consolidation using secondary language"
msgstr "使用次要語言整併字串"

#: workflows.rst:299
msgid ""
"When :ref:`component-intermediate` cannot be used to consolidate the "
"strings, you can choose one of the translations to act as a secondary "
"language. The language can be configured in a project (:ref:`project-"
"secondary_language`) or in a component (:ref:`component-"
"secondary_language`). It is then shown to the translators while translating "
"(see :ref:`secondary-languages`) and can be optionally used as a source for "
"machine translations (see :ref:`mt-sources`)."
msgstr ""
"當無法使用 :ref:`component-intermediate` 整合字串時，您可以選擇其中一種譯文作"
"為第二語言。可以在專案（:ref:`project-secondary_language`）或元件"
"（:ref:`component-secondary_language`）中設定語言。然後在譯者翻譯時會顯示該第"
"二語言（見 :ref:`secondary-languages`），您也可以選擇將其用作機器翻譯的來源"
"（見 :ref:`mt-sources`）。"

#: workflows.rst:307
msgid ""
"This setup can be useful with mixed language source strings and "
"consolidating them into a single translation, which is then used as a "
"baseline for other work."
msgstr ""
"此設定對混合的語言來源字串非常有用，可以將它們整合為單一翻譯，然後用作其他工"
"作的基準。"

#: workflows.rst:313
msgid "Source strings reviews"
msgstr "來源字串檢閱"

#: workflows.rst:315
msgid ""
"With :ref:`project-source_review` enabled, the review process can be applied "
"for source strings. Once enabled, users can report issues with source "
"strings. The actual process depends on whether bilingual or monolingual "
"formats are in use."
msgstr ""
":ref:`project-source_review` 可以對來源字串應用稽核流程。啟用後，使用者可以報"
"告來源字串中的問題。實際過程取決於使用的是雙語還是單語格式。"

#: workflows.rst:319
msgid ""
"For monolingual formats, source string review functions similarly "
"to :ref:`reviews` — once an issue with a source string is reported, the "
"source string is marked as :guilabel:`Needs editing`."
msgstr ""
"對於單語言格式，來源字串稽核功能與 :ref:`reviews` 相似——一旦報告了來源字串的"
"問題，來源字串就會被標記為 :guilabel:`需要編輯`。"

#: workflows.rst:323
msgid ""
"Bilingual formats do not allow direct editing of source strings (these are "
"typically extracted directly from the source code). In this case, "
"a :guilabel:`Source needs review` label is attached to strings reported by "
"translators. You should review such strings and either edit them in the "
"source code, or remove the label."
msgstr ""
"雙語格式不允許直接編輯來源字串（通常都是直接從原始碼中提取來源字串）。在這種"
"情況下，:guilabel:`原文需要稽核` 標籤會被附加到譯者報告的字串上。您應該複查此"
"類字串，然後要麼編輯原始碼，要麼刪除標籤。"

